#7863;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m cao c&#7845;p, v&#7899;i m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; m&#7899;i, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7889;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&amp;ecirc;u d&amp;ugrave;ng &#432;a chu&#7897;ng v&amp;agrave; cu&#7889;i c&amp;ugrave;ng l&amp;agrave; t&amp;igrave;m ki&#7871;m m&#7903; r&#7897;ng th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u,.. ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; nh&#432; v&#7853;y m&#7899;i kh&#7855;c ph&#7909;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng &#7913; &#273;&#7885;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m nh&#432; hi&#7879;n nay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7873; ph&amp;iacute;a c&#417; quan qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c, qua b&amp;agrave;i h&#7885;c xi-m&#259;ng l&amp;ograve; &#273;&#7913;ng, v&amp;agrave; nay l&amp;agrave; g&#7841;ch ceramic v&amp;agrave; granit, thi&#7871;t ngh&#297; &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7871;n l&amp;uacute;c c&#7847;n ch&#7845;n ch&#7881;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c v&#7873; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng n&amp;oacute;i chung v&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t ceramic v&amp;agrave; granit n&amp;oacute;i ri&amp;ecirc;ng. Tr&#432;&#7899;c m&#7855;t, c&#7847;n c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p gi&#7919;a c&amp;aacute;c ng&amp;agrave;nh ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng, c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng trong vi&#7879;c r&amp;agrave; so&amp;aacute;t l&#7841;i quy ho&#7841;ch t&#7893;ng th&#7875; c&amp;aacute;c khu c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p, c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c duy&#7879;t, ki&amp;ecirc;n quy&#7871;t d&#7915;ng c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n m&#7899;i chu&#7849;n b&#7883; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i c&amp;oacute; bi&#7879;n ph&amp;aacute;p gi&amp;uacute;p c&amp;aacute;c DN c&#7911;ng c&#7889;, ph&amp;aacute;t huy hi&#7879;u qu