 ngh&#7873; v&amp;agrave; lu&amp;ocirc;n s&#7861;n s&amp;agrave;ng ph&#7909;c v&#7909; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','18/10/2011','18/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/Generate/nhamay1.jpg',39,3,13396,'admin',1,'','nh&agrave; m&aacute;y, mikado, granit, ceramic',NULL,NULL,NULL,'nh&agrave; m&aacute;y, mikado, granit, ceramic',0,0,0,'','','',4,'Mikado',1,0,0,0),(6,'Ch&#7885;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng th&#7901;i l&#7841;m ph&aacute;t','X&acirc;y nh&agrave; l&agrave; m&#7897;t quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh r&#7845;t l&#7899;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i m&#7895;i gia &#273;&igrave;nh, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t l&agrave; trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n b&atilde;o gi&aacute; nh&#432; hi&#7879;n nay. Gi&aacute; c&#7843; c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u nh&#432; c&aacute;t, xi m&#259;ng, s&#7855;t, th&eacute;p ... bi&#7871;n &#273;&#7897;ng v&#7899;i xu h&#432;&#7899;ng gia t&#259;ng m&#7895;i ng&agrave;y.','&lt;p&gt;Th&#7871; nh&#432;ng, v&#7851;n r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh d&amp;acirc;n d&#7909;ng r&#7909;c r&#7883;ch &#273;&amp;agrave;o m&amp;oacute;ng, x&amp;acirc;y nh&amp;agrave; t&#7915; m&#7845;y th&amp;aacute;ng nay, k&#7875; c&#7843; trong th&amp;aacute;ng 7 &amp;acirc;m l&#7883;ch v&#7915;a qua.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tranh th&#7911; x&amp;acirc;y nh&amp;agrave; d&amp;ugrave;... l&#7841;m ph&amp;aacute;t&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng t&#259;ng gi&amp;aacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7853;p nh&#7853;t h&amp;agrave;ng ng&amp;agrave;y tr&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c k&amp;ecirc;nh b&amp;aacute;o &#273;&amp;agrave;i, nh&#432;ng h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7845;t v&#7851;n quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh x&amp;acirc;y trong n&#259;m nay. Nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i b&amp;agrave;y t&#7887; quan &#273;i&#7875;m, th&#7901;i bu&#7893;i b&amp;acirc;y gi&#7901;, ch&#7881; to&amp;agrave;n th&#7845;y gi&amp;aacute; l&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7913; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gi&#7843;m, nh&#432; chuy&#7879;n x&#259;ng d&#7847;u, gi&#7843;m m&#7897;t ch&amp;uacute;t l&amp;agrave; s&#7869; l&#7841;i t&#259;ng nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n, n&amp;ecirc;n th&amp;ocirc;i, &#273;&amp;atilde; quy&#7871;t c&amp;oacute; nh&amp;agrave; th&amp;igrave; x&amp;acirc;y ngay ch&#7913; &#273;&#7907;i n&#259;m sau, ch&#7855;c g&amp;igrave; s&#7889; ti&#7873;n d&amp;agrave;nh d&#7909;m s&#7869; &#273;&#7911;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u chia s&#7867;: &amp;ldquo;N&#259;m nay th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n &#273;&amp;oacute;ng b&#259;ng, tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n l&#432;&#7907;ng h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng x&amp;acirc;y nh&amp;agrave; d&amp;acirc;n d&#7909;ng v&#7851;n kh&amp;aacute; &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh. Ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;atilde; chu&#7849;n b&#7883; s&#7861;n t&amp;acirc;m l&amp;yacute; v&amp;agrave; chu&#7849;n b&#7883; m&#7897;t kho&#7843;n b&amp;ugrave; &#273;&#7855;p t&#7881; l&#7879; l&#7841;m ph&amp;aacute;t c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;350&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/xaydungdandung.JPG&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n &#273;&amp;oacute;ng b&#259;ng, tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n l&#432;&#7907;ng h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng x&amp;acirc;y nh&amp;agrave; d&amp;acirc;n d&#7909;ng v&#7851;n kh&amp;aacute; &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;i m&#7897;t v&amp;ograve;ng c&amp;aacute;c khu d&amp;acirc;n c&#432; m&#7899;i nh&#432; 6B Intresco, B&amp;igrave;nh Ch&amp;aacute;nh ho&#7863;c An Ph&amp;uacute; An Kh&amp;aacute;nh, Qu&#7853;n 2, c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh v&#7851;n n&#7889;i ti&#7871;p nhau x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng b&#7845;t ch&#7845;p th&amp;aacute;ng 7 ki&amp;ecirc;ng k&#7925;, v&amp;igrave; nhi&#7873;u ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; cho r&#7857;ng cu&#7889;i n&#259;m, s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i x&amp;acirc;y nh&amp;agrave; t&#259;ng cao v&amp;agrave; nh&#432; nhi&#7873;u n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c gi&amp;aacute; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u s&#7869; c&amp;ograve;n t&#259;ng h&#417;n n&#7919;a.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&#272;i&#7873;u quan tr&#7885;ng nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh x&amp;acirc;y nh&amp;agrave;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Khi &#273;&amp;atilde; quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh x&amp;acirc;y nh&amp;agrave;, th&amp;igrave; ngo&amp;agrave;i v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; l&#7899;n thi&#7871;t k&#7871; c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh, th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh c&#361;ng &#273;&#7873;u quan t&amp;acirc;m &#273;&#7871;n chi ph&amp;iacute; v&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng v&amp;igrave; n&amp;oacute; quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&#7871;n to&amp;agrave;n b&#7897; c&#7897;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo ch&#7883; Thanh B&amp;igrave;nh, m&#7897;t ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; &#273;ang x&amp;acirc;y &#7903; Qu&#7853;n 2 trao &#273;&#7893;i, t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh kinh t&#7871; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, ai c&#361;ng th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t vi&#7879;c chi ti&amp;ecirc;u c&#361;ng nh&#432; c&amp;acirc;n nh&#7855;c r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u trong c&amp;aacute;c kho&#7843;n chi ph&amp;iacute;, ch&#7883; c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng ngo&#7841;i l&#7879;. Khi k&amp;yacute; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng v&#7899;i nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u, ch&#7883; quan t&amp;acirc;m r&#7845;t k&#7929; &#273;&#7871;n &#273;&#417;n gi&amp;aacute;, lu&amp;ocirc;n mu&#7889;n ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m m&#7897;t c&amp;aacute;ch h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute; nh&#432;ng v&#7851;n &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; th&#7871;, &#273;&#7875; ch&#7883; v&amp;agrave; nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u &#273;i &#273;&#7871;n th&#7889;ng nh&#7845;t c&amp;aacute;c v&#7853;t li&#7879;u c&#7911;a ph&#7847;n x&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc; c&#361;ng m&#7845;t kh&amp;aacute; nhi&#7873;u th&#7901;i gian, v&amp;igrave; ch&#7883; hi&#7875;u r&amp;otilde;, ph&#7847;n th&amp;ocirc; l&amp;agrave; c&#7889;t l&amp;otilde;i, quan tr&#7885;ng nh&#7845;t cho c&#7843; c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;350&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/xaydungdandung2.JPG&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nVi&#7879;c t&amp;igrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&amp;agrave; cung c&#7845;p c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng v&#7899;i m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Khi x&amp;acirc;y nh&amp;agrave;, t&amp;ocirc;i &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t quan t&amp;acirc;m &#273;&#7871;n vi&#7879;c ch&#7885;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u s&#7855;t th&amp;eacute;p, xi m&#259;ng v&amp;agrave; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ph&#432;&#417;ng &amp;aacute;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng t&#432;&#417;i ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cao. C&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m nhi&#7873;u th&#7913; trong qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n, trang tr&amp;iacute; nh&amp;agrave; c&#7917;a, nh&#432;ng b&#7897; khung nh&amp;agrave; th&amp;igrave; t&amp;ocirc;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; ch&#7875;nh m&#7843;ng, nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u ph&#7843;i mua &#273;&amp;uacute;ng lo&#7841;i ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u thi c&amp;ocirc;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Vi&#7879;c t&amp;igrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&amp;agrave; cung c&#7845;p c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng v&#7899;i m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, nh&#432; l&#7901;i anh Ho&amp;agrave;ng L&amp;acirc;n, m&#7897;t nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u c&amp;oacute; ti&#7871;ng trong gi&#7899;i x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng S&amp;agrave;i G&amp;ograve;n, th&amp;igrave;: &amp;ldquo;Ch&#7885;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u t&#7889;t v&amp;agrave; chi ph&amp;iacute; ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n &#432;u ti&amp;ecirc;n s&#7889; 1 c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;. &#272;&#7875; t&amp;igrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ngu&#7891;n cung &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u &#273;&amp;oacute; c&#361;ng t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#7889;i kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, nh&#432;ng gi&amp;aacute; tr&#7883; mang l&#7841;i th&amp;igrave; ho&amp;agrave;n to&amp;agrave;n x&#7913;ng &#273;&amp;aacute;ng. C&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng, ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&amp;aacute;nh gi&amp;aacute; cao, t&#259;ng uy t&amp;iacute;n trong ngh&#7873;, v.v&amp;hellip; &#272;&#417;n c&#7917; nh&#432; v&#7899;i ph&#7847;n th&amp;ocirc;, ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng t&#432;&#417;i Holcim. L&#7921;a ch&#7885;n n&amp;agrave;y gi&amp;uacute;p nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u thi c&amp;ocirc;ng thu&#7853;n ti&#7879;n nhanh ch&amp;oacute;ng, an to&amp;agrave;n lao &#273;&#7897;ng v&amp;agrave; v&#7879; sinh m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng trong khi v&#7851;n &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh &#7903; m&#7913;c t&#7889;t nh&#7845;t.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMong r&#7857;ng d&amp;ugrave; ch&#7883;u &amp;aacute;p l&#7921;c l&#7841;m ph&amp;aacute;t, c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave; nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u v&#7851;n s&amp;aacute;ng su&#7889;t l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&amp;aacute;c ngu&#7891;n cung v&#7853;t li&#7879;u gi&amp;aacute; &amp;ldquo;v&#7915;a chi&amp;rdquo; m&amp;agrave; v&#7851;n &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o an to&amp;agrave;n thi c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh &#7903; m&#7913;c cao nh&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','20/10/2011','20/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/xaydungdandung.JPG',23,2,1702,'admin',1,'','v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, mikado ceramic, ceramic',NULL,NULL,NULL,'v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, mikado ceramic, ceramic',0,0,0,'','','',4,'Theo Th&ocirc;ng tin doanh nghi&#7879;p',1,0,0,0),(7,'Ng&agrave;nh VLXD: Ng&#7855;c ngo&#7843;i t&igrave;m l&#7889;i tho&aacute;t','Trong b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m chung c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n (B&#272;S), ng&agrave;nh v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng (VLXD) c&#361;ng &#273;ang v&#7853;t l&#7897;n t&igrave;m c&aacute;ch th&aacute;o g&#7905; kh&oacute; kh&#259;n. Th&#7871; nh&#432;ng, b&#7871; t&#7855;c &#273;&#7847;u ra, ng&#7863;t ngh&egrave;o v&#7873; v&#7889;n c&#7897;ng v&#7899;i s&#7921; c&#7841;nh tranh quy&#7871;t li&#7879;t tr&ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;ang &#273;&#7849;y nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p xi m&#259;ng, th&eacute;p&hellip; &#273;&#7871;n b&#7901; v&#7921;c ph&aacute; s&#7843;n.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; ch&#7853;m, h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n cao&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;K&#7875; t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2011, c&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7899;i s&#7921; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n chung c&#7911;a n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871; v&amp;agrave; s&#7921; &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng B&#272;S, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p ng&amp;agrave;nh VLXD ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7889;i m&#7863;t v&#7899;i v&amp;ocirc; v&amp;agrave;n &amp;aacute;p l&#7921;c. Th&#7889;ng k&amp;ecirc; c&#7911;a Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam (VSA) cho bi&#7871;t t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7871;n gi&#7919;a th&amp;aacute;ng 9, t&#7893;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7891;n kho c&#7911;a th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 400.000 t&#7845;n v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p 520.000 t&#7845;n, g&#7845;p &#273;&amp;ocirc;i so v&#7899;i m&#7913;c d&#7921; tr&#7919; b&amp;igrave;nh qu&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng th&amp;aacute;ng c&#7911;a doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y th&amp;eacute;p ch&#7881; v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh 50-60% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t, th&#7853;m ch&amp;iacute; ng&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&#7875; h&#7841;n ch&#7871; thua l&#7895;. V&#7899;i l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7891;n kho n&amp;agrave;y, l&amp;atilde;i doanh nghi&#7879;p ph&#7843;i tr&#7843; h&amp;agrave;ng th&amp;aacute;ng g&#7847;n 150 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng. T&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; doanh nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t xi m&#259;ng c&#361;ng &#273;ang ch&#7853;t v&#7853;t t&amp;igrave;m c&amp;aacute;ch gi&#7843;i ph&amp;oacute;ng h&amp;agrave;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o t&#7915; nay &#273;&#7871;n cu&#7889;i n&#259;m, kho&#7843;ng 20% doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7869; b&#7883; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n. Do s&#7913;c mua gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh trong 2 th&amp;aacute;ng g&#7847;n &#273;&amp;acirc;y, nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y th&amp;eacute;p bu&#7897;c ph&#7843;i c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t &#273;&amp;aacute;ng k&#7875; v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t l&#7841;c h&#7853;u c&amp;oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng b&#7883; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n tr&#432;&#7899;c nh&#7845;t. &#272;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i c&#7843;nh b&amp;aacute;o v&amp;agrave;i n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c, b&amp;acirc;y gi&#7901; c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p n&amp;agrave;y m&#7899;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u th&#7845;m th&amp;iacute;a khi th&amp;eacute;p l&amp;agrave;m ra b&amp;aacute;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7871;n 50%, l&amp;acirc;m v&amp;agrave;o th&#7871; b&amp;iacute; tr&#432;&#7899;c &amp;aacute;p l&#7921;c l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng cao&amp;hellip;(&amp;Ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n Ti&#7871;n Ngh&#7883;, Ph&amp;oacute; Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch VSA)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo s&#7889; li&#7879;u c&#7911;a T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty C&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p Xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam (Vicem), h&#7871;t th&amp;aacute;ng 9-2011, t&#7893;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng xi m&#259;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; m&#7899;i &#273;&#7841;t 14,53 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n so v&#7899;i m&#7909;c ti&amp;ecirc;u 20,7 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n c&#7843; n&#259;m 2011 (ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; n&#7897;i &#273;&#7883;a 19,55 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u 1,15 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n nay l&#432;&#7907;ng xi m&#259;ng v&amp;agrave; clinker t&#7891;n kho c&#7911;a Vicem v&amp;agrave;o kho&#7843;ng 2 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n. Nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p v&amp;agrave; xi m&#259;ng ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&#7847;m ch&#7915;ng, ch&#7881; 20% tr&amp;ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t, th&#7853;m ch&amp;iacute; nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y ph&#7843;i t&#7841;m d&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t d&amp;ugrave; ch&#432;a tuy&amp;ecirc;n b&#7889; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong th&amp;aacute;ng 8, tr&#7915; 3 doanh nghi&#7879;p l&amp;agrave; Tam &#272;i&#7879;p, B&amp;uacute;t S&#417;n v&amp;agrave; B&#7881;m S&#417;n, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i thu&#7897;c Vicem &#273;&#7873;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7841;t ch&#7881; ti&amp;ecirc;u v&#7873; doanh s&#7889; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909;. M&#7897;t s&#7889; doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p kh&amp;aacute; n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng nh&#432; V&#7841;n L&#7907;i, Th&amp;eacute;p &#272;&amp;igrave;nh V&#361; (H&#7843;i Ph&amp;ograve;ng), CTCP luy&#7879;n th&amp;eacute;p S&amp;ocirc;ng &#272;&amp;agrave;, CTCP th&amp;eacute;p C&#7917;u Long Vinashin&amp;hellip; c&#361;ng &#273;&#7873;u &#7903; trong t&amp;igrave;nh c&#7843;nh &amp;ldquo;ng&#7855;c ngo&#7843;i&amp;rdquo;, ph&#7843;i t&#7841;m ng&#432;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c VLXD kh&amp;aacute;c nh&#432; c&amp;aacute;t, s&#7887;i, &#273;&amp;aacute; &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t, trang tr&amp;iacute; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t, b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng&amp;hellip; c&#361;ng chung s&#7889; ph&#7853;n. Theo th&#7889;ng k&amp;ecirc; c&#7911;a Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i G&#7889;m s&#7913; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam, l&#432;&#7907;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t t&#7891;n kho &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i h&#417;n 30 tri&#7879;u m2 d&amp;ugrave; c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y ch&#7881; ch&#7841;y kho&#7843;ng 70% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t. H&#7897;i VLXD Vi&#7879;t Nam c&#361;ng cho bi&#7871;t m&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng t&#7891;n kho l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n Xu&amp;acirc;n Trung, T&#7893;ng th&#432; k&amp;yacute; Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i K&amp;iacute;nh Vi&#7879;t Nam, cho bi&#7871;t n&#259;m nay l&#432;&#7907;ng k&amp;iacute;nh t&#7891;n kho g&#7845;p 2 l&#7847;n n&#259;m 2010, gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n t&#7909;t gi&#7843;m t&#7899;i 48% trong v&amp;ograve;ng 5 th&amp;aacute;ng tr&#7903; l&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y. Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i K&amp;iacute;nh c&amp;oacute; 120 h&#7897;i vi&amp;ecirc;n, ch&#7881; v&amp;agrave;i h&#7897;i vi&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;oacute; l&amp;atilde;i c&amp;ograve;n &#273;a s&#7889; h&amp;ograve;a v&amp;agrave; l&#7895; v&#7889;n. Tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7921;c t&#7871;, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p ng&amp;agrave;nh VLXD &#273;ang tr&#7843;i qua th&#7901;i k&#7923; kh&#7911;ng ho&#7843;ng k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i nh&#7845;t t&#7915; tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7871;n nay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong nhi&#7873;u th&amp;aacute;ng qua, c&amp;aacute;c c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng kinh doanh VLXD t&#7841;i H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i, TPHCM lu&amp;ocirc;n trong t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng &#7871; &#7849;m. Gi&amp;aacute; VLXD th&#7901;i gian qua h&#7847;u nh&#432; kh&amp;ocirc;ng t&#259;ng nh&#432;ng v&#7851;n r&#7845;t &amp;iacute;t ng&#432;&#7901;i mua. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, &#273;i&#7873;u &#273;&amp;aacute;ng b&amp;aacute;o &#273;&#7897;ng hi&#7879;n nay l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t l&#7841;c h&#7853;u, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; manh m&amp;uacute;n, ti&amp;ecirc;u t&#7889;n &#273;i&#7879;n nhi&#7873;u, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&#7845;p&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nguy c&#417; hi&#7875;n hi&#7879;n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&amp;oacute;i v&#7889;n l&amp;agrave; bi&#7875;u hi&#7879;n d&#7877; th&#7845;y &#7903; t&#7845;t c&#7843; doanh nghi&#7879;p VLXD th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y. C&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&amp;acirc;y v&amp;agrave;i th&amp;aacute;ng, trong cu&#7897;c h&#7885;p v&#7899;i B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch H&#272;QT T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam, L&amp;ecirc; V&#259;n Chung, t&#7915;ng b&#7913;c x&amp;uacute;c: &amp;ldquo;&#272;i vay l&amp;uacute;c n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng ch&#7881; l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7875; n&#7845;u ch&amp;aacute;o &#259;n qua b&#7919;a. L&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n ch&#7881; v&amp;agrave;i ph&#7847;n tr&#259;m l&amp;agrave;m sao c&amp;oacute; ti&#7873;n &#273;&#7875; tr&#7843; l&amp;atilde;i tr&amp;ecirc;n 20%. Th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng m&amp;agrave; d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#7889;n th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u si&#7871;t &#273;&#7871;n m&#7913;c c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, kinh doanh &#273;&#7893; b&#7875;, ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; &#273;&amp;ograve;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&#7907;. T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Xi m&#259;ng l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&#7921;c s&#7921; nh&#432;ng l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n ch&#7881; kho&#7843;ng 2-3%. N&#7871;u t&amp;iacute;nh l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n tr&amp;ecirc;n t&#7893;ng v&#7889;n b&#7887; ra 12.000 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng, coi nh&#432; doanh nghi&#7879;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; l&amp;atilde;i&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, doanh nghi&#7879;p xi m&#259;ng &#273;ang ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7889;i m&#7863;t v&#7899;i s&#7921; c&#7841;nh tranh quy&#7871;t li&#7879;t khi th&#7915;a c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t. Theo d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o c&#7911;a &amp;ocirc;ng L&amp;ecirc; V&#259;n Chung, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; xi m&#259;ng s&#7869; c&amp;ograve;n c&#259;ng th&#7859;ng v&amp;igrave; th&#7901;i gian t&#7899;i ngu&#7891;n cung xi m&#259;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7851;n ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c t&#259;ng. Ri&amp;ecirc;ng trong n&#259;m 2011 to&amp;agrave;n ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; th&amp;ecirc;m 11 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n m&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, t&#7913;c l&#432;&#7907;ng xi m&#259;ng d&#432; th&#7915;a n&#259;m nay d&#7921; ki&#7871;n 4-5 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n v&amp;agrave; v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2012 s&#7869; x&#7845;p x&#7881; 8 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o, l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; xi m&#259;ng m&#7895;i n&#259;m t&#259;ng kho&#7843;ng 10%. Nh&#432;ng v&#7899;i t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; s&#7909;t gi&#7843;m c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#432; hi&#7879;n nay, d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o n&amp;agrave;y tr&#7903; th&amp;agrave;nh l&#7841;c h&#7853;u. B&#7903;i th&amp;aacute;ng 7-2010 l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; xi m&#259;ng c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c h&#417;n 4 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, c&amp;ograve;n th&amp;aacute;ng 7-2011 ch&#7881; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c 3,7 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, b&#7857;ng 67% so v&#7899;i th&amp;aacute;ng 3 c&amp;ugrave;ng n&#259;m. Kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n n&#7919;a c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p l&amp;agrave; ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng r&#7845;t ng&#7841;i cho doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p vay v&#7889;n. Theo &#273;&amp;oacute;, tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;acirc;y doanh nghi&#7879;p vay th&#7871; ch&#7845;p ch&amp;iacute;nh b&#7857;ng h&amp;agrave;ng h&amp;oacute;a nay ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u ph&#7843;i c&amp;oacute; th&amp;ecirc;m t&amp;agrave;i s&#7843;n kh&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7871;n nay, t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c kho&#7843;ng 9 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n/n&#259;m. Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, th&amp;aacute;ng 6 v&amp;agrave; th&amp;aacute;ng 7, m&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng m&#7895;i th&amp;aacute;ng t&#7889;i &#273;a kho&#7843;ng 300.000 t&#7845;n/th&amp;aacute;ng, d&#432;&#7899;i 50% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i c&#7911;a to&amp;agrave;n ng&amp;agrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y &#273;ang khi&#7871;n nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p &amp;ldquo;ho&#7843;ng&amp;rdquo; khi d&#7921; ki&#7871;n &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2015, c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c ch&#7881; c&#7847;n kho&#7843;ng 15 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n th&amp;eacute;p v&amp;agrave; n&#259;m 2020 l&amp;agrave; 20 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n th&amp;eacute;p, trong khi t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871; c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i 26 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n/n&#259;m, ch&#432;a k&#7875; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n 5 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n c&#7911;a T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n Tata (&#7844;n &#272;&#7897;) li&amp;ecirc;n doanh v&#7899;i T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam t&#7841;i H&amp;agrave; T&#297;nh, d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n th&amp;eacute;p t&#7845;m c&amp;aacute;n n&amp;oacute;ng B&amp;agrave; R&#7883;a - V&#361;ng T&amp;agrave;u (T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam mua l&#7841;i c&#7911;a T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n Essar) 2 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n/n&#259;m&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;333&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/vlxd2.JPG&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;T&#7847;m nh&amp;igrave;n quy ho&#7841;ch?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7875; &amp;ldquo;b&#7855;t b&#7879;nh&amp;rdquo; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng VLXD Vi&#7879;t Nam. Theo c&amp;aacute;c chuy&amp;ecirc;n gia, nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n do &#273;&#7875; ki&#7873;m ch&#7871; l&#7841;m ph&amp;aacute;t, Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; &amp;aacute;p d&#7909;ng nhi&#7873;u bi&#7879;n ph&amp;aacute;p c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng, t&#7841;m d&#7915;ng, ho&amp;atilde;n c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh ch&#432;a th&#7853;t c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t khi&#7871;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng B&#272;S r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng &#273;&amp;oacute;ng b&#259;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n s&amp;acirc;u xa l&amp;agrave; do quy ho&#7841;ch ng&amp;agrave;nh VLXD nh&#432; th&amp;eacute;p, xi m&#259;ng b&#7845;t h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute;. T&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng - d&amp;ugrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; l&#7907;i th&#7871; - nh&#432;ng v&#7851;n &#273;ua nhau m&#7901;i g&#7885;i &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng, th&amp;eacute;p. Theo s&#7889; li&#7879;u c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng, &#273;&#7871;n nay trong 65 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;oacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871; t&#7915; 100.000 t&#7845;n/n&#259;m tr&#7903; l&amp;ecirc;n, c&amp;oacute; t&#7899;i 32 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng thu&#7897;c danh m&#7909;c quy ho&#7841;ch &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, t&#7853;p trung &#7903; c&amp;aacute;c t&#7881;nh B&amp;agrave; R&#7883;a - V&#361;ng T&amp;agrave;u, H&#7843;i Ph&amp;ograve;ng, Thanh H&amp;oacute;a, H&#7843;i D&#432;&#417;ng...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong s&#7889; n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;oacute; h&#417;n 20 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng c&#7845;p sai th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n&amp;hellip; C&amp;ograve;n c&amp;acirc;u chuy&#7879;n v&#7873; &amp;ldquo;v&#7905;&amp;rdquo; quy ho&#7841;ch xi m&#259;ng d&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#432; qu&amp;aacute; quen thu&#7897;c, &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7873; c&#7853;p nhi&#7873;u t&#7915; v&amp;agrave;i n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&#432; v&#7853;y c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; th&#7845;y, vi&#7879;c ph&amp;aacute; v&#7905; quy ho&#7841;ch VLXD v&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng h&#7879; l&#7909;y m&amp;agrave; n&amp;oacute; mang l&#7841;i, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t v&#7899;i ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p, xi m&#259;ng r&#7845;t r&amp;otilde; r&amp;agrave;ng. Sau giai &#273;o&#7841;n &amp;ldquo;&#273;&amp;oacute;i g&amp;oacute;p&amp;rdquo;, th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m &amp;ldquo;no d&#7891;n&amp;rdquo; l&#7841;i g&#7863;p ph&#7843;i kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n v&#7873; kinh t&#7871; n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p lao &#273;ao. M&#7863;t kh&amp;aacute;c, trong khi t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng m&#7845;y kh&#7843; quan, nhi&#7873;u s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m d&#432; th&#7915;a c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t g&#7845;p &#273;&amp;ocirc;i so v&#7899;i nhu c&#7847;u nh&#432;ng nhi&#7873;u s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m l&#7841;i ph&#7843;i nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u v&#7899;i s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng l&#7899;n nh&#432; th&amp;eacute;p t&#7845;m, th&amp;eacute;p cu&#7897;n c&amp;aacute;n n&amp;oacute;ng&amp;hellip; khi&#7871;n cho ng&amp;agrave;nh m&#7845;t c&amp;acirc;n &#273;&#7889;i nghi&amp;ecirc;m tr&#7885;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n doanh nghi&#7879;p ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p c&#361;ng &#273;ang &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n v&#7899;i nguy c&#417; b&#7883; ki&#7879;n ch&#7889;ng b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; t&#7915; Hoa K&#7923;, Th&amp;aacute;i Lan, Indonesia. R&amp;otilde; r&amp;agrave;ng, l&amp;uacute;c n&amp;agrave;y, cu&#7897;c kh&#7911;ng ho&#7843;ng th&#7915;a th&amp;eacute;p, xi m&#259;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ograve;n &#7903; d&#7841;ng &amp;ldquo;nguy c&#417;&amp;rdquo; m&amp;agrave; &#273;ang hi&#7879;n h&#7919;u, t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u c&#7921;c &#273;&#7871;n ch&amp;iacute;nh c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p, &#273;&#7849;y ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p, xi m&#259;ng v&amp;agrave; nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p VLXD kh&amp;aacute;c v&