c t&#7899;i, nh&#432;ng ph&#7909; gia b&ecirc; t&ocirc;ng (PGBT) hi&#7879;n &#273;ang gi&#7919; vai tr&ograve; quan tr&#7885;ng trong x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, trong n&#7895; l&#7921;c c&#7841;nh tranh hi&#7879;n nay, ph&#7909; gia n&#7897;i v&#7851;n b&#7883; &amp;ldquo;thua ngay tr&amp;ecirc;n s&amp;acirc;n nh&amp;agrave;&amp;rdquo;. &#272;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng th&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;uacute;c c&amp;aacute;c DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u n&amp;agrave;y ph&#7843;i tr&#259;n tr&#7903; t&amp;igrave;m l&#7889;i ra sao cho h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;334&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/vatlieu1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng n&#7897;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng thua k&amp;eacute;m h&amp;agrave;ng ngo&#7841;i&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;acirc;y, PGBT th&#432;&#7901;ng &amp;iacute;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7855;c &#273;&#7871;n trong c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng b&#7903;i b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng cho nh&amp;agrave; th&#7845;p t&#7847;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng c&amp;oacute; m&amp;aacute;c 200 (20N/mm2), thi c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7857;ng ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&amp;aacute;p th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng, kh&#7889;i l&#432;&#7907;ng nh&#7887; n&amp;ecirc;n nhu c&#7847;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng PGBT kh&amp;ocirc;ng cao; th&amp;ecirc;m n&#7919;a l&amp;agrave; th&amp;oacute;i quen v&amp;agrave; s&#7921; hi&#7875;u bi&#7871;t v&#7873; PGBT ch&#432;a nhi&#7873;u c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n ph&#7909; gia &amp;iacute;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng trong thi c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&#432;ng hi&#7879;n nay ph&#7909; gia l&amp;agrave; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; thi&#7871;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trong th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7847;n c&#7911;a b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;igrave; n&#7871;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; ph&#7909; gia th&amp;igrave; b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u &#273;a d&#7841;ng c&#7911;a c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; thi c&amp;ocirc;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t khi s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; thi c&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng ph&#7849;m c&amp;oacute; c&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7897; cao t&#7915; 40 - 60N/mm2, n&#7871;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ph&#7909; gia th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c y&#7871;u t&#7889; n&amp;agrave;y n&amp;ecirc;n hi&#7879;n nay ph&#7909; gia &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i trong s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; thi c&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng trong nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y c&#361;ng nh&#432; tr&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7921; ph&#7893; c&#7853;p r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i PGBT trong x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng hi&#7879;n nay c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; &#273;&amp;oacute;ng g&amp;oacute;p r&#7845;t l&#7899;n c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c Cty 100% v&#7889;n n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&amp;agrave;i. Trong kho&#7843;ng 10 n&#259;m tr&#7903; l&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y, c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;atilde; nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; kinh doanh PGBT. Nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7873; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng PGBT n&#7897;i, TS Nguy&#7877;n H&amp;ugrave;ng Minh - Gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c Trung t&amp;acirc;m ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; v&amp;agrave; VLXD (Vi&#7879;n Khoa h&#7885;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng) cho bi&#7871;t: S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c Cty trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7885;i chung l&amp;agrave; ph&#7909; gia n&#7897;i v&#7873; nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u &#273;&#7875; pha ch&#7871;, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t ph&#7909; gia &#273;&#7873;u ph&#7843;i nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u &#273;&#7871;n 90%, n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;oacute; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng v&amp;agrave; t&amp;iacute;nh &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;aacute;c nhi&#7873;u so v&#7899;i ph&#7909; gia c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c Cty 100% v&#7889;n n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&amp;agrave;i. &#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; n&amp;oacute;i v&#7873; lo&#7841;i ph&#7909; gia th&amp;ocirc;ng d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7875; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng ph&#7849;m &#273;&#7897; s&#7909;t cao v&#7899;i c&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7897; n&amp;eacute;n &#7903; tu&#7893;i 28 ng&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#7841;t 40 - 45N/mm2 v&amp;igrave; lo&#7841;i b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng n&amp;agrave;y chi&#7871;m &#273;a s&#7889; trong k&#7871;t c&#7845;u b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng hi&#7879;n nay. Ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; ph&#7909; gia &#273;&#7875; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng 50 - 70N/mm2 th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c Cty trong n&#432;&#7899;c ch&#432;a b&#7855;t k&#7883;p v&#7873; m&#7897;t s&#7889; ch&#7881; ti&amp;ecirc;u c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; so v&#7899;i ph&#7909; gia nh&#7853;p ngo&#7841;i m&amp;agrave; th&amp;ocirc;i. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng lo&#7841;i b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng n&amp;agrave;y chi&#7871;m t&#7927; tr&#7885;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nhi&#7873;u. V&#7873; m&#7863;t ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng, &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i m&amp;aacute;c b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng th&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng th&amp;igrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh PGBT n&#7897;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng thua k&amp;eacute;m g&amp;igrave; h&amp;agrave;ng ngo&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gi&amp;uacute;p gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh 50 - 60%&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng th&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y, nh&#432;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7889;t l&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;atilde; b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c v&amp;igrave; c&amp;ograve;n ph&#7843;i ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c v&amp;agrave;o kh&amp;acirc;u ti&#7871;p th&#7883; v&amp;agrave; t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh. Tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng hi&#7879;n nay &#273;ang c&amp;oacute; d&#7845;u hi&#7879;u c&#7841;nh tranh kh&#7889;c li&#7879;t c&#7911;a PGBT n&#7897;i so v&#7899;i PGBT ngo&#7841;i, nh&#432;ng c&amp;oacute; v&#7867; PGBT n&#7897;i v&#7851;n &#7903; m&#7913;c c&#7841;nh tranh &amp;ldquo;y&#7871;u th&#7871;&amp;rdquo;. Kh&#7843;o s&amp;aacute;t qua m&#7897;t v&amp;agrave;i c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh l&#7899;n, th&amp;igrave; PGBT &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7851;n l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u c&#7911;a Sika, Mapei, Basf&amp;hellip; B&#7903;i l&amp;yacute; do c&#361;ng kh&amp;aacute; &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n l&amp;agrave; khi c&#7841;nh tranh tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, c&amp;aacute;c Cty n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&amp;agrave;i c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u &#432;u th&#7871; so v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c Cty trong n&#432;&#7899;c nh&#432;: C&amp;oacute; ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch ti&#7871;p th&#7883; t&#7889;t, c&amp;oacute; th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng, c&amp;oacute; v&#7889;n l&#7899;n. C&amp;ograve;n ph&#7847;n l&#7899;n c&amp;aacute;c c&#417; s&#7903; kinh SXKD ph&#7909; gia n&#7897;i th&#432;&#7901;ng tr&#7921;c thu&#7897;c c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u, ho&#7863;c c&amp;aacute;c Cty nh&#7887; n&amp;ecirc;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; ti&#7873;m l&#7921;c t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh m&#7841;nh, ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch ti&#7871;p th&#7883; ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p, chuy&amp;ecirc;n nghi&#7879;p. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; th&#7871;, ph&#7909; gia ngo&#7841;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng trong c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng l&#7899;n, c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n l&#7899;n c&amp;ograve;n ph&#7909; gia n&#7897;i ph&#7847;n l&#7899;n ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng cho c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n nh&#7887;, ho&#7863;c cho c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&amp;oacute; v&#7889;n t&#432; nh&amp;acirc;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7883;nh cho r&#7857;ng do t&#7891;n t&#7841;i c&#7911;a t&#432; t&#432;&#7903;ng s&amp;iacute;nh ngo&#7841;i c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n g&amp;oacute;p ph&#7847;n gi&amp;uacute;p ph&#7909; gia ngo&#7841;i l&#7845;n &amp;aacute;t h&amp;agrave;ng n&#7897;i v&amp;agrave; chi&#7871;m &#273;&#7871;n 80% th&#7883; ph&#7847;n &#7903; Vi&#7879;t Nam hi&#7879;n nay. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute; kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; ph&#7911; nh&#7853;n m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&#417; s&#7903; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t PGBT trong n&#432;&#7899;c k&amp;eacute;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#361;ng &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7887; &#273;&#7871;n uy t&amp;iacute;n c&#7911;a PGBT n&#7897;i trong th&#7901;i bu&#7893;i c&#7841;nh tranh nh&#432; hi&#7879;n nay. Th&#7921;c t&#7871;, c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; khi s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ph&#7909; gia ngo&#7841;i, g&#7863;p tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7841;t m&amp;aacute;c ho&#7863;c c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; c&#7889; th&amp;igrave; h&amp;agrave;nh &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7871;n l&amp;agrave; t&amp;igrave;m l&#7895;i &#7903; xi m&#259;ng hay c&amp;aacute;c y&#7871;u t&#7889; c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; kh&amp;aacute;c, c&amp;ograve;n khi s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ph&#7909; gia n&#7897;i, n&#7871;u b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; &amp;ldquo;v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873;&amp;rdquo; th&amp;igrave; s&#7869; t&amp;igrave;m l&#7895;i &#7903; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng ph&#7909; gia. &#272;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; l&#7889;i suy ngh&#297; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7857;ng c&#7911;a t&#432; t&#432;&#7903;ng s&amp;iacute;nh ngo&#7841;i. V&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;acirc;y c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n &#273;&#7875; h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; ch&#7885;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m PGBT ngo&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, d&amp;ugrave; ch&#7881; chi&#7871;m th&#7883; ph&#7847;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng l&#7899;n tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#432;ng s&#7921; ra &#273;&#7901;i c&#7911;a ph&#7909; gia n&#7897;i &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&amp;aacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; &#273;&#7897;c quy&#7873;n c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c h&amp;atilde;ng h&amp;oacute;a ph&#7849;m x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&amp;agrave;i, l&amp;agrave;m gi&#7843;m 50 - 60% gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh c&#7911;a h&amp;oacute;a ph&#7849;m x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng n&amp;oacute;i chung v&amp;agrave; c&#7911;a PGBT n&amp;oacute;i ri&amp;ecirc;ng so v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; &#7903; giai &#273;o&#7841;n &#273;&#7897;c quy&#7873;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n nay ch&amp;uacute;ng ta &#273;&amp;atilde; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nhi&#7873;u lo&#7841;i PGBT v&#7899;i ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7889;t, &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh, gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh r&#7867; d&amp;ugrave;ng cho nhi&#7873;u lo&#7841;i b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng th&amp;ocirc;ng d&#7909;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&amp;agrave; th&#7921;c t&#7871; &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng trong nhi&#7873;u c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh, tr&#7841;m tr&#7897;n b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng ph&#7849;m. V&#7899;i s&#7921; n&#7895; l&#7921;c ti&#7871;p th&#7883; c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; SXKD PGBT trong n&#432;&#7899;c, ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; &#273;&amp;uacute;ng &#273;&#7855;n c&#7911;a Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave; s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i &#273;&#7883;nh ki&#7871;n s&amp;iacute;nh ngo&#7841;i c&#7911;a kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng trong t&#432;&#417;ng lai th&amp;igrave; ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n PGBT s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; l&#7907;i th&#7871; c&#7841;nh tranh &#273;&#7875; d&#7847;n n&amp;acirc;ng cao th&#7883; ph&#7847;n trong th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&amp;oacute;a ph&#7849;m x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','22/10/2011','22/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/vatlieu1.jpg',23,2,1862,'huyennt',1,'phu-gia-be-tong-noi-dam-bao-chat-luong-giup-giam-gia-thanh',' Ph&#7909; gia b&ecirc; t&ocirc;ng n&#7897;i, mikado ceramic',NULL,NULL,NULL,' Ph&#7909; gia b&ecirc; t&ocirc;ng n&#7897;i, mikado ceramic',0,0,0,'','','admin',3,'dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(22,'V&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#7871; nh&#432;ng gi&aacute; v&#7851;n t&#259;ng','&#272;&#7847;u n&#259;m, s&#7913;c ti&ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng kh&ocirc;ng cao. N&#259;m nay, vi&#7879;c h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&aacute;c m&#7863;t h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7873;u t&#259;ng gi&aacute; &#273;&atilde; khi&#7871;n cho th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&agrave;y c&agrave;ng y&ecirc;n &#7855;ng.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;420&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/vatlieuxd.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7883; B&#259;ng, ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng B&amp;igrave;nh B&#259;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7889; Ho&amp;agrave;ng Qu&#7889;c Vi&#7879;t (H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i) cho bi&#7871;t, g&#7847;n &#273;&amp;acirc;y, h&#7847;u nh&#432; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#273;&#7873;u t&#259;ng gi&amp;aacute;. G&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;t t&#259;ng kho&#7843;ng 10.000- 15.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/m2. Hi&#7879;n g&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;t n&#7873;n c&#7911;a H&#7841; Long c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n l&amp;agrave; 95.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/m2. &#272;&amp;aacute; &#7889;p c&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; m&#7913;c t&#259;ng kho&#7843;ng 5.000- 10.000  &#273;&#7891;ng/m2, &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&amp;aacute;n ra &#7903; m&#7913;c 150.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/m2. G&#7841;ch x&amp;acirc;y t&#259;ng kho&#7843;ng 100 &#273;&#7891;ng/vi&amp;ecirc;n, c&amp;aacute;t t&#259;ng kho&#7843;ng 50.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/xe (kho&#7843;ng 13m3)&amp;hellip;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#361;ng theo ch&#7883; B&#259;ng, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng kh&amp;aacute; tr&#7847;m l&#7855;ng v&amp;agrave;o nh&#7919;ng th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m, song n&#259;m nay, do gi&amp;aacute; t&#259;ng c&amp;agrave;ng khi&#7871;n cho s&#7913;c mua gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7883; Ti&amp;ecirc;n Th&amp;uacute;y, ch&#7911; m&#7897;t c&#7911;a h&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;aacute;c c&#361;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7889; n&amp;agrave;y th&amp;igrave; chia s&#7867;, hi&#7879;n nay do s&#7913;c mua kh&amp;ocirc;ng cao n&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n ra c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng ch&#7881; t&#259;ng nh&#7865;. V&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y, &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n h&amp;agrave;ng c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; tr&#7883; l&#7899;n c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; ch&amp;uacute;t l&#7901;i, c&amp;ograve;n v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i mua l&#7867; s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng nh&#7887; th&amp;igrave; ch&#7881; l&amp;agrave; b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7875; gi&#7919; kh&amp;aacute;ch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &amp;ocirc;ng L&amp;ecirc; V&#259;n T&#7899;i, V&#7909; tr&#432;&#7903;ng V&#7909; V&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng (B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng) gi&amp;aacute; x&#259;ng d&#7847;u, &#273;i&#7879;n, nh&#7919;ng nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u quan tr&#7885;ng trong qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng t&#259;ng khi&#7871;n gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c v&#7853;t li&#7879;u n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng t&#259;ng l&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u d&#7877; hi&#7875;u.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, &amp;ocirc;ng c&#361;ng khuy&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;o c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p c&#7847;n xem x&amp;eacute;t l&#7841;i qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; m&#7899;i, ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m t&#7889;i &#273;a c&amp;aacute;c chi ph&amp;iacute; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; h&#7841; gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng xi m&#259;ng, &amp;ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n V&#259;n &#272;i&#7879;p, Ch&amp;aacute;nh v&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam cho hay, hai th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng n&amp;agrave;y ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;t 6,2 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, th&#7845;p h&#417;n so v&#7899;i m&#7913;c c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923; n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c l&amp;agrave; 7 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;V&#7899;i t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; theo d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o v&amp;agrave;o kho&#7843;ng 10% v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7841;t m&#7913;c 55- 56 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, l&#7869; ra trong 2 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2011, s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7841;t kho&#7843;ng 8 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n m&#7899;i l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7841;t y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ocirc;ng &#272;i&#7879;p n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7921;c t&#7871; t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u th&amp;aacute;ng hai, m&#7897;t s&#7889; doanh nghi&#7879;p trong ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh t&#259;ng gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;ecirc;m 60.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n v&amp;agrave; b&amp;aacute;n ra &#7903; m&#7913;c t&#7915; 900.000 &#273;&#7891;ng- 1,36 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n, tu&#7923; theo ch&#7911;ng lo&#7841;i v&amp;agrave; khu v&#7921;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Sau khi gi&amp;aacute; x&#259;ng d&#7847;u v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; &#273;i&#7879;n ch&amp;iacute;nh th&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh t&#259;ng, h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p v&#7851;n &#273;ang trong qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh xem x&amp;eacute;t, ch&#432;a c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; v&#7873; m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; m&#7899;i. Theo th&amp;ocirc;ng tin t&#7915; &amp;ocirc;ng &#272;i&#7879;p, t&#7899;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y khi gi&amp;aacute; than b&amp;aacute;n cho s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t xi m&#259;ng ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c t&#259;ng th&amp;igrave; gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n c&#7911;a m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng n&amp;agrave;y ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n c&#361;ng s&#7869; b&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&#7907;t t&#259;ng m&#7899;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, theo &amp;ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n V&#259;n Ki&amp;ecirc;n, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch H&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng qu&#7843;n tr&#7883; C&amp;ocirc;ng ty C&#7893; ph&#7847;n Xi m&#259;ng X18 s&#7913;c mua tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng hi&#7879;n nay kh&amp;ocirc;ng cao s&#7869; khi&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ty xi m&#259;ng c&amp;oacute; quy m&amp;ocirc; nh&#7887; v&#7899;i c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t ch&#7881; 100.000 t&#7845;n/n&#259;m nh&#432; X18 s&#7869; r&#7845;t kh&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; t&#259;ng gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n, th&#7853;m ch&amp;iacute; c&amp;ograve;n ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7889;i m&#7863;t v&#7899;i thua l&#7895; do c&amp;aacute;c y&#7871;u t&#7889; &#273;&#7847;u v&amp;agrave;o li&amp;ecirc;n t&#7909;c t&#259;ng cao.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng k&amp;iacute;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, do s&#7921; t&#259;ng gi&amp;aacute; &#273;&amp;aacute;ng k&#7875; c&#7911;a x&#259;ng d&#7847;u v&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7879;n g&#7847;n &#273;&amp;acirc;y &#273;&amp;atilde; khi&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t ph&#7843;i ch&amp;iacute;nh th&#7913;c &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n t&#7915; ng&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n c&#7911;a th&amp;aacute;ng 3 t&#7915; 15-17%, tu&#7923; theo s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m. &amp;ldquo;&#272;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;agrave;m cho s&#7913;c mua tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng gi&#7843;m &#273;&amp;aacute;ng k&#7875; so v&#7899;i tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;oacute;&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ocirc;ng Tr&#7847;n Quang Th&amp;aacute;i, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i K&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;agrave; Thu&#7927; tinh Vi&#7879;t Nam cho hay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7915; 1/3, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; ch&amp;iacute;nh th&#7913;c t&#259;ng gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n th&amp;ecirc;m t&#7915; 300.000- 500.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. Gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p xu&#7845;t x&#432;&#7903;ng t&#7841;i c&amp;aacute;c t&#7881;nh mi&#7873;n B&#7855;c &#273;ang &#