#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch men c&#7911;a MIKADO &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n theo 5 c&ocirc;ng &#273;o&#7841;n ch&iacute;nh, bao g&#7891;m c&ocirc;ng &#273;o&#7841;n chu&#7849;n b&#7883; b&#7897;t x&#432;&#417;ng, c&ocirc;ng &#273;o&#7841;n &eacute;p v&agrave; s&#7845;y g&#7841;ch, c&ocirc;ng &#273;o&#7841;n tr&aacute;ng men, c&ocirc;ng &#273;o&#7841;n nung g&#7841;ch, v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng &#273;o&#7841;n cu&#7889;i l&agrave; ph&acirc;n lo&#7841;i v&agrave; &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;a. Chu&#7849;n b&#7883; b&#7897;t x&#432;&#417;ng:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u th&amp;ocirc; bao g&#7891;m &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t v&amp;agrave; tr&amp;agrave;ng th&#7841;ch &#273;&#432;&#7907;c mua v&#7873; Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y theo k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o kho d&#7921; tr&#7919; theo t&#7915;ng lo&#7841;i ri&amp;ecirc;ng bi&#7879;t tr&amp;ecirc;n c&#417; s&#7903; y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u &#273;&#417;n ph&#7889;i li&#7879;u. Sau &#273;&amp;oacute;, C&amp;aacute;c nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&amp;acirc;n &#273;&#7883;nh l&#432;&#7907;ng theo t&#7915;ng ch&#7911;ng lo&#7841;i, n&#7841;p v&amp;agrave;o ph&#7877;u &#273;&#7883;nh l&#432;&#7907;ng v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chuy&#7875;n v&amp;agrave;o m&amp;aacute;y nghi&#7873;n bi b&#7857;ng h&#7879; th&#7889;ng b&#259;ng t&#7843;i ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i. T&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y, c&amp;aacute;c nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nghi&#7873;n m&#7883;n, tr&#7897;n l&#7851;n nhau v&amp;agrave; ho&amp;agrave; tr&#7897;n v&#7899;i n&#432;&#7899;c sao cho t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n m&#7897;t h&#7895;n h&#7907;p h&#7891; c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7897; &#7849;m kho&#7843;ng 36% &#273;&#7897; &#7849;m. R&#7891;i h&#7895;n h&#7907;p h&#7891; n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&#7843; v&amp;agrave;o b&#7875; ch&#7913;a c&amp;oacute; m&amp;aacute;y khu&#7845;y. T&#7915; b&#7875; khu&#7845;y, h&#7891; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&amp;agrave;m &#273;&#7891;ng nh&#7845;t, qua c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;o&#7841;n s&amp;agrave;ng l&#7885;c rung, l&#7885;c s&#7855;t t&#7915; r&#7891;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#417;m c&#7845;p v&amp;agrave;o l&amp;ograve; s&#7845;y phun. H&#7891; sau khi s&#7845;y phun s&#7869; &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c d&#7841;ng b&#7897;t c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7897; &#7849;m kho&#7843;ng 6% &#273;&#7897; &#7849;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#259;ng t&#7843;i v&amp;agrave; g&#7847;u n&amp;acirc;ng &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o d&#7921; tr&#7919; trong c&amp;aacute;c sil&amp;ocirc; ch&#7913;a.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;b. &amp;Eacute;p v&amp;agrave; s&#7845;y g&#7841;ch:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#7902; c&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;o&#7841;n n&amp;agrave;y, b&#7897;t &amp;eacute;p &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&amp;aacute;o ra kh&#7887;i sil&amp;ocirc; t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng, &#273;&#432;a qua b&#259;ng t&#7843;i v&amp;agrave; g&#7847;u n&amp;acirc;ng, chuy&#7875;n v&amp;agrave;o ph&#7877;u c&#7911;a m&amp;aacute;y &amp;eacute;p v&amp;agrave; c&#7845;p theo khu&amp;ocirc;n &amp;eacute;p. M&amp;aacute;y &amp;eacute;p v&#7899;i l&#7921;c &amp;eacute;p t&#7889;i &#273;a 2.500 t&#7845;n ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng theo ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&amp;agrave;i &#273;&#7863;t s&#7861;n. G&#7841;ch sau khi &amp;eacute;p &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&#7841;y ra kh&#7887;i khu&amp;ocirc;n, r&#7891;i th&#7893;i s&#7841;ch b&#7909;i v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chuy&#7875;n v&amp;agrave;o l&amp;ograve; s&#7845;y &#273;&#7913;ng. G&#7841;ch &#7903; c&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;o&#7841;n n&amp;agrave;y tr&#432;&#7899;c khi &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o s&#7845;y g&#7885;i l&amp;agrave; g&#7841;ch m&#7897;c. &#7902; l&amp;ograve; s&#7845;y &#273;&#7913;ng, g&#7841;ch &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7845;y trung b&amp;igrave;nh kho&#7843;ng 75 ph&amp;uacute;t v&#7899;i nhi&#7879;t &#273;&#7897; s&#7845;y t&#7889;i &#273;a l&amp;agrave; 250oC.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;c. Tr&amp;aacute;ng men:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Men &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gia c&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7861;n v&amp;agrave; d&#7921; tr&#7919; trong b&#7875; ch&#7913;a d&amp;ugrave;ng &#273;&#7875; c&#7845;p cho ph&amp;acirc;n x&#432;&#7903;ng tr&amp;aacute;ng men. Khi g&#7841;ch sau khi &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7845;y &#7903; l&amp;ograve; s&#7845;y &#273;&#7913;ng xong, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c theo b&#259;ng chuy&#7873;n d&#7851;n &#273;&#432;a th&#7859;ng v&amp;agrave;o d&amp;acirc;y chuy&#7873;n tr&amp;aacute;ng men, l&amp;agrave;m s&#7841;ch, phun &#7849;m r&#7891;i ph&#7911; men v&amp;agrave; in hoa v&#259;n trang tr&amp;iacute; b&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;c thi&#7871;t b&#7883; chuy&amp;ecirc;n d&amp;ugrave;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;d. Nung g&#7841;ch &#273;&amp;atilde; tr&amp;aacute;ng men:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;G&#7841;ch sau khi &#273;&amp;atilde; tr&amp;aacute;ng men trang tr&amp;iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a qua m&amp;aacute;y x&#7871;p t&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&#7871;p l&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c xe l&#432;u ch&#7913;a. Sau &#273;&amp;oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c v&#7853;n chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7871;n m&amp;aacute;y d&#7905; t&#7843;i v&amp;agrave; c&#7845;p v&amp;agrave;o l&amp;ograve; nung thanh l&#259;n. T&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y, l&amp;ograve; nung thanh l&#259;n, g&#7841;ch &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nung &#7903; nhi&#7879;t &#273;&#7897; t&#7915; 1.150o &amp;ndash; 1.180o C.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;e. Ph&amp;acirc;n lo&#7841;i v&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;oacute;ng g&amp;oacute;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;G&#7841;ch sau khi nung, qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng thanh l&#259;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o b&#259;ng chuy&#7873;n ph&amp;acirc;n lo&#7841;i t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng, x&#7871;p ch&#7891;ng v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&amp;oacute;ng g&amp;oacute;i h&#7897;p c&amp;aacute;c t&amp;ocirc;ng, d&amp;aacute;n keo, in nh&amp;atilde;n, b&#7885;c nilon v&amp;agrave; x&#7871;p l&amp;ecirc;n xe n&amp;acirc;ng h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o kho th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7849;m.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSau khi d&amp;acirc;y chuy&#7873;n s&#7889; 3 &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, C&amp;ocirc;ng ty &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7853;p trung &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; chi&#7873;u s&amp;acirc;u v&#7873; m&amp;aacute;y m&amp;oacute;c, thi&#7871;t b&#7883;, nh&#7857;m t&#7841;o ra s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&#7841;t ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cao, &#273;a d&#7841;ng ho&amp;aacute; v&#7873; k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave; m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m. Trong n&#259;m 2007 C&amp;ocirc;ng ty &#273;&amp;atilde; nhanh ch&amp;oacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; m&amp;aacute;y in Rotocolor v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;a ra th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng 130 m&#7851;u m&#7899;i t&#259;ng 21% so v&#7899;i n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c, &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng k&#7883;p th&#7901;i v&#7873; nhu c&#7847;u th&#7849;m m&#7929; c&#7843; ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&amp;ecirc;u d&amp;ugrave;ng. .&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','26/10/2011','26/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/quytrinh.jpg',41,13,14627,'admin',1,'quy-trinh-san-xuat-gach-ceramic','quy tr&igrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, mikado ceramic',NULL,NULL,NULL,'quy tr&igrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, mikado ceramic',0,0,0,'','','admin',4,'MIKADO',1,0,0,0),(76,'C&aacute;ch ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch l&aacute;t n&#7873;n','&#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i nh&agrave; ph&#7889; c&oacute; m&#7863;t ti&#7873;n d&#432;&#7899;i 5 m, n&ecirc;n ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch tr&#417;n nh&#7861;n &#273;&#7875; d&#7877; lau r&#7917;a. H&#417;n n&#7919;a, do th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;i ch&acirc;n tr&#7847;n v&agrave;o nh&agrave;, th&#7853;m ch&iacute; ng&#7891;i, n&#7857;m ngay tr&ecirc;n n&#7873;n n&ecirc;n g&#7841;ch tr&#417;n s&#7869; thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i h&#417;n. M&agrave;u th&igrave; ch&#7885;n t&ocirc;ng s&aacute;ng l&agrave;m ch&#7911; &#273;&#7841;o. C&oacute; th&#7875; d&ugrave;ng m&agrave;u s&#7851;m, nh&#432;ng ch&#7881; &#7903; ph&#7847;n vi&#7873;n.','&lt;p&gt;Nh&amp;agrave; nh&#7887; ch&#7881; n&amp;ecirc;n d&amp;ugrave;ng g&#7841;ch nh&#7887;, t&#7889;i &#273;a 40x40 cm/vi&amp;ecirc;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Bi&#7879;t th&#7921; hay nh&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; d&amp;ugrave;ng g&#7841;ch &#273;a d&#7841;ng h&#417;n nh&#432; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i th&amp;ocirc; m&#7897;c, c&amp;oacute; b&#7873; m&#7863;t nh&amp;aacute;m s&#7847;n s&amp;ugrave;i, g&#7841;ch men m&amp;aacute;t, &#273;&amp;aacute; t&#7921; nhi&amp;ecirc;n... K&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905; vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch c&#361;ng linh &#273;&#7897;ng t&#7915; nh&#7887; &#273;&#7871;n l&#7899;n, trang tr&#7885;ng h&#417;n th&amp;igrave; d&amp;ugrave;ng g&#7841;ch nh&#7861;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&amp;agrave; v&#432;&#7901;n, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; l&amp;aacute;t nh&#7919;ng lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch t&#7921; nhi&amp;ecirc;n, th&amp;ocirc; m&#7897;c h&#417;n d&#7841;ng nh&amp;agrave; bi&#7879;t th&#7921; nh&#432; &#273;&amp;aacute; ch&#7867;, g&#7841;ch &#273;inh x&#7871;p &#273;&#7913;ng, b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7887;i hay m&#7843;nh g&#7889;m x&#7871;p t&#7841;o h&amp;igrave;nh tr&amp;ecirc;n n&#7873;n xi m&#259;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;L&amp;aacute;t g&#7841;ch theo c&amp;aacute;c khu v&#7921;c ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; l&amp;aacute;t nhi&#7873;u kh&#7893; g&#7841;ch, m&amp;agrave;u x&#7917; l&amp;yacute; phong ph&amp;uacute; gi&#7919;a s&#7855;c &#273;&#7853;m, nh&#7841;t v&amp;igrave; &#273;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian t&#7841;o &#7845;n tu&#7907;ng. C&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#273;i&#7875;m h&#7885;a ti&#7871;t b&#7857;ng g&#7841;ch vi&#7873;n, t&#7841;o h&amp;igrave;nh vu&amp;ocirc;ng, tr&amp;ograve;n, m&#7843;ng nh&#7845;n to&amp;agrave;n n&#7873;n ph&amp;ograve;ng hay &#7903; gi&#7919;a v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch c&amp;ugrave;ng ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u ho&#7863;c k&#7871;t h&#7907;p g&#7895;, g&#7889;m...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; x&amp;acirc;y gi&#7853;t c&#7845;p &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o s&#7921; kh&amp;aacute;c bi&#7879;t gi&#7919;a hai kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ch&#7885;n m&amp;agrave;u nh&#7841;t h&#417;n cho c&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;c b&amp;igrave;nh y&amp;ecirc;n. N&#7871;u c&amp;oacute; &#273;i&#7875;m xuy&#7871;t hoa v&#259;n th&amp;igrave; n&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7885;n m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n, d&#7883;u, kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7875; t&#432;&#417;ng ph&#7843;n m&#7841;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;ograve;ng sinh ho&#7841;t chung x&#7917; l&amp;yacute; t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#7891;ng nh&#432; ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n nh&#432;ng c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; linh ho&#7841;t, bi&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;ch m&#7897;t ch&amp;uacute;t &#273;&#7875; l&amp;agrave;m t&#259;ng s&#7921; &#7845;m c&amp;uacute;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&amp;agrave; v&#7879; sinh c&amp;oacute; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch chuy&amp;ecirc;n d&#7909;ng v&#7899;i &#273;&#7897; nh&amp;aacute;m s&#7847;n cao ch&#7889;ng tr&#432;&#7907;t. T&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921;, s&amp;acirc;n th&#432;&#7907;ng, ban c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;aacute;nh d&amp;ugrave;ng g&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;ng. H&amp;igrave;nh th&#7913;c l&amp;aacute;t &#7903; c&amp;aacute;c v&#7883; tr&amp;iacute; n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; sinh &#273;&#7897;ng h&#417;n, t&#7841;o h&amp;igrave;nh sin, ch&#7919; U, ch&#7919; C... N&#7871;u d&amp;ugrave;ng g&#7841;ch nung, c&#7847;n &#273;&#7875; m&#7841;ch v&#7919;a to, &#273;&#7911; s&#7913;c b&amp;aacute;m ch&#7855;c v&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;t ch&#7889;ng th&#7845;m. K&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch &#273;a d&#7841;ng nh&#432; 30x20, 30x30,15x30 cm...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911;, n&#7871;u c&amp;oacute; &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u g&#7895; s&amp;agrave;n, th&#7843;m. V&#7899;i g&#7841;ch th&amp;igrave; n&amp;ecirc;n d&amp;ugrave;ng kh&#7893; l&#7899;n h&#417;n 30 cm, h&#7841;n ch&#7871; trang tr&amp;iacute;, &#273;i&#7875;m xuy&#7871;t v&amp;igrave; qu&amp;aacute; nhi&#7873;u v&#7853;t d&#7909;ng trong ph&amp;ograve;ng s&#7869; l&amp;agrave;m r&#7889;i. C&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; l&amp;aacute;t xoay nghi&amp;ecirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o s&#7921; m&#7899;i l&#7841;, thay v&amp;igrave; l&amp;aacute;t xu&amp;ocirc;i theo chi&#7873;u vu&amp;ocirc;ng v&#7913;c c&#7911;a ph&amp;ograve;ng. T&amp;ocirc;ng m&amp;agrave;u ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p l&amp;agrave; nh&#7841;t v&amp;agrave; h&#417;i &#7917;ng s&#7855;c n&amp;oacute;ng nh&#432; kem, h&#7891;ng hay v&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#7845;t... Ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u g&#7841;ch nh&#7861;n b&amp;oacute;ng hay h&#417;i nh&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7873;u c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; d&amp;ugrave;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','26/10/2011','26/10/2011','',41,13,9243,'admin',1,'cach-chon-gach-lat-nen','c&aacute;ch ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch l&aacute;t n&#7873;n, mikado ceramic, g&#7841;ch l&aacute;t',NULL,NULL,NULL,'c&aacute;ch ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch l&aacute;t n&#7873;n, mikado ceramic, g&#7841;ch l&aacute;t',0,0,0,'','','',4,'MIKADO',1,0,0,0),(77,'B&#7855;c Giang: Khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y kh&ocirc;ng nung','&#272;&#7875; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m g&#7841;ch ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cao, c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trong c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, nhi&#7873;u ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&atilde; nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u, t&igrave;m hi&#7875;u v&agrave; &#273;&#432;a v&agrave;o &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng h&#7879; th&#7889;ng d&acirc;y chuy&#7873;n m&aacute;y m&oacute;c thi&#7871;t b&#7883; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7899;i quy m&ocirc; l&#7899;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t GKN.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng VLXD t&#7841;i B&#7855;c Giang, g&#7841;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung (GKN) &#273;&amp;atilde; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n t&#7915; kh&amp;aacute; l&amp;acirc;u. &#272;&#7875; c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m g&#7841;ch ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cao, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trong t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng d&amp;acirc;n d&#7909;ng, c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p, giao th&amp;ocirc;ng, thu&#7927; l&#7907;i&amp;hellip; nhi&#7873;u ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&amp;atilde; nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u, t&amp;igrave;m hi&#7875;u v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng h&#7879; th&#7889;ng d&amp;acirc;y chuy&#7873;n m&amp;aacute;y m&amp;oacute;c thi&#7871;t b&#7883; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7899;i quy m&amp;ocirc; l&#7899;n nh&#432; Cty TNHH B&amp;igrave;nh &#272;&#7883;nh &#273;&amp;atilde; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t GKN t&#7915; n&#259;m 2007 (c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871; t&#7915; 10 - 20 tri&#7879;u vi&amp;ecirc;n/n&#259;m). S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#7911;a Cty &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a b&amp;agrave;n t&#7881;nh v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c t&#7881;nh l&amp;acirc;n c&#7853;n nh&#432; B&#7855;c Ninh, L&#7841;ng S&#417;n, H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;386&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/khuyen_khich_sx_GKN.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;(&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo l&#7897; tr&amp;igrave;nh xo&amp;aacute; b&#7887; l&amp;ograve; g&#7841;ch th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng quy &#273;&#7883;nh t&#7841;i Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 147/2009/Q&#272;-UBND ng&amp;agrave;y 31/12/2009 c&#7911;a UBND t&#7881;nh B&#7855;c Giang, &#273;&#7871;n th&amp;aacute;ng 3/2012 s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; 7/10 huy&#7879;n, TP ph&#7843;i ch&#7845;m d&#7913;t ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7871;n h&#7871;t th&amp;aacute;ng 3/2013, tr&amp;ecirc;n to&amp;agrave;n t&#7881;nh kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ograve;n ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng. Nh&#432; v&#7853;y s&#7869; gi&#7843;m kho&#7843;ng 50% s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng g&#7841;ch nung hi&#7879;n c&amp;oacute; tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a b&amp;agrave;n t&#7881;nh, l&amp;agrave;m &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng nhi&#7873;u &#273;&#7871;n kh&#7843; n&#259;ng cung &#7913;ng g&#7841;ch x&amp;acirc;y cho c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh. V&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y, chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t GKN &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c khuy&#7871;n kh&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t theo h&#432;&#7899;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, quy m&amp;ocirc; l&#7899;n, k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c l&#7899;n, nh&#7865; &#273;&#7875; thay th&#7871; d&#7847;n g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t nung.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; c&amp;oacute; h&#432;&#7899;ng ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n t&#7889;t cho s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m GKN, S&#7903; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng B&#7855;c Giang &#273;ang ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c t&#7893; ch&#7913;c t&#7889;t c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c tuy&amp;ecirc;n truy&#7873;n, qu&amp;aacute;n tri&#7879;t c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; th&#7875; trong ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng v&amp;agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n th&#7845;y r&amp;otilde; nh&#7919;ng &#432;u &#273;i&#7875;m, l&#7907;i th&#7871; trong vi&#7879;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng GKN; &#432;u ti&amp;ecirc;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng GKN v&amp;agrave;o c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng; khuy&#7871;n kh&amp;iacute;ch c&amp;aacute;c th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7847;n kinh t&#7871; tham gia v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&amp;agrave; kinh doanh c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y, l&#7907;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;','28/10/2011','28/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/khuyen_khich_sx_GKN.jpg',23,2,2450,'huyennt',1,'bac-giang-khuyen-khich-san-xuat-va-su-dung-vat-lieu-xay-khong-nung','g&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung, khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, VLXD, mikado ceramic',NULL,NULL,NULL,'g&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung, khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, VLXD, mikado ceramic',0,0,0,'','','',3,'diaoconline.vn',1,0,0,0),(78,'H&agrave; N&#7897;i s&#7869; di d&#7901;i h&agrave;ng lo&#7841;t c&#417; s&#7903; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t VLXD','Ng&agrave;y 28-10, S&#7903; X&acirc;y d&#7921;ng H&agrave; N&#7897;i &#273;&atilde; c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; Quy ho&#7841;ch ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng (VLXD) TP H&agrave; N&#7897;i &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2020, &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2030.','\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; quy ho&#7841;ch chuy&amp;ecirc;n ng&amp;agrave;nh &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t v&amp;agrave; c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; sau khi c&amp;oacute; Quy ho&#7841;ch chung x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Th&#7911; &#273;&amp;ocirc;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTheo &#273;&amp;oacute;, trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2020, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t VLXD c&#7911;a H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i s&#7869; l&amp;agrave; ng&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p th&amp;acirc;n thi&#7879;n m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng. C&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t theo ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&amp;aacute;p truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u t&#7889;n nhi&amp;ecirc;u li&#7879;u, hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; kinh t&#7871; th&#7845;p, g&amp;acirc;y &amp;ocirc; nhi&#7877;m m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng s&#7869; ph&#7843;i x&#7917; l&amp;yacute;, lo&#7841;i b&#7887; d&#7847;n. Ri&amp;ecirc;ng &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng, ng&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2012. D&#7921; ki&#7871;n, t&#7893;ng v&#7889;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; cho c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t VLXD trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n t&#7915; nay &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2015 l&amp;agrave; h&#417;n 9.400 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng, n&#259;m 2016-2020 l&amp;agrave; h&#417;n 3.000 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nQuy ho&#7841;ch &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;a ra ph&#432;&#417;ng h&#432;&#7899;ng di d&#7901;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&#417; s&#7903; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n t&#7915; nay &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2015 g&#7891;m 12 &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ty: CP g&#7841;ch ng&amp;oacute;i Th&#7841;ch B&amp;agrave;n, CP B&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Th&#7883;nh Li&#7879;t&amp;hellip; Giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2016-2020 di chuy&#7875;n 5 c&#417; s&#7903;, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ty: CP Vi&#7879;t M&#7929;, CP Viglacera &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng Anh&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','29/10/2011','29/10/2011','',23,2,1737,'huyennt',1,'ha-noi-se-di-doi-hang-loat-co-so-san-xuat-vlxd','VLXD, &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng. x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'VLXD, &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng. x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n',0,0,0,'','','',3,'hanoimoi.com.vn',1,0,0,1),(79,'H&agrave; N&#7897;i: C&ocirc;ng b&#7889; quy ho&#7841;ch ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n VLXD &#273;&#7871;n 2030','Quy ho&#7841;ch chuy&ecirc;n ngh&agrave;nh &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&ecirc; duy&#7879;t v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; sau khi c&oacute; Quy ho&#7841;ch x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng Th&#7911; &#273;&ocirc;.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7903; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i v&#7915;a c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; Quy ho&#7841;ch ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng (VLXD) th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2020, &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2030. &#272;&amp;acirc;y c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; quy ho&#7841;ch chuy&amp;ecirc;n ng&amp;agrave;nh &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t v&amp;agrave; c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; sau khi c&amp;oacute; Quy ho&#7841;ch chung x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Th&#7911; &#273;&amp;ocirc;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTheo quy ho&#7841;ch, giai &#273;o&#7841;n &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2020, c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t VLXD c&#7911;a H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o l&amp;agrave; ng&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p th&amp;acirc;n thi&#7879;n m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng, h&#432;&#7899;ng t&#7899;i n&#7873;n c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p xanh, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i VLXD kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung, x&#7917; l&amp;yacute; v&amp;agrave; lo&#7841;i b&#7887; d&#7847;n c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t theo ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&amp;aacute;p truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u t&#7889;n nhi&amp;ecirc;u li&#7879;u, hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; kinh t&#7871; th&#7845;p, g&amp;acirc;y &amp;ocirc; nhi&#7877;m m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng, ng&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2012. Quy ho&#7841;ch c&#361;ng &#273;&#7863;t m&#7909;c ti&amp;ecirc;u trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n &#273;&#7871;n 2015, t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; t&#259;ng gia str&#7883; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p VLXD &#273;&#7841;t 17%/n&#259;m, giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2016-2020 &#273;&#7841;t 16%. &#272;&#7871;n 2020, ng&amp;agrave;nh n&amp;agrave;y s&#7869; &#273;&amp;oacute;ng g&amp;oacute;p cho ng&amp;acirc;n s&amp;aacute;ch TP kho&#7843;ng 3.800 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng. &#272;&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n nh&#7919;ng d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; theo quy ho&#7841;ch, d&#7921; ki&#7871;n t&#7893;ng v&#7889;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; cho ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p VLXD trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n t&#7915; nay &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2015 l&amp;agrave; h&#417;n 9.400 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng, t&#7915; 2016-2020 l&amp;agrave; h&#417;n 3.000 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;417&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/vat_lieu_xay_dung_khong_nung.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;V&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Quy ho&#7841;ch c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;a ra ph&#432;&#417;ng h&#432;&#7899;ng di d&#7901;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&#417; s&#7903; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n t&#7915; nay &#273;&#7871;n 2015 g&#7891;m 12 &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; C&amp;ocirc;ng ty CP g&#7841;ch ng&amp;oacute;i Th&#7841;c B&amp;agrave;n, C&amp;ocirc;ng ty CP b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Th&#7883;nh Li&#7879;t&amp;hellip; Trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2016-2020 di chuy&#7875;n 5 c&#417; s&#7903;, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; C&amp;ocirc;ng ty CP Vi&#7879;t M&#7929;, C&amp;ocirc;ng ty CP Viglacera &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng Anh&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nVi&#7879;c c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; quy ho&#7841;ch s&#7869; l&amp;agrave; c&#259;n c&#7913; cho c&amp;aacute;c ng&amp;agrave;nh, c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, c&amp;aacute;c DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t VLXD c&#7911;a TP l&#7853;p c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, chu&#7849;n b&#7883; l&#7921;c l&#432;&#7907;ng, t&amp;igrave;m ngu&#7891;n v&#7889;n &#273;&#7875; tri&#7875;n khai c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i n&amp;acirc;ng cao c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;','29/10/2011','29/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/vat_lieu_xay_dung_khong_nung.jpg',23,2,1750,'huyennt',1,'ha-noi-cong-bo-quy-hoach-phat-trien-vlxd-den-2030','g&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung, quy ho&#7841;ch, mikadoceramic, VLXD, ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'g&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung, quy ho&#7841;ch, mikadoceramic, VLXD, ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(80,'Th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng th&eacute;p &#273;ang &hellip; r&#7889;i lo&#7841;n','&ldquo;&#272;&atilde; c&oacute; hi&#7879;n t&#432;&#7907;ng c&aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p ch&#7883;u l&#7895;, h&#7841; gi&aacute; b&aacute;n b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch t&#259;ng m&#7913;c chi&#7871;t kh&#7845;u, gi&#7843;m c&#432;&#7899;c v&#7853;n t&#7843;i, cho &#273;&#7841;i l&yacute; tr&#7843; ch&#7853;m &#273;&#7875; ti&ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&agrave;ng&hellip; &#273;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y &#273;ang g&acirc;y r&#7889;i lo&#7841;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng.&rdquo; - Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i th&eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam l&ecirc;n ti&#7871;ng.','\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;500&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/thep_ton.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;Th&amp;eacute;p t&#7891;n kho &#273;ang ch&#7901; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Doanh nghi&#7879;p ki&#7879;n nhau b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Chi&#7873;u 27/10, B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7893; ch&#7913;c h&#7897;i ngh&#7883; t&amp;igrave;m gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p th&amp;aacute;o g&#7905; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n cho ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p. T&#7841;i h&#7897;i ngh&#7883;, &amp;ocirc;ng Ph&#7841;m Ch&amp;iacute; C&#432;&#7901;ng, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p th&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam (VSA) cho bi&#7871;t, trong 10 th&amp;aacute;ng qua, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p tuy gi&#7919; &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh nh&#432;ng hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; th&#7845;p, t&#7891;n kho t&#259;ng cao, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; ng&amp;agrave;y c&amp;agrave;ng ch&#7853;m, &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng nghi&amp;ecirc;m tr&#7885;ng t&#7899;i &#273;&#7901;i s&#7889;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng nh&amp;acirc;n v&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; kinh doanh c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u nh&#432; nh&#7919;ng n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c, m&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; kh&amp;aacute;, t&#7891;n kho c&#7911;a DN th&amp;eacute;p ch&#7881; &#7903; m&#7913;c 250 &amp;ndash; 300 ngh&amp;igrave;n t&#7845;n, nay &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i h&#417;n 500 ngh&amp;igrave;n t&#7845;n, m&#7913;c r&#7845;t &#273;&amp;aacute;ng lo ng&#7841;i trong b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t &#7903; m&#7913;c cao v&amp;agrave; doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p ph&#7843;i vay v&#7889;n ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng r&#7845;t l&#7899;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;a ra d&#7851;n ch&#7913;ng v&#7873; gi&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang &#7903; m&#7913;c b&amp;aacute;o &#273;&#7897;ng. C&#7909; th&#7875; ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p hi&#7879;n &#7903; m&#7913;c 14 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n, chi ph&amp;iacute; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t (t&#7915; ph&amp;ocirc;i c&amp;aacute;n ra th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7849;m) kho&#7843;ng 1,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;ng. Nh&#432;ng &#273;&#7875; b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng 15,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n l&amp;agrave; r&#7845;t kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;&#272;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; hi&#7879;n t&#432;&#7907;ng c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p ch&#7883;u l&#7895;, h&#7841; gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n b&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;ch t&#259;ng m&#7913;c chi&#7871;t kh&#7845;u, gi&#7843;m c&#432;&#7899;c v&#7853;n t&#7843;i, cho &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute; tr&#7843; ch&#7853;m &#273;&#7875; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng&amp;hellip; &#273;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y &#273;ang r&amp;acirc;y r&#7889;i lo&#7841;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng&lt;/em&gt;.&amp;rdquo; - &amp;ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nghi&amp;ecirc;m tr&#7885;ng h&#417;n, vi&#7879;c n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c VSA nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7883;nh c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7869; l&amp;agrave; m&#7847;m m&#7889;ng cho c&amp;aacute;c v&#7909; ki&#7879;n ch&#7889;ng b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; trong th&#7901;i gian t&#7899;i khi m&amp;agrave; ngay trong ch&amp;iacute;nh n&#7897;i b&#7897; Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng ki&#7879;n c&amp;aacute;o cho l&amp;agrave; b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; gi&#7919;a T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam v&amp;agrave; Posco Vi&#7879;t Nam.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7873; ph&amp;iacute;a doanh nghi&#7879;p, &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Posco Vi&#7879;t Nam cho r&#7857;ng, tr&#432;&#7899;c ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; nh&#7857;m ki&#7873;m ch&#7871; l&#7841;m ph&amp;aacute;t c&#7911;a Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911;, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p c&#7889; g&#7855;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u ra c&amp;aacute;c th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&amp;agrave;i l&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u t&#7845;t y&#7871;u.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, vi&#7879;c xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u hi&#7879;n nay c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p c&#361;ng g&#7863;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;iacute;t kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n do ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch b&#7843;o h&#7897; ng&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng s&#7903; t&#7841;i. &#272;i&#7875;n h&amp;igrave;nh nh&#432; ngay trong khu v&#7921;c ASEAN l&amp;agrave; Th&amp;aacute;i Lan, Indonesia&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam, Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; l&#7841;i ch&#432;a xem x&amp;eacute;t v&#7873; thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p h&amp;agrave;ng r&amp;agrave;o k&#7929; thu&#7853;t &#273;&#7875; ng&#259;n ch&#7863;n t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u th&amp;eacute;p ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng k&amp;eacute;m v&amp;agrave;o Vi&#7879;t Nam.&amp;rdquo; &amp;ndash; v&#7883; &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n n&amp;agrave;y n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&amp;aacute;ng ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute;, &amp;ocirc;ng Tr&#7847;n Tu&#7845;n D&#432;&#417;ng, T&#7893;ng Gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t c&amp;ograve;n c&#7843;nh b&amp;aacute;o, kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c gi&#7843;m, suy tho&amp;aacute;i kinh t&#7871; th&#7871; gi&#7899;i &#273;ang tr&#7903; l&#7841;i khi&#7871;n nhu c&#7847;u th&amp;eacute;p tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i gi&#7843;m, k&amp;eacute;o gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p gi&#7843;m. Nguy c&#417; nh&amp;igrave;n th&#7845;y l&amp;agrave; th&amp;eacute;p ngo&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; tr&amp;agrave;n v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&#7849;y c&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh th&#7871; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n h&#417;n do ph&#7843;i c&#7841;nh tranh v&#7899;i th&amp;eacute;p ngo&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Doanh nghi&#7879;p ph&#7843;i t&#7921; c&#7913;u m&amp;igrave;nh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o c&#7911;a c&#7843; l&amp;atilde;nh &#273;&#7841;o V&#7909; C&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p n&#7863;ng v&amp;agrave; V&#7909; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng trong n&#432;&#7899;c c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng th&amp;igrave;, n&#259;m nay &#273;&amp;atilde; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n nh&#432;ng n&#259;m sau c&amp;ograve;n ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n h&#417;n v&amp;igrave; Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng, t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng GDP n&#259;m 2012 d&#7921; ki&#7871;n s&#7869; ch&#7881; kho&#7843;ng t&#7915; 6 - 6,5% &#273;&#7875; ki&#7875;m so&amp;aacute;t CPI v&#7873; d&#432;&#7899;i 1 con s&#7889;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh s&#7913;c c&#7847;u chung s&#7909;t gi&#7843;m, ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng ngo&amp;agrave;i l&#7873;. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y, &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i m&#7863;t v&#7899;i kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n n&amp;agrave;y, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p ph&#7843;i n&#7895; l&#7921;c t&#7921; c&#7913;u m&amp;igrave;nh b&#7857;ng vi&#7879;c c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m chi ph&amp;iacute;, h&#7841; gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh &#273;&#7875; c&#7841;nh tranh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p x&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh. L&amp;atilde;nh &#273;&#7841;o t&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t cho bi&#7871;t, gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng ph&amp;oacute; v&#7899;i kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n c&#7911;a doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p l&amp;agrave; ti&#7871;t gi&#7843;m s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng, tr&amp;aacute;nh t&#7891;n kho &#273;&#7875; ph&#7843;i ch&#7883;u chi ph&amp;iacute; v&#7889;n vay; &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m c&amp;aacute;c chi ph&amp;iacute; qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute;, n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o ra s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh c&#7841;nh tranh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7893;ng C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam (VNStell) c&#361;ng &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; &#432;u ti&amp;ecirc;n ngo&#7841;i t&#7879; cho ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p b&#7903;i th&amp;eacute;p c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng ph&#7843;i th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n b&amp;igrave;nh &#7893;n gi&amp;aacute;, l&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; vai tr&amp;ograve; quan tr&#7885;ng trong n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;ang tr&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7901; v&amp;agrave;o vi&#7879;c B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng c&#7847;n t&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c gi&amp;aacute;m s&amp;aacute;t th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, th&amp;ocirc;ng tin &#273;&amp;uacute;ng, k&#7883;p th&#7901;i, tr&amp;aacute;nh t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u c&#7921;c do nhi&#7877;u th&amp;ocirc;ng tin nh&#432; DN ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n, n&#7907; x&#7845;u&amp;hellip; d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n c&amp;oacute; d&#432; lu&#7853;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng t&#7889;t, &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, kinh doanh c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7873; d&amp;agrave;i h&#7841;n, doanh nghi&#7879;p c&#361;ng &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng c&#7847;n xem x&amp;eacute;t kh&#7843; n&#259;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng ph&#432;&#417;ng &amp;aacute;n t&amp;aacute;i c&#7845;u tr&amp;uacute;c ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p. &#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; c&#417; h&#7897;i &#273;&#7875; nh&amp;igrave;n l&#7841;i &#273;i&#7875;m m&#7841;nh, y&#7871;u &#273;&#7875; t&amp;aacute;i c&#7845;u tr&amp;uacute;c cho ng&amp;agrave;nh hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;','29/10/2011','29/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/thep_ton.jpg',23,2,2092,'huyennt',1,'thi-truong-thep-dang-…-roi-loan','th&eacute;p, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, r&#7889;i lo&#7841;n, VLXD',NULL,NULL,NULL,'th&eacute;p, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, r&#7889;i lo&#7841;n, VLXD',0,0,0,'','','',3,'dothi.net',1,1,0,0),(81,'Doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p hoang mang v&igrave; l&#7895;','Ng&agrave;nh th&eacute;p hoang mang v&igrave; ti&ecirc;u th&#7909; ch&#7853;m, l&#7895; cu&#7889;i n&#259;m &quot;&#259;n&quot; h&#7871;t l&atilde;i &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m.','\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;B&amp;aacute;n ch&#7853;m, l&#7895; cu&#7889;i n&#259;m &#259;n h&#7871;t l&amp;atilde;i &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7899;i m&#7913;c t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng d&#7921; ki&#7871;n &amp;acirc;m 7,69%, n&#259;m 2011 s&#7869; l&#7843; n&#259;m &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p. T&#7841;i cu&#7897;c h&#7885;p m&#7899;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y t&#7841;i B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng, &amp;ocirc;ng Ph&#7841;m Ch&amp;iacute; C&#432;&#7901;ng, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam cho bi&#7871;t, t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7871;n nay, t&#7893;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&amp;atilde; gi&#7843;m g&#7847;n 10%. Nh&#7919;ng ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng, c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m chi ti&amp;ecirc;u, ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng si&#7871;t ch&#7863;t t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng khi&#7871;n cho c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n &#273;&amp;oacute;ng b&#259;ng, k&amp;eacute;o theo, ng&amp;agrave;nh v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng nh&#432; th&amp;eacute;p ch&#7883;u &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng r&#7845;t l&#7899;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7847;u n&#259;m, ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;ograve;n &#273;ang ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; t&#7889;t, nh&#432;ng sau khi Ngh&#7883; quy&#7871;t 11 ra &#273;&#7901;i, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u gi&#7843;m d&#7847;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p t&amp;iacute;nh to&amp;aacute;n, hi&#7879;n nay, th&amp;eacute;p gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; 200.000-300.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. Gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p b&amp;aacute;n t&#7841;i nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng k&#7875; VAT &#432;&#7899;c kho&#7843;ng 15 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n trong khi gia ph&amp;ocirc;i tr&amp;ecirc;n 14 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. &#272;&amp;aacute;ng ra, &#273;&#7875; h&amp;ograve;a v&#7889;n, s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;eacute;p ph&#7843;i b&amp;aacute;n gi&amp;aacute; 15,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. Nh&#432; v&#7853;y, hi&#7879;n nay c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;&#7873;u &#273;ang ph&#7843;i ch&#7883;u l&#7895;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t vay cao nh&#432; hi&#7879;n nay th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng doanh nghi&#7879;p n&amp;agrave;o c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; tr&#7843; n&#7907;, hay ti&#7871;p c&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c v&#7889;n. Doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p l&amp;atilde;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c 10% l&amp;agrave; m&#7915;ng l&#7855;m r&#7891;i, nh&#432;ng hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i l&amp;atilde;i vay l&amp;agrave; 20%, th&#7853;m ch&amp;iacute; h&#417;n th&amp;igrave; ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; l&#7895;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;quot;, &amp;ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng cho bi&#7871;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;N&#7871;u 3 th&amp;aacute;ng n&#7919;a, t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7851;n th&#7871; n&amp;agrave;y to&amp;agrave;n b&#7897; l&amp;atilde;i c&#7911;a doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p &#7903; giai &#273;o&#7841;n &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m s&#7869; tr&#7903; v&#7873; con s&#7889; 0 ho&#7863;c s&#7869; &amp;quot;&amp;acirc;m&amp;quot; v&#7889;n. &#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;n t&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; l&#7863;p l&#7841;i 2-3 n&#259;m nay trong ng&amp;agrave;nh, c&#7913; v&amp;agrave;i th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p l&amp;atilde;i l&#7899;n, &#273;&#7871;n cu&#7889;i n&#259;m l&#7841;i &amp;acirc;m v&#7889;n v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ch&#7883;u l&#7895; t&#7899;i c&#7843; n&#259;m sau&lt;/em&gt;&amp;quot;, &amp;ocirc;ng Ph&#7841;m Ch&amp;iacute; C&#432;&#7901;ng lo l&#7855;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/doanh_nghiep_thep_hoang_mang_vi_lo1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;M&#7897;t s&#7889; doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p hi&#7879;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng, d&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCho &#273;&#7871;n nay, m&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p n&amp;agrave;o c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n, nh&#432;ng th&#7921;c t&#7871; doanh nghi&#7879;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng, d&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute;. V&amp;iacute; d&#7909;, c&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;eacute;p V&#7841;n L&#7907;i trong cu&#7897;c h&#7885;p &#272;&#7841;i h&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng C&#7893; &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng g&#7847;n &#273;&amp;acirc;y &#273;&amp;atilde; tuy&amp;ecirc;n b&#7889; b&amp;aacute;n c&#417; s&#7903; c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; trong th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&#7897;i &#273;&#7883;a&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo c&amp;acirc;u chuy&#7879;n c&#7911;a &amp;ocirc;ng Ph&#7841;m Ch&amp;iacute; C&#432;&#7901;ng, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang xu&#7889;ng d&#7889;c m&#7897;t c&amp;aacute;ch th&#7843;m h&#7841;i trong khi c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;igrave; hoang mang v&amp;agrave; th&#7853;m ch&amp;iacute;, &#273;&amp;atilde; c&#7841;nh tranh kh&amp;ocirc;ng l&amp;agrave;nh m&#7841;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;iacute;a xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u, 2 s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ch&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;agrave; th&amp;eacute;p cu&#7897;n c&amp;aacute;n ngu&#7897;i xu&#7845;t sang Indonesi &#273;&amp;atilde; b&#7883; ki&#7879;n b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute;, &#7889;ng th&amp;eacute;p m&#7899;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y nh&#7845;t c&#361;ng b&#7883; ki&#7879;n b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; t&#7841;i M&#7929;. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i &#7903; &#273;&amp;oacute;, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m tr&amp;aacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;n, m&#7841; k&#7869;m c&#361;ng b&#7883; ki&#7879;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#272;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; chuy&#7879;n doanh nghi&#7879;p b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; nhau, d&#7851;n t&#7899;i ki&#7879;n c&amp;aacute;o n&#7897;i b&#7897;. Ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n c&amp;ograve;n k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i, ph&#7843;i t&#7921; c&#7913;u m&amp;igrave;nh tr&#432;&#7899;c l&amp;agrave; th&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;i&#7879;p chung c&#7911;a c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng doanh nghi&#7879;p ng&amp;agrave;nh n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7841;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng trong n&#432;&#7899;c, &#273;&amp;atilde; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n hi&#7879;n t&#432;&#7907;ng b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; &#7903; m&#7897;t v&amp;agrave;i doanh nghi&#7879;p n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&amp;atilde; l&#7895; c&amp;ograve;n l&#7895; th&amp;ecirc;m. Nhu c&#7847;u chung v&#7873; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&#7911;a n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871; kh&amp;ocirc;ng cao n&amp;ecirc;n doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;oacute; gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; t&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&amp;agrave; bao. Khi kh&amp;ocirc;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, doanh nghi&#7879;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; b&amp;agrave;n b&#7841;c chia s&#7867; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n chung, chia s&#7867; th&#7883; ph&#7847;n, n&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; ch&amp;agrave;o c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&amp;aacute;c r&#7845;t kh&amp;aacute;c nhau, d&#7851;n t&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ki&#7879;n c&amp;aacute;o trong n&#7897;i b&#7897; c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong ng&amp;agrave;nh, nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; m&#7841;nh, s&#7903; h&#7919;u c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; l&amp;ograve; cao nh&#432; T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam, c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t th&amp;igrave; c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh t&#7889;t, do c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7911; nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u, v&#7889;n. C&amp;ograve;n c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ty kh&amp;aacute;c nh&#432; V&#7841;n L&#7907;i, &#272;&amp;igrave;nh V&#361; &#273;&#7873;u &#273;&amp;atilde; c&#7841;n ki&#7879;t nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u &#273;&#7847;u v&amp;agrave;o, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&#7847;m ch&#7915;ng. Khi ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; v&amp;agrave;i doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;oacute; l&amp;ograve; cao mua qu&#7863;ng n&amp;ecirc;n ngay c&#7843; vi&#7879;c b&amp;aacute;n qu&#7863;ng s&#7855;t &#7903; c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng c&#361;ng r&#7845;t kh&amp;oacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Nghi&amp;ecirc;m Xu&amp;acirc;n &#272;a, Ph&amp;oacute; T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam cho hay, 10 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m, l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p c&#7911;a t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty &#273;&amp;atilde; gi&#7843;m 2,7% so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923;, l&amp;agrave; m&#7913;c gi&#7843;m s&amp;uacute;t &#273;&amp;aacute;ng k&#7875;. Trong &#273;&amp;oacute;, th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng gi&#7843;m gi&#7843;m 6,7% so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923;. 10 th&amp;aacute;ng qua, 50% &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; trong T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;t 60% k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t n&#259;m, nhi&#7873;u &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; ph&#7843;i &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch 2011 v&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;n &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; 3 &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; b&#7883; l&#7895;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7883; Ph&amp;oacute; T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c n&amp;agrave;y b&#259;n kho&#259;n: &amp;quot;M&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; ph&amp;iacute;a Ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch gi&#7843;m l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t huy &#273;&#7897;ng, cho vay nh&#432;ng th&#7921;c t&#7871; ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7845;y gi&#7843;m. Hi&#7879;n, l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t &#273;i vay v&#7851;n h&#417;n 20%/n&#259;m ch&#7913; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; chuy&#7879;n &#273;&amp;atilde; xu&#7889;ng 17-19%&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;270&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/doanh_nghiep_thep_hoang_mang_vi_lo2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;C&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p ph&#7843;i t&#7921; c&#7913;u m&amp;igrave;nh l&amp;agrave; ch&amp;iacute;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;h&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nKh&#7843; n&#259;ng ti&#7871;p c&#7853;n v&#7889;n n&amp;oacute;i chung v&#7851;n r&#7845;t h&#7841;n ch&#7871; v&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng ch&#7885;n l&#7885;c kh&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&#7875; tr&amp;aacute;nh t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n ngo&#7841;i t&#7879; v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n l&amp;agrave; n&#7895;i lo l&#7899;n cho doanh nghi&#7879;p. Hai ng&amp;agrave;y h&amp;ocirc;m nay, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ngo&#7841;i t&#7879; l&#7841;i &#273;&amp;oacute;ng b&#259;ng do b&#7883; ki&#7875;m so&amp;aacute;t g&#7855;t gao. Hi&#7879;n, tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng hai t&#7927; gi&amp;aacute; khi&#7871;n cho chi ph&amp;iacute; v&#7889;n c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; t&#259;ng cao l&amp;ecirc;n. Trong 10 th&amp;aacute;ng, ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i c&amp;oacute; l&amp;atilde;i nh&#432;ng c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ch&amp;ecirc;nh l&#7879;ch t&#7927; gi&amp;aacute; trong qu&amp;yacute; 4 s&#7869; v&amp;eacute;t h&#7871;t kho&#7843;n l&amp;atilde;i n&amp;agrave;y&lt;/em&gt;&amp;quot;, &amp;ocirc;ng &#272;a n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gi&#7843;m s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&#7875; t&#7921; c&#7913;u m&amp;igrave;nh tr&#432;&#7899;c&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;R&#7845;t th&#7859;ng th&#7855;n v&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7873;m t&#297;nh, &amp;ocirc;ng Tr&#7847;n Tu&#7845;n D&#432;&#417;ng, T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t, b&amp;agrave;y t&#7887;: &amp;quot;Kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n cho ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p s&#7869; c&amp;ograve;n k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i n&#7919;a. V&amp;igrave; nh&#7919;ng ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch c&#7911;a Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; theo Ngh&#7883; quy&#7871;t 11 l&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;uacute;ng v&amp;agrave; s&#7869; c&amp;ograve;n duy tr&amp;igrave; trong th&#7901;i gian d&amp;agrave;i t&#7899;i, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n &#273;i xu&#7889;ng l&amp;agrave; do v&amp;agrave;i n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng qu&amp;aacute; n&amp;oacute;ng n&amp;ecirc;n c&#361;ng s&#7869; kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; ph&#7909;c h&#7891;i nhanh trong ng&#7855;n h&#7841;n. Nhu c&#7847;u gi&#7843;m n&amp;ecirc;n nguy c&#417; th&amp;eacute;p th&#7915;a l&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute;&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &amp;ocirc;ng D&#432;&#417;ng, ch&amp;uacute;ng ta ph&#7843;i h&#7885;c theo th&#7871; gi&#7899;i, ph&#7843;i ti&#7871;t gi&#7843;m s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng cho ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;ang b&#7883; thu h&#7865;p. Thep H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t chi&#7871;m th&#7883; ph&#7847;n l&#7899;n th&#7913; hai &#7903; Vi&#7879;t Nam nh&#432;ng hi&#7879;n c&#361;ng ch&#7881; ch&#7841;y 80% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t. Co h&#7865;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t l&amp;uacute;c n&amp;agrave;y v&#7915;a l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m t&#7891;n kho, v&#7915;a gi&#7843;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi ph&amp;iacute; n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng, t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Nghi&amp;ecirc;m Xu&amp;acirc;n &#272;a c&#361;ng &#273;&#7891;ng t&amp;igrave;nh cho r&#7857;ng, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p c&#7847;n ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c kh&#7843;o s&amp;aacute;t m&#7903; r&#7897;ng th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng xu&amp;acirc;t kh&#7849;u &#273;&#7875; h&#7895; tr&#7907; cho ph&#7847;n n&#7897;i &#273;&#7883;a b&#7883; gi&#7843;m, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, tranh th&#7911; t&amp;aacute;i c&#7845;u tr&amp;uacute;c ch&amp;iacute;nh m&amp;igrave;nh, s&#7855;p x&#7871;p l&#7841;i c&amp;aacute;c c&#417; s&#7903; l&#432;u th&amp;ocirc;ng th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&#7875; ti&#7871;t gi&#7843;m chi ph&amp;iacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, &amp;ocirc;ng Ho&amp;agrave;ng V&#259;n T&amp;ograve;ng, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Gang th&amp;eacute;p Th&amp;aacute;i Nguy&amp;ecirc;n c&#361;ng cho hay, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&#7901;i gian qua c&#7911;a &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; ch&#7881; b&#7857;ng 70-71%. Ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i b&#7855;t bu&#7897;c ph&#7843;i gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh, t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m &#273;&#7871;n nay &#273;&amp;atilde; ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7899;i 150 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng so v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch &#273;&#7863;t ra.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng L&amp;ecirc; Minh H&#7843;i, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch C&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t &#272;&#7913;c cho r&#7857;ng, v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&amp;agrave;n s&amp;acirc;u, k&#7929;. Hi&#7879;n ch&amp;uacute;ng ta &#273;ang l&#7895; n&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7843;i &#273;i &#273;&#7871;n v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; m&#7845;u ch&#7889;t l&amp;agrave; ph&#7843;i x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng mang l&#432;&#7899;i b&amp;aacute;n h&amp;agrave;ng. C&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p l&#7899;n n&amp;ecirc;n th&amp;agrave;nh l&#7853;p nh&amp;oacute;m G &#273;&#7875; b&amp;agrave;n b&#7841;c v&amp;agrave; t&#7915; &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ty nh&#7887; s&#7869; theo nh&amp;oacute;m G...Do m&#7841;ng l&#432;&#7899;i ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i hi&#7879;n r&#7845;t l&#7911;ng c&#7911;ng, ai c&#361;ng ch&#7913;ng minh n&#259;ng l&#7921;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t cao v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;a ra gi&amp;aacute; kh&amp;ocirc;ng h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute;. Vi&#7879;t &#272;&#7913;c cho r&#7857;ng, n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;a ra m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; c&amp;oacute; l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n nh&#7845;t &#273;&#7883;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#432;&#7899;c nhi&#7873;u gi&amp;atilde;i b&amp;agrave;y c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p, &amp;ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n M&#7841;nh Qu&amp;acirc;n, V&#7909; tr&#432;&#7903;ng V&#7909; C&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p n&#7863;ng chia s&#7867;, kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n v&#7873; l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t cao th&amp;igrave; Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u bi&#7879;n ph&amp;aacute;p. Nh&#432;ng ph&amp;iacute;a ch&#7911; quan, ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p ph&#7843;i t&amp;iacute;nh to&amp;aacute;n l&#7853;p h&amp;agrave;ng r&amp;agrave;o k&#7929; thu&#7853;t ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i &#273;&#7863;c th&amp;ugrave; trong n&#432;&#7899;c, &#273;&#7875; c&#7841;nh tranh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c v&#7899;i th&amp;eacute;p nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u. N&#7871;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng l&amp;agrave; ng&amp;agrave;nh s&#7869; r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o c&#7843;nh &amp;quot;ch&amp;uacute;ng ta ch&#7863;t ch&amp;acirc;n ch&amp;iacute;nh m&amp;igrave;nh&amp;quot;. C&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p ph&#7843;i c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t c&#7909; th&#7875; &#273;&#7875; ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i c&amp;oacute; t&#7893;ng h&#7907;p hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;iacute;a B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng s&#7869; c&#7889; g&#7855;ng th&#432;&#417;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&#7871;p v&#7899;i Ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7875; th&amp;aacute;o g&#7905; cho c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p m&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave;, th&amp;eacute;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng thu&#7897;c di&#7879;n &#432;u ti&amp;ecirc;n ngo&#7841;i t&#7879;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#259;m 2012, t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh s&#7869; kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;aacute; h&#417;n ngay n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p ph&#7843;i c&amp;oacute; li&#7879;u li&#7879;u m&amp;agrave; &#7913;ng ph&amp;oacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;quot;&#272;&#432;&#417;ng nhi&amp;ecirc;n, Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&amp;agrave; b&#7897; ng&amp;agrave;nh s&#7869; ph&#7843;i th&amp;aacute;o g&#7905; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n cho doanh nghi&#7879;p. T&#432;&#417;ng lai ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p v&#7851;n s&amp;aacute;ng s&#7911;a ch&#7913; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i qu&amp;aacute; &#273;en t&#7889;i v&amp;igrave; nhu c&#7847;u c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m n&amp;agrave;y trong qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n &#273;&#7845;t n&#432;&#7899;c c&amp;ograve;n r&#7845;t l&#7899;n, c&amp;ograve;n nhi&#7873;u c&#417; h&#7897;i ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n. M&#7895;i doanh nghi&#7879;p c&#7847;n c&amp;oacute; gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p c&#7909; th&#7875; t&amp;ugrave;y &#273;&#7863;c th&amp;ugrave; c&#7911;a ri&amp;ecirc;ng &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; m&amp;igrave;nh, nh&#432;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n tinh th&#7847;n chung l&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n s&#7855;p t&#7899;i c&amp;ograve;n kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n. Ch&amp;uacute;ng ta ph&#7843;i t&#7921; tr&amp;ocirc;ng mong v&amp;agrave;o s&#7913;c m&amp;igrave;nh l&amp;agrave; ch&amp;iacute;nh&lt;/em&gt;&amp;quot;, Th&#7913; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng L&amp;ecirc; D&#432;&#417;ng Quang nh&#7845;n m&#7841;nh.&lt;/p&gt;','31/10/2011','31/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/doanh_nghiep_thep_hoang_mang_vi_lo2.jpg',23,2,1810,'huyennt',1,'doanh-nghiep-thep-hoang-mang-vi-lo','doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p, hoang mang,',NULL,NULL,NULL,'doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p, hoang mang,',0,0,0,'','','',3,'xaydungvietnam.vn',1,0,0,1),(82,'H&agrave; N&#7897;i: C&ocirc;ng b&#7889; quy ho&#7841;ch ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n VLXD &#273;&#7871;n 2030','S&#7903; X&acirc;y d&#7921;ng H&agrave; N&#7897;i v&#7915;a c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; Quy ho&#7841;ch ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng (VLXD) th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2020, &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2030.','&lt;p&gt;&#272;&amp;acirc;y c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; quy ho&#7841;ch chuy&amp;ecirc;n ng&amp;agrave;nh &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t v&amp;agrave; c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; sau khi c&amp;oacute; Quy ho&#7841;ch chung x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Th&#7911; &#273;&amp;ocirc;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo quy ho&#7841;ch, giai &#273;o&#7841;n &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2020, c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t VLXD c&#7911;a H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o l&amp;agrave; ng&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p th&amp;acirc;n thi&#7879;n m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng, h&#432;&#7899;ng t&#7899;i n&#7873;n c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p xanh, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i VLXD kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung, x&#7917; l&amp;yacute; v&amp;agrave; lo&#7841;i b&#7887; d&#7847;n c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t theo ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&amp;aacute;p truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u t&#7889;n nhi&amp;ecirc;u li&#7879;u, hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; kinh t&#7871; th&#7845;p, g&amp;acirc;y &amp;ocirc; nhi&#7877;m m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng, ng&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2012. Quy ho&#7841;ch c&#361;ng &#273;&#7863;t m&#7909;c ti&amp;ecirc;u trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n &#273;&#7871;n 2015, t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; t&#259;ng gia str&#7883; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p VLXD &#273;&#7841;t 17%/n&#259;m, giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2016-2020 &#273;&#7841;t 16%. &#272;&#7871;n 2020, ng&amp;agrave;nh n&amp;agrave;y s&#7869; &#273;&amp;oacute;ng g&amp;oacute;p cho ng&amp;acirc;n s&amp;aacute;ch TP kho&#7843;ng 3.800 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng. &#272;&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n nh&#7919;ng d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; theo quy ho&#7841;ch, d&#7921; ki&#7871;n t&#7893;ng v&#7889;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; cho ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p VLXD trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n t&#7915; nay &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2015 l&amp;agrave; h&#417;n 9.400 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng, t&#7915; 2016-2020 l&amp;agrave; h&#417;n 3.000 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Quy ho&#7841;ch c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;a ra ph&#432;&#417;ng h&#432;&#7899;ng di d&#7901;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&#417; s&#7903; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n t&#7915; nay &#273;&#7871;n 2015 g&#7891;m 12 &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; C&amp;ocirc;ng ty CP g&#7841;ch ng&amp;oacute;i Th&#7841;c B&amp;agrave;n, C&amp;ocirc;ng ty CP b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Th&#7883;nh Li&#7879;t&amp;hellip; Trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2016-2020 di chuy&#7875;n 5 c&#417; s&#7903;, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; C&amp;ocirc;ng ty CP Vi&#7879;t M&#7929;, C&amp;ocirc;ng ty CP Viglacera &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng Anh&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;334&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/ha-noi-cong-bo-pt-vlxd.JPG&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Vi&#7879;c c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; quy ho&#7841;ch s&#7869; l&amp;agrave; c&#259;n c&#7913; cho c&amp;aacute;c ng&amp;agrave;nh, c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, c&amp;aacute;c DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t VLXD c&#7911;a TP l&#7853;p c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, chu&#7849;n b&#7883; l&#7921;c l&#432;&#7907;ng, t&amp;igrave;m ngu&#7891;n v&#7889;n &#273;&#7875; tri&#7875;n khai c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i n&amp;acirc;ng cao c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','01/11/2011','01/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/ha-noi-cong-bo-pt-vlxd.JPG',23,2,1877,'huyennt',1,'ha-noi-cong-bo-quy-hoach-phat-trien-vlxd-den-2030','VLXD, &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng, quy ho&#7841;ch,  ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'VLXD, &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng, quy ho&#7841;ch,  ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://kientrucvietnam.org.vn',1,0,0,0),(83,'Ng&agrave;nh th&eacute;p v&#7851;n l&#7841;c quan trong d&agrave;i h&#7841;n','M&#7863;c d&ugrave; c&aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;ang g&#7863;p nhi&#7873;u kh&oacute; kh&#259;n nh&#432;ng nh&#7919;ng &aacute;ch t&#7855;c v&#7873; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t kinh doanh trong hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n quy ho&#7841;ch chung c&#7911;a to&agrave;n ng&agrave;nh trong nh&#7919;ng n&#259;m t&#7899;i.','\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNh&#7919;ng d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o l&#7841;c quan &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &amp;ocirc;ng Ph&#7841;m Ch&amp;iacute; C&#432;&#7901;ng, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam (VSA) &#273;&#432;a ra b&#7903;i l&#432;&#7907;ng th&amp;eacute;p ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o s&#7869; c&amp;ograve;n t&#259;ng cao trong th&#7901;i gian t&#7899;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trao &#273;&#7893;i v&#7899;i Th&#7901;i b&amp;aacute;o Kinh t&#7871; S&amp;agrave;i G&amp;ograve;n Online ng&amp;agrave;y 1-11, &amp;ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;a ra d&#7851;n ch&#7913;ng l&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;n s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng th&amp;eacute;p b&amp;igrave;nh qu&amp;acirc;n &#273;&#7847;u ng&#432;&#7901;i c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam m&#7899;i &#7903; kho&#7843;ng 130 kg th&amp;eacute;p/ng&#432;&#7901;i v&amp;agrave; ph&#7843;i t&#259;ng l&amp;ecirc;n 200-300 kg th&amp;eacute;p/ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#7871;u Vi&#7879;t Nam mu&#7889;n tr&#7903; th&amp;agrave;nh n&#432;&#7899;c c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &amp;ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng, nh&#7919;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n c&#7911;a doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p hi&#7879;n nay ch&#7883;u t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng b&#7903;i ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch chung c&#7911;a k&amp;igrave;m ch&#7871; l&#7841;m ph&amp;aacute;t, c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng&amp;hellip; Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, nh&#7919;ng &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p c&#361;ng ch&#7881; l&amp;agrave; t&#7841;m th&#7901;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Vi&#7879;c &#273;&amp;oacute;ng c&#7917;a m&#7897;t s&#7889; doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p th&#7901;i gian qua, theo &amp;ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng, m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n c&#361;ng do c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p l&amp;agrave;m &#259;n manh m&amp;uacute;n, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;agrave;i b&#7843;n d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n chuy&#7879;n d&#432; th&#7915;a c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t, ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n. &amp;Ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;i&#7873;u nay c&#361;ng gi&amp;uacute;p ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p t&amp;aacute;i c&#417; c&#7845;u theo h&#432;&#7899;ng ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n b&#7873;n v&#7919;ng h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;oacute;i, &#273;&#7875; ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n b&#7873;n v&#7919;ng, tr&amp;aacute;nh l&#7863;p l&#7841;i t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &amp;aacute;ch t&#7855;c khi th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng c&amp;oacute; bi&#7871;n &#273;&#7897;ng, doanh nghi&#7879;p n&amp;ecirc;n ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c x&amp;uacute;c ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u. B&#7857;ng ch&#7913;ng cho th&#7845;y nh&#7919;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p trong th&#7901;i gian qua &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;m b&#7899;t m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n l&amp;agrave; nh&#7901; v&amp;agrave;o vi&#7879;c &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh l&#432;&#7907;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong 10 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m nay, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&amp;atilde; xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u x&#7845;p x&#7881; 1,3 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, th&amp;eacute;p &#7889;ng, th&amp;eacute;p cu&#7897;n c&amp;aacute;n ngu&#7897;i, t&amp;ocirc;n m&#7841; k&#7869;m, t&amp;ocirc;n m&#7841; m&amp;agrave;u, &#273;&#7841;t kim ng&#7841;ch kho&#7843;ng 1,5 t&#7881; &#273;&amp;ocirc; la M&#7929;, t&#259;ng m&#7841;nh so v&#7899;i kim ng&#7841;ch 1,3 t&#7881; &#273;&amp;ocirc; la M&#7929; trong c&#7843; n&#259;m 2010.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; ho&amp;agrave;n ch&#7881;nh v&amp;agrave; &#273;ang tr&amp;igrave;nh Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; xem x&amp;eacute;t, ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t &#273;&#7873; &amp;aacute;n &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh &amp;ldquo;Quy ho&#7841;ch ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n h&#7879; th&#7889;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng th&amp;eacute;p giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2011 - 2020, t&#7847;m nh&amp;igrave;n 2025&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng cho bi&#7871;t m&#7909;c ti&amp;ecirc;u trong &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh quy ho&#7841;ch l&#7847;n n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;agrave; nh&#7857;m t&#7853;p trung h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i th&amp;eacute;p thi&#7871;u nhi&#7873;u, ch&#432;a s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c nh&#432; th&amp;eacute;p cu&#7897;n c&amp;aacute;n n&amp;oacute;ng, th&amp;eacute;p ch&#7871; t&#7841;o c&#417; kh&amp;iacute;, th&amp;eacute;p h&#7907;p kim &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m b&#7899;t nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u, tr&amp;aacute;nh &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; tr&amp;agrave;n lan.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','02/11/2011','02/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/nganh-thep-van-lac-quan.jpg',23,2,1828,'huyennt',1,'nganh-thep-van-lac-quan-trong-dai-han','ngh&agrave;nh th&eacute;p, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, VLXD',NULL,NULL,NULL,'ngh&agrave;nh th&eacute;p, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, VLXD',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://vatlieuxaydung.batdongsan.com.vn',1,0,0,0),(84,'Th&eacute;p: B&#7883; ki&#7879;n ch&#7889;ng b&aacute;n ph&aacute; gi&aacute;','V&#7915;a qua, theo ngu&#7891;n tin t&#7915; C&#7909;c qu&#7843;n l&yacute; c&#7841;nh tranh, c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a ng&agrave;nh &#7889;ng th&eacute;p cu&#7897;n cacbon c&#7911;a Hoa K&#7923; (CWP) &#273;&atilde; n&#7897;p &#273;&#417;n ki&#7879;n ch&#7889;ng b&aacute;n ph&aacute; gi&aacute; v&agrave; ch&#7889;ng tr&#7907; c&#7845;p &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m CWP c&#7911;a &#7844;n &#272;&#7897;, Oman, C&aacute;c Ti&#7875;u v&#432;&#417;ng qu&#7889;c &#7842; R&#7853;p Th&#7889;ng nh&#7845;t v&agrave; Vi&#7879;t Nam.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Th&amp;eacute;p: B&#7883; ki&#7879;n ch&#7889;ng b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;0&quot; height=&quot;0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/thepcuon.JPG&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;0&quot; height=&quot;0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/thepcuon.JPG&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;400&quot; height=&quot;286&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/thepcuon.JPG&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&#272;&#432;&#7907;c bi&#7871;t, &#273;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; lo&#7841;i th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&#432;&#7907;c d&amp;ugrave;ng trong ng&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, trang tr&amp;iacute; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t d&amp;acirc;n d&#7909;ng v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; thu&#7871; nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u sang M&#7929; &#7903; m&#7913;c 0%.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p Vi&#7879;t Nam trong danh s&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&#417;n ki&#7879;n l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ty t&#432; nh&amp;acirc;n, li&amp;ecirc;n doanh nh&#432;: Hoa Sen Group, H&#7919;u Li&amp;ecirc;n &amp;Aacute; Ch&amp;acirc;u, H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t, Vinapipe,&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; th&amp;ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; bi&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7897; ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; v&amp;agrave; ch&#7889;ng tr&#7907; c&#7845;p b&#7883; c&amp;aacute;o bu&#7897;c. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, c&amp;oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng M&#7929; s&#7869; y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u &amp;aacute;p d&#7909;ng ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&amp;aacute;p ch&#7889;ng b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871; phi th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i Vi&#7879;t Nam. &#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; l&#7847;n th&#7913; 2 M&#7929; ki&#7879;n Vi&#7879;t Nam v&#7873; ch&#7889;ng tr&#7907; c&#7845;p v&amp;agrave; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c s&#7869; g&amp;acirc;y tranh c&amp;atilde;i b&#7903;i c&amp;ugrave;ng l&amp;uacute;c ki&#7879;n ch&#7889;ng tr&#7907; c&#7845;p v&amp;agrave; ch&#7889;ng b&amp;aacute;n gi&amp;aacute; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&amp;aacute;p &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871; phi th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng.&lt;/p&gt;','02/11/2011','02/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/thepcuon.JPG',23,2,1855,'huyennt',1,'thep-bi-kien-chong-ban-pha-gia','VLXD, th&eacute;p cu&#7889;n, ch&#7889;ng b&aacute;n ph&aacute; gi&aacute;',NULL,NULL,NULL,'VLXD, th&eacute;p cu&#7889;n, ch&#7889;ng b&aacute;n ph&aacute; gi&aacute;',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://cafeland.vn',1,1,0,1),(85,'V&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m theo b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n','&#272;&#7883;a &#7889;c &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m &#273;&atilde; k&eacute;o th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng &ldquo;l&#7841;nh&rdquo; theo, d&ugrave; &#273;ang v&agrave;o cao &#273;i&#7875;m x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng cu&#7889;i n&#259;m.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7883;u &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng n&#7863;ng n&#7873; nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; th&amp;eacute;p. &#7870; &#7849;m tri&#7873;n mi&amp;ecirc;n t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m &#273;&#7871;n h&#7871;t th&amp;aacute;ng 10, l&#432;&#7907;ng ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p v&amp;agrave; th&amp;eacute;p th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7849;m t&#7891;n kho l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 900.000 t&#7845;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Th&amp;eacute;p &amp;ldquo;lao&amp;rdquo; theo b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; &#273;&amp;atilde; gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n nhi&#7873;u l&#7847;n nh&#432;ng th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng th&amp;eacute;p v&#7851;n ch&#432;a kh&#7903;i s&#7855;c. Theo l&amp;atilde;nh &#273;&#7841;o m&#7897;t c&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;eacute;p t&#7841;i TP HCM, &#273;&#7875; b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng, doanh nghi&#7879;p n&amp;agrave;y, t&#7915; 3 th&amp;aacute;ng nay, li&amp;ecirc;n t&#7909;c gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;. Hi&#7879;n nay, gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p b&amp;aacute;n t&#7841;i nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng k&#7875; VAT kho&#7843;ng 15 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n, trong khi gi&amp;aacute; ph&amp;ocirc;i &#273;&amp;atilde; 14 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. M&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;ang ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c gi&#7843;m 200.000 - 300.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n so v&#7899;i qu&amp;yacute; tr&#432;&#7899;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;335&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/vat-lieu-xay-dung-am-dam-theo-bat-dong-san.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;T&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;h&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng B&#272;S &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m &#273;&amp;atilde; k&amp;eacute;o ng&amp;agrave;nh VLXD &amp;quot;l&#7841;nh&amp;quot; theo.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7841;i bu&#7893;i h&#7885;p th&amp;aacute;o g&#7905; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n cho ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p do B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, chi&#7873;u 27/10, &amp;ocirc;ng Tr&#7847;n Tu&#7845;n D&#432;&#417;ng, T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t, cho bi&#7871;t, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n tr&#7847;m l&#7855;ng, nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ng&#7915;ng thi c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p &#273;&#7871;n ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p, nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng. Nhu c&#7847;u th&amp;eacute;p gi&#7843;m v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y th&#7915;a th&amp;eacute;p. &amp;Ocirc;ng Ph&#7841;m Ch&amp;iacute; C&#432;&#7901;ng, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam, ph&amp;agrave;n n&amp;agrave;n: Trong 9 th&amp;aacute;ng qua, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng ch&#7881; g&#7847;n 6,1 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, b&#7857;ng 96,02% so v&#7899;i n&#259;m 2010. D&#7921; ki&#7871;n, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p c&#7843; n&#259;m 2011 gi&#7843;m 7,69% so v&#7899;i n&#259;m 2010. Ph&amp;oacute; t&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam, Nghi&amp;ecirc;m Xu&amp;acirc;n &#272;a th&#7915;a nh&#7853;n, 10 th&amp;aacute;ng qua, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;t 1,9 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, gi&#7843;m 2% so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923; n&#259;m ngo&amp;aacute;i, nh&#432;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; gi&#7843;m t&#7899;i 6,7%, t&#7891;n kho 185.000 t&#7845;n... &amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;C&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7871;n 10 ng&amp;agrave;y trong 1 th&amp;aacute;ng ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m n&amp;agrave;o&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo;, l&amp;atilde;nh &#273;&#7841;o m&#7897;t c&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;eacute;p than th&#7903;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng c&amp;ograve;n cho bi&#7871;t hi&#7879;n &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p l&amp;ecirc;n ti&#7871;ng b&amp;aacute;n c&#417; s&#7903; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ty kh&amp;aacute;c ph&#7843;i ch&#7841;y d&#432;&#7899;i c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t, kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; nguy c&#417; ng&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;L&#7895; v&#7851;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7849;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Xi m&#259;ng c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem l&amp;agrave; ng&amp;agrave;nh &amp;ldquo;n&amp;oacute;ng&amp;rdquo; khi l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7891;n kho kh&amp;ocirc;ng thua k&amp;eacute;m th&amp;eacute;p. Ch&#7881; ri&amp;ecirc;ng t&#7841;i T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty C&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p Xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam (Vicem) &#273;ang t&#7891;n kho&#7843;ng 2 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n xi m&#259;ng v&amp;agrave; clinker. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, tr&amp;aacute;i v&#7899;i di&#7877;n bi&#7871;n c&#7911;a th&amp;eacute;p l&amp;agrave; s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; v&amp;agrave; m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7873;u gi&#7843;m th&amp;igrave; gi&amp;aacute; xi m&#259;ng l&#7841;i t&#259;ng kho&#7843;ng 5% so v&#7899;i qu&amp;yacute; tr&#432;&#7899;c. C&#7909; th&#7875;, gi&amp;aacute; xi m&#259;ng Holcim qu&amp;yacute; tr&#432;&#7899;c 86.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/bao th&amp;igrave; nay l&amp;ecirc;n 91.000 &#273;&#7891;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&amp;aacute;c nh&#432; g&#7841;ch, c&amp;aacute;t, &#273;&amp;aacute;&amp;hellip; c&#361;ng chung s&#7889; ph&#7853;n khi s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; kh&amp;aacute; ch&#7853;m. Theo s&#7889; li&#7879;u th&#7889;ng k&amp;ecirc; c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh g&#7889;m, l&#432;&#7907;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t t&#7891;n kho &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;ecirc;n tr&amp;ecirc;n 30 tri&#7879;u m2. C&amp;ograve;n ng&amp;agrave;nh k&amp;iacute;nh m&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; gi&#7843;m h&#417;n 40% so v&#7899;i qu&amp;yacute; tr&#432;&#7899;c v&#7851;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng, d&#7921; &#273;o&amp;aacute;n l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho s&#7869; t&#259;ng g&#7845;p 2 l&#7847;n so v&#7899;i n&#259;m 2010. Theo &amp;ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n Quang Vinh, T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c C&amp;ocirc;ng ty x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; (Citicons), &#273;&amp;uacute;ng ra gi&amp;aacute; ph&#7843;i t&#259;ng do gi&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7847;u v&amp;agrave;o t&#259;ng&amp;hellip; nh&#432;ng do h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n nhi&#7873;u qu&amp;aacute;, ai c&#361;ng mu&#7889;n b&amp;aacute;n ra &#273;&#7875; thu h&#7891;i v&#7889;n v&#7873; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7843;i gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; 5 - 7% &#273;&#7875; mong thu ti&#7873;n m&#7863;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7913; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Nguy&#7877;n Tr&#7847;n Nam c&#361;ng x&amp;aacute;c nh&#7853;n, ng&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t xi-m&#259;ng, b&amp;ecirc;-t&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; b&#7883; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng n&#7863;ng. &amp;ldquo;L&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; xi m&#259;ng ch&#7853;m, t&#7891;n kho &#7903; h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng t&#7915; c&#7885;c ch&#7883;u &#7913;ng l&#7921;c cho &#273;&#7871;n k&#7871;t c&#7845;u b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng l&#7855;p r&amp;aacute;p t&#259;ng g&#7845;p &#273;&amp;ocirc;i. C&amp;ocirc;ng nh&amp;acirc;n &#273;&amp;atilde; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u ph&#7843;i ngh&#7881; vi&#7879;c&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ocirc;ng n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;T&#7915; th&amp;aacute;ng 6/2011, c&amp;ocirc;ng ty t&amp;ocirc;i ch&#7881; k&amp;yacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c 1 c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7871;n nay kh&amp;ocirc;ng k&amp;yacute; th&amp;ecirc;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng n&amp;agrave;o. &#272;&amp;atilde; th&#7871;, m&#7897;t s&#7889; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;ang l&amp;agrave;m c&#361;ng ph&#7843;i ng&#432;ng do ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; k&#7865;t v&#7889;n. Hi&#7879;n v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n m&#7897;t v&amp;agrave;i c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh &#273;ang ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432;ng ch&#7881; c&#7847;m ch&#7915;ng. Nhi&#7873;u c&amp;ocirc;ng ty x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&amp;aacute;c c&#361;ng r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh c&#7843;nh t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; khi kh&amp;ocirc;ng k&amp;yacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7903;i c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n &#273;ang ng&#7915;ng thi c&amp;ocirc;ng. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng m&#7899;i, nh&#432;ng h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng c&#361; c&#361;ng t&#7855;t, v&amp;igrave; ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng gi&#7843;i ng&amp;acirc;n v&#7889;n &#273;&#7875; nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u c&amp;oacute; ti&#7873;n mua VLXD thi c&amp;ocirc;ng&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo;. (&amp;Ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n Quang Vinh, T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c Citicons).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;','03/11/2011','03/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/vat-lieu-xay-dung-am-dam-theo-bat-dong-san.jpg',23,2,1839,'huyennt',1,'vat-lieu-xay-dung-am-dam-theo-bat-dong-san','th&eacute;p lao v&agrave;o B&#272;S, VLXD &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m theo B&#272;S',NULL,NULL,NULL,'th&eacute;p lao v&agrave;o B&#272;S, VLXD &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m theo B&#272;S',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'http://www.diaoconline.vn',1,0,0,0),(86,'Doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p : Kh&oacute; kh&#259;n ch&#7891;ng ch&#7845;t','V&#7899;i th&#7921;c tr&#7841;ng t&#7891;n kho kho&#7843;ng 500.000 t&#7845;n v&agrave; vi&#7879;c ti&ecirc;u th&#7909; li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c &ldquo;xu&#7889;ng d&#7889;c kh&ocirc;ng phanh&rdquo;, t&#7915; m&#7913;c 480.000 t&#7845;n trong th&aacute;ng 8, &#273;&atilde; gi&#7843;m 100.000 t&#7845;n v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 9 v&agrave; trong th&aacute;ng 10 ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;t x&#7845;p x&#7881; 300.000 t&#7845;n, ng&agrave;nh th&eacute;p &#273;ang trong t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng &ldquo;ch&#7907; chi&#7873;u&rdquo;.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Tin-tuc/?aid=54&quot;&gt; Th&amp;eacute;p: B&#7883; ki&#7879;n ch&#7889;ng ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Tin-tuc/?aid=53&quot;&gt;Ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p v&#7851;n l&#7841;c quan trong d&amp;agrave;i h&#7841;n&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Tin-tuc/?aid=51&quot;&gt; Doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p hoang mang v&amp;igrave; l&#7895;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Ph&#7841;m Ch&amp;iacute; C&#432;&#7901;ng - Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p (VSA) cho bi&#7871;t t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang &#7903; m&#7913;c... &amp;acirc;m 7,69%, 20% DN th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang r&#7845;t kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i t&amp;aacute;i c&#417; c&#7845;u n&#7871;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng mu&#7889;n b&#7883; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2012.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;B&amp;aacute;n m&amp;igrave;nh&amp;rdquo; &#273;&#7875;... tr&#7843; n&#7907;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; cho t&#7899;i th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; DN n&amp;agrave;o ch&amp;iacute;nh th&#7913;c c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n, song v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i, c&#7897;ng v&#7899;i kho&#7843;n l&amp;atilde;i ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; khi&#7871;n nhi&#7873;u DN l&amp;acirc;m v&amp;agrave;o c&#7843;nh &amp;ldquo;&#273;&#432;&#7901;ng c&amp;ugrave;ng&amp;rdquo; l&amp;agrave; ph&#7843;i rao b&amp;aacute;n t&amp;agrave;i s&#7843;n &#273;&#7875; tr&#7843; n&#7907;. &#272;i&#7875;n h&amp;igrave;nh trong s&#7889; n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;agrave; Cty th&amp;eacute;p V&#7841;n L&#7907;i, m&#7899;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y ng&amp;agrave;y 18/10/2011, t&#7841;i &#272;&#7841;i h&#7897;i c&#7893; &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7845;t th&#432;&#7901;ng, DN n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;atilde; th&amp;ocirc;ng qua vi&#7879;c b&amp;aacute;n t&amp;agrave;i s&#7843;n Cty &#273;&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n vi&#7879;c tr&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c kho&#7843;n n&#7907; cho ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; n&#7907;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;335&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/doanh-nghiep-thep--kho-khan-chong-chat.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang &#273;&#7889;i m&#7863;t v&#7899;i l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho &#7903; m&#7913;c cao,hi&#7879;n c&amp;oacute; kho&#7843;ng 500.000 t&#7845;n, g&#7845;p &#273;&amp;ocirc;i l&amp;uacute;c b&amp;igrave;nh th&#432;&#7901;ng &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &amp;ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng, v&#7899;i t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p li&amp;ecirc;n ti&#7871;p gi&#7843;m nh&#432; hi&#7879;n nay c&#7897;ng v&#7899;i &amp;ldquo;b&amp;agrave;i ca&amp;rdquo; mu&amp;ocirc;n th&#7911;a: &amp;ldquo;&#272;&#7847;u n&#259;m l&amp;atilde;i l&#7899;n, cu&#7889;i n&#259;m &amp;acirc;m v&amp;agrave;o&amp;rdquo; c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh tr&#432;&#7899;c sau g&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c DN c&#361;ng s&#7869; ph&#7843;i &amp;ldquo;ra &#273;i&amp;rdquo;. C&#7909; th&#7875; hi&#7879;n nay, ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang &#273;&#7889;i m&#7863;t v&#7899;i l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho &#7903; m&#7913;c cao, hi&#7879;n kho&#7843;ng 500.000 t&#7845;n, g&#7845;p &#273;&amp;ocirc;i l&amp;uacute;c b&amp;igrave;nh th&#432;&#7901;ng. T&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng n&amp;agrave;y &#273;ang di&#7877;n ra &#7903; nh&#7919;ng DN th&amp;eacute;p m&#7899;i ra &#273;&#7901;i, &#273;ang ch&#7883;u chi ph&amp;iacute; l&amp;atilde;i vay l&#7899;n, trong khi h&amp;agrave;ng l&amp;agrave;m ra kh&amp;ocirc;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c. Gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p b&amp;aacute;n t&#7841;i nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng k&#7875; thu&#7871; gi&amp;aacute; tr&#7883; gia t&#259;ng kho&#7843;ng 15 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n; gi&amp;aacute; ph&amp;ocirc;i tr&amp;ecirc;n 14 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, &#273;&#7875; h&amp;ograve;a v&#7889;n, DN ph&#7843;i b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c 15,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. &amp;ldquo;&#272;i&#7873;u &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; ngh&#297;a l&amp;agrave; DN &#273;ang ch&#7883;u l&#7895;. N&#7871;u 3 th&amp;aacute;ng n&#7919;a, t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh v&#7851;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7893;i, to&amp;agrave;n b&#7897; s&#7889; l&amp;atilde;i t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m s&#7869; tr&#7903; v&#7873; 0 ho&#7863;c &amp;acirc;m&amp;rdquo; - &amp;Ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nL&#7869; th&#432;&#7901;ng t&amp;igrave;nh, khi l&amp;agrave;m &#259;n kinh doanh c&amp;oacute; l&amp;atilde;i th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng sao, nh&#432;ng h&#7877; kinh doanh kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c DN th&#432;&#7901;ng t&amp;igrave;m &#273;&#7911; m&#7885;i c&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&#7875; b&amp;aacute;n cho b&#7857;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng ho&amp;aacute; c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh. &#272;&amp;atilde; v&#7853;y &amp;ldquo;ho&#7841; v&amp;ocirc; &#273;&#417;n ch&amp;iacute;&amp;rdquo;, khi th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;ang g&#7863;p kh&amp;oacute; th&amp;igrave; ph&amp;iacute;a xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u, 2 s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ch&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;agrave; th&amp;eacute;p cu&#7897;n c&amp;aacute;n ngu&#7897;i xu&#7845;t sang Indonesia &#273;&amp;atilde; b&#7883; ki&#7879;n b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute;, &#7889;ng th&amp;eacute;p m&#7899;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y nh&#7845;t c&#361;ng b&#7883; ki&#7879;n b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; t&#7841;i M&#7929;. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i &#7903; &#273;&amp;oacute;, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m tr&amp;aacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;n, m&#7841; k&#7869;m c&#361;ng b&#7883; ki&#7879;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DN ph&#7843;i t&#7921; c&#7913;u m&amp;igrave;nh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#432;&#7899;c nh&#7919;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p, Th&#7913; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng L&amp;ecirc; D&#432;&#417;ng Quang cho r&#7857;ng, th&#7901;i gian t&#7899;i ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p s&#7869; v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n g&#7863;p kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, c&#7847;n h&#432;&#7899;ng th&amp;aacute;o g&#7905;, song DN ph&#7843;i ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng th&amp;aacute;o g&#7905; ch&#7913; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7901; ai kh&amp;aacute;c. D&#297; nhi&amp;ecirc;n, Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&amp;agrave; B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng c&amp;oacute; tr&amp;aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m gi&amp;uacute;p &#273;&#7905; v&#7873; m&#7863;t ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch, nh&#432;ng b&#7843;n th&amp;acirc;n c&amp;aacute;c DN ph&#7843;i t&#7921; th&amp;acirc;n v&#7853;n &#273;&#7897;ng l&amp;agrave; ch&amp;iacute;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7891;ng t&amp;igrave;nh v&#7899;i quan &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng, nhi&#7873;u DN cho bi&#7871;t b&#7843;n th&amp;acirc;n h&#7885; c&#361;ng &#273;ang &amp;ldquo;g&#7891;ng m&amp;igrave;nh&amp;rdquo; &#273;&#7875; v&#432;&#7907;t kh&amp;oacute; trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n hi&#7879;n nay. B&#7857;ng ch&#7913;ng l&amp;agrave; nhi&#7873;u DN &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&#7843;i t&#7921; ti&#7871;t gi&amp;aacute;m s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng v&amp;agrave; t&#7921; t&amp;igrave;m c&amp;aacute;c gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p &#273;&#7889;i ph&amp;oacute; v&#7899;i t&amp;igrave;nh th&#7871;. &amp;Ocirc;ng Tr&#7847;n Tu&#7845;n D&#432;&#417;ng - T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t, DN &#273;&#7913;ng th&#7913; hai v&#7873; s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c cho bi&#7871;t, DN n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&#7843;i c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m 20% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t do kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nC&amp;ugrave;ng quan &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y, &amp;ocirc;ng Ho&amp;agrave;ng V&#259;n T&amp;ograve;ng - Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Cty Gang th&amp;eacute;p Th&amp;aacute;i Nguy&amp;ecirc;n c&#361;ng cho hay, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&#7901;i gian qua c&#7911;a &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; ch&#7881; b&#7857;ng 70-71%. DN bu&#7897;c ph&#7843;i gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh, t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m &#273;&#7871;n nay &#273;&amp;atilde; ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7899;i 150 t&#7881; &#273;&#7891;ng so v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh nh&#7919;ng vi&#7879;c t&#7921; th&amp;acirc;n v&#7853;n &#273;&#7897;ng c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh, c&amp;aacute;c DN c&#361;ng mong mu&#7889;n Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; c&#7847;n c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng bi&#7879;n ph&amp;aacute;p ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i th&amp;ocirc;ng l&#7879; qu&#7889;c t&#7871; &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m l&#432;&#7907;ng nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u, ch&#7889;ng gian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c v&amp;agrave; h&#7841;n ch&#7871; xu&#7845;t qu&#7863;ng sang n&#432;&#7899;c n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c chuy&amp;ecirc;n gia cho r&#7857;ng, ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p c&#7847;n t&amp;iacute;nh t&#7899;i vi&#7879;c l&#7853;p h&amp;agrave;ng r&amp;agrave;o k&#7929; thu&#7853;t ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i &#273;&#7863;c th&amp;ugrave; trong n&#432;&#7899;c, &#273;&#7875; c&#7841;nh tranh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c v&#7899;i th&amp;eacute;p nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u. &#272;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y &#7903; nhi&#7873;u n&#432;&#7899;c c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, tr&#432;&#7899;c nh&#7919;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n v&#7873; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; c&#361;ng nh&#432; s&#7921; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#7891; &#7841;t, ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p c&#7847;n t&amp;iacute;nh t&#7899;i gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p t&amp;aacute;i c&#417; c&#7845;u, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p mua b&amp;aacute;n, s&amp;aacute;p nh&#7853;p l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p t&#7889;t v&amp;igrave; ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;oacute; n&#259;ng l&#7921;c m&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7911; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh v&#7921;c d&#7853;y c&amp;aacute;c DN l&amp;agrave;m &#259;n k&amp;eacute;m hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;, ch&#7859;ng h&#7841;n nh&#432; th&#432;&#417;ng v&#7909; Th&amp;eacute;p &#272;&amp;igrave;nh V&#361; b&amp;aacute;n 70% n&#7907; cho nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&#7911;a Australia l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t v&amp;iacute; d&#7909;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n','03/11/2011','03/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/doanh-nghiep-thep--kho-khan-chong-chat.jpg',23,2,2007,'huyennt',1,'doanh-nghiep-thep-kho-khan-chong-chat','doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p, kh&oacute; kh&#259;n ch&#7891;ng ch&#7845;t, ph&aacute; s&#7843;n, VLXD',NULL,NULL,NULL,'doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p, kh&oacute; kh&#259;n ch&#7891;ng ch&#7845;t, ph&aacute; s&#7843;n, VLXD',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(87,'Doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p thu h&#7865;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t','C&aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p l&#7899;n ng&agrave;nh th&eacute;p &#273;ang n&#7895; l&#7921;c ti&#7871;t gi&#7843;m s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng, s&#7855;p x&#7871;p l&#7841;i s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t nh&#7857;m v&#432;&#7907;t qua giai &#273;o&#7841;n b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng kh&oacute; kh&#259;n hi&#7879;n nay.','&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c tin li&amp;ecirc;n quan:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Tin-tuc/?aid=53&quot;&gt;Ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p v&#7851;n l&#7841;c quan trong d&amp;agrave;i h&#7841;n&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Tin-tuc/?aid=54&quot;&gt;Th&amp;eacute;p: B&#7883; ki&#7879;n ch&#7889;ng ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Tin-tuc/?aid=51&quot;&gt; Doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p hoang mang v&amp;igrave; l&#7895;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Tin-tuc/?aid=56&quot;&gt;Doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p: kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n ch&#7891;ng ch&#7845;t&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;R&#7845;t th&#7859;ng th&#7855;n khi nh&amp;igrave;n nh&#7853;n v&#7873; c&amp;aacute;c t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng b&amp;ecirc;n ngo&amp;agrave;i &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng t&#7899;i s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, kinh doanh c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p, tr&#7843; l&#7901;i ph&#7887;ng v&#7845;n c&#7911;a ph&amp;oacute;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n B&amp;aacute;o &#272;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&#7847;u tu&#7847;n n&amp;agrave;y, &amp;ocirc;ng Tr&#7847;n Tu&#7845;n D&#432;&#417;ng, T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t (HPG) cho r&#7857;ng, kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p do gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng l&amp;agrave; kh&amp;oacute; tr&amp;aacute;nh kh&#7887;i. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n l&#7841;i &#273;ang ch&#7883;u nh&#7919;ng t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng x&#7845;u v&amp;agrave; d&#7921; &#273;o&amp;aacute;n ph&#7843;i v&amp;agrave;i n&#259;m n&#7919;a m&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ph&#7909;c h&#7891;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;365&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/doanh-nghiep-thep-thu-hep-san-xuat.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;ograve;n t&#7891;n &#273;&#7885;ng h&amp;agrave;ng tr&#259;m t&#7845;n th&amp;eacute;p.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTrong khi kinh t&#7871; trong n&#432;&#7899;c kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, th&amp;igrave; t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh th&#7871; gi&#7899;i c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng s&amp;aacute;ng s&#7911;a g&amp;igrave;. &amp;ldquo;Gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p th&#7871; gi&#7899;i gi&#7843;m, gi&amp;aacute; nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u c&#361;ng gi&#7843;m, s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng v&amp;agrave; nhu c&#7847;u &#273;&#7873;u gi&#7843;m v&amp;agrave; nguy c&#417; th&#7915;a th&amp;eacute;p l&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7853;t&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ocirc;ng D&#432;&#417;ng n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&amp;iacute;nh b&#7903;i v&#7853;y, d&amp;ugrave; l&amp;agrave; nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p l&#7899;n t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam, v&#7899;i doanh thu t&#7915; th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang chi&#7871;m kho&#7843;ng 50% doanh thu c&#7911;a to&amp;agrave;n T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n, nh&#432;ng &amp;ocirc;ng D&#432;&#417;ng th&#7915;a nh&#7853;n, &amp;ldquo;doanh nghi&#7879;p (DN) Vi&#7879;t Nam ph&#7843;i h&#7885;c c&amp;aacute;ch m&amp;agrave; th&#7871; gi&#7899;i &#273;ang l&amp;agrave;m&amp;rdquo;. Theo &#273;&amp;oacute;, HPG &#273;&amp;atilde; quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh ti&#7871;t gi&#7843;m s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, ch&#7881; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng 80% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m t&#7891;n kho, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i &#273;&#432;a ra c&amp;aacute;c gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m ti&amp;ecirc;u hao n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng, nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u nh&#7857;m ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh trong &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t, b&amp;aacute;n h&amp;agrave;ng gi&#7843;m s&amp;uacute;t hi&#7879;n nay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Gi&#7843;m s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p l&#7899;n kh&amp;aacute;c &amp;aacute;p d&#7909;ng. &amp;Ocirc;ng Nghi&amp;ecirc;m Xu&amp;acirc;n &#272;a, Ph&amp;oacute; t&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam &amp;ndash; C&amp;ocirc;ng ty c&#7893; ph&#7847;n (VNSteel) cho hay, trong 10 th&amp;aacute;ng qua, VNSteel s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kho&#7843;ng 1,9 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, gi&#7843;m 2% so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923; n&#259;m 2010, c&amp;ograve;n ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; gi&#7843;m g&#7847;n 4%. Trong h&#7879; th&#7889;ng c&#7911;a VNSteel, &#273;&amp;atilde; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng l&#7895; &#7903; m&#7897;t s&#7889; DN.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTi&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh, g&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;oacute; cho c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t. Th&#7915;a nh&#7853;n th&#7921;c tr&#7841;ng n&amp;agrave;y, &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n c&#7911;a Pomina Group, nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t &#7903; mi&#7873;n Nam cho hay, nhu c&#7847;u c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ph&amp;iacute;a Nam hi&#7879;n ch&#7881; b&#7857;ng 75% so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923; n&#259;m ngo&amp;aacute;i. &#272;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; DN ch&#7881; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng 20 ng&amp;agrave;y/th&amp;aacute;ng, do kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nB&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, vi&#7879;c h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho qu&amp;aacute; l&#7899;n, nguy c&#417; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n &#7903; nh&#7919;ng DN kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng t&amp;igrave;m ki&#7871;m v&#7889;n trong &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng c&#259;ng th&#7859;ng, vay v&#7889;n kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n hi&#7879;n nay c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7855;c t&#7899;i. &amp;ldquo;Ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; DN th&amp;eacute;p n&amp;agrave;o ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n, nh&#432;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u DN th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#7889;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t; n&#7871;u t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh x&#7845;u ti&#7871;p di&#7877;n, s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u DN ph&#7843;i &#273;&amp;oacute;ng c&#7917;a&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ocirc;ng Ph&#7841;m Ch&amp;iacute; C&#432;&#7901;ng, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam (VSA) c&#7843;nh b&amp;aacute;o.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7921;c t&#7871;, &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng r&#7845;t c&#7847;m ch&#7915;ng nh&#432; l&amp;ograve; cao c&#7911;a C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p V&#7841;n L&#7907;i hay Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y Ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p &#272;&amp;igrave;nh V&#361;, b&#7903;i thi&#7871;u nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7911; t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7875; mua qu&#7863;ng, ph&#7909;c v&#7909; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t ph&amp;ocirc;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Vi&#7879;c t&amp;igrave;m th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u cho c&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng d&#7877; d&amp;agrave;ng. Hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i, s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u sang m&#7897;t s&#7889; n&#432;&#7899;c, nh&#432; Indonesia, M&#7929;, Canada, nh&#432;ng &#273;&#7875; tr&#7909; v&#7919;ng t&#7841;i c&amp;aacute;c th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng d&#7877;. &amp;Ocirc;ng L&amp;ecirc; Minh H&#7843;i, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch H&#272;QT C&amp;ocirc;ng ty &#7888;ng th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t &#272;&#7913;c cho hay, t&#7841;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng M&#7929;, s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#7889;ng th&amp;eacute;p c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam ph&#7843;i c&#7841;nh tranh gay g&#7855;t v&#7899;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c nh&#432; &#7844;n &#272;&#7897;, Oman...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7841;i di&#7879;n C&amp;ocirc;ng ty TNHH Th&amp;eacute;p Posco Vi&#7879;t Nam cho bi&#7871;t, Posco Vi&#7879;t Nam c&amp;oacute; t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7871;n vi&#7879;c xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u th&amp;eacute;p sang c&amp;aacute;c th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng trong khu v&#7921;c, nh&#432;ng c&amp;aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#432;a ra nhi&#7873;u h&#7841;n ch&#7871;, nh&#432; h&amp;agrave;ng r&amp;agrave;o ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng, thu&#7871; nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u, thu&#7871; ch&#7889;ng b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7875; b&#7843;o v&#7879; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c. Ch&#7859;ng h&#7841;n, ngo&amp;agrave;i c&amp;aacute;c y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u v&#7873; ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7841;t theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh, Th&amp;aacute;i Lan, Indonesia v&amp;agrave; Malaysia c&amp;ograve;n &#273;&#432;a ra m&#7913;c thu&#7871; nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;aacute;n ngu&#7897;i l&#7847;n l&#432;&#7907;t l&amp;agrave; 5%, 10% v&amp;agrave; 20-50%.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Vi&#7879;t Nam c&#361;ng n&amp;ecirc;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&amp;aacute;c ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n k&#7929; thu&#7853;t &#273;&#7875; h&#7841;n ch&#7871; t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng &#273;&#7893; b&#7897; c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;eacute;p t&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c kh&amp;aacute;c, g&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n cho s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c trong &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n hi&#7879;n nay&amp;rdquo;, &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Posco Vi&#7879;t Nam ki&#7871;n ngh&#7883;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Li&amp;ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n vi&#7879;c th&amp;aacute;o g&#7905; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n cho ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p, &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n V&#7909; Ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch thu&#7871; (B&#7897; T&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh) cho r&#7857;ng, kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; t&#259;ng gi&#7843;m thu&#7871; li&amp;ecirc;n t&#7909;c, b&#7903;i nh&#432; v&#7853;y s&#7869; c&amp;agrave;ng l&amp;agrave;m r&#7889;i &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c DN. Tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7921;c t&#7871;, t&#259;ng thu&#7871; nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u th&amp;eacute;p t&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c ASEAN s&#7869; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u t&amp;aacute;c d&#7909;ng, b&#7903;i khung thu&#7871; n&amp;agrave;y theo cam k&#7871;t &#273;&amp;atilde; &#7903; m&#7913;c th&#7845;p. H&#417;n n&#7919;a, vi&#7879;c t&#259;ng thu&#7871; ph&#7843;i ch&#7881; ra r&amp;otilde; r&amp;agrave;ng l&amp;agrave; v&#7899;i m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng n&amp;agrave;o, t&#259;ng bao nhi&amp;ecirc;u, ch&#7913; kh&amp;ocirc;ng n&amp;ecirc;n n&amp;oacute;i chung chung. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, &#273;&#7875; h&#7895; tr&#7907; DN &#273;&#7889;i ph&amp;oacute; v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c v&#7909; ki&#7879;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i, V&#7909; Ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch thu&#7871; c&#361;ng khuy&#7871;n ngh&#7883; DN n&amp;ecirc;n h&#7907;p t&amp;aacute;c t&#7889;t v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c c&#417; quan h&#7919;u tr&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&#7875; xem x&amp;eacute;t c&amp;aacute;c y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u, ki&#7879;n ch&#7889;ng b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; c&amp;oacute; vi ph&#7841;m cam k&#7871;t c&#7911;a T&#7893; ch&#7913;c Th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i th&#7871; gi&#7899;i (WTO) hay kh&amp;ocirc;ng, thay v&amp;igrave; t&#7921; m&amp;igrave;nh ch&#7889;ng &#273;&#7905; v&amp;igrave; s&#7907; b&#7883; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng t&#7899;i b&amp;aacute;n h&amp;agrave;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','03/11/2011','03/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/doanh-nghiep-thep-thu-hep-san-xuat.jpg',23,2,2110,'huyennt',1,'doanh-nghiep-thep-thu-hep-san-xuat','doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p, VLXD, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, thu h&#7865;p',NULL,NULL,NULL,'doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p, VLXD, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, thu h&#7865;p',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(88,'S&#7841;ch 1 t&#7845;n n&#432;&#7899;c nhi&#7877;m ph&oacute;ng x&#7841; b&#7857;ng 1 gram v&#7853;t li&#7879;u m&#7899;i','M&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y c&aacute;c nh&agrave; khoa h&#7885;c t&#7841;i &#272;H C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; Queensland (&Uacute;c) cho bi&#7871;t &#273;&atilde; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u th&ocirc;ng minh &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i c&oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng h&#7845;p th&#7909; v&agrave; lo&#7841;i b&#7887; ch&#7845;t ph&oacute;ng x&#7841; trong n&#432;&#7899;c r&#7845;t hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; gi&uacute;p ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m l&#432;&#7907;ng n&#432;&#7899;c l&#7899;n.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y &#273;i&#7879;n h&#7841;t nh&amp;acirc;n th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng g&#7847;n ngu&#7891;n n&#432;&#7899;c nh&#7857;m m&#7909;c &#273;&amp;iacute;ch l&amp;agrave;m m&amp;aacute;t nhi&#7879;t th&#7843;i c&#7911;a nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y. &#272;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;oacute; ngh&#297;a l&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c s&#7869; b&#7883; nhi&#7877;m ph&amp;oacute;ng x&#7841; n&#7871;u x&#7843;y ra th&#7843;m ho&#7841; h&#7841;t nh&amp;acirc;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;283&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/pxa.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;GS Zhu Huai-Yong v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c s&#7907;i nano titanate c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; lo&#7841;i b&#7887; ch&#7845;t ph&amp;oacute;ng x&#7841; t&#7915; n&#432;&#7899;c b&#7883; &amp;ocirc; nhi&#7877;m&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7853;t li&#7879;u th&amp;ocirc;ng minh do GS Zhu Huai-Yong t&#7841;i &#272;H C&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; Queensland h&#7907;p t&amp;aacute;c v&#7899;i T&#7893; ch&#7913;c C&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; v&amp;agrave; Khoa h&#7885;c H&#7841;t nh&amp;acirc;n &amp;Uacute;c v&amp;agrave; &#272;H Pennsylvania (M&#7929;) ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;u t&#7841;o b&#7903;i c&amp;aacute;c s&#7907;i v&amp;agrave; &#7889;ng nano Titanate. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng gi&#7889;ng nh&#432; c&amp;aacute;c ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&amp;aacute;p l&amp;agrave;m s&#7841;ch hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u m&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng h&#7845;p th&#7909; c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7845;t ph&amp;oacute;ng x&#7841; ch&#7871;t ng&#432;&#7901;i trong ngu&#7891;n n&#432;&#7899;c &amp;ocirc; nhi&#7877;m. Ch&#7845;t ph&amp;oacute;ng x&#7841; sau &#273;&amp;oacute; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&#7917; l&amp;yacute; an to&amp;agrave;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng g&amp;acirc;y ra nguy c&#417; r&amp;ograve; r&#7881; cho d&amp;ugrave; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u c&amp;oacute; b&#7883; &#432;&#7899;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&#7911;a thi&#7871;t b&#7883; nh&#432; sau: khi n&#432;&#7899;c &amp;ocirc; nhi&#7877;m ch&#7843;y qua c&amp;aacute;c &#7889;ng v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c s&#7907;i nano, ion c&#7911;a c&#7911;a ph&amp;oacute;ng x&#7841; Cesium (Cs +) b&#7883; m&#7855;c k&#7865;t t&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y do s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i c&#7845;u tr&amp;uacute;c c&#7911;a v&#7853;t li&#7879;u. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, b&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;ch th&amp;ecirc;m c&amp;aacute;c tinh th&#7875; nano oxit b&#7841;c tr&amp;ecirc;n b&#7873; m&#7863;t, c&#7845;u tr&amp;uacute;c nano c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; gi&#7919; l&#7841;i c&amp;aacute;c ion i-&#7889;t ph&amp;oacute;ng x&#7841; (I-). Nh&#7919;ng ion n&amp;agrave;y sau &#273;&amp;oacute; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7875; &#273;i&#7873;u tr&#7883; b&#7879;nh ung th&#432; tuy&#7871;n gi&amp;aacute;p, hay d&amp;ugrave;ng l&amp;agrave;m c&amp;aacute;c thi&#7871;t b&#7883; th&#259;m d&amp;ograve; v&amp;agrave; ch&#7849;n &#273;o&amp;aacute;n y t&#7871;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;M&#7897;t gam s&#7907;i nano c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; l&amp;agrave;m s&#7841;ch &amp;iacute;t nh&#7845;t 1 t&#7845;n n&#432;&#7899;c nhi&#7877;m x&#7841;&amp;rdquo;, Gi&amp;aacute;o s&#432; Zhu cho bi&#7871;t. &amp;ldquo;V&#7853;t li&#7879;u s&#7869; gi&amp;uacute;p ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m m&#7897;t l&#432;&#7907;ng n&#432;&#7899;c l&#7899;n v&amp;agrave; ng&#259;n ch&#7863;n nguy c&#417; ph&amp;oacute;ng x&#7841; ng&#7845;m v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&#7845;t&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n nay &amp;Uacute;c l&amp;agrave; qu&#7889;c gia s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t Titania, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u th&amp;ocirc; d&amp;ugrave;ng &#273;&#7875; ch&#7871; t&#7841;o s&#7907;i v&amp;agrave; &#7889;ng nano Titanate, l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t th&#7871; gi&#7899;i.&lt;/p&gt;','03/11/2011','03/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/pxa.jpg',23,2,1705,'huyennt',1,'sach-1-tan-nuoc-nhiem-phong-xa-bang-1-gram-vat-lieu-moi','V&#7853;t li&#7879;u th&ocirc;ng minh, ch&#7845;t ph&oacute;ng x&#7841;, VLXD',NULL,NULL,NULL,'V&#7853;t li&#7879;u th&ocirc;ng minh, ch&#7845;t ph&oacute;ng x&#7841;, VLXD',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://khoahoc.baodatviet.vn',1,0,0,0),(89,'G&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&aacute;t: h&agrave;ng l&#7853;u ho&agrave;nh h&agrave;nh, h&agrave;ng t&#7891;n b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng','C&ugrave;ng ch&#7883;u kh&oacute; kh&#259;n v&#7899;i ng&agrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t VLXD trong th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i, g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&aacute;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;ang r&#417;i v&agrave;o t&igrave;nh c&#7843;nh &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m ch&#432;a t&#7915;ng c&oacute;.','&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;igrave; &#273;&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7879;, h&amp;agrave;ng b&amp;aacute;n &#7871; &#7849;m l&#7841;i th&amp;ecirc;m vi&#7879;c ph&#7843;i g&#7891;ng m&amp;igrave;nh c&#7841;nh tranh v&#7899;i h&amp;agrave;ng ngo&#7841;i, h&amp;agrave;ng nh&#7853;p l&#7853;u&amp;hellip; khi&#7871;n cho th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;agrave;ng th&amp;ecirc;m hiu h&#7855;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;337&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/vat-lieu-xay-dung.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;C&amp;aacute;c c&#417; s&#7903; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t &#273;&#7873;u g&#7863;p kh&amp;oacute;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Ch&#432;a khi n&amp;agrave;o kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n nh&#432; b&amp;acirc;y gi&#7901;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;ang l&amp;agrave; m&amp;ugrave;a x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, nh&#432;ng thay v&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; t&#7845;p n&#7853;p mua b&amp;aacute;n nh&#432; nh&#7919;ng n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c th&amp;igrave; t&#7841;i c&amp;aacute;c c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng, &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute; kinh doanh VLXD b&amp;acirc;y gi&#7901; &#273;&#7873;u ch&#7883;u chung m&#7897;t t&amp;igrave;nh c&#7843;nh ng&#432;&#7901;i mua th&#432;a th&#7899;t, &#273;&#417;n &#273;&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng &amp;iacute;t &#7887;i. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i kh&amp;aacute;ch mua h&amp;agrave;ng, h&#7885; th&#432;&#7901;ng ch&#7885;n nh&#7919;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u c&amp;oacute; ph&amp;acirc;n kh&amp;uacute;c gi&amp;aacute; trung b&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i kh&#7843; n&#259;ng chi tr&#7843;. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; th&#7871;, ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&amp;ecirc;u d&amp;ugrave;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng &#432;u ti&amp;ecirc;n h&#417;n v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&#7865;p, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng kh&amp;aacute; v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; trung b&amp;igrave;nh b&#7845;t k&#7875; h&amp;agrave;ng n&#7897;i hay h&amp;agrave;ng ngo&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Anh Tr&#7847;n Nguy&#7877;n Chi&#7871;n (Thanh Nh&amp;agrave;n - H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i) cho bi&#7871;t: T&amp;ocirc;i &#273;ang ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n c&#259;n h&#7897; m&#7899;i, n&amp;ecirc;n c&#361;ng qua c&amp;aacute;c c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng VLXD &#273;&#7875; tham kh&#7843;o gi&amp;aacute; c&#361;ng nh&#432; t&amp;igrave;m s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p. Th&#7921;c t&#7871; th&amp;igrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i mua c&#361;ng ch&#7859;ng th&#7875; bi&#7871;t c&#7909; th&#7875; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ki&#7875;m &#273;&#7883;nh th&#7871; n&amp;agrave;o, ch&#7881; quan s&amp;aacute;t b&#7857;ng m&#7855;t th&#432;&#7901;ng, h&#7887;i qua kinh nghi&#7879;m c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&amp;aacute;c &#273;&amp;atilde; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&#7897;ng th&amp;ecirc;m t&#432; v&#7845;n c&#7911;a ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng&amp;hellip; th&amp;igrave; quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh mua th&amp;ocirc;i. N&amp;ecirc;n cho d&amp;ugrave; h&amp;agrave;ng n&#7897;i, hay h&amp;agrave;ng ngo&#7841;i (&#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&#7843; h&amp;agrave;ng Trung Qu&#7889;c), ch&#7881; c&#7847;n gi&amp;aacute; trung b&amp;igrave;nh v&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7889;t th&amp;igrave; t&amp;ocirc;i ch&#7885;n th&amp;ocirc;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7913;c mua tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng s&#7909;t gi&#7843;m kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; th&#7875; hi&#7879;n qua th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng mua l&#7867; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n, m&amp;agrave; ngay c&#7843; &#273;&#417;n &#273;&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c Cty x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&#361;ng kh&amp;aacute; th&#432;a th&#7899;t. Nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7851;n l&amp;agrave; B&#272;S &amp;ldquo;&#273;&amp;oacute;ng b&#259;ng&amp;rdquo; n&amp;ecirc;n vi&#7879;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; mua v&#7853;t li&#7879;u ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n cho c&#259;n h&#7897; v&#7851;n h&#7841;n ch&#7871;. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n do &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng kinh t&#7871; trong n&#432;&#7899;c, th&amp;igrave; g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t Vi&#7879;t Nam l&#7841;i &#273;ang ph&#7843;i &amp;ldquo;m&#7879;t m&#7887;i&amp;rdquo; v&#7899;i s&#7921; c&#7841;nh tranh c&#7911;a h&amp;agrave;ng nh&#7853;p l&#7853;u, gian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo th&amp;ocirc;ng tin m&#7899;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y c&#7911;a Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i G&#7889;m s&#7913; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam (VIBCA) th&amp;igrave;: Hi&#7879;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t t&#7891;n kho t&#7841;i c&amp;aacute;c Cty trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#432;&#7899;c kho&#7843;ng 30 tri&#7879;u m2, t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng 2 ngh&amp;igrave;n t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng. So v&#7899;i s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; c&#7911;a n&#259;m 2010 l&amp;agrave; 330 tri&#7879;u m2 (b&#7857;ng 88% l&#432;&#7907;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; 79% n&#259;ng l&#7921;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t) th&amp;igrave; d&#7921; ki&#7871;n n&#259;m 2011, l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam ch&#7881; kho&#7843;ng 290 tri&#7879;u m2/n&#259;m (b&#7857;ng 70% n&#259;ng l&#7921;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t theo c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t). M&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n quan tr&#7885;ng d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng ng&amp;agrave;nh g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t l&amp;acirc;m v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c VIBCA nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7883;nh l&amp;agrave; do bu&amp;ocirc;n l&#7853;u v&amp;agrave; gian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c. C&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng gian l&#7853;n v&#7873; gi&amp;aacute;, thu&#7871; su&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7853;p trung &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch ceramic, &#273;&amp;aacute; x&#7867; granit (&#273;&amp;aacute; hoa c&#432;&#417;ng) v&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;aacute; x&#7867; marble (&#273;&amp;aacute; c&#7849;m th&#7841;ch) nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u (NK) c&amp;oacute; xu&#7845;t x&#7913; t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#259;m 2011, l&#432;&#7907;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t nh&#7853;p v&amp;agrave;o ng&amp;agrave;y c&amp;agrave;ng t&#259;ng, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; h&amp;agrave;ng l&#7853;u v&amp;agrave; gian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i di&#7877;n ra r&#7845;t ph&#7913;c t&#7841;p, tinh vi &#273;&amp;atilde; g&amp;acirc;y nhi&#7873;u kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n cho c&amp;aacute;c DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t Vi&#7879;t Nam. T&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;nggian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t di&#7877;n ra kh&amp;aacute; &#273;a d&#7841;ng nh&#432;: Gian l&#7853;n v&#7873; s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng khai b&amp;aacute;o khi NK; xu&#7845;t tr&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;oacute;a &#273;&#417;n mua h&amp;agrave;ng v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p h&#417;n nhi&#7873;u so v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; th&#7921;c&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&#272;&#7889;i m&#7863;t v&#7899;i h&amp;agrave;ng l&#7853;u, gian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo th&#7889;ng k&amp;ecirc; c&#7911;a VIBCA th&amp;igrave; n&#259;m 2010, l&#432;&#7907;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t NK l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i 95,5 tri&#7879;u USD, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; l&#432;&#7907;ng g&#7841;ch NK t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c l&amp;agrave; 76,119 tri&#7879;u USD. &amp;ldquo;&#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; con s&#7889; th&#7845;p h&#417;n r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u so v&#7899;i l&#432;&#7907;ng NK kh&amp;ocirc;ng ki&#7875;m so&amp;aacute;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c&amp;rdquo;- l&amp;agrave; nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch VIBCA - &amp;ocirc;ng &#272;inh Quang Huy. Hi&#7879;n nay, Trung Qu&#7889;c c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t kho&#7843;ng 6 t&#7927; m&amp;sup2;/n&#259;m g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t, chi&#7871;m 2/3 s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng to&amp;agrave;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i. C&#7841;nh tranh b&#7857;ng gi&amp;aacute; r&#7867;, m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; &#273;a d&#7841;ng, hi&#7879;n Trung Qu&#7889;c &#273;ang th&#7889;ng l&#297;nh th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t to&amp;agrave;n c&#7847;u v&amp;agrave; &amp;ldquo;l&#7845;n &amp;aacute;t&amp;rdquo; ngay c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng n&#432;&#7899;c c&amp;oacute; b&#7873; d&amp;agrave;y truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng v&amp;agrave; n&#259;ng l&#7921;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t l&#7899;n nh&#432; Italy, T&amp;acirc;y Ban Nha.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Huy ph&amp;acirc;n t&amp;iacute;ch: H&amp;igrave;nh th&#7913;c gian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i hi&#7879;n nay &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7893; ch&#7913;c d&#432;&#7899;i d&#7841;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i NK xu&#7845;t tr&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;oacute;a &#273;&#417;n mua h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p h&#417;n nhi&#7873;u so v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; th&#7921;c ph&#7843;i mua. Th&#7921;c ch&#7845;t c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; coi &#273;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; h&amp;oacute;a &#273;&#417;n c&#7911;a h&amp;agrave;ng b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute;. Do &#273;&amp;oacute;, m&#7913;c thu&#7871; NK &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&amp;aacute;nh gi&amp;aacute; tr&amp;ecirc;n m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p h&#417;n gi&amp;aacute; th&#7921;c d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t c&amp;oacute; xu&#7845;t x&#7913; t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o Vi&#7879;t Nam c&#7841;nh tranh kh&amp;ocirc;ng l&amp;agrave;nh m&#7841;nh v&#7899;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&amp;ugrave;ng lo&#7841;i s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c. Vi&#7879;c gian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;atilde; di&#7877;n ra nhi&#7873;u n&#259;m v&amp;agrave; ng&amp;agrave;y c&amp;agrave;ng nghi&amp;ecirc;m tr&#7885;ng l&amp;agrave;m &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7887; &#273;&#7871;n ng&amp;agrave;nh g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/gach-op-lat-ton-kho.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;0&quot; height=&quot;0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/gach-op-lat-ton-kho.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;G&#7841;ch &#7889;p &#273;ang l&amp;aacute;t t&#7891;n kho cao do th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m v&amp;agrave; n&#7841;n h&amp;agrave;ng l&#7853;u ho&amp;agrave;nh h&amp;agrave;nh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTr&#432;&#7899;c t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng n&amp;agrave;y, v&#7915;a qua, VIBCA c&amp;ugrave;ng c&amp;aacute;c DN &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7893; ch&#7913;c h&#7897;i ngh&#7883; v&#7899;i C&#7909;c &#272;i&#7873;u tra ch&#7889;ng bu&amp;ocirc;n l&#7853;u - T&#7893;ng c&#7909;c H&#7843;i quan &#273;&#7875; ph&#7843;n &amp;aacute;nh s&#7921; vi&#7879;c gian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i n&amp;agrave;y. Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i G&#7889;m s&#7913; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&#361;ng &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; T&#7893;ng c&#7909;c H&#7843;i quan ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;o c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; tr&#7921;c thu&#7897;c ki&#7875;m so&amp;aacute;t ch&#7863;t ch&#7869; vi&#7879;c NK m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t qua c&#7917;a kh&#7849;u ch&amp;iacute;nh; t&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng ki&#7875;m so&amp;aacute;t ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng bu&amp;ocirc;n l&#7853;u qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng m&amp;ograve;n, l&#7889;i m&#7903; bi&amp;ecirc;n gi&#7899;i &#273;&#7875; h&#7841;n ch&#7871; l&#432;&#7907;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t v&amp;agrave;o n&#7897;i &#273;&#7883;a Vi&#7879;t Nam. &#272;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; T&#7893;ng c&#7909;c H&#7843;i quan v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c c&#417; quan h&#7919;u quan th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n nghi&amp;ecirc;m t&amp;uacute;c, ch&#7863;t ch&#7869; Th&amp;ocirc;ng t&#432; 14/2010/TT-BXD Quy &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7873; qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m, h&amp;agrave;ng h&amp;oacute;a VLXD g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t nh&#7857;m &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng h&amp;oacute;a v&amp;igrave; quy&#7873;n l&#7907;i c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&amp;ecirc;u d&amp;ugrave;ng v&amp;agrave; ki&#7875;m so&amp;aacute;t s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng NK.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; c&#7913;u ng&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t Vi&#7879;t Nam ra kh&#7887;i kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n trong th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i, VIBCA g&#7917;i B&#7897; T&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh v&#7873; vi&#7879;c &#273;&#432;a m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t v&amp;agrave;o danh m&#7909;c r&#7911;i ro, tr&amp;ecirc;n c&#417; s&#7903; &#273;&amp;oacute; &amp;aacute;p gi&amp;aacute; t&amp;iacute;nh thu&#7871; tr&amp;ecirc;n m&amp;eacute;t vu&amp;ocirc;ng theo t&#7915;ng lo&#7841;i k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c, ch&#7913; kh&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;iacute;nh thu&#7871; theo h&amp;oacute;a &#273;&#417;n mua h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c do DN nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u xu&#7845;t tr&amp;igrave;nh th&amp;ocirc;ng quan. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, &#273;&#7875; th&amp;uacute;c &#273;&#7849;y ng&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t VLXD trong n&#432;&#7899;c ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n, l&#7845;y l&#7841;i th&#7883; ph&#7847;n, c&#7847;n c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7875; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n l&amp;agrave;nh m&#7841;nh th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng B&#272;S c&amp;ugrave;ng s&#7921; n&#7895; l&#7921;c m&#7841;nh h&#417;n c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c DN trong vi&#7879;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; m&amp;aacute;y m&amp;oacute;c, thi&#7871;t b&#7883; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, n&amp;acirc;ng cao ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng, gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','04/11/2011','07/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/vat-lieu-xay-dung.jpg',23,2,2675,'huyennt',1,'gach-op-lat-hang-lau-hoanh-hanh-hang-ton-bat-dong','g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&aacute;t, VLXD, h&agrave;ng l&#7853;u, h&agrave;ng t&#7891;n b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng',NULL,NULL,NULL,'g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&aacute;t, VLXD, h&agrave;ng l&#7853;u, h&agrave;ng t&#7891;n b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'http://dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(90,'C&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c ti&ecirc;u th&#7909; 39,1 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n xi m&#259;ng','M&#7863;c d&ugrave; v&#7851;n c&ograve;n nhi&#7873;u kh&oacute; kh&#259;n trong s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t kinh doanh do l&#7841;m ph&aacute;t cao, c&aacute;c ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng si&#7871;t ch&#7863;t ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng cho vay t&iacute;n d&#7909;ng, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng B&#272;S tr&#7847;m l&#7855;ng... nh&#432;ng v&#7899;i s&#7921; n&#7895; l&#7921;c c&#7889; g&#7855;ng c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh, c&aacute;c DN thu&#7897;c B&#7897; v&#7851;n c&oacute; m&#7913;c t&#259;ng so v&#7899;i v&#7899;i c&u