b&#7857;ng 72,3% so k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch n&#259;m. Th&amp;aacute;ng 10 s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng xi m&#259;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7841;t 3,54 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, gi&#7843;m kh&amp;aacute; m&#7841;nh so v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c th&amp;aacute;ng qu&amp;yacute; II do &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7911;a th&#7901;i ti&#7871;t m&#432;a nhi&#7873;u v&amp;agrave; s&#7921; tr&#7847;m l&#7855;ng c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng B&#272;S, 10 th&amp;aacute;ng n&#259;m &#432;&#7899;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&#7841;t 39,1 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, b&#7857;ng 71% k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch n&#259;m.&lt;/p&gt;','08/11/2011','08/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/luong-xi-mang.jpg',23,2,1758,'huyennt',1,'ca-nuoc-tieu-thu-39-1-trieu-tan-xi-mang','VLXD, xi m&#259;ng, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t',NULL,NULL,NULL,'VLXD, xi m&#259;ng, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://www.xaydungvietnam.vn',1,0,0,0),(91,'Th&eacute;p &#7871;, DN ki&#7879;n nhau b&aacute;n ph&aacute; gi&aacute;','C&aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p (DN) s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&eacute;p &#273;ang v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng ch&#7853;t v&#7853;t. N&#7871;u t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng n&agrave;y ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c duy tr&igrave; th&ecirc;m v&agrave;i ba th&aacute;ng n&#7919;a, ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n m&#7885;i kho&#7843;n l&atilde;i c&aacute;c DN c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m s&#7869; b&#7857;ng kh&ocirc;ng, th&#7853;m ch&iacute; l&agrave; &acirc;m.','&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c tin li&amp;ecirc;n quan:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Tin-tuc/?aid=53&quot;&gt; Ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p v&#7851;n l&#7841;c quan trong d&amp;agrave;i h&#7841;n&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Tin-tuc/?aid=54&quot;&gt; Th&amp;eacute;p: B&#7883; ki&#7879;n ch&#7889;ng ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Tin-tuc/?aid=51&quot;&gt; Doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p hoang mang v&amp;igrave; l&#7895;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Tin-tuc/?aid=56&quot;&gt;Doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p: kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n ch&#7891;ng ch&#7845;t&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Tin-tuc/?aid=57&quot;&gt;Doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p thu h&#7865;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;580&quot; height=&quot;439&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/doanh-nghiep-thep-kho-khan.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Qu&amp;aacute; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; DN th&amp;eacute;p ph&#7843;i d&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&#272;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; t&amp;acirc;m tr&#7841;ng chung c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n c&amp;aacute;c DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c &amp;quot;than&amp;quot; v&#7899;i B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng t&#7841;i cu&#7897;c h&#7885;p chi&#7873;u 27.10, v&amp;agrave; mong b&#7897; ch&#7911; qu&#7843;n c&amp;oacute; h&#432;&#7899;ng th&amp;aacute;o g&#7905; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kh&amp;oacute; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909;, DN b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &amp;ocirc;ng Ph&#7841;m Ch&amp;iacute; C&#432;&#7901;ng, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam (VSA), l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p 2 th&amp;aacute;ng g&#7847;n &#273;&amp;acirc;y s&#7909;t gi&#7843;m nghi&amp;ecirc;m tr&#7885;ng. Ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p trong th&amp;aacute;ng 9 v&#7915;a qua ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;t 381.000 t&#7845;n, gi&#7843;m h&#417;n 100.000 t&#7845;n so v&#7899;i th&amp;aacute;ng 8. D&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p trong th&amp;aacute;ng 10 n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7869; c&amp;ograve;n th&#7845;p h&#417;n c&#7843; th&amp;aacute;ng 9, &#432;&#7899;c kho&#7843;ng 300.000 t&#7845;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ngay DN ch&#7911; l&#7921;c nh&#432; T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam, 10 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&#7841;t 1,79 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, gi&#7843;m 6,7% so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923; n&#259;m 2010. Hay nh&#432; T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n Th&amp;eacute;p H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t &amp;ndash; &#273;&#7913;ng th&#7913; 2 v&#7873; c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t nh&#432;ng hai th&amp;aacute;ng nay c&#361;ng ch&#7881; ch&#7841;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c 80% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t, &#273;&#7875; tr&amp;aacute;nh d&#432; th&#7915;a cung, l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7883; thu h&#7865;p, l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho l&#7899;n, trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, d&amp;ugrave; ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;a ra ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh &#432;u &#273;&amp;atilde;i l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t vay cho DN t&#7915; 17-19%/n&#259;m, nh&#432;ng th&#7921;c t&#7871; DN ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p v&#7851;n ch&#432;a th&#7875; ti&#7871;p c&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ngu&#7891;n v&#7889;n n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#361;ng theo Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam: &lt;em&gt;&amp;quot;Hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; DN th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n, nh&#432;ng DN th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang thua l&#7895; n&#7863;ng l&#7855;m r&#7891;i, n&#7871;u 2 th&amp;aacute;ng cu&#7889;i n&#259;m v&#7851;n ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c kinh doanh &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7883; thu h&#7865;p th&amp;igrave; ph&#7847;n l&amp;atilde;i c&#7911;a 10 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m coi nh&#432; &#273;i tong&lt;/em&gt;&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;n t&#432;&#7907;ng l&#7863;p l&#7841;i 2-3 n&#259;m nay. V&amp;agrave;i th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m l&amp;atilde;i l&#7899;n, cu&#7889;i n&#259;m &amp;acirc;m, l&#7895; t&#7899;i c&#7843; n&#259;m sau. Th&#7921;c t&#7871; doanh nghi&#7879;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng, &#273;&amp;atilde; d&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t. &#272;&#417;n c&#7917;, C&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;eacute;p V&#7841;n L&#7907;i trong cu&#7897;c h&#7885;p &#272;&#7841;i h&#7897;i c&#7893; &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng g&#7847;n &#273;&amp;acirc;y &#273;&amp;atilde; tuy&amp;ecirc;n b&#7889; ng&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Quan ng&#7841;i h&#417;n, &amp;ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng th&amp;ocirc;ng tin, &#273;ang c&amp;oacute; hi&#7879;n t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7841;nh tranh kh&amp;ocirc;ng l&amp;agrave;nh m&#7841;nh gi&#7919;a c&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p v&#7899;i nhau. Nhi&#7873;u DN b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; ngay t&#7841;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n nhi&#7873;u DN &#273;ang ch&amp;agrave;o gi&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p h&#417;n gi&amp;aacute; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7915; 200.000 -300.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; v&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;m l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;em&gt;Khi ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; trong n&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave; c&#7843; xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, c&amp;aacute;c DN trong n&#432;&#7899;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; b&amp;agrave;n b&#7841;c chia s&#7867; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n chung, chia s&#7867; th&#7883; ph&#7847;n m&amp;agrave; l&#7841;i ch&amp;agrave;o gi&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p h&#417;n &#273;&#7889;i t&amp;aacute;c nh&#7857;m gi&amp;agrave;nh b&#7841;n h&amp;agrave;ng n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; hi&#7879;n t&#432;&#7907;ng DN ki&#7879;n c&amp;aacute;o nhau trong n&#7897;i b&#7897; Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;&lt;/em&gt;i&amp;quot;- &amp;ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng b&amp;igrave;nh lu&#7853;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7921;c t&#7871;, trong n&#7897;i b&#7897; Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng ki&#7879;n c&amp;aacute;o cho l&amp;agrave; b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; gi&#7919;a T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam v&amp;agrave; Posco Vi&#7879;t Nam.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ph&#7843;i t&#7921; c&#7913;u m&amp;igrave;nh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng, ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng, t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng c&#7911;a Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n s&#7869; c&amp;ograve;n k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i, v&#7899;i &#273;&amp;agrave; n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; c&amp;ograve;n k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i sang n&#259;m 2012.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh s&#7913;c mua s&#7909;t gi&#7843;m, ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; &#273;&#7913;ng ngo&amp;agrave;i l&#7873;. Suy tho&amp;aacute;i kinh t&#7871; th&#7871; gi&#7899;i &#273;ang tr&#7903; l&#7841;i khi&#7871;n nhu c&#7847;u th&amp;eacute;p tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i gi&#7843;m, k&amp;eacute;o gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p gi&#7843;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nguy c&#417; nh&amp;igrave;n th&#7845;y l&amp;agrave; th&amp;eacute;p ngo&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; tr&amp;agrave;n v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&#7849;y c&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh th&#7871; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n h&#417;n do ph&#7843;i c&#7841;nh tranh v&#7899;i th&amp;eacute;p ngo&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7913; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng L&amp;ecirc; D&#432;&#417;ng Quang cho r&#7857;ng, t&#432;&#417;ng lai c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p l&amp;agrave; r&#7845;t s&amp;aacute;ng s&#7911;a, nhu c&#7847;u th&amp;eacute;p trong nh&#7919;ng n&#259;m t&#7899;i c&amp;ograve;n nhi&#7873;u. V&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y, c&amp;aacute;c DN ph&#7843;i t&#7921; c&#7913;u m&amp;igrave;nh tr&#432;&#7899;c khi &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7913;u. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute; ph&#7843;i ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng, v&#7853;t t&#432;, nguy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, c&amp;aacute;c DN c&#7847;n h&#7907;p t&amp;aacute;c ch&#7863;t ch&#7869; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i ph&amp;oacute; v&#7899;i v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; ch&#7889;ng b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute;,&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;','08/11/2011','08/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/doanh-nghiep-thep-kho-khan.jpg',23,2,1964,'huyennt',1,'thep-e-dn-kien-nhau-ban-pha-gia','doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p, kh&oacute; kh&#259;n, b&aacute;n ph&aacute; gi&aacute;',NULL,NULL,NULL,'doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p, kh&oacute; kh&#259;n, b&aacute;n ph&aacute; gi&aacute;',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'http://dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(92,'Ng&agrave;nh nh&#7921;a x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng: &ldquo;V&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute;&rdquo; b&#7903;i &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng v&agrave; tr&#7919; nguy&ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u','V&#7889;n vay ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng c&oacute; t&aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#7871;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843; kinh doanh c&#7911;a 6 doanh nghi&#7879;p, tuy nhi&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng l&#7899;n ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; DAG.','&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;6 doanh nghi&#7879;p thu&#7897;c nh&amp;oacute;m nh&#7921;a x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng - bao b&amp;igrave; nh&#7921;a x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng g&#7891;m: CTCP Nh&#7921;a B&amp;igrave;nh Minh (MCK: BMP), CTCP Nh&#7921;a Thi&#7871;u Ni&amp;ecirc;n Ti&#7873;n Phong (MCK: NTP), CTCP T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n Nh&#7921;a &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;Aacute; (MCK: DAG), CTCP Nh&#7921;a &#272;&#7891;ng Nai (MCK: DNP), CTCP Nh&#7921;a &#272;&amp;agrave; N&#7861;ng (MCK: DPC), CTCP Nh&#7921;a R&#7841;ng &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng (MCK: RDP) &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; B&amp;aacute;o c&amp;aacute;o t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh 9 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2011.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong 6 doanh nghi&#7879;p, ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; 2 doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;oacute; l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n tr&#432;&#7899;c thu&#7871; gi&#7843;m so v&#7899;i 9 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2010 l&amp;agrave; DPC v&amp;agrave; DAG.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5/6 doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;oacute; bi&amp;ecirc;n l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n g&#7897;p gi&#7843;m&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;Sau 9 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2011 ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, b&amp;aacute;o c&amp;aacute;o k&#7871;t qu&#7843; kinh doanh c&#7911;a 6 doanh nghi&#7879;p ng&amp;agrave;nh nh&#7921;a x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng ni&amp;ecirc;m y&#7871;t tr&amp;ecirc;n 2 S&#7903; giao d&#7883;ch ch&#7913;ng kho&amp;aacute;n cho th&#7845;y l&#7907;i th&#7871; &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n thu&#7897;c v&#7873; doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;oacute; k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch d&#7921; tr&#7919; nguy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u t&#7889;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;5/6 doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;oacute; bi&amp;ecirc;n l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n g&#7897;p gi&#7843;m, ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; RDP. Theo gi&#7843;i tr&amp;igrave;nh c&#7911;a m&#7897;t s&#7889; doanh nghi&#7879;p trong ng&amp;agrave;nh, trong k&#7923; gi&amp;aacute; v&#7889;n h&amp;agrave;ng b&amp;aacute;n t&#259;ng cao do gi&amp;aacute; nguy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u t&#259;ng, chi ph&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7847;u v&amp;agrave;o nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u t&#259;ng do &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7911;a t&#7927; gi&amp;aacute;, c&#361;ng nh&#432; chi ph&amp;iacute; v&#7853;n chuy&#7875;n, &#273;i&#7879;n t&#259;ng, nh&amp;acirc;n c&amp;ocirc;ng t&#259;ng. &#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n ch&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;agrave;m cho bi&amp;ecirc;n l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n g&#7897;p c&#7911;a h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p gi&#7843;m ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; RDP.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;550&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/nganhnhua1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;Theo gi&#7843;i tr&amp;igrave;nh c&#7911;a RDP, trong qu&amp;yacute; II/2011 s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; bao b&amp;igrave;, m&amp;agrave;ng &#273;i m&#432;a t&#259;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;agrave;m cho doanh thu t&#259;ng; qu&amp;yacute; III/2011, s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; t&#259;ng so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923;, b&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute; C&amp;ocirc;ng ty c&amp;oacute; k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch d&#7921; tr&#7919; nguy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u t&#7889;t. &#272;&amp;acirc;y c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; xem l&amp;agrave; nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n ch&amp;iacute;nh gi&amp;uacute;p RDP c&#7843;i thi&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c bi&amp;ecirc;n l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n g&#7897;p c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&#272;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh b&amp;aacute;n h&amp;agrave;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;N&#432;&#7899;c l&amp;ecirc;n thuy&#7873;n l&amp;ecirc;n&amp;rdquo;, gi&amp;aacute; v&#7889;n h&amp;agrave;ng b&amp;aacute;n t&#259;ng v&#7851;n ch&#432;a ph&#7843;i l&amp;agrave; nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n ch&amp;iacute;nh t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#7871;n k&#7871;t qu&#7843; kinh doanh cu&#7889;i c&amp;ugrave;ng c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p ng&amp;agrave;nh nh&#7921;a. B&#7903;i tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7921;c t&#7871;, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p nh&#432; BMP, NTP bi&amp;ecirc;n l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n g&#7897;p gi&#7843;m nh&#7865;, l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n tr&#432;&#7899;c thu&#7871; v&#7851;n t&#259;ng d&amp;ugrave; cho c&amp;aacute;c chi ph&amp;iacute; b&amp;aacute;n h&amp;agrave;ng, chi ph&amp;iacute; qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; doanh nghi&#7879;p, chi ph&amp;iacute; l&amp;atilde;i vay t&#259;ng. &#272;i&#7875;n h&amp;igrave;nh DNP c&amp;oacute; bi&amp;ecirc;n l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n g&#7897;p gi&#7843;m h&#417;n 25% nh&#432;ng l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n tr&#432;&#7899;c thu&#7871; t&#259;ng 38,4% so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923; n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;550&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/nganhnhua2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;S&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; t&#259;ng so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923; n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c l&amp;agrave; m&#7845;u ch&#7889;t gi&amp;uacute;p c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p v&#432;&#7907;t qua r&amp;agrave;o c&#7843;n gi&amp;aacute; v&#7889;n cao. Doanh thu thu&#7847;n b&amp;aacute;n h&amp;agrave;ng v&amp;agrave; cung c&#7845;p d&#7883;ch v&#7909; 9 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; DPC gi&#7843;m 0,9%, c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i 5 doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;&#7873;u c&amp;oacute; m&#7913;c t&#259;ng t&#7915; 27% &#273;&#7871;n 62,1% so v&#7899;i 9 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2010.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;G&#7863;p kh&amp;oacute; v&#7899;i l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t cao?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong 6 doanh nghi&#7879;p, c&amp;oacute; 2 doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;oacute; l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n tr&#432;&#7899;c thu&#7871; gi&#7843;m so v&#7899;i 9 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2010 l&amp;agrave; DPC v&amp;agrave; DAG. &#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; c&#7843; 2 doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;oacute; chi ph&amp;iacute; l&amp;atilde;i vay 9 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m t&#259;ng so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923; n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c cao nh&#7845;t trong nh&amp;oacute;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;550&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/nganhnhua3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, x&amp;eacute;t v&#7873; t&#7927; tr&#7885;ng chi ph&amp;iacute; l&amp;atilde;i vay/doanh thu thu&#7847;n 9 th&amp;aacute;ng DAG cao nh&#7845;t nh&amp;oacute;m kho&#7843;ng 6%, DPC ch&#7881; 1,3% th&#7845;p h&#417;n DNP v&amp;agrave; RDP.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;550&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/nganhnhua4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;Theo DAG, l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t t&#259;ng cao n&#259;m 2011 n&amp;ecirc;n chi ph&amp;iacute; l&amp;atilde;i vay c&#7911;a DAG lu&amp;ocirc;n duy tr&amp;igrave; &#7903; m&#7913;c cao&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;550&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/nganhnhua5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;V&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t cao th&#7921;c s&#7921; c&amp;oacute; g&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;oacute; cho c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p, nh&#432;ng c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng trong qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh b&amp;aacute;n h&amp;agrave;ng, k&#7871;t qu&#7843; kinh doanh s&#7869; kh&#7843; quan h&#417;n. B&#7903;i th&#7921;c t&#7871; cho th&#7845;y, DPC do doanh thu thu&#7847;n gi&#7843;m 0,9%, bi&amp;ecirc;n l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n g&#7897;p gi&#7843;m 6% so v&#7899;i 9 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2010, d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n tr&#432;&#7899;c thu&#7871; gi&#7843;m 30,5%; c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i  3 doanh nghi&#7879;p kh&amp;aacute;c d&amp;ugrave; c&amp;oacute; l&amp;atilde;i vay t&#259;ng nh&#432;ng doanh thu thu&#7847;n t&#259;ng m&#7841;nh, l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n tr&#432;&#7899;c thu&#7871; t&#259;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;550&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/nganhnhua6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;Ngo&#7841;i tr&#7915; BMP kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; l&amp;atilde;i c&#417; b&#7843;n tr&amp;ecirc;n m&#7895;i c&#7893; phi&#7871;u (EPS) c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i trong 5 doanh nghi&#7879;p ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; 2 doanh nghi&#7879;p DNP v&amp;agrave; RDP c&amp;oacute; EPS 9 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2011 t&#259;ng so v&#7899;i 9 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2010. &#272;&amp;acirc;y c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; 2 doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;oacute; m&#7913;c t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n tr&#432;&#7899;c thu&#7871; cao nh&#7845;t nh&amp;oacute;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;M&#7897;t s&#7889; ch&#7881; ti&amp;ecirc;u kh&amp;aacute;c:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;550&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/nganhnhua7.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','09/11/2011','09/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/nganhnhua1.jpg',23,2,1868,'huyennt',1,'nganh-nhua-xay-dung-“vuot-kho”-boi-day-manh-ban-hang-va-tru-nguyen-vat-lieu','Nh&#7921;a, doanh thu, x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, VLXD, b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng, tr&#7919; nguy&ecirc;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Nh&#7921;a, doanh thu, x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, VLXD, b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng, tr&#7919; nguy&ecirc;n',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'http://cafef.vn',1,0,0,0),(93,'C&#7845;m tri&#7879;t &#273;&#7875; vi&#7879;c d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#7845;t s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t n&ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch ng&oacute;i &#273;&#7845;t s&eacute;t nung','B&#7897; X&acirc;y d&#7921;ng v&#7915;a c&oacute; v&#259;n b&#7843;n &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; UBND c&aacute;c T&#7881;nh,Th&agrave;nh ph&#7889; t&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c qu&#7843;n l&yacute; nh&agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c v&#7873; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t l&agrave; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; ch&#7863;t ch&#7869; c&aacute;c d&#7921; &aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch ng&oacute;i &#273;&#7845;t s&eacute;t nung.','\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; t&#7893;ng h&#7907;p, b&amp;aacute;o c&amp;aacute;o Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&amp;agrave;o cu&#7889;i n&#259;m 2011 v&#7873; t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 567/2010/Q&#272;- TTg c&#7911;a Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911;, Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 15/2000/Q&#272;-BXD ng&amp;agrave;y 24/7/2000 v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c Th&amp;ocirc;ng t&#432; c&#7911;a B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng; B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng v&#7915;a c&amp;oacute; v&#259;n b&#7843;n &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; UBND c&amp;aacute;c T&#7881;nh, Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; tr&#7921;c thu&#7897;c Trung &#432;&#417;ng t&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c v&#7873; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t l&amp;agrave; qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; ch&#7863;t ch&#7869; c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch ng&amp;oacute;i &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t nung. C&#7845;m tri&#7879;t &#273;&#7875; vi&#7879;c d&amp;ugrave;ng &#273;&#7845;t s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch ng&amp;oacute;i &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t nung; c&#7845;m nung g&#7841;ch b&#7857;ng l&amp;ograve; th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng; t&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng tri&#7875;n khai Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n VLXKN t&#7915;ng b&#432;&#7899;c thay th&#7871; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u nung. Ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;o ki&#7875;m tra, t&#7893;ng h&#7907;p, b&amp;aacute;o c&amp;aacute;o k&#7871;t qu&#7843; tri&#7875;n khai, th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n c&amp;aacute;c V&#259;n b&#7843;n n&amp;oacute;i tr&amp;ecirc;n theo c&amp;aacute;c n&#7897;i dung sau:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nT&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh l&#7853;p quy ho&#7841;ch v&amp;agrave; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n quy ho&#7841;ch ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2005-2010; 2011-2015 t&#7847;m nh&amp;igrave;n 2020. T&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u v&amp;agrave; quy ho&#7841;ch v&amp;ugrave;ng nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u &#273;&#7875; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch ng&amp;oacute;i &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t nung tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a b&amp;agrave;n. T&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch ng&amp;oacute;i nung v&amp;agrave; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a b&amp;agrave;n (s&#7889; li&#7879;u l&#7853;p theo bi&#7875;u m&#7851;u). K&#7871;t qu&#7843; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n l&#7897; tr&amp;igrave;nh xo&amp;aacute; b&#7887;, chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i c&amp;aacute;c l&amp;ograve; g&#7841;ch th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng sang l&amp;ograve; c&amp;oacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; ti&amp;ecirc;n ti&#7871;n. T&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh tri&#7875;n khai c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c v&#7873; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng VLXD, vi&#7879;c th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n h&#7907;p qui v&amp;agrave; c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; h&#7907;p qui, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c qui &#273;&#7883;nh t&#7841;i 04 Th&amp;ocirc;ng t&#432; n&amp;oacute;i tr&amp;ecirc;n. C&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n v&#432;&#7899;ng m&#7855;c v&amp;agrave; ki&#7871;n ngh&#7883; .&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTh&#7913; tr&#432;&#7903;ng Nguy&#7877;n Tr&#7847;n Nam cho bi&#7871;t: Theo s&#7889; li&#7879;u b&amp;aacute;o c&amp;aacute;o c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c t&#7881;nh, th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; v&amp;agrave; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; kh&#7843;o s&amp;aacute;t t&#7841;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng cho th&#7845;y, nhi&#7873;u &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7893; ch&#7913;c tri&#7875;n khai, th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n nghi&amp;ecirc;m t&amp;uacute;c c&amp;aacute;c Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh tr&amp;ecirc;n. &#272;&#7871;n th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m gi&#7919;a n&#259;m 2011, m&#7897;t s&#7889; &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; lo&#7841;i b&#7887; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c l&amp;ograve; th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; ph&#7845;n &#273;&#7845;u lo&#7841;i b&#7887; ho&amp;agrave;n to&amp;agrave;n c&amp;aacute;c l&amp;ograve; th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch ng&amp;oacute;i &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t nung, khuy&#7871;n kh&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung (VLXKN) nh&#432;: t&#7881;nh H&#7843;i D&#432;&#417;ng, t&#7881;nh &#272;&#7891;ng Nai, t&#7881;nh B&#7855;c Ninh&amp;hellip; v&amp;agrave; th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; H&#7891; Ch&amp;iacute; Minh. M&#7897;t s&#7889; t&#7881;nh &#273;&amp;atilde; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng l&#7897; tr&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; tri&#7875;n khai th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n, song nhi&#7873;u t&#7881;nh th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n c&amp;aacute;c Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh tr&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;ograve;n h&#7841;n ch&#7871;, c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7889; t&#7881;nh v&#7851;n t&#7891;n t&#7841;i l&amp;ograve; th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng ngay trong, ven th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889;, th&#7883; x&amp;atilde;, th&#7883; tr&#7845;n g&amp;acirc;y &amp;ocirc; nhi&#7877;m m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng, l&amp;agrave;m &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng t&#7899;i &#273;&#7901;i s&#7889;ng d&amp;acirc;n sinh, hu&#7927; ho&#7841;i c&amp;acirc;y tr&#7891;ng v&#7853;t nu&amp;ocirc;i, g&amp;acirc;y b&#7913;c x&amp;uacute;c trong x&amp;atilde; h&#7897;i nh&#432;: V&#297;nh Long, An Giang... &#7903; m&#7897;t s&#7889; t&#7881;nh, t&#7893;ng s&#7889; l&amp;ograve; th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch ng&amp;oacute;i c&amp;ograve;n r&#7845;t l&#7899;n nh&#432;: An Giang, B&#7855;c Giang, H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i, V&#297;nh Ph&amp;uacute;c, Ph&amp;uacute; Th&#7885;, &#272;&#7891;ng Th&amp;aacute;p, V&#297;nh Long... . &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t c&amp;oacute; t&#7881;nh tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;acirc;y &#273;&amp;atilde; xo&amp;aacute; b&#7887; l&amp;ograve; nung g&#7841;ch th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng m&#7897;t c&amp;aacute;ch tri&#7879;t &#273;&#7875;, song m&#7845;y n&#259;m g&#7847;n &#273;&amp;acirc;y l&#7841;i ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n nhi&#7873;u tr&#7903; l&#7841;i nh&#432; t&#7881;nh Th&amp;aacute;i B&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','13/11/2011','13/11/2011','',23,2,1977,'huyennt',1,'cam-triet-de-viec-dung-dat-san-xuat-nong-nghiep-san-xuat-gach-ngoi-dat-set-nung','g&#7841;ch ng&oacute;i, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, &#273;&#7845;t s&eacute;t nung, c&#7845;m tri&#7879;t, VLXD ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'g&#7841;ch ng&oacute;i, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, &#273;&#7845;t s&eacute;t nung, c&#7845;m tri&#7879;t, VLXD ',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'http://dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(94,'S&#7917; d&#7909;ng r&#7897;ng r&atilde;i g&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung','Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, th&#7921;c t&#7871; cho th&#7845;y, v&#7851;n c&ograve;n nhi&#7873;u r&agrave;o c&#7843;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i s&#7921; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&#7911;a ng&agrave;nh v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng m&#7899;i n&agrave;y.','&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNhi&#7873;u n&#259;m qua, c&amp;aacute;c ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch th&amp;uacute;c &#273;&#7849;y s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung (VLXKN), ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; g&#7841;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung (GKN) &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c ban h&amp;agrave;nh. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, th&#7921;c t&#7871; cho th&#7845;y, v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n nhi&#7873;u r&amp;agrave;o c&#7843;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i s&#7921; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng m&#7899;i n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng kh&amp;oacute; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m GKN c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u lo&#7841;i nh&#432;: g&#7841;ch xi-m&#259;ng - c&#7889;t li&#7879;u (g&#7841;ch Block), g&#7841;ch b&amp;ecirc;-t&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7885;t, g&#7841;ch b&amp;ecirc;-t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; ch&#432;ng &amp;aacute;p..., nh&#432;ng t&#7921;u trung &#273;&#7873;u c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7863;c t&amp;iacute;nh &#432;u vi&#7879;t: nh&#7865;, th&amp;acirc;n thi&#7879;n v&amp;agrave; ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m. Song, tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, t&#7927; l&#7879; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u n&amp;agrave;y hi&#7879;n c&amp;ograve;n r&#7845;t th&#7845;p. Nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; do th&amp;oacute;i quen s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7845;t nung, x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng theo l&#7889;i th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n. V&#7873; ch&#7911; quan, &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; do vi&#7879;c ch&#7853;m ban h&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh m&#7913;c, ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n, h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n thi c&amp;ocirc;ng, nghi&#7879;m thu c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh... d&#7851;n t&#7899;i kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n v&#7873; d&#7921; to&amp;aacute;n, thanh quy&#7871;t to&amp;aacute;n c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;oacute; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng VLXKN. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh kinh t&#7871; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m c&#361;ng t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng m&#7841;nh &#273;&#7871;n vi&#7879;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; d&amp;ograve;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m m&#7899;i n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;oacute; V&#7909; tr&#432;&#7903;ng V&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng (B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng) Ph&#7841;m V&#259;n B&#7855;c cho bi&#7871;t, n&#7871;u c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng GKN &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng theo &#273;&amp;uacute;ng ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; th&amp;igrave; t&#7927; tr&#7885;ng VLXKN s&#7869; &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kho&#7843;ng 18% t&#7893;ng kh&#7889;i l&#432;&#7907;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng. C&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c hi&#7879;n c&amp;oacute; g&#7847;n 30 doanh nghi&#7879;p (DN) l&#7853;p d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, nh&#432;ng m&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; b&#7843;y d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7899;i c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t m&#7897;t tri&#7879;u m3/n&#259;m, hai d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&amp;atilde; l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t thi&#7871;t b&#7883; xong nh&#432;ng ch&#432;a &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&#7917; v&amp;agrave; h&#417;n 12 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;ang trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n chu&#7849;n b&#7883; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;. Do &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng t&#7915; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m, m&#7897;t s&#7889; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ph&#7843;i ho&amp;atilde;n, gi&amp;atilde;n ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897;. Nhi&#7873;u DN &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&amp;oacute; &amp;yacute; &#273;&#7883;nh qu&#7843;ng b&amp;aacute; r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i d&amp;ograve;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m m&#7899;i n&amp;agrave;y nh&#432;ng &#273;&amp;agrave;nh &amp;quot;ng&#7853;m ng&amp;ugrave;i&amp;quot; g&amp;aacute;c l&#7841;i do kh&#7843; n&#259;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7843;i thi&#7879;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c C&amp;ocirc;ng ty c&#7893; ph&#7847;n b&amp;ecirc;-t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; ch&#432;ng &amp;aacute;p Viglacera Nguy&#7877;n &amp;ETH;&#7913;c H&#432;ng chia s&#7867;, c&amp;ocirc;ng ty m&#7899;i &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t t&#7915; cu&#7889;i n&#259;m 2010, nh&#432;ng hi&#7879;n nay l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7891;n kho &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i v&amp;agrave;i tr&#259;m ngh&amp;igrave;n m3, tr&#7883; gi&amp;aacute; t&amp;aacute;m t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng, trong khi, c&amp;ocirc;ng ty v&#7851;n &#273;ang ph&#7843;i g&amp;aacute;nh l&amp;atilde;i vay ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7915; 22,5% &#273;&#7871;n 23%/n&#259;m. H&#417;n n&#7919;a, d&amp;acirc;y chuy&#7873;n c&#7911;a nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y l&amp;agrave; s&#7921; pha tr&#7897;n gi&#7919;a c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; &amp;ETH;&#7913;c v&amp;agrave; thi&#7871;t b&#7883; nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c n&amp;ecirc;n khi &amp;aacute;p d&#7909;ng t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam c&#361;ng ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; b&#7897; quy chu&#7849;n t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng. Hi&#7879;n nay, b&#7897; ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;ang &amp;aacute;p d&#7909;ng l&amp;agrave; b&#7897; ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n c&#7911;a ch&amp;acirc;u &amp;Acirc;u, khi&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c kh&amp;oacute; &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, vi&#7879;c tuy&amp;ecirc;n truy&#7873;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch m&#7899;i n&amp;agrave;y ch&#432;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quan t&amp;acirc;m v&amp;agrave; ch&#7853;m ban h&amp;agrave;nh b&#7897; ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n &#273;&#7883;nh m&#7913;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i lo&#7841;i GKN, d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o d&#7921; to&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7875; quy&#7871;t to&amp;aacute;n c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh. Hi&#7879;n nay, c&amp;ocirc;ng ty m&#7899;i ch&#7881; b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&#7889;i l&#432;&#7907;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m khi&amp;ecirc;m t&#7889;n cho m&#7897;t c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7889;n ng&amp;acirc;n s&amp;aacute;ch Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c, c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i ch&#7911; y&#7871;u ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; trong c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;oacute; v&#7889;n n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&amp;agrave;i v&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;atilde; b&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7847;u m&#7903; r&#7897;ng sang khu v&#7921;c nh&amp;agrave; d&amp;acirc;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tuy&amp;ecirc;n truy&#7873;n, qu&#7843;ng b&amp;aacute; g&#7855;n v&#7899;i c&#417; ch&#7871; th&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; ph&#7911; nh&#7853;n nh&#7919;ng &#432;u th&#7871; c&#7911;a GKN so v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch nung th&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng. GKN c&amp;oacute; t&#7927; tr&#7885;ng g&#7847;n b&#7857;ng m&#7897;t n&#7917;a &#273;&#7871;n hai ph&#7847;n ba so v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7863;c &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t nung, c&amp;oacute; k&#7871;t c&#7845;u nhi&#7873;u l&#7895; kh&amp;iacute;, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;acirc;n b&#7889; &#273;&#7873;u v&#7899;i m&#7853;t &#273;&#7897; cao n&amp;ecirc;n t&amp;iacute;nh n&#259;ng c&amp;aacute;ch &amp;acirc;m t&#7889;t g&#7845;p hai l&#7847;n so v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch x&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i gi&#7919; &#7845;m cho ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; v&#7873; m&amp;ugrave;a &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng, m&amp;aacute;t v&#7873; m&amp;ugrave;a h&amp;egrave;, ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m &#273;i&#7879;n n&#259;ng (c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ti&#7871;t gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7871;n 40% chi ph&amp;iacute; &#273;i&#7879;n n&#259;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; c&#7911;a m&amp;aacute;y &#273;i&#7873;u h&amp;ograve;a), gi&#7843;i ph&amp;oacute;ng &#273;&#7897; &#7849;m v&amp;agrave; lo&#7841;i tr&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; li&amp;ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n n&#7845;m m&#7889;c. G&#7841;ch s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t theo nhi&#7873;u k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&amp;agrave; ch&amp;iacute;nh x&amp;aacute;c, gi&amp;uacute;p r&amp;uacute;t ng&#7855;n th&#7901;i gian thi c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n... &amp;ETH;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, v&#7899;i th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7847;n c&#7845;u t&#7841;o l&amp;agrave; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u tr&#417; v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7845;t v&amp;ocirc; c&#417;, c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i GKN c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7897; c&#7913;ng, &#273;&#7897; b&#7873;n, kh&#7843; n&#259;ng ch&#7889;ng ch&amp;aacute;y cao, &amp;iacute;t ti&amp;ecirc;u t&#7889;n nhi&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u v&amp;agrave; r&#7845;t th&amp;acirc;n thi&#7879;n v&#7899;i m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng. M&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; gi&amp;aacute; GKN c&amp;ograve;n cao h&#417;n so v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch nung, nh&#432;ng n&#7871;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ho&amp;agrave;n to&amp;agrave;n GKN th&amp;igrave; t&#7893;ng m&#7913;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; gi&#7843;m t&#7915; 7 &#273;&#7871;n 10% so v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch nung th&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng, trong khi ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; x&amp;acirc;y nhanh g&#7845;p hai &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m l&#7847;n. V&#7853;y l&amp;agrave;m th&#7871; n&amp;agrave;o &#273;&#7875; GKN c&amp;oacute; ch&#7895; &#273;&#7913;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7873; ph&#432;&#417;ng di&#7879;n qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c, c&#7847;n c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p quy&#7871;t li&#7879;t v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897;, tr&#432;&#7899;c m&#7855;t s&#7899;m ban h&amp;agrave;nh ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n li&amp;ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n thi&#7871;t k&#7871;, thi c&amp;ocirc;ng, nghi&#7879;m thu... c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh s&#7917; d&#7909;ng VLXKN. Song song v&#7899;i &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p t&amp;igrave;m l&#7897; tr&amp;igrave;nh th&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p x&amp;oacute;a b&#7887; ho&amp;agrave;n to&amp;agrave;n c&amp;aacute;c l&amp;ograve; g&#7841;ch th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; l&#7841;c h&#7853;u, &amp;ocirc; nhi&#7877;m m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng. Theo Ph&amp;oacute; V&#7909; tr&#432;&#7903;ng Ph&#7841;m V&#259;n B&#7855;c, do ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; b&#7897; quy chu&#7849;n n&amp;ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u DN &#273;&amp;atilde; m&#432;&#7907;n c&#7899; &#273;&#7875; kh&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng VLXKN v&amp;agrave;o x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng. H&#417;n n&#7919;a, quy &#273;&#7883;nh b&#7855;t bu&#7897;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng 30% GKN cho nh&amp;agrave; ch&amp;iacute;n t&#7847;ng m&#7899;i ch&#7881; &amp;aacute;p d&#7909;ng cho c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7889;n Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;n v&#7851;n ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; ch&#7871; t&amp;agrave;i x&#7917; ph&#7841;t. V&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y, gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; l&amp;agrave; n&amp;ecirc;n g&#7855;n vi&#7879;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng GKN v&#7899;i vi&#7879;c c&#7845;p ph&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, v&#7915;a &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n, m&amp;agrave; v&#7851;n &#273;&amp;uacute;ng ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, c&#7847;n t&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng tuy&amp;ecirc;n truy&#7873;n, qu&#7843;ng b&amp;aacute; r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i &#273;&#7875; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n, DN nh&#7853;n th&#7913;c &#273;&amp;uacute;ng &#273;&#7855;n v&#7873; VLXKN, nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; GKN, t&#7915; &#273;&amp;oacute; thay &#273;&#7893;i th&amp;oacute;i quen s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng. M&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; l&amp;agrave; d&amp;ograve;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m m&#7899;i, l&#7841;i &#273;&#432;a ra th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&amp;agrave;o th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, nh&#432;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;igrave; th&#7871; m&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t VLXKN &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;eacute;p coi nh&#7865; c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c truy&#7873;n th&amp;ocirc;ng. &amp;ETH;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m GKN &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tuy&amp;ecirc;n truy&#7873;n kh&amp;aacute; m&#7841;nh m&#7869;, nh&#432;ng khi th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n c&amp;oacute; d&#7845;u hi&#7879;u ch&#7919;ng l&#7841;i th&amp;igrave; th&a