;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/xi-mang-2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;0&quot; height=&quot;0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/xi-mang-2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nQu&amp;aacute; nhi&#7873;u x&amp;iacute; nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t xi m&#259;ng c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n g&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;oacute; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNgay c&#7843; doanh nghi&#7879;p v&#7889;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c coi l&amp;agrave; m&#7841;nh v&#7873; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u, v&#7899;i chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n b&amp;agrave;i b&#7843;n nh&#432; H&amp;agrave; Ti&amp;ecirc;n, Ho&amp;agrave;ng Th&#7841;ch, B&#7881;m S&#417;n c&#7911;a T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty C&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p Xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam (Vicem), hay m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&amp;ocirc;ng ty li&amp;ecirc;n doanh c&#361;ng r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o c&#7843;nh b&#7883; thu h&#7865;p th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng. T&amp;iacute;nh chung, sau 10 th&amp;aacute;ng ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, th&#7883; ph&#7847;n c&#7911;a Vicem b&#7883; gi&#7843;m g&#7847;n 3% v&amp;agrave; song h&amp;agrave;nh v&#7899;i s&#7921; suy gi&#7843;m &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; kho&#7843;n l&#7895; tr&amp;ecirc;n 220 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo Vicem, chi ph&amp;iacute; t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh t&#259;ng cao, nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n m&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, ph&#7843;i tr&#7843; n&#7907; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, chi ph&amp;iacute; v&#7853;t t&#432; &#273;&#7847;u v&amp;agrave;o nh&#432; gi&amp;aacute; x&#259;ng t&#259;ng 32 - 43%, &#273;i&#7879;n t&#259;ng 15,28%, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t l&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; than t&#259;ng 88%, c&#7897;ng v&#7899;i s&#7921; tr&#7847;m l&#7855;ng c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n &#273;&amp;atilde; k&amp;eacute;o t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh kinh doanh c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng &#273;i xu&#7889;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh kh&#7911;ng ho&#7843;ng, c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, doanh nghi&#7879;p l&amp;acirc;u n&#259;m trong ng&amp;agrave;nh, c&amp;oacute; s&#7861;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, s&#7861;n kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng c&amp;ograve;n ph&#7843;i ch&#7853;t v&#7853;t duy tr&amp;igrave; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng kinh doanh, th&amp;igrave; v&#7899;i doanh nghi&#7879;p ra &#273;&#7901;i sau, n&#7871;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; v&#432;&#7907;t tr&#7897;i v&#7873; c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879;, gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh v&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7897;c chi&amp;ecirc;u &#273;&#7875; chi&#7871;m l&#297;nh th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng&amp;hellip;, kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n l&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; nh&amp;igrave;n th&#7845;y tr&#432;&#7899;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;413&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/xi-mang.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng &#272;&#7891;ng B&amp;agrave;nh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Xi m&#259;ng &#272;&#7891;ng B&amp;agrave;nh (L&#7841;ng S&#417;n) gia nh&#7853;p th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng xi m&#259;ng cu&#7889;i n&#259;m 2010 sau 4 n&#259;m x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, nh&#432;ng sau ch&#432;a &#273;&#7847;y 1 n&#259;m ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, &#273;&amp;atilde; l&#7895; 141 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng v&amp;agrave; theo b&amp;aacute;o c&amp;aacute;o m&#7899;i nh&#7845;t, doanh nghi&#7879;p n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng tr&#7843; n&#7907;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#259;m 2006, D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n xi m&#259;ng &#272;&#7891;ng B&amp;agrave;nh, c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 910.000 t&#7845;n xi m&#259;ng/n&#259;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&#7903;i c&amp;ocirc;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, c&amp;oacute; t&#7893;ng v&#7889;n 1.298,2 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng, nh&#432;ng do ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; thi c&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7853;m 2 n&#259;m, m&#7913;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;igrave; th&#7871; &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7897;i l&amp;ecirc;n 1.505 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng. &#272;i&#7873;u &#273;&amp;aacute;ng n&amp;oacute;i l&amp;agrave;, ngay t&#7915; th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n n&amp;agrave;y, ng&amp;agrave;nh ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng c&#7843;nh b&amp;aacute;o v&#7873; d&#432; th&#7915;a ngu&#7891;n cung xi m&#259;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#7847;n n&amp;oacute;i th&amp;ecirc;m r&#7857;ng, D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Xi m&#259;ng &#272;&#7891;ng B&amp;agrave;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; b&#7903;i c&amp;aacute;c c&#7893; &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng s&amp;aacute;ng l&#7853;p l&amp;agrave; T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty C&#417; kh&amp;iacute; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng (Coma), T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty M&amp;aacute;y v&amp;agrave; Thi&#7871;t b&#7883; c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p (Mie), C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Xi m&#259;ng L&#7841;ng S&#417;n. Th&#7921;c t&#7871;, ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; ch&#7881; g&amp;oacute;p 52,485 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng, chi&#7871;m kho&#7843;ng 3,49% t&#7893;ng m&#7913;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, ph&#7847;n v&#7889;n thi&#7871;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c vay t&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c t&#7893; ch&#7913;c t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh g&#7891;m Ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng &#272;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave; Ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n Vi&#7879;t Nam (272,142 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng), Ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng N&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p v&amp;agrave; Ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n n&amp;ocirc;ng th&amp;ocirc;n Vi&#7879;t Nam (183,467 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng), Ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng ANZ (747,850 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Gi&#7843; thi&#7871;t, n&#7871;u th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng xi m&#259;ng ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n b&amp;igrave;nh th&#432;&#7901;ng, kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7883; t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng b&#7903;i kh&#7911;ng ho&#7843;ng v&amp;agrave; ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng, khi&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n l&#7899;n ho&#7863;c ph&#7843;i gi&amp;atilde;n ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897;, ho&#7863;c d&#7915;ng &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, th&amp;igrave; ch&#7855;c h&#7859;n c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t xi m&#259;ng m&#7899;i tham gia th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#432; Xi m&#259;ng &#272;&#7891;ng B&amp;agrave;nh s&#7869; d&#7877; th&#7903; h&#417;n &#273;&amp;ocirc;i ch&amp;uacute;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, Xi m&#259;ng &#272;&#7891;ng B&amp;agrave;nh l&#7841;i l&amp;agrave; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&#7899;i 80% t&#7915; ngu&#7891;n v&#7889;n vay, th&#7901;i gian &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i th&amp;ecirc;m 2 n&#259;m, chi ph&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; b&#7883; &#273;&#7897;i l&amp;ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u, c&#7897;ng th&amp;ecirc;m v&#7889;n vay l&#432;u &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#7875; duy tr&amp;igrave; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, n&amp;ecirc;n kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n c&amp;agrave;ng ch&#7891;ng ch&#7845;t. Theo t&amp;iacute;nh to&amp;aacute;n c&#7911;a B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, t&#7915; n&#259;m 2011 &#273;&#7871;n 2015, doanh nghi&#7879;p n&amp;agrave;y s&#7869; thi&#7871;u kho&#7843;ng 600 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;&#7875; tr&#7843; n&#7907; c&amp;aacute;c t&#7893; ch&#7913;c t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng v&amp;agrave; b&amp;ugrave; &#273;&#7855;p ngu&#7891;n ti&#7873;n m&#7845;t c&amp;acirc;n &#273;&#7889;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch H&#272;QT Vicem, &amp;ocirc;ng L&amp;ecirc; V&#259;n Chung cho r&#7857;ng, c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n xi m&#259;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; b&#7857;ng ngo&#7841;i t&#7879;. Sau th&#7901;i gian kh&#7911;ng ho&#7843;ng t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh, l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng t&#259;ng, c&#7897;ng th&amp;ecirc;m tr&#432;&#7907;t gi&amp;aacute;, c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c thu h&#7891;i v&#7889;n v&amp;agrave; tr&#7843; n&#7907; l&amp;agrave; g&amp;aacute;nh n&#7863;ng l&#7899;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i doanh nghi&#7879;p. Ri&amp;ecirc;ng t&#7841;i Vicem, v&#7899;i 7 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#259;m 2011, d&#7921; ki&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p s&#7869; ph&#7843;i tr&#7843; kho&#7843;n n&#7907; kho&#7843;ng 3.200 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng, t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng m&#7913;c v&#7889;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; m&#7899;i m&#7897;t nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng l&#7899;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#361;ng theo &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n Vicem, vi&#7879;c tuy&amp;ecirc;n b&#7889; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n &#273;ang l&amp;agrave; ph&#432;&#417;ng &amp;aacute;n c&#7847;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7871;n v&#7899;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n xi m&#259;ng qu&amp;aacute; y&#7871;u. M&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; vi&#7879;c ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7869; khi&#7871;n m&#7897;t b&#7897; ph&#7853;n lao &#273;&#7897;ng g&#7863;p kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, nh&#432;ng &#273;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7897;ng th&amp;aacute;i c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; t&amp;aacute;i c&#417; c&#7845;u ng&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p quan tr&#7885;ng n&amp;agrave;y. &#272;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, vi&#7879;c &#273;&amp;agrave;o th&#7843;i nh&#7919;ng nh&amp;acirc;n t&#7889; k&amp;eacute;m n&#259;ng l&#7921;c c&#7841;nh tranh c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t &#273;&#7875; l&amp;agrave;nh m&#7841;nh h&amp;oacute;a ng&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p xi m&#259;ng.&lt;/p&gt;','17/11/2011','17/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/xi-mang-2.jpg',23,2,1721,'huyennt',1,'doanh-nghiep-xi-mang-viet-nam-phuong-an-pha-san-duoc-tinh-den','xi m&#259;ng, nh&agrave; m&aacute;y, VLXD, d&#7921; &aacute;n, doanh nghi&#7879;p, ph&aacute; s&#7843;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'xi m&#259;ng, nh&agrave; m&aacute;y, VLXD, d&#7921; &aacute;n, doanh nghi&#7879;p, ph&aacute; s&#7843;n',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(98,'Ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n g&#7841;ch AAC: H&#432;&#7899;ng t&#7899;i &ldquo;v&#7853;t li&#7879;u xanh&rdquo;','H&#432;&#7903;ng &#7913;ng v&agrave; g&#7845;p r&uacute;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; nh&agrave; m&aacute;y, thi&#7871;t b&#7883; d&acirc;y chuy&#7873;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7853;t li&#7879;u kh&ocirc;ng nung Nh&#432;ng &#273;&#7871;n nay, sau g&#7847;n hai n&#259;m, c&aacute;c DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7851;n c&ograve;n loay hoay t&igrave;m &#273;&#7847;u ra cho s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m.','\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n ch&#432;a hi&#7875;u&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7875;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&amp;iacute;nh &#432;u &#273;i&#7875;m v&#432;&#7907;t tr&#7897;i c&#7911;a &amp;ldquo;s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m xanh&amp;rdquo; n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c DN h&#432;&#7903;ng &#7913;ng nhi&#7879;t t&amp;igrave;nh ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung (VLXKN), trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; k&#7875; &#273;&#7871;n s&#7921; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n m&#7841;nh m&#7869; c&#7911;a b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7865;. &#272;&#7871;n nay &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; 8 nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; ch&#432;ng &amp;aacute;p AAC &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; 1 nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y chu&#7849;n b&#7883; &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871; 1,5 tri&#7879;u m3/n&#259;m, 17 c&#417; s&#7903; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7885;t v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871; g&#7847;n 0,2 tri&#7879;u m3. T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7865; hi&#7879;n c&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; 1,7 tri&#7879;u m3/n&#259;m. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; 13 nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; ch&#432;ng &amp;aacute;p v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 2,3 tri&#7879;u m3 &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, s&#7869; &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#259;m 2012. Do &#273;&amp;oacute;, theo t&amp;iacute;nh to&amp;aacute;n c&#7911;a H&#7897;i VLXD th&amp;igrave; &#273;&#7871;n h&#7871;t n&#259;m 2012 s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 3,8 tri&#7879;u m3 b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute;, ch&#432;a k&#7875; 13 DN &#273;ang l&#7853;p d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ho&#7863;c c&amp;oacute; k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 2,25 tri&#7879;u m3.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7921; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n nhanh &#273;&#7871;n m&#7913;c ch&amp;oacute;ng m&#7863;t c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7865; &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7863;t ra m&#7897;t c&amp;acirc;u h&#7887;i l&#7899;n v&#7873; l&#7889;i &#273;i c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m khi m&amp;agrave; kh&#7855;p c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&#361;ng nh&#432; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n &amp;ldquo;l&#417; m&#417;&amp;rdquo; v&#7873; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m n&amp;agrave;y. Kh&amp;ocirc;n ngoan v&amp;agrave; nh&#7841;y b&amp;eacute;n, nhi&#7873;u DN &#273;&amp;atilde; t&amp;igrave;m v&amp;agrave; thuy&#7871;t ph&#7909;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7841;n h&amp;agrave;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh, tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; n&amp;agrave;o c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#432; th&#7871; n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m v&#7851;n b&#7883; &amp;ldquo;&#7871;&amp;rdquo; v&amp;agrave; t&#7891;n kho ho&#7863;c ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng h&#7871;t c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871;. Nhi&#7873;u c&#417; s&#7903; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng cao nh&#7845;t ch&#432;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c 50% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t, th&#7845;p nh&#7845;t ch&#7881; b&#7857;ng 20% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t. C&amp;oacute; c&#417; s&#7903; &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7891;n kho t&#7841;i b&amp;atilde;i l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n tr&amp;ecirc;n 10 ngh&amp;igrave;n m3 s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m (b&#7857;ng s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng 1 th&amp;aacute;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t). M&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y ph&#7843;i t&#7841;m d&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;iacute;t c&amp;aacute;c h&#7897;i ngh&#7883; m&#7903;, h&#7897;i &amp;yacute; k&amp;iacute;n gi&#7919;a c&amp;aacute;c DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7865; &#273;&amp;atilde; di&#7877;n ra &#273;&#7875; c&amp;ugrave;ng h&#7907;p l&#7921;c t&amp;igrave;m l&#7889;i &#273;i cho s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n &#272;&#7913;c H&#432;ng - Gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c Cty CP B&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; VIGLACERA (B&#7855;c Ninh) cho bi&#7871;t: Hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i, ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i &#273;ang &#273;&#7913;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u th&amp;aacute;ch th&#7913;c &#273;&#7875; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t cho s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m g&#7841;ch AAC. T&amp;iacute;nh ph&amp;aacute;p l&amp;yacute; cho s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m AAC ch&#432;a &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; khi&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;c DN ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i r&#7845;t kh&amp;oacute; b&amp;aacute;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m v&amp;agrave;o c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng. C&#361;ng c&amp;ugrave;ng &amp;yacute; ki&#7871;n, &amp;ocirc;ng Ki&#7873;u V&#259;n M&amp;aacute;t - T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c Cty CP S&amp;ocirc;ng &#272;&amp;agrave; Cao C&#432;&#7901;ng (H&#7843;i D&#432;&#417;ng) cho r&#7857;ng: V&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; m&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c DN ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i quan t&amp;acirc;m ch&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u ra cho s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m. T&amp;ocirc;i ngh&#297; &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7871;n l&amp;uacute;c c&#7847;n quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; cao t&#7847;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng t&#7915; 50 - 70% g&#7841;ch nh&#7865; t&#7915; n&#259;m 2012 ch&#7913; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i khuy&#7871;n kh&amp;iacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng 30% g&#7841;ch nh&#7865; nh&#432; hi&#7879;n nay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;T&amp;igrave;m c&amp;aacute;ch th&amp;aacute;o g&#7905;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i, kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7865; nh&#432; g&#7841;ch AAC m&amp;agrave; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i VLXD c&#361;ng &#273;ang &#7871; h&amp;agrave;ng do kinh t&#7871; n&#432;&#7899;c ta &#273;ang g&#7863;p kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, l&#7841;m ph&amp;aacute;t cao, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7883; c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng B&#272;S tr&#7847;m l&#7855;ng, l&amp;atilde;i vay t&#259;ng cao&amp;hellip; Trong v&#259;n b&#7843;n g&#7917;i Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; c&#361;ng nh&#432; B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, H&#7897;i VLXD c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#432;a ra nh&#7919;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n m&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch AAC &#273;ang g&#7863;p ph&#7843;i, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; nh&#7845;n m&#7841;nh &#273;&#7871;n vi&#7879;c: &#272;&#7871;n nay ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; b&#7845;t c&#7913; m&#7897;t Th&amp;ocirc;ng t&#432; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh 567/Q&#272;-TTg k&amp;egrave;m theo; c&amp;aacute;c v&#259;n b&#7843;n li&amp;ecirc;n quan nh&#432;: Ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n, &#273;&#7883;nh m&#7913;c v&#7853;t t&#432;, nh&amp;acirc;n c&amp;ocirc;ng, quy ph&#7841;m thi&#7871;t k&#7871;, thi c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; nghi&#7879;m thu c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh s&#7917; d&#7909;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7865; c&#361;ng ch&#432;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ban h&amp;agrave;nh, n&amp;ecirc;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; c&#417; s&#7903; &#273;&#7875; thi&#7871;t k&#7871;, x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, ki&#7875;m tra, gi&amp;aacute;m s&amp;aacute;t, nghi&#7879;m thu, thanh quy&#7871;t to&amp;aacute;n c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh&amp;hellip; &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7889;n Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c, g&#7847;n nh&#432; 100% s&#7889; c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh kh&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7865;. V&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, c&amp;aacute;c Cty t&#432; v&#7845;n thi&#7871;t k&#7871;, c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n c&amp;ograve;n nhi&#7873;u nghi ng&#7841;i khi chuy&#7875;n qua s&#7917; d&#7909;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m m&#7899;i v&amp;agrave; ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; c&#417; s&#7903; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;a c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7865; v&amp;agrave;o thi&#7871;t k&#7871; c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t th&#7921;c t&#7871; c&#361;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&amp;igrave;n nh&#7853;n nghi&amp;ecirc;m t&amp;uacute;c, &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; trong qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n, c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; g&#7841;ch AAC c&amp;ograve;n thi&#7871;u kinh nghi&#7879;m v&amp;agrave; ngu&#7891;n v&#7889;n c&amp;ograve;n h&#7841;n ch&#7871;, n&amp;ecirc;n nh&#7853;p c&amp;aacute;c d&amp;acirc;y chuy&#7873;n c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; v&#7899;i tr&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#7897; trung b&amp;igrave;nh ho&#7863;c th&#7845;p, thi&#7871;u &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897;, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng thi&#7871;t b&#7883; kh&amp;ocirc;ng t&#7889;t, c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c chuy&#7875;n giao c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879;, k&#7929; thu&#7853;t s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; ti&#7871;p thu c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; ch&#432;a t&#7889;t. &#272;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7887; &#273;&#7871;n ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m. H&#417;n n&#7919;a, g&#7841;ch AAC &#273;&#432;a ra th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; cao h&#417;n so v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch nung truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh t&#7887; ra kh&amp;ocirc;ng m&#7863;n m&amp;agrave; v&#7899;i &amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m xanh&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo; n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng L&amp;ecirc; V&#259;n T&#7899;i - V&#7909; tr&#432;&#7903;ng V&#7909; VLXD (B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng) cho bi&#7871;t: Nh&amp;igrave;n ra th&#7871; gi&#7899;i, th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung h&#7885; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch AAC. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, &#7903; Vi&#7879;t Nam, g&#7841;ch AAC l&amp;agrave; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u m&#7899;i v&#7899;i c&#7843; ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&amp;agrave; nh&amp;agrave; qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute;. Nh&#432;ng v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng &#432;u &#273;i&#7875;m v&#432;&#7907;t tr&#7897;i n&amp;ecirc;n ngo&amp;agrave;i b&#7897; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m TCVN 7959:2008 &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i block g&#7841;ch b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; ch&#432;ng &amp;aacute;p &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ban h&amp;agrave;nh n&#259;m 2008 th&amp;igrave; B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng th&#7845;y nh&#7845;t thi&#7871;t c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i ban h&amp;agrave;nh nh&#7919;ng b&#7897; t&amp;agrave;i li&#7879;u ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n thi c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; nghi&#7879;m thu; t&amp;agrave;i li&#7879;u &#273;&#7883;nh m&#7913;c kinh t&#7871; k&#7929; thu&#7853;t&amp;hellip; &#273;&#7875; h&#7895; tr&#7907; cho vi&#7879;c ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n g&#7841;ch AAC &#7903; Vi&#7879;t Nam. Do &#273;&amp;oacute;, B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; giao nhi&#7879;m v&#7909; cho Vi&#7879;n VLXD, Vi&#7879;n Kinh t&#7871; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, Vi&#7879;n Khoa h&#7885;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u, b&#7893; sung v&amp;agrave; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n c&amp;aacute;c ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n &#273;&amp;atilde; ban h&amp;agrave;nh cho &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7881; ti&amp;ecirc;u v&#7873; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m. C&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; t&amp;iacute;ch c&#7921;c tri&#7875;n khai ho&amp;agrave;n ch&#7881;nh, trong th&#7901;i gian t&#7899;i s&#7869; ban h&amp;agrave;nh. C&amp;aacute;c DN c&#361;ng v&amp;igrave; th&#7871; c&#7847;n kh&#7855;c ph&#7909;c nh&#7919;ng nh&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i&#7875;m c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&#7875; ti&#7871;p c&#7853;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, m&#7903; ra th&#7901;i &amp;ldquo;v&#7853;t li&#7879;u xanh&amp;rdquo; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n, c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&#7897;t c&amp;aacute;ch ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n, r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng th&#7845;y nh&#7845;t thi&#7871;t c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i ban h&amp;agrave;nh nh&#7919;ng b&#7897; t&amp;agrave;i li&#7879;u ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n thi c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; nghi&#7879;m thu; t&amp;agrave;i li&#7879;u &#273;&#7883;nh m&#7913;c kinh t&#7871; k&#7929; thu&#7853;t&amp;hellip; &#273;&#7875; h&#7895; tr&#7907; cho vi&#7879;c ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n g&#7841;ch AAC &#7903; Vi&#7879;t Nam&lt;/em&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;','18/11/2011','18/11/2011','',23,2,1802,'huyennt',1,'phat-trien-gach-aac-huong-toi-“vat-lieu-xanh”','g&#7841;ch, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, kh&ocirc;ng nung',NULL,NULL,NULL,'g&#7841;ch, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, kh&ocirc;ng nung',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://www.xaydungvietnam.vn',1,0,0,0),(99,'Th&eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam b&#7883; &#273;i&#7873;u tra ch&#7889;ng b&aacute;n ph&aacute; gi&aacute; t&#7841;i M&#7929;','C&#7909;c Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; c&#7841;nh tranh (B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng) cho bi&#7871;t B&#7897; Th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i M&#7929; (DOC) v&#7915;a ch&iacute;nh th&#7913;c &#273;i&#7873;u tra ch&#7889;ng b&aacute;n ph&aacute;