cute;c nh&agrave; khoa h&#7885;c M&#7929; v&#7915;a ch&#7871; t&#7841;o th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u nh&#7865; h&#417;n x&#7889;p t&#7899;i 100 l&#7847;n, si&ecirc;u r&#7895;ng v&agrave; c&oacute; c&#7845;u tr&uacute;c tr&#7853;t t&#7921;.','\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;313&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/vat-lieu-nhe-nhat-the-gioi.jpeg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7853;t li&#7879;u n&amp;agrave;y ch&#7913;a t&#7899;i 99,99% kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute;, n&amp;oacute; nh&#7865; &#273;&#7871;n m&#7913;c c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7881;nh b&amp;ocirc;ng hoa b&#7891; c&amp;acirc;u anh m&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; b&#7845;t k&#7923; s&#7921; dao &#273;&#7897;ng n&amp;agrave;o. &#7842;nh: Ph&amp;ograve;ng th&amp;iacute; nghi&#7879;m HRL.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n b&#7903;i nh&amp;oacute;m c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; khoa h&#7885;c &#273;&#7871;n t&#7915; ph&amp;ograve;ng th&amp;iacute; nghi&#7879;m LHR, Trung t&amp;acirc;m Composites, &#272;&#7841;i h&#7885;c California v&amp;agrave; Vi&#7879;n c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; California. C&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; khoa h&#7885;c &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7841;o ra v&#7853;t li&#7879;u m&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; c&#7845;u tr&amp;uacute;c h&amp;igrave;nh l&#432;&#7899;i bao g&#7891;m c&amp;aacute;c &#7889;ng niken r&#7895;ng si&amp;ecirc;u nh&#7887;, c&amp;oacute; th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7847;n ch&#7913;a t&#7899;i 99,99% l&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; v&amp;agrave; ch&#7881; 1% l&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;t r&#7855;n v&#7899;i k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905; nanomet, micron v&amp;agrave; mm.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;oacute;, lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u nh&#7865; nh&#7845;t tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; Aerogel, c&amp;ograve;n g&#7885;i l&amp;agrave; &amp;quot;kh&amp;oacute;i &#273;&amp;oacute;ng b&#259;ng&amp;quot;. Lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;oacute; t&#7927; tr&#7885;ng 1 mg m&#7895;i cm2, nh&#7865; h&#417;n c&#7843; kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; v&#7899;i nhi&#7879;t &#273;&#7897; trong ph&amp;ograve;ng. Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u m&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; khoa h&#7885;c t&#7841;o ra ch&#7881; n&#7863;ng 0,9 mg m&#7895;i cm2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;B&amp;iacute; quy&#7871;t l&amp;agrave; k&#7871;t n&#7889;i c&amp;aacute;c &#7889;ng r&#7895;ng v&#7899;i nhau t&#7841;o th&amp;agrave;nh m&#7897;t t&#7845;m l&#432;&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7897; d&amp;agrave;y b&#7857;ng m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n ngh&amp;igrave;n s&#7907;i t&amp;oacute;c c&#7911;a con ng&#432;&#7901;i&amp;quot;, Science Daily d&#7851;n l&#7901;i ti&#7871;n s&#297; Tobias Schaedler, ph&amp;ograve;ng th&amp;iacute; nghi&#7879;m LHR.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; khoa h&#7885;c cho bi&#7871;t, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u m&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng trong s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&amp;aacute;c &#273;i&#7879;n c&#7921;c pin gi&amp;uacute;p t&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;i&#7879;n n&#259;ng v&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;m chi ph&amp;iacute; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t cho b&#7897; pin th&#7871; h&#7879; m&#7899;i. N&amp;oacute; c&amp;ograve;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng cho qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh h&#7845;p thu &amp;acirc;m thanh, ch&#7889;ng rung v&amp;agrave; s&#7889;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;William Carter, m&#7897;t th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n trong nh&amp;oacute;m nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u, mi&amp;ecirc;u t&#7843; thi&#7871;t k&#7871; c&#7911;a lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u m&#7899;i nh&#432; m&#7897;t phi&amp;ecirc;n b&#7843;n thu nh&#7887; c&#7911;a th&amp;aacute;p Eiffel, t&#7913;c l&amp;agrave; n&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7897; b&#7873;n cao, nh&#432;ng b&amp;ecirc;n trong ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;Ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7841;o ra cu&#7897;c c&amp;aacute;ch m&#7841;ng trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u v&#7873; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u si&amp;ecirc;u nh&#7865;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ocirc;ng William Carter n&amp;oacute;i th&amp;ecirc;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;K&#7871;t qu&#7843; nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u &#273;&#259;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n t&#7841;p ch&amp;iacute; Science s&#7889; ra cu&#7889;i tu&#7847;n tr&#432;&#7899;c.&lt;/p&gt;','22/11/2011','22/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/vat-lieu-nhe-nhat-the-gioi.jpeg',23,2,1885,'huyennt',1,'vat-lieu-moi-nhe-hon-xop-100-lan','th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, g&#7841;ch, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u nh&#7865;, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u m&#7899;i, c&#7845;u tr&uacute;c',NULL,NULL,NULL,'th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, g&#7841;ch, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u nh&#7865;, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u m&#7899;i, c&#7845;u tr&uacute;c',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(101,'Th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng g&#7841;ch n&#7897;i &#273;ang k&ecirc;u c&#7913;u','V&#7915;a qua, theo c&ocirc;ng v&#259;n c&#7911;a Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i G&#7889;m s&#7913; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng VN (VIBCA), ng&agrave;nh g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&aacute;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;ang l&acirc;m v&agrave;o t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng kh&oacute; kh&#259;n do g&#7841;ch nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c (TQ) s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c &ldquo;chi&ecirc;u&rdquo;: gian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i, tr&#7889;n thu&#7871;, nh&#7853;p l&#7853;u...','\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&#7847;n l&#7899;n c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7873;u c&amp;oacute; ngu&#7891;n g&#7889;c xu&#7845;t x&#7913; t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;G&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t c&amp;oacute; xu&#7845;t x&#7913; t&#7915; TQ hi&#7879;n nay tr&amp;agrave;n ng&#7853;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; &#7903; c&amp;aacute;c th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; l&#7899;n nh&#432; Tp.HCM, H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i... m&amp;agrave; c&amp;ograve;n th&amp;acirc;m nh&#7853;p c&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c v&amp;ugrave;ng th&amp;ocirc;n qu&amp;ecirc;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gi&amp;aacute; n&amp;agrave;o c&#361;ng c&amp;oacute;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kh&#7843;os&amp;aacute;t tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i hi&#7879;n nay, c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t c&#7911;a TQ ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; g&#7841;ch granite, ceramic l&amp;aacute;t n&#7873;n lo&#7841;i l&#7899;n k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c 60x60cm, 80x80cm ho&#7863;c g&#7841;ch &#7889;p t&#432;&#7901;ng, nh&amp;agrave; v&#7879; sinh k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905; 30x45cm, 30x60cm. Ch&#7881; c&#7847;n nh&amp;igrave;n v&amp;agrave;o ch&#7911;ng lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch TQ &#273;ang b&amp;agrave;y b&amp;aacute;n, kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng s&#7869; ph&#7843;i... ch&amp;oacute;ng m&#7863;t v&amp;igrave; ki&#7875;u d&amp;aacute;ng v&amp;agrave; m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c c&#7911;a g&#7841;ch TQ qu&amp;aacute; phong ph&amp;uacute;, &#273;a d&#7841;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u ch&amp;iacute;nh ng&#7841;ch s&#7869; v&#432;&#7907;t 100 tri&#7879;u USD&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTheo VIBCA, n&#259;m 2009 t&#7893;ng kim ng&#7841;ch nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i kho&#7843;ng 70 tri&#7879;u USD, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; nh&#7853;p t&#7915; TQ &#273;&#7871;n 51 tri&#7879;u USD. N&#259;m 2010, kim ng&#7841;ch nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t v&amp;agrave;o th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng VN l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i 95,5 tri&#7879;u USD, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; 76 tri&#7879;u USD l&amp;agrave; nh&#7853;p t&#7915; TQ. N&#259;m 2011, VIBCA cho r&#7857;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u t&#7915; TQ c&amp;oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng v&#432;&#7907;t 100 tri&#7879;u USD.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo VIBCA, c&amp;aacute;c s&#7889; li&#7879;u n&amp;oacute;i tr&amp;ecirc;n ch&#432;a t&amp;iacute;nh nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ti&#7875;u ng&#7841;ch v&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;ng l&#7853;u bi&amp;ecirc;n gi&#7899;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTh&#7883;nh h&amp;agrave;nh nh&#7845;t hi&#7879;n nay l&amp;agrave; lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch granite v&amp;acirc;n loang s&amp;aacute;ng m&amp;agrave;u, v&amp;acirc;n m&amp;agrave;u &#273;&amp;aacute;, m&amp;agrave;u t&#7889;i, v&amp;acirc;n gi&#7843; c&#7893;, lo&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; hoa v&#259;n nh&amp;acirc;n t&#7841;o (nh&#432; v&amp;acirc;n gi&#7843; g&#7895;), v&amp;agrave;ng kem nh&#432; m&amp;agrave;u l&amp;ocirc;ng g&amp;agrave; con ho&#7863;c h&#417;i n&amp;acirc;u... Ch&#7883; Nguy&#7879;t, nh&amp;acirc;n vi&amp;ecirc;n b&amp;aacute;n h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7841;i c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng Kh&#432;&#417;ng Tu&#7845;n (&#273;&#432;&#7901;ng Ho&amp;agrave;ng Qu&#7889;c Vi&#7879;t, H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i), cho bi&#7871;t gi&amp;aacute; g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t TQ b&amp;igrave;nh th&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7915; 180.000-260.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/m2, lo&#7841;i &#273;&#7855;t h&#417;n kho&#7843;ng 400.000-500.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/m2... t&amp;ugrave;y lo&#7841;i v&amp;agrave; m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;So v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c, gi&amp;aacute; g&#7841;ch TQ r&#7867; h&#417;n 20.000-50.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/m2 (t&amp;ugrave;y lo&#7841;i, k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo m&#7897;t s&#7889; ng&#432;&#7901;i kinh doanh &#7903; H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i, m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7865;p, ch&#7911;ng lo&#7841;i phong ph&amp;uacute;, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; r&#7867; h&#417;n h&amp;agrave;ng trong n&#432;&#7899;c l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng l&amp;yacute; do ch&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7875; ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&amp;ecirc;u d&amp;ugrave;ng ch&#7885;n mua c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch xu&#7845;t x&#7913; t&#7915; TQ. &#272;&amp;acirc;y c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n khi&#7871;n nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p nh&#7853;p g&#7841;ch TQ v&amp;agrave;o VN nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n &#273;&#7875; kinh doanh, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;iacute;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u b&#7857;ng &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ti&#7875;u ng&#7841;ch &#7903; c&#7917;a kh&#7849;u M&amp;oacute;ng C&amp;aacute;i (Qu&#7843;ng Ninh)... tr&#7889;n thu&#7871; n&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;aacute; c&amp;agrave;ng r&#7867; h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;G&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t TQ t&#7841;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng Tp.HCM c&#361;ng phong ph&amp;uacute; kh&amp;ocirc;ng k&amp;eacute;m H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i. Ch&#7883; Nguy&#7879;t H&#7891;ng, ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng H&#7891;ng Anh (&#273;&#432;&#7901;ng T&amp;ocirc; Hi&#7871;n Th&amp;agrave;nh, Q.10), cho hay n&#7871;u c&amp;oacute; m&#432;&#7901;i ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&amp;aacute;ch v&amp;agrave;o ti&#7879;m h&#7887;i mua g&#7841;ch th&amp;igrave; c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7871;n t&amp;aacute;m ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#7885;n mua g&#7841;ch c&#7911;a TQ ch&#7881; v&amp;igrave; &amp;ldquo;gi&amp;aacute; m&#7873;m, l&#7841;i nhi&#7873;u ki&#7875;u, tha h&#7891; ch&#7885;n&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n Long, ph&#7909; tr&amp;aacute;ch v&#7853;t t&#432; C&amp;ocirc;ng ty TNHH x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Minh Khoa (Q.T&amp;acirc;n B&amp;igrave;nh), cho r&#7857;ng n&#7871;u so s&amp;aacute;nh tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p m&#7851;u g&#7841;ch granite lo&#7841;i 60x60cm c&#7911;a h&amp;atilde;ng T. v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch TQ th&amp;igrave; &amp;ldquo;m&amp;agrave;u h&amp;agrave;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7865;p, kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;oacute;ng c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng s&amp;aacute;ng, trong khi g&#7841;ch c&#7911;a TQ nh&amp;igrave;n b&#7855;t m&#7855;t v&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c m&amp;agrave;u r&#7845;t s&#7889;ng &#273;&#7897;ng&amp;rdquo;. Ch&#432;a k&#7875; m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; c&#7911;a g&#7841;ch TQ kh&amp;aacute; m&#7873;m khi c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n ch&#7881; dao &#273;&#7897;ng 160.000-170.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/m2, trong khi g&#7841;ch trong n&#432;&#7899;c t&#7915; tr&amp;ecirc;n 180.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/m2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng V., m&#7897;t nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, cho bi&#7871;t ngay c&#7843; khi ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch cho c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#7889;i l&#7899;n, nhi&#7873;u ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; khi &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u c&#361;ng &#273;&#7873;u ch&#7885;n h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7915; TQ ch&#7881; v&amp;igrave; y&#7871;u t&#7889; th&#7849;m m&#7929;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, gi&#7899;i &amp;ldquo;&#273;&amp;aacute;nh&amp;rdquo; g&#7841;ch TQ nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u cho bi&#7871;t khi h&amp;agrave;ng v&#7873; &#273;&#7871;n VN, bao b&amp;igrave; b&amp;ecirc;n ngo&amp;agrave;i c&#7911;a g&#7841;ch TQ &#273;&#7873;u b&#7883; l&#7897;t h&#7871;t. Thay v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&amp;oacute;, t&amp;ecirc;n c&#7911;a &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; nh&#7853;p h&amp;agrave;ng s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c vi&#7871;t t&#7855;t v&amp;agrave; d&amp;aacute;n tr&amp;ecirc;n g&amp;oacute;c c&#7911;a th&amp;ugrave;ng h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#7875; c&amp;aacute;c c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng l&#7845;y b&amp;aacute;n d&#7877; d&amp;agrave;ng ph&amp;acirc;n bi&#7879;t ngu&#7891;n cung.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u c&amp;ograve;n kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh n&#7871;u bi&#7871;t &amp;ldquo;t&#7853;n l&amp;ograve;&amp;rdquo; c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7847;u m&#7889;i nh&#7853;p g&#7841;ch TQ, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; l&#7845;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&amp;aacute; r&#7867; h&#417;n gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n l&#7867; ngo&amp;agrave;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng 20.000-30.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/m2 v&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i qua nhi&#7873;u kh&amp;acirc;u b&amp;aacute;n l&#7867; trung gian.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;550&quot; height=&quot;309&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/thi-truong-gach.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;G&#7841;ch Trung Qu&#7889;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&amp;agrave;y b&amp;aacute;n tr&amp;agrave;n ng&#7853;p tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng Ho&amp;agrave;ng Qu&#7889;c Vi&#7879;t, H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;G&#7841;ch n&#7897;i... ng&#7855;c ngo&#7843;i&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &amp;ocirc;ng &#272;inh Quang Huy - ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch VIBCA, ngo&amp;agrave;i vi&#7879;c &#273;&#7847;u ra th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng b&#7883; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng b&#7903;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n &#273;&amp;oacute;ng b&#259;ng, t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t TQ nh&#7853;p l&#7853;u, gian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i, tr&#7889;n thu&#7871; qua &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng bi&#7875;n, bi&amp;ecirc;n m&#7853;u l&amp;agrave; nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n &lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;g&amp;oacute;p ph&#7847;n l&amp;agrave;m th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; l&#7851;n c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng trong n&#432;&#7899;c l&amp;acirc;m v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh th&#7871; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n nh&#7845;t t&#7915; tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7871;n nay&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ngo&amp;agrave;i m&#7913;c t&#7891;n kho c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c VIBCA ghi nh&#7853;n x&#7845;p x&#7881; g&#7847;n 30 tri&#7879;u m2 (t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7871;n cu&#7889;i th&amp;aacute;ng 10/2011), &amp;ocirc;ng Huy cho bi&#7871;t l&#432;&#7907;ng g&#7841;ch granite l&#7851;n ceramic ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; trong n&#259;m 2011 &#432;&#7899;c ch&#7881; b&#7857;ng 70% l&#432;&#7907;ng g&#7841;ch n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;atilde; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#259;m 2010, t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng kho&#7843;ng 217 tri&#7879;u m2. N&#7871;u so v&#7899;i n&#259;ng l&#7921;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i trong c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n h&#417;n 400 tri&#7879;u m2/n&#259;m, con s&#7889; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; d&#7921; ki&#7871;n n&amp;oacute;i tr&amp;ecirc;n qu&#7843; l&amp;agrave; r&#7845;t th&#7845;p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a &amp;ocirc;ng Huy, gian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n nh&#7845;t hi&#7879;n nay xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n d&#432;&#7899;i h&amp;igrave;nh th&#7913;c doanh nghi&#7879;p nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u xu&#7845;t tr&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;oacute;a &#273;&#417;n mua h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7915; TQ v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p h&#417;n nhi&#7873;u so v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; tr&#7883; th&#7921;c t&#7871; t&#7915; 50-70%, k&amp;ecirc; khai s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u &amp;iacute;t h&#417;n s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng th&#7921;c t&#7871;, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng h&amp;oacute;a &#273;&#417;n quay v&amp;ograve;ng v&amp;agrave; h&#7907;p th&#7913;c h&amp;oacute;a vi&#7879;c th&amp;ocirc;ng quan n&#7845;p d&#432;&#7899;i h&amp;igrave;nh th&#7913;c &amp;ldquo;cho nhu c&#7847;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y, d&amp;ugrave; thu&#7871; su&#7845;t nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u g&#7841;ch t&#7915; TQ theo &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ch&amp;iacute;nh ng&#7841;ch &#273;ang &#7903; m&#7913;c 25% (ho&#7863;c h&#417;n, t&amp;ugrave;y m&amp;atilde; h&amp;agrave;ng) nh&#432;ng do khai b&amp;aacute;o qu&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p, thu&#7871; nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u m&amp;agrave; Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c thu v&#7873; ch&#7859;ng &#273;&amp;aacute;ng l&amp;agrave; bao tr&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;aacute; tr&#7883;... khai kh&#7889;ng c&#7911;a doanh nghi&#7879;p nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u. &amp;ldquo;Vi&#7879;c gian l&#7853;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i n&amp;agrave;y di&#7877;n ra li&amp;ecirc;n t&#7909;c nhi&#7873;u n&#259;m qua v&amp;agrave; ng&amp;agrave;y c&amp;agrave;ng nghi&amp;ecirc;m tr&#7885;ng. &#272;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;agrave;m ng&amp;agrave;nh g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c ng&amp;agrave;y c&amp;agrave;ng l&amp;acirc;m v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;ang &#273;&#7913;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c nguy c&#417; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n&amp;rdquo; - &amp;ocirc;ng Huy b&#7913;c x&amp;uacute;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong c&amp;ocirc;ng v&#259;n kh&#7849;n g&#7917;i Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; m&#7899;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y, VIBCA ki&#7871;n ngh&#7883; &#273;&#432;a m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u t&#7915; TQ v&amp;agrave;o danh m&#7909;c r&#7911;i ro v&amp;agrave; &amp;aacute;p gi&amp;aacute; thu&#7871; t&amp;iacute;nh tr&amp;ecirc;n m&amp;eacute;t vu&amp;ocirc;ng, theo t&#7915;ng lo&#7841;i k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c. C&#7909; th&#7875; &amp;aacute;p &#7903; m&#7913;c t&#7915; 5-12 USD/m2 &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch ceramic tr&amp;aacute;ng men m&amp;atilde; s&#7889; HS 6908, t&#7915; 5-13 USD/m2 &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch ceramic m&amp;agrave;i b&amp;oacute;ng ho&#7863;c gi&#7843; c&#7893; m&amp;atilde; s&#7889; HS 6907.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;ograve;n hi&#7879;n nay, vi&#7879;c t&amp;iacute;nh thu&#7871; ch&#7881; d&#7921;a theo h&amp;oacute;a &#273;&#417;n mua h&amp;agrave;ng c&#7911;a doanh nghi&#7879;p nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u n&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7847;n l&#7899;n doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;&#7873;u k&amp;ecirc; khai gi&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p h&#417;n r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u so v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; tr&#7883; th&#7921;c t&#7871; &#273;&#7875; &amp;ldquo;n&amp;eacute;&amp;rdquo; thu&#7871;.&lt;/p&gt;','22/11/2011','22/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/thi-truong-gach.jpg',23,2,2651,'huyennt',1,'thi-truong-gach-noi-dang-keu-cuu','g&#7841;ch, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i, k&ecirc;u c&#7913;u',NULL,NULL,NULL,'g&#7841;ch, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i, k&ecirc;u c&#7913;u',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://www.xaydungvietnam.vn',1,0,0,1),(102,'Ra m&#7855;t s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m B&ecirc; t&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; c&#7845;p c&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7897; 6','C&ocirc;ng ty CP B&ecirc; t&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; Viglacera v&#7915;a cho ra m&#7855;t d&ograve;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m m&#7899;i B&ecirc; t&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; c&#7845;p c&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7897; 6 d&agrave;nh cho c&aacute;c d&#7921; &aacute;n x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng cao c&#7845;p.','&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/san-pham-betong.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m B&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; c&#7845;p c&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7897; 6 &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&amp;aacute;c ti&amp;ecirc;u ch&amp;iacute; k&#7929; thu&#7853;t v&#432;&#7907;t tr&#7897;i so v&#7899;i B&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; th&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng hi&#7879;n &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i cho c&amp;aacute;c cho c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh cao t&#7847;ng. C&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7897; n&amp;eacute;n c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&#7841;t cao 6 ~ 7,5 MPA (b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7841;t: 4 ~ 5 MPA). Kh&#7889;i l&#432;&#7907;ng th&#7875; t&amp;iacute;ch nh&#7865;: 700 ~ 850kg/m3&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7897; n&amp;eacute;n cao cho ph&amp;eacute;p &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o t&amp;iacute;nh v&#7919;ng ch&#7855;c cho c&amp;aacute;c kh&#7889;i t&#432;&#7901;ng nh&amp;agrave; bi&#7879;t th&#7921; v&amp;agrave; li&#7873;n k&#7873;, &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o v&#7873; m&#7863;t an ninh cho ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;. C&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7897; b&#7913;c t&#432;&#7901;ng c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng t&#7889;t vi&#7879;c khoan, c&#7855;t, b&#7855;t v&amp;iacute;t v&amp;agrave; treo c&amp;aacute;c v&#7853;t d&#7909;ng trong nh&amp;agrave; nh&#432;: t&#7911; b&#7871;p, l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t &#273;i&#7879;n n&#432;&#7899;c, tivi, tranh &#7843;nh trang tr&amp;iacute; c&#7905; l&#7899;n&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m B&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; Viglacera c&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7897; 6 c&amp;oacute; k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c 150 x 200 x 600mm gi&amp;uacute;p thi c&amp;ocirc;ng d&#7877; d&amp;agrave;ng, ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; thi c&amp;ocirc;ng nhanh, ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m nh&amp;acirc;n c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; v&#7853;t t&#432; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng cho ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;. V&#7899;i chi&#7873;u d&amp;agrave;y 150mm, gi&amp;uacute;p gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7897; d&amp;agrave;y c&#7911;a t&#432;&#7901;ng so v&#7899;i t&#432;&#7901;ng 220mm truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng, t&#259;ng di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng cho ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m B&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; c&#7845;p c&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7897; 6 l&#7847;n &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#432;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7887;a thu&#7853;n v&#7899;i Ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Khu ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; Xu&amp;acirc;n Ph&#432;&#417;ng v&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t s&#7889; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n nh&amp;agrave; bi&#7879;t th&#7921;, li&#7873;n k&#7873; &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o s&#7917; d&#7909;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Vi&#7879;c &#273;&#432;a ra th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m B&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; c&#7845;p &#273;&#7897; 6 m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh vai tr&amp;ograve; ti&amp;ecirc;n phong c&#7911;a T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Viglacera n&amp;oacute;i chung v&amp;agrave; C&amp;ocirc;ng ty CP B&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; Viglacera n&amp;oacute;i ri&amp;ecirc;ng trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u m&#7899;i cho th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng. &lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','23/11/2011','23/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/san-pham-betong.jpg',23,2,1781,'huyennt',1,'ra-mat-san-pham-be-tong-khi-cap-cuong-do-6','b&ecirc; t&ocirc;ng, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m',NULL,NULL,NULL,'b&ecirc; t&ocirc;ng, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://www.diaoconline.vn',1,0,0,0),(103,'D&ugrave;ng th&#7843;m &#273;&uacute;ng c&aacute;ch','Th&#7901;i ti&#7871;t chuy&#7875;n m&ugrave;a c&#361;ng l&agrave; l&uacute;c nhi&#7873;u gia &#273;&igrave;nh mang c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i th&#7843;m ra s&#7917; d&#7909;ng. Kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; gi&uacute;p gi&#7919; nhi&#7879;t, gi&#7843;m ti&#7871;ng &#7891;n, gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7897; nguy hi&#7875;m khi tr&#7867; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, th&#7843;m c&ograve;n gi&uacute;p t&#7841;o phong c&aacute;ch, l&agrave;m &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n cho kh&ocirc;ng gian n&#7897;i th&#7845;t.','\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;324&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/dung-tham.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;a s&#7889; th&#7843;m tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng hi&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7853;p t&#7915; Th&amp;aacute;i Lan, Indonesia, Malaysia, Trung Qu&#7889;c, Singapore&amp;hellip; Th&#7843;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&#7871;t c&#7845;u theo d&#7841;ng cu&#7897;n ho&#7863;c t&#7845;m. Th&#7843;m cu&#7897;n c&amp;oacute; kh&#7893; 3,66m ho&#7863;c 4m, ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7875; l&amp;oacute;t to&amp;agrave;n b&#7897; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch s&amp;agrave;n. D&#7841;ng t&#7845;m r&#7901;i v&#7899;i k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905; 1,6m x 2,3m ho&#7863;c 2m x 3m th&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p &#273;&#7875; trang tr&amp;iacute; ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch ho&#7863;c ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u th&#7843;m th&#432;&#7901;ng l&amp;agrave; l&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7915;u, len, s&#7907;i nh&amp;acirc;n t&#7841;o, ni l&amp;ocirc;ng, olefin&amp;hellip; &#272;&#7855;t ti&#7873;n nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng t&#7845;m th&#7843;m b&#7857;ng l&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7915;u, gi&amp;aacute; kho&#7843;ng 10 tri&#7879;u &#273;/t&#7845;m tr&#7903; l&amp;ecirc;n, v&#7899;i k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905; 1,6m x 2,3m ho&#7863;c 2m x 3m, ho&#7863;c 2 tri&#7879;u &#273;/m2. Th&#7843;m len &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#432;a chu&#7897;ng h&#417;n c&#7843; v&amp;igrave; &#273;a d&#7841;ng m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c, m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7897; b&#7873;n cao. Th&#7843;m len d&#7841;ng t&#7845;m dao &#273;&#7897;ng t&#7915; 4 - 20 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng, d&#7841;ng cu&#7897;n t&#7915; 0,5 - 1,2 tri&#7879;u &#273;/m2. Th&#7843;m b&#7857;ng l&#7909;c b&amp;igrave;nh hay c&amp;oacute;i c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n l&#7921;a cho c&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian nh&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t b&#7857;ng g&#7895;. Gi&amp;aacute; lo&#7841;i th&#7843;m n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;aacute; m&#7873;m, kho&#7843;ng 20 ngh&amp;igrave;n &#273;/m2&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7843;m ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p cho nh&#7919;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian kh&amp;eacute;p k&amp;iacute;n, &amp;iacute;t b&#7909;i. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng th&#7843;m trong c&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian &#7849;m th&#7845;p nh&#432; nh&amp;agrave; b&#7871;p, g&amp;aacute;c x&amp;eacute;p ho&#7863;c trong ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n v&amp;igrave; th&#7843;m d&#7877; &#7849;m m&#7889;c v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;oacute; v&#7879; sinh. M&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; nhi&#7873;u lo&#7841;i th&#7843;m c&amp;oacute; t&amp;iacute;nh n&#259;ng ch&#7889;ng &#7849;m, ch&#7889;ng ch&amp;aacute;y, nh&#432;ng c&#361;ng c&#7847;n tr&amp;aacute;nh n&#432;&#7899;c, tr&amp;aacute;nh l&#7917;a &#7903; khu v&#7921;c tr&#7843;i th&#7843;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7885;n th&#7843;m ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u ni l&amp;ocirc;ng cho nh&#7919;ng n&#417;i c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; &#273;i l&#7841;i v&amp;agrave; c&#7885; x&amp;aacute;t nhi&#7873;u. Khi mua th&#7843;m ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u m&amp;acirc;y tre l&amp;aacute;, n&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7885;n lo&#7841;i &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7849;m s&#7845;y v&amp;agrave; x&#7917; l&amp;yacute; m&#7889;i m&#7885;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7843;m nhanh b&#7883; h&#432;, xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p l&amp;agrave; do s&#7921; c&#7885; x&amp;aacute;t ho&#7863;c b&#7883; &#7849;m m&#7889;c. Do &#273;&amp;oacute;, c&#7847;n h&#7841;n ch&#7871; t&#7889;i &#273;a vi&#7879;c di chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7891; v&#7853;t tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7843;m, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7891; v&#7853;t c&amp;oacute; g&amp;oacute;c c&#7841;nh, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i tr&amp;aacute;nh &#273;&#7893; n&#432;&#7899;c l&amp;ecirc;n th&#7843;m. N&#7871;u l&#7905; b&#7883; &#273;&#7893; n&#432;&#7899;c hay nh&#7919;ng lo&#7841;i ch&#7845;t l&#7887;ng c&amp;oacute; m&amp;agrave;u l&amp;ecirc;n th&#7843;m, c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i kh&#7855;c ph&#7909;c ngay b&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;ch s&#7845;y, gi&#7863;t kh&amp;ocirc; b&#7857;ng ch&#7845;t t&#7849;y r&#7917;a chuy&amp;ecirc;n d&#7909;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7843;m l&amp;agrave; v&#7853;t r&#7845;t b&amp;aacute;m b&#7909;i n&amp;ecirc;n c&#7847;n th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&amp;ecirc;n h&amp;uacute;t b&#7909;i, &amp;iacute;t nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; m&#7895;i tu&#7847;n. Sau 3 - 6 th&amp;aacute;ng, n&amp;ecirc;n gi&#7863;t th&#7843;m m&#7897;t l&#7847;n, kh&amp;ocirc;ng gi&#7863;t b&#7857;ng b&#7897;t gi&#7863;t th&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i th&#7843;m l&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7915;u, ch&#7881; n&amp;ecirc;n gi&#7863;t tay b&#7857;ng d&#7847;u g&#7897;i &#273;&#7847;u ho&#7863;c s&#7919;a t&#7855;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','24/11/2011','24/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/dung-tham.jpg',23,2,1836,'huyennt',1,'dung-tham-dung-cach','th&#7843;m, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, t&#7845;m th&#7843;m, c&aacute;ch d&ugrave;ng',NULL,NULL,NULL,'th&#7843;m, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, t&#7845;m th&#7843;m, c&aacute;ch d&ugrave;ng',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://www.xaydungvietnam.vn',1,0,0,0),(104,'Tri&#7875;n l&atilde;m v&agrave; h&#7897;i ngh&#7883; qu&#7889;c t&#7871; v&#7873; thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; chi&#7871;u s&aacute;ng t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam 2011','C&ugrave;ng v&#7899;i c&aacute;c ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n ng&agrave;nh chi&#7871;u s&aacute;ng t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam, m&#7897;t s&#7889; d&#7921; &aacute;n c&#7911;a Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c n&agrave;y c&#361;ng s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u t&#7841;i Tri&#7875;n l&atilde;m v&agrave; H&#7897;i ngh&#7883; qu&#7889;c t&#7871; v&#7873; Thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&agrave; C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; chi&#7871;u s&aacute;ng t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tri&#7875;n l&amp;atilde;m v&amp;agrave; H&#7897;i ngh&#7883; qu&#7889;c t&#7871; v&#7873; Thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&amp;agrave; C&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam - 2011 LIGHTING WORLD IN VIETNAM, m&#7897;t s&#7921; ki&#7879;n l&#7899;n c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng, ch&amp;iacute;nh th&#7913;c khai m&#7841;c s&amp;aacute;ng nay ng&amp;agrave;y 24/11 t&#7841;i Trung t&amp;acirc;m H&#7897;i ch&#7907; v&amp;agrave; Tri&#7875;n l&amp;atilde;m T&amp;acirc;n B&amp;igrave;nh (TBECC - 446, Ho&amp;agrave;ng V&#259;n Th&#7909;, qu&#7853;n T&amp;acirc;n B&amp;igrave;nh, TP.HCM) v&amp;agrave; k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i &#273;&#7871;n ng&amp;agrave;y 26/11.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/ong-tran-trong-hue.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;0&quot; height=&quot;0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/ong-tran-trong-hue.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Tr&#7847;n Tr&#7885;ng Hu&#7879;- Gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c C&amp;ocirc;ng ty chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng TP ph&amp;aacute;t bi&#7875;u t&#7841;i L&#7877; khai m&#7841;c.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7841;i h&#417;n 200 gian h&amp;agrave;ng c&#7911;a Tri&#7875;n l&amp;atilde;m, kh&amp;aacute;ch tham quan &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ti&#7871;p c&#7853;n 5 nh&amp;oacute;m s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m tr&#432;ng b&amp;agrave;y ch&amp;iacute;nh, g&#7891;m thi&#7871;t b&#7883; chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng; chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng c&#7889; &#273;&#7883;nh; chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng LED/OLED, linh ph&#7909; ki&#7879;n chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng; thi&#7871;t b&#7883; (ch&#7871; t&#7841;o, ki&#7875;m tra, &#273;o l&#432;&#7901;ng, th&#7917; nghi&#7879;m, &#273;&amp;aacute;nh gi&amp;aacute;); c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m kh&amp;aacute;c nh&#432; k&#7929; thu&#7853;t chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng/thi&#7871;t k&#7871;/d&#7883;ch v&#7909;&amp;hellip; C&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m n&amp;agrave;y do c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p Vi&#7879;t Nam v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;&#7871;n t&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c qu&#7889;c gia v&amp;agrave; v&amp;ugrave;ng l&amp;atilde;nh th&#7893; c&amp;oacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; v&amp;agrave; thi&#7871;t b&#7883; chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng ti&amp;ecirc;n ti&#7871;n nh&#432; Italy, T&amp;acirc;y Ban Nha, B&#7881;, &amp;Aacute;o, H&amp;agrave;n Qu&#7889;c, Nh&#7853;t B&#7843;n, Trung Qu&#7889;c, &#7844;n &#272;&#7897;&amp;hellip; gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u, tr&#432;ng b&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, t&#7841;i Tri&#7875;n l&amp;atilde;m, c&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch li&amp;ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n ng&amp;agrave;nh chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam, m&#7897;t s&#7889; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&#7911;a Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; Vi&#7879;t Nam trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng hi&#7879;u su&#7845;t cao t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam (VEEPL), D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n N&amp;acirc;ng cao hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng trong c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p nh&#7887; v&amp;agrave; v&#7915;a t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam (PECSME 2006-2010)&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Lu&#7853;t S&#7917; d&#7909;ng n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m v&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; &#273;&amp;atilde; ch&amp;iacute;nh th&#7913;c c&amp;oacute; hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c c&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7899;i Ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7889; 21/2011/N&#272;-CP quy ho&#7841;ch chi ti&#7871;t v&amp;agrave; bi&#7879;n ph&amp;aacute;p thi h&amp;agrave;nh Lu&#7853;t S&#7917; d&#7909;ng n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m v&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;. Theo &#273;&amp;oacute;, vi&#7879;c &amp;aacute;p d&#7909;ng t&#7889;t c&amp;aacute;c thi&#7871;t b&#7883; c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; gi&amp;uacute;p n&amp;acirc;ng cao hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng v&amp;agrave; ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m &#273;i&#7879;n n&#259;ng l&amp;agrave; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; b&#7855;t bu&#7897;c v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p, m&#7903; ra th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng r&#7845;t l&#7899;n cho ng&amp;agrave;nh thi&#7871;t b&#7883; chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, Vi&#7879;t Nam &#273;ang c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, tri&#7875;n khai nh&#432; c&amp;aacute;c khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; cao c&#7845;p, c&#417; s&#7903; h&#7841; t&#7847;ng quan tr&#7885;ng c&#7845;p qu&#7889;c gia, c&amp;aacute;c trung t&amp;acirc;m th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i, khu c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p, kh&amp;aacute;ch s&#7841;n, cao &#7889;c v&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng, h&#7879; th&#7889;ng ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng, b&#7843;o hi&#7875;m... S&#7921; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n m&#7841;nh m&#7869; n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7841;o nhu c&#7847;u l&#7899;n v&#7873; c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng, Do v&#7853;y, Tri&#7875;n l&amp;atilde;m c&amp;ograve;n t&#7841;o c&#417; h&#7897;i giao l&#432;u, t&amp;igrave;m hi&#7875;u &#273;&#7889;i t&amp;aacute;c v&amp;agrave; h&#7907;p t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, kinh doanh gi&#7919;a c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p trong ng&amp;agrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tri&#7875;n l&amp;atilde;m v&amp;agrave; H&#7897;i ngh&#7883; qu&#7889;c t&#7871; v&#7873; Thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&amp;agrave; C&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam - 2011 LIGHTING WORLD IN VIETNAM do C&amp;ocirc;ng ty c&#7893; ph&#7847;n H&#7897;i ch&#7907; tri&#7875;n l&amp;atilde;m v&amp;agrave; qu&#7843;ng c&amp;aacute;o Vi&#7879;t Nam (VIETFAIR) v&amp;agrave; C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Stavis H&amp;agrave;n Qu&#7889;c t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, v&#7899;i s&#7921; &#7911;ng h&#7897; v&amp;agrave; b&#7843;o tr&#7907; c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng, B&#7897; Khoa h&#7885;c v&amp;agrave; C&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879;, Vi&#7879;n Khoa h&#7885;c v&amp;agrave; C&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879;, UBND TP.HCM, D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng hi&#7879;u su&#7845;t cao t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam (VEEPL), H&#7897;i Chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam, Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i LED H&amp;agrave;n Qu&#7889;c. OSRAM, Philips, FAWOO-KIDI, SBC l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; t&amp;agrave;i tr&#7907; ch&amp;iacute;nh c&#7911;a s&#7921; ki&#7879;n n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;','25/11/2011','25/11/2011','',23,2,1933,'huyennt',1,'trien-lam-va-hoi-nghi-quoc-te-ve-thiet-bi-va-cong-nghe-chieu-sang-tai-viet-nam-2011','vlxd, tri&#7875;n l&atilde;m, d&#7921; &aacute;n, H&#7897;i ngh&#7883;, qu&#7889;c t&#7871;, Thi&#7871;t b&#7883;, C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; ,chi&#7871;u s&aacute;ng',NULL,NULL,NULL,'vlxd, tri&#7875;n l&atilde;m, d&#7921; &aacute;n, H&#7897;i ngh&#7883;, qu&#7889;c t&#7871;, Thi&#7871;t b&#7883;, C&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; ,chi&#7871;u s&aacute;ng',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(105,'Th&eacute;p x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng l&#7841;i b&#7883; l&agrave;m gi&aacute;','S&#7913;c ti&ecirc;u th&#7909; r&#7845;t th&#7845;p, gi&aacute; ph&ocirc;i th&eacute;p, th&eacute;p ph&#7871; li&#7879;u gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh nh&#432;ng c&aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&eacute;p v&#7851;n &ldquo;neo&rdquo; gi&aacute; &#7903; m&#7913;c cao','\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7901;i gian qua c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&#7849;y gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng l&amp;ecirc;n kh&amp;aacute; cao, trong khi s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng y&#7871;u. &#272;&#7875; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng, c&amp;aacute;c h&amp;atilde;ng th&amp;eacute;p s&#7861;n s&amp;agrave;ng tr&amp;iacute;ch m&#7913;c hoa h&#7891;ng cho &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute;, m&amp;ocirc;i gi&#7899;i l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i 1 tri&#7879;u - 1,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n, c&amp;ograve;n gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n l&#7867; tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng cao ng&#7845;t ng&#432;&#7903;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;T&#259;ng gi&amp;aacute; k&amp;iacute;ch th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo gi&#7899;i kinh doanh th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&amp;atilde; gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh t&#7915; gi&#7919;a n&#259;m 2011 do suy tho&amp;aacute;i kinh t&#7871; v&amp;agrave; Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c t&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng si&#7871;t ch&#7863;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng. &amp;Ocirc;ng &#272;&#7895; Duy Th&amp;aacute;i, T&#7893;ng Gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t, cho bi&#7871;t: S&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;ang gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh ngay trong m&amp;ugrave;a x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng l&amp;agrave; do &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7879; v&amp;agrave; t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh nh&amp;agrave; &#7903; ri&amp;ecirc;ng l&#7867;, d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&#259;n h&#7897; b&#7883; &#273;&amp;oacute;ng b&#259;ng k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i. C&#361;ng theo &amp;ocirc;ng Th&amp;aacute;i, c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y th&amp;eacute;p c&#7911;a Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t &#273;&#7873;u &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&#7843;i gi&#7843;m c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t &#273;&#7871;n 50%. Nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y th&amp;eacute;p c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c h&amp;atilde;ng kh&amp;aacute;c c&#361;ng gi&#7843;m ph&amp;acirc;n n&#7917;a c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t ho&#7863;c ch&#7881; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&#7847;m ch&#7915;ng, th&#7853;m ch&amp;iacute; c&amp;oacute; doanh nghi&#7879;p ph&#7843;i rao b&amp;aacute;n nh&amp;agrave; x&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7875; tr&#7843; n&#7907; ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng v&amp;igrave; l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t qu&amp;aacute; cao.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/Thep-xay-dung-lai-bi-lam-gia.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Gi&amp;aacute; ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh nh&#432;ng gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p v&#7851;n r&#7845;t cao.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&#272;&#7875; k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7847;u, c&amp;aacute;c h&amp;atilde;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&amp;atilde; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &amp;ldquo;chi&amp;ecirc;u&amp;rdquo; k&amp;iacute;ch gi&amp;aacute; b&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&#7891;ng lo&#7841;t &#273;&#7849;y gi&amp;aacute; t&#259;ng 2 &#273;&#7907;t trong th&amp;aacute;ng 8-2011 v&#7899;i m&#7913;c t&#259;ng t&#7893;ng c&#7897;ng kho&#7843;ng 1 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. Nhi&#7873;u h&amp;atilde;ng c&amp;ograve;n phao tin l&amp;agrave; s&#7869; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c t&#259;ng gi&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&amp;aacute;nh v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;acirc;m l&amp;yacute; gi&#7899;i kinh doanh s&#7855;t th&amp;eacute;p c&#361;ng nh&#432; nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7843;i mua th&amp;eacute;p d&#7921; tr&#7919; v&amp;igrave; lo ng&#7841;i gi&amp;aacute; t&#259;ng. &amp;ldquo;Chi&amp;ecirc;u&amp;rdquo; n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;atilde; mang l&#7841;i hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;  kh&amp;aacute; r&amp;otilde; khi s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p trong th&amp;aacute;ng 8 t&#259;ng kh&amp;aacute; cao, l&amp;ecirc;n 483.000 t&#7845;n. Gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p ni&amp;ecirc;m y&#7871;t t&#7841;i c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 18,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, sang th&amp;aacute;ng 9, s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng b&#7845;t ng&#7901; gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh tr&#7903; l&#7841;i, ch&#7881; c&amp;ograve;n 381.000 t&#7845;n v&amp;agrave; th&amp;aacute;ng 10 gi&#7843;m c&amp;ograve;n 320.000 t&#7845;n. Nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n l&amp;agrave; do gi&#7899;i kinh doanh tr&#7919; h&amp;agrave;ng qu&amp;aacute; nhi&#7873;u trong th&amp;aacute;ng 8, nh&#432;ng sau &#273;&amp;oacute; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng nh&#432; d&#7921; ki&#7871;n n&amp;ecirc;n h&#7885; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ograve;n m&#7863;n m&amp;agrave; l&#7845;y th&amp;ecirc;m h&amp;agrave;ng. Nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i am hi&#7875;u th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng ti&#7871;t l&#7897;: Khi kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng, l&#7869; ra c&amp;aacute;c h&amp;atilde;ng th&amp;eacute;p s&#7869; ph&#7843;i gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; tr&#7903; l&#7841;i &#273;&#7875; k&amp;iacute;ch th&amp;iacute;ch th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng. Th&#7871; nh&#432;ng h&#7885; &#273;&amp;atilde; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7885;n c&amp;aacute;ch n&amp;agrave;y m&amp;agrave; l&#7841;i h&#7907;p s&#7913;c &#273;&#7875; &amp;ldquo;neo&amp;rdquo; gi&amp;aacute; b&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;ch m&amp;oacute;c n&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c m&#7889;i l&amp;agrave;m &#259;n quen bi&#7871;t chi chi&#7871;t kh&#7845;u v&#7899;i m&#7913;c cao, t&#7915; 1 tri&#7879;u - 1,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n &#273;&#7875; gi&#7919; gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#7903; m&#7913;c 18,5 tri&#7879;u - 18,6 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. Do gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n l&#7867; qu&amp;aacute; cao n&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;agrave;ng th&amp;ecirc;m &#7871; &#7849;m. Theo th&#7889;ng k&amp;ecirc; s&#417; b&#7897;, trong th&amp;aacute;ng 10, m&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&#7911;a T&#7893;ng C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam (v&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng Tp.HCM), C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vina Kyoei, C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Pomina&amp;hellip; gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7871;n 50%.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ch&amp;ecirc;nh l&#7879;ch gi&amp;aacute; qu&amp;aacute; l&#7899;n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n Ti&#7871;n Nghi, Ph&amp;oacute; Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam, cho bi&#7871;t t&#7915; th&amp;aacute;ng 10 &#273;&#7871;n nay, gi&amp;aacute; qu&#7863;ng s&#7855;t, ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p v&amp;agrave; c&#7843; th&amp;eacute;p ph&#7871; li&#7879;u tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng th&#7871; gi&#7899;i li&amp;ecirc;n t&#7909;c gi&#7843;m (t&#7893;ng m&#7913;c gi&#7843;m c&#7911;a gi&amp;aacute; ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p kho&#7843;ng 100 USD/t&#7845;n). D&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o gi&amp;aacute; s&#7869; c&amp;ograve;n ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh t&#7915; nay &#273;&#7871;n cu&#7889;i n&#259;m v&amp;agrave; k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i &#273;&#7871;n nh&#7919;ng th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2012.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7871; nh&#432;ng gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7849;m trong n&#432;&#7899;c v&#7851;n &#7903; m&#7913;c cao. C&amp;aacute;c h&amp;atilde;ng th&amp;eacute;p gi&#7843;i th&amp;iacute;ch ch&#432;a th&#7875; gi&#7843;m l&amp;agrave; do hi&#7879;n nay c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ngu&#7891;n nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;oacute; v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; cao; n&#7871;u gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n s&#7869; b&#7883; l&#7895; n&#7863;ng. C&amp;ograve;n theo gi&#7899;i kinh doanh, s&#7903; d&#297; c&amp;aacute;c h&amp;atilde;ng th&amp;eacute;p ch&#432;a ch&#7883;u gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; l&amp;agrave; do s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;ang qu&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p, n&#7871;u gi&#7843;m l&amp;uacute;c n&amp;agrave;y r&#7845;t d&#7877; t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng t&amp;acirc;m l&amp;yacute; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng  mu&#7889;n ch&#7901; gi&amp;aacute; xu&#7889;ng n&#7919;a m&#7899;i mua, l&amp;uacute;c &#273;&amp;oacute; s&#7869; g&amp;acirc;y b&#7845;t l&#7907;i cho nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTheo t&amp;iacute;nh to&amp;aacute;n c&#7911;a gi&#7899;i chuy&amp;ecirc;n m&amp;ocirc;n: Th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m th&amp;aacute;ng 10, khi gi&amp;aacute; ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;ograve;n &#7903; m&#7913;c 660 USD - 670 USD/t&#7845;n th&amp;igrave; gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng ch&#7881; kho&#7843;ng 16 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. &#272;&#7871;n nay, gi&amp;aacute; ph&amp;ocirc;i ch&#7881; c&amp;ograve;n 600 USD/t&#7845;n, t&amp;iacute;nh ra gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t ch&#432;a t&#7899;i 14 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. N&#7871;u c&#7897;ng c&#7843; thu&#7871; GTGT th&amp;igrave; gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n c&#361;ng ch&#432;a t&#7899;i 15,4 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n l&#7867; tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng hi&#7879;n nay l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 18,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n, m&#7897;t m&#7913;c c&amp;aacute;ch bi&#7879;t qu&amp;aacute; l&#7899;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng th&amp;eacute;p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;T&#259;ng gi&amp;aacute; r&#7891;i l&#7841;i khuy&#7871;n m&amp;atilde;i&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&amp;ocirc;ng tin t&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng t&#7841;i Tp.HCM, s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; xi m&#259;ng trong nhi&#7873;u th&amp;aacute;ng qua gi&#7843;m r&#7845;t m&#7841;nh, so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923; n&#259;m ngo&amp;aacute;i &#273;&amp;atilde; gi&#7843;m h&#417;n 50%. Tuy s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; gi&#7843;m nh&#432;ng g&#7847;n &#273;&amp;acirc;y, m&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng l&#7841;i &#273;&#7849;y gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n t&#259;ng th&amp;ecirc;m kho&#7843;ng 7.500 &#273;&#7891;ng/bao 50 kg. Hi&#7879;n xi m&#259;ng H&amp;agrave; Ti&amp;ecirc;n 1 c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n l&#7867; 93.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/bao, Holcim 92.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/bao&amp;hellip; Do ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; y&#7871;u n&amp;ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u h&amp;atilde;ng xi m&#259;ng khuy&#7871;n m&amp;atilde;i mua 100 bao t&#7863;ng 2 - 5 bao, t&amp;ugrave;y h&amp;atilde;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','28/11/2011','28/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/Thep-xay-dung-lai-bi-lam-gia.jpg',23,2,1781,'huyennt',1,'thep-xay-dung-lai-bi-lam-gia','x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, l&agrave;m gi&aacute;, s&#7913;c ti&ecirc;u th&#7909;, th&eacute;p, th&eacute;p ph&#7871; li&#7879;u, gi&#7843;m, t&#259;ng',NULL,NULL,NULL,'x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, l&agrave;m gi&aacute;, s&#7913;c ti&ecirc;u th&#7909;, th&eacute;p, th&eacute;p ph&#7871; li&#7879;u, gi&#7843;m, t&#259;ng',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'http://www.xaydungvietnam.vn',1,0,0,0),(106,'Doanh nghi&#7879;p xi m&#259;ng: Ph&aacute; s&#7843;n g&#7847;n k&#7873;','C&oacute; &iacute;t nh&#7845;t ba nh&agrave; m&aacute;y xi m&#259;ng &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; rao b&aacute;n &#273;&#7875; l&#7845;y ti&#7873;n tr&#7843; n&#7907;. R&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u c&ocirc;ng ty xi m&#259;ng kh&aacute;c c&oacute; t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh &#273;ang c&#259;ng nh&#432; d&acirc;y &#273;&agrave;n. Trong ng&agrave;nh, c&#7909;m t&#7915; &ldquo;ph&aacute; s&#7843;n&rdquo; &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i trong cu&#7897;c n&oacute;i &#273;&#7871;n, trong khi ch&#7881; m&#7899;i h&#417;n m&#7897;t n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p v&#7851;n mu&#7889;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&agrave;o xi m&#259;ng.','\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;hi x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch kinh doanh cho n&#259;m 2011 v&amp;agrave;o cu&#7889;i n&#259;m ngo&amp;aacute;i, T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty C&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam (Vicem) &#273;&amp;atilde; l&#432;&#7901;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c nhi&#7873;u kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n &#273;ang ch&#7901; &#7903; ph&amp;iacute;a tr&#432;&#7899;c, n&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7881; &#273;&#7863;t ra m&#7909;c ti&amp;ecirc;u l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n &#7903; m&#7913;c 1.251 t&#7881; &#273;&#7891;ng (gi&#7843;m g&#7847;n 350 t&#7881; &#273;&#7891;ng so v&#7899;i n&#259;m 2010 v&amp;agrave; kho&#7843;ng 883 t&#7881; &#273;&#7891;ng so v&#7899;i n&#259;m 2009). C&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7911;a t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng d&amp;aacute;m k&#7923; v&#7885;ng nhi&#7873;u v&amp;agrave;o m&#7913;c t&#259;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909;, n&amp;ecirc;n c&#361;ng ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;a ra m&#7913;c doanh thu t&#259;ng kho&#7843;ng 5-10%. K&#7871; ho&#7841;ch &#273;&amp;oacute; nay &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n. V&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; Vicem v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n &#273;ang &#273;&#7889;i &#273;&#7847;u l&amp;agrave; l&amp;agrave;m sao &#273;&#7875; kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7883; thua l&#7895; v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; ngu&#7891;n thu &#273;&#7911; &#273;&#7875; tr&#7843; n&#7907;. Nh&#432;ng xem ra vi&#7879;c gi&#7843;i b&amp;agrave;i to&amp;aacute;n n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng d&#7877;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7871;n th&amp;aacute;ng 10-2011, k&#7871;t qu&#7843; kinh doanh c&#7911;a Vicem &#273;&amp;atilde; l&#7895; &#273;&#7871;n 220 t&#7881; &#273;&#7891;ng, &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#432;a t&#7915;ng x&#7843;y ra trong nhi&#7873;u n&#259;m qua. Nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n c&#361;ng ph&#7843;i c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; 10-20%. M&#7897;t doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;oacute; n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7919;ng ch&#7855;c, v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u &#273;&amp;atilde; kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7895; &#273;&#7913;ng v&#7919;ng ch&#7855;c tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng xi m&#259;ng, nh&#432; Vicem m&amp;agrave; c&amp;ograve;n thua l&#7895; kh&amp;aacute; n&#7863;ng nh&#432; v&#7853;y, th&amp;igrave; nh&#7919;ng doanh nghi&#7879;p m&#7899;i tham gia th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; t&amp;ecirc;n tu&#7893;i, c&amp;ograve;n bi &#273;&amp;aacute;t h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Sau b&#7889;n doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n trong ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng m&#7845;t kh&#7843; n&#259;ng tr&#7843; n&#7907;, ph&#7843;i c&#7847;u c&#7913;u B&#7897; T&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh tr&#7843; thay nh&#7919;ng kho&#7843;n vay &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, nay l&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; th&amp;ecirc;m m&#7897;t s&#7889; &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; kh&amp;aacute;c r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng m&#7845;t thanh kho&#7843;n. Trong s&#7889; &#273;&amp;oacute;, ba &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; &#273;ang &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; b&amp;aacute;n l&#7841;i nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y cho Vicem, nh&#432;ng b&#7843;n th&amp;acirc;n t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng &#273;ang ch&#7853;t v&#7853;t v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c kho&#7843;n n&#7907; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7871;n h&#7841;n, n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;oacute; l&#7869; ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t trong s&#7889; &#273;&amp;oacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o, s&#7913;c mua c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m t&#7899;i, v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; l&amp;agrave; n&#259;m t&#7899;i n&#7919;a, ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; d&#7845;u hi&#7879;u g&amp;igrave; s&amp;aacute;ng s&#7911;a h&#417;n n&#259;m nay. Do th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n &#273;ang lao d&#7889;c, ngu&#7891;n v&#7889;n tr&amp;aacute;i phi&#7871;u ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; c&#7845;p cho c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh, l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng cao ng&#7845;t ng&#432;&#7903;ng, n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; th&amp;ecirc;m nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p xi m&#259;ng r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, th&#7853;m ch&amp;iacute; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7913;c mua c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng gi&#7843;m s&amp;uacute;t l&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;ograve;n m&#7841;nh gi&amp;aacute;ng v&amp;agrave;o ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng &#273;ang tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&amp;agrave; m&#7903; r&#7897;ng n&#259;ng l&#7921;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t. Nh&#7919;ng doanh nghi&#7879;p l&#7841;c quan nh&#7845;t c&#361;ng ch&#7881; d&amp;aacute;m hy v&#7885;ng m&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; xi m&#259;ng c&#7911;a to&amp;agrave;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&#259;m nay b&#7857;ng v&#7899;i n&#259;m ngo&amp;aacute;i, t&#7913;c kho&#7843;ng 50 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n. Mu&#7889;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#432; th&#7871;, trong hai th&amp;aacute;ng 11 v&amp;agrave; 12, m&#7895;i th&amp;aacute;ng ph&#7843;i b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &amp;iacute;t nh&#7845;t 5 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n. Nh&#432;ng kh&#7843; n&#259;ng n&amp;agrave;y r&#7845;t kh&amp;oacute;, khi m&amp;agrave; s&#7913;c mua trong nh&#7919;ng th&amp;aacute;ng qua li&amp;ecirc;n t&#7909;c gi&#7843;m, t&#7915; kho&#7843;ng 4,8 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n/th&amp;aacute;ng trong nh&#7919;ng th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m, &#273;&#7871;n nay ch&#7881; c&amp;ograve;n 3,5 - 3,6 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n/th&amp;aacute;ng. Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, n&#259;ng l&#7921;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t xi m&#259;ng th&amp;igrave; t&#259;ng li&amp;ecirc;n t&#7909;c. Hi&#7879;n c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871; &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 65 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n v&amp;agrave; c&amp;ograve;n &#273;ang t&#259;ng ti&#7871;p, v&amp;igrave; nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng s&#7855;p x&amp;acirc;y xong, &#273;ang chu&#7849;n b&#7883; &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Chi ph&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7847;u v&amp;agrave;o t&#259;ng m&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;atilde; h&#7841; g&#7909;c nh&#7919;ng doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;ang ng&#7855;c ngo&#7843;i v&amp;agrave; khi&#7871;n nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p m&#7841;nh l&amp;acirc;m b&#7879;nh. Chi ph&amp;iacute; x&#259;ng d&#7847;u t&#259;ng 32-43%, &#273;i&#7879;n t&#259;ng 15,28%, t&#7927; gi&amp;aacute; ngo&#7841;i t&#7879; 9%, v&#7887; bao t&#259;ng 25% v&amp;agrave; than, ngu&#7891;n n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng ch&amp;iacute;nh s&#7917; d&#7909;ng trong ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng, t&#259;ng g&#7847;n 90%. &amp;ldquo;Hi&#7879;n nay ch&#7859;ng doanh nghi&#7879;p n&amp;agrave;o d&amp;aacute;m ngh&#297; &#273;&#7871;n vi&#7879;c t&#259;ng gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n. L&amp;agrave;m nh&#432; v&#7853;y s&#7869; l&#7853;p t&#7913;c m&#7845;t th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&amp;agrave; ch&#7871;t ngay. Ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n b&amp;aacute;n d&#432;&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh, ch&#7883;u l&#7895;, d&amp;ugrave; sao c&#361;ng c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng lay l&#7855;t, k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&amp;agrave;y n&amp;agrave;o hay ng&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;oacute;&amp;rdquo;, gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c m&#7897;t c&amp;ocirc;ng ty xi m&#259;ng chua ch&amp;aacute;t n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/Doanh-nghiep-xi-mang-Pha-san-gan-ke.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;C&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o, s&#7913;c mua c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m t&#7899;i n&#7919;a, ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; d&#7845;u hi&#7879;u g&amp;igrave; s&amp;aacute;ng s&#7911;a h&#417;n n&#259;m nay&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nC&amp;oacute; th&#7875; n&amp;oacute;i, ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng &#273;ang r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh th&#7871; ti&#7871;n tho&amp;aacute;i l&#432;&#7905;ng nan. Nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;ograve;n &#273;ang x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y d&#7903; dang. T&#7845;t c&#7843; doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng &#273;&#7873;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ngu&#7891;n v&#7889;n vay. Trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; vay &#273;&#7871;n 80% t&#7893;ng ngu&#7891;n v&#7889;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;. Bi k&#7883;ch nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ngu&#7891;n v&#7889;n vay trong n&#432;&#7899;c, v&#7899;i l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t 19-21,5%/n&#259;m. &#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng doanh nghi&#7879;p s&#7869; ch&#7871;t tr&#432;&#7899;c. V&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ch&#432;a ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh, doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;oacute; mu&#7889;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; ti&#7871;p c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, v&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng n&amp;agrave;o d&amp;aacute;m gi&#7843;i ng&amp;acirc;n trong b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh kinh t&#7871; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n nh&#432; hi&#7879;n nay. Nh&#432;ng ng&#7915;ng l&#7841;i c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng xong, v&amp;igrave; n&#7871;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; &#273;&#432;a nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y v&amp;agrave;o ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, s&#7869; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; d&amp;ograve;ng ti&#7873;n v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&#7875; tr&#7843; n&#7907; g&#7889;c v&amp;agrave; l&amp;atilde;i. Nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh m&#7897;t v&amp;agrave;i n&#259;m g&#7847;n &#273;&amp;acirc;y c&#361;ng ch&#7859;ng kh&amp;aacute; h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;H&amp;agrave;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; b&amp;aacute;n d&#432;&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh, n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;agrave;ng l&amp;agrave;m c&amp;agrave;ng l&#7895; n&#7863;ng v&amp;agrave; n&#7907; n&#7847;n th&amp;ecirc;m ch&#7891;ng ch&#7845;t. Mu&#7889;n b&amp;aacute;n l&#7841;i nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y &#273;&#7875; c&#7855;t l&#7895; c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, v&amp;igrave; ngay c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng doanh nghi&#7879;p c&amp;oacute; th&#7921;c l&#7921;c nh&#7845;t c&#361;ng ch&#432;a th&#7875; v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh h&#7871;t c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t, th&amp;igrave; c&amp;ograve;n ai d&amp;aacute;m m&#7841;o hi&#7875;m &#273;&#7875; mua.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t b&#7847;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; u &amp;aacute;m &#273;ang bao tr&amp;ugrave;m l&amp;ecirc;n ng&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p xi m&#259;ng. Nh&#432;ng m&#7897;t s&#7889; ng&#432;&#7901;i trong ng&amp;agrave;nh cho r&#7857;ng, &#273;&amp;oacute; m&#7899;i ch&#7881; l&amp;agrave; kh&#7903;i &#273;&#7847;u c&#7911;a m&#7897;t c&#417;n b&amp;atilde;o kh&#7911;ng ho&#7843;ng &#273;ang &#7853;p &#273;&#7871;n. V&#7899;i t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng m&#7845;t thanh kho&#7843;n, thi&#7871;u kh&#7843; n&#259;ng tr&#7843; n&#7907; &#273;ang lan ra nhanh ch&amp;oacute;ng, s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;iacute;t doanh nghi&#7879;p ph&#7843;i t&#7915; gi&amp;atilde; ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng.&lt;/p&gt;','28/11/2011','28/11/2011','',23,2,1802,'huyennt',1,'doanh-nghiep-xi-mang-pha-san-gan-ke','xi m&#259;ng, VLXD, ph&aacute; s&#7843;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'xi m&#259;ng, VLXD, ph&aacute; s&#7843;n',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://www.thesaigontimes.vn',1,0,0,0),(107,'Th&ecirc;m d&#7921; &aacute;n th&eacute;p &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quy ho&#7841;ch','Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; Nguy&#7877;n T&#7845;n D&#361;ng v&#7915;a ch&#7845;p thu&#7853;n ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng b&#7893; sung d&#7921; &aacute;n nh&agrave; m&aacute;y luy&#7879;n c&aacute;n th&eacute;p ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cao t&#7841;i t&#7881;nh Ninh B&igrave;nh v&agrave;o Quy ho&#7841;ch ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n ng&agrave;nh th&eacute;p giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2007 &ndash; 2015, c&oacute; x&eacute;t &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2025.','\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;389&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/thep-quy-hoach.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo th&amp;ocirc;ng tin &#273;&#259;ng t&#7843;i tr&amp;ecirc;n C&#7893;ng th&amp;ocirc;ng tin Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917; chi&#7873;u ng&amp;agrave;y 22-11, d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y luy&#7879;n c&amp;aacute;n th&amp;eacute;p ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cao t&#7841;i t&#7881;nh Ninh B&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;oacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 1 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p vu&amp;ocirc;ng/n&#259;m v&amp;agrave; 500.000 t&#7845;n th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;aacute;n h&#7907;p kim d&#7921; &#7913;ng l&#7921;c/n&#259;m do C&amp;ocirc;ng ty tr&amp;aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m h&#7919;u h&#7841;n C&amp;aacute;n th&amp;eacute;p Tam&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&#272;i&#7879;m l&amp;agrave;m ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTrao &#273;&#7893;i v&#7899;i Th&#7901;i b&amp;aacute;o Kinh t&#7871; S&amp;agrave;i G&amp;ograve;n Online ng&amp;agrave;y 23-11 v&#7873; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n n&amp;oacute;i tr&amp;ecirc;n, &amp;ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n Ti&#7871;n Nghi, Ph&amp;oacute; ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam (VSA), cho bi&#7871;t hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i m&#7899;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y c&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; v&#259;n b&#7843;n g&#7903;i Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; n&amp;ecirc;u &amp;yacute; ki&#7871;n c&#7911;a hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7891;ng t&amp;igrave;nh  tri&#7875;n khai d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n th&amp;eacute;p n&amp;agrave;y b&#7903;i hi&#7879;n ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c v&#7851;n ch&#432;a &#273;&#7911; v&amp;agrave; th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;aacute;n h&#7907;p kim d&#7921; &#7913;ng l&#7921;c d&amp;ugrave;ng trong x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n thi&#7871;u so v&#7899;i nhu c&#7847;u.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &amp;ocirc;ng Nghi, hi&#7879;n t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871; ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c l&amp;agrave; 6 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n trong n&#259;m 2011 ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t kho&#7843;ng 4,3 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i ph&#7843;i nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u tr&amp;ecirc;n 1 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n n&#7919;a. Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c c&#361;ng m&#7899;i ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;aacute;n h&#7907;p kim d&#7921; &#7913;ng l&#7921;c c&#7911;a C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t n&amp;ecirc;n c&#7847;n th&amp;ecirc;m nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t lo&#7841;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;eacute;p ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cao n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;','30/11/2011','30/11/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/11-2011/thep-quy-hoach.jpg',23,2,1742,'huyennt',1,'them-du-an-thep-duoc-quy-hoach',' Th&ecirc;m d&#7921; &aacute;n th&eacute;p &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quy ho&#7841;ch',NULL,NULL,NULL,' Th&ecirc;m d&#7921; &aacute;n th&eacute;p &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quy ho&#7841;ch',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(108,'Ng&agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng v&agrave; b&agrave;i to&aacute;n v&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute; cho n&#259;m 2012','Gi&#7843;i ph&aacute;p n&agrave;o &#273;&#7875; ng&agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng v&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute; trong b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh n&#259;m 2012 ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t t&iacute;n d&#7909;ng, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&ocirc;ng v&#7851;n h&#7841;n ch&#7871;. V&agrave; v&#7873; l&acirc;u d&agrave;i, ng&agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; ph&#7843;i c&#7841;nh tranh &#7903; trong n&#432;&#7899;c m&agrave; c&ograve;n c&#7843; trong khu v&#7921;c khi mu&#7889;n &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u?','\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7873; t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t kinh doanh 9 th&amp;aacute;ng n&#259;m 2011, T&#7893;ng C&amp;ocirc;ng ty xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam (VICEM) c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; l&#7895; 219 t&#7881; &#273;&#7891;ng. Theo VICEM, nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n l&#7895; l&amp;agrave; do c&amp;aacute;c chi ph&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7847;u v&amp;agrave;o t&#259;ng cao nh&#432; l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t vay v&#7889;n ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i 20%, gi&amp;aacute; than t&#259;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n 40%, x&#259;ng d&#7847;u t&#259;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n 32%...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo th&#7841;c s&#297; L&#432;&#417;ng Xu&amp;acirc;n Tu&amp;acirc;n, Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i V&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng (VLXD), nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n n&#7919;a khi&#7871;n ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng b&#7883; l&#7895; l&amp;agrave; do ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng l&amp;agrave;m th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n tr&#7847;m l&#7855;ng. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; h&#7841;n ch&#7871; nhu c&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; xi m&#259;ng. Theo VICEM, t&#7891;n kho c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng &#273;ang t&#259;ng l&amp;ecirc;n m&#7913;c lo ng&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n v&#7873; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909;, Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Xi m&#259;ng cho bi&#7871;t, nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n xi m&#259;ng, ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; c&#7911;a Trung Qu&#7889;c &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2006 &amp;ndash; 2008 &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7871;n th&#7901;i k&#7923; tr&#7909;c tr&#7863;c. V&amp;iacute; d&#7909; xi m&#259;ng Lam Th&#7841;ch II, Y&amp;ecirc;n B&amp;igrave;nh, H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t, &#272;&#7891;ng B&amp;agrave;nh, S&amp;ocirc;ng Thao&amp;hellip; Theo th&#7889;ng k&amp;ecirc;, do d&amp;acirc;y chuy&#7873;n thi&#7871;u &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897;, thi&#7871;t b&#7883; k&amp;eacute;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng&amp;hellip; n&amp;ecirc;n h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y m&#7899;i &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&#7873;u g&#7863;p tr&#7909;c tr&#7863;c trong qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, ti&amp;ecirc;u hao nhi&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u l&#7899;n l&amp;agrave;m t&#259;ng chi ph&amp;iacute; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t. Chi ph&amp;iacute; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t t&#259;ng, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ch&#7853;m ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; l&amp;agrave; nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n khi&#7871;n nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n xi m&#259;ng l&amp;acirc;m v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng l&#7895; nh&#432; nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng Ho&amp;agrave;ng Mai, Tam &#272;i&#7879;p, Th&amp;aacute;i Nguy&amp;ecirc;n v&amp;agrave; &#272;&#7891;ng B&amp;agrave;nh&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;328&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/nganh-xi-mang.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;M&#7897;t nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; l&amp;ograve; quay&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTrong m&#7897;t b&amp;aacute;o c&amp;aacute;o c&#7911;a B&#7897; T&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh g&#7917;i Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; &#273;&amp;aacute;nh gi&amp;aacute; t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7843; n&#7907; c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n xi m&#259;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; b&#7843;o l&amp;atilde;nh cho bi&#7871;t, c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n vay v&#7889;n n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&amp;agrave;i &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n 1998 &amp;ndash; 2007 &#273;&#7871;n nay &#273;&amp;atilde; gi&#7843;i ng&amp;acirc;n xong v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7871;n h&#7841;n tr&#7843; n&#7907;. Theo nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a B&#7897; T&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh, trong v&amp;ograve;ng 3 &amp;ndash; 5 n&#259;m t&#7899;i, s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; th&amp;ecirc;m nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n xi m&#259;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n trong vi&#7879;c tr&#7843; n&#7907; do k&#7871;t qu&#7843; kinh doanh kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&#7843; quan d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n m&#7845;t c&amp;acirc;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7873; ngu&#7891;n &#273;&#7875; tr&#7843; n&#7907; v&#7889;n vay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&amp;aacute;nh gi&amp;aacute; t&#7891;n t&#7841;i c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam, Th&#7913; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Nguy&#7877;n Tr&#7847;n Nam cho r&#7857;ng, t&#7891;n t&#7841;i c&#417; b&#7843;n nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;agrave; chi ph&amp;iacute; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&amp;ograve;n cao. C&#7909; th&#7875;, m&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u hao &#273;i&#7879;n, than, d&#7847;u c&amp;ograve;n qu&amp;aacute; l&#7899;n khi&#7871;n gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m b&#7883; &#273;&#7897;i l&amp;ecirc;n. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, n&#259;ng su&#7845;t lao &#273;&#7897;ng c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh c&#361;ng &#273;ang k&amp;eacute;m nh&#7845;t trong kh&#7889;i doanh nghi&#7879;p li&amp;ecirc;n doanh, Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave; t&#432; nh&amp;acirc;n, th&#7853;m ch&amp;iacute; th&#7845;p h&#417;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i &#273;&#7871;n 10 l&#7847;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo TS Tr&#7847;n V&#259;n Huynh, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i VLXD, c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng ph&#7843;i t&amp;igrave;m c&amp;aacute;ch t&#7853;n d&#7909;ng nhi&#7879;t th&#7843;i, kh&amp;iacute; th&#7915;a &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi ph&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7847;u v&amp;agrave;o. Ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi ph&amp;iacute; n&amp;agrave;y, ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng s&#7869; t&#259;ng s&#7913;c c&#7841;nh tranh &#273;&amp;aacute;ng k&#7875;. &#272;&#7875; vi&#7879;c ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7849;y nhanh, Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&amp;agrave; B&#7897; ch&#7911; qu&#7843;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ph&#7843;i ban h&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7871; t&amp;agrave;i m&#7841;nh, b&#7855;t bu&#7897;c c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng c&amp;oacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 2.500 t&#7845;n clinker/ng&amp;agrave;y tr&#7903; l&amp;ecirc;n (c&#7843; c&#361; v&amp;agrave; chu&#7849;n b&#7883; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;) ph&#7843;i l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t h&#7879; th&#7889;ng t&#7853;n d&#7909;ng nhi&#7879;t kh&amp;iacute; th&#7843;i l&amp;ograve; nung &#273;&#7875; ph&amp;aacute;t &#273;i&#7879;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2015, nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y n&amp;agrave;o kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n th&amp;igrave; ki&amp;ecirc;n quy&#7871;t c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m 25% s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng &#273;i&#7879;n cung c&#7845;p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Th&#7913; hai, &lt;/em&gt;ph&#7843;i h&#7841;n ch&#7871; cho ph&amp;eacute;p &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t xi m&#259;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t nh&#7887; (350.000 &amp;ndash; 600.000 t&#7845;n/n&#259;m) v&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y n&amp;agrave;y s&#7869; ti&amp;ecirc;u hao n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng nhi&#7873;u g&#7845;p 1,5 &amp;ndash; 1,6 l&#7847;n so v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i. Ch&#7845;m d&#7913;t c&#7843; vi&#7879;c chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng l&amp;ograve; &#273;&#7913;ng sang l&amp;ograve; quay c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t nh&#7887; v&amp;igrave; theo quy ho&#7841;ch t&#7893;ng th&#7875; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n ng&amp;agrave;nh, giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2011 &amp;ndash; 2015, ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; 8 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&amp;oacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 900.000 t&#7845;n/n&#259;m. Giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2016 &amp;ndash; 2020 l&amp;agrave; 7 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7871;n giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2021 &amp;ndash; 2030 v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n 2 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t nh&#7887;. Nh&#7919;ng nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y c&amp;oacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t nh&#7887; &#273;&#7873;u l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y c&amp;oacute; ngh&#7879; th&#7845;p, kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i m&#7909;c ti&amp;ecirc;u c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p h&amp;oacute;a, hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i h&amp;oacute;a ng&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p xi m&#259;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Th&#7913; ba&lt;/em&gt;, v&#7873; l&amp;acirc;u d&amp;agrave;i, quy ho&#7841;ch ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i kh&#7855;c ph&#7909;c hi&#7879;n t&#432;&#7907;ng n&#417;i c&#7847;n th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, n&#417;i &#273;&amp;atilde; th&#7915;a v&#7851;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;. V&amp;iacute; d&#7909;, ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng &#273;ang t&#7853;p trung &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; qu&amp;aacute; nhi&#7873;u v&amp;agrave;o m&#7897;t s&#7889; v&amp;ugrave;ng &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n v&#7853;n t&#7843;i kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n nh&#432; H&amp;agrave; Nam, Ninh B&amp;igrave;nh. Hi&#7879;n c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t t&#7841;i khu v&#7921;c n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i 20 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n/n&#259;m. Trong khi m&#7897;t s&#7889; n&#417;i c&#7847;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; s&#7899;m l&#7841;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tri&#7875;n khai nh&#432; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n xi m&#259;ng &#7903; Th&#7841;nh M&#7929;, t&#7881;nh Qu&#7843;ng Nam. D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;oacute; m&#7887; &#273;&amp;aacute; v&amp;ocirc;i l&#7899;n &#7903; A S&#7901; - Th&#7841;nh M&#7929;, tr&#7919; l&#432;&#7907;ng 350 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, r&#7845;t hi&#7871;m c&amp;oacute; &#7903; mi&#7873;n Trung m&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; khai th&amp;aacute;c s&#7899;m &#273;&#7875; ph&#7909;c v&#7909; khu v&#7921;c mi&#7873;n Trung, T&amp;acirc;y Nguy&amp;ecirc;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Quy ho&#7841;ch t&#7893;ng th&#7875; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n ng&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2011 &amp;ndash; 2020 v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7871;n 2030 &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t (th&amp;aacute;ng 8/2011), B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&#7847;n s&#7899;m qu&amp;aacute;n tri&#7879;t quy ho&#7841;ch n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#7875; c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, ch&amp;iacute;nh quy&#7873;n c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng n&#7855;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quy ho&#7841;ch v&amp;agrave; quy&#7871;t t&amp;acirc;m th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n. B&#7897; c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i k&#7883;p th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh ngay c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p ho&#7863;c c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; n&#259;ng l&#7921;c tri&#7875;n khai d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n.&lt;/p&gt;','06/12/2011','06/12/2011