273;&#432;&#7907;c coi l&agrave; m&agrave;u c&#7911;a ho&agrave;ng t&#7897;c, m&agrave;u c&#7911;a s&#7921; sang tr&#7885;ng, quy&#7873;n qu&yacute;, cao sang.','\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/mau-phong/mau-vang-am-cung.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ng&amp;agrave;y nay, m&amp;agrave;u v&amp;agrave;ng c&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i v&amp;agrave; ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n h&#417;n v&#7899;i &#273;&#7901;i s&#7889;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#7853;t c&#7911;a m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i. S&#7921; &#7845;m &amp;aacute;p m&amp;agrave; g&#7847;n g&#361;i, sang tr&#7885;ng nh&#432;ng th&amp;acirc;n thi&#7879;n c&#7911;a m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c n&amp;agrave;y khi&#7871;n cho n&amp;oacute; lu&amp;ocirc;n l&amp;agrave; s&#7921; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#432;a th&amp;iacute;ch c&#7911;a nhi&#7873;u chuy&amp;ecirc;n gia n&#7897;i th&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, vi&#7879;c ph&#7889;i k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c kh&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7875; sao cho s&#7855;c m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;agrave;y ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh chung c&#7911;a kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian s&#7889;ng v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng qu&amp;aacute; ch&amp;oacute;i, l&#7841;c l&amp;otilde;ng l&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng h&#7873; &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/mau-phong/mau-vang-am-cung1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nM&amp;agrave;u v&amp;agrave;ng - d&amp;ugrave; &#7903; s&#7855;c &#273;&#7897; n&amp;agrave;o c&#361;ng &#273;&#7873;u to&amp;aacute;t l&amp;ecirc;n v&#7867; r&#7921;c r&#7905;, n&#259;ng &#273;&#7897;ng v&amp;agrave; &#7845;m c&amp;uacute;ng. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; th&#7871; khi ch&#7885;n gam m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;agrave;m m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7841;o cho m&#7897;t kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian n&amp;agrave;o &#273;&amp;oacute; trong ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh, b&#7841;n c&#7847;n ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute; ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c chi ti&#7871;t n&#7897;i th&#7845;t, gam m&amp;agrave;u chung c&#7911;a c&#7843; c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; c&#361;ng nh&#432; c&amp;aacute;c &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n trong n&#7897;i th&#7845;t kh&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o s&#7921; trung h&amp;ograve;a cho kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&#7919;ng s&#7855;c m&amp;agrave;u hay &#273;&#432;&#7907;c d&amp;ugrave;ng &#273;&#7875; ph&#7889;i c&amp;ugrave;ng m&amp;agrave;u v&amp;agrave;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng m&amp;agrave;u t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#7889;i tr&#7847;m nh&#432; m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;acirc;u nh&#7841;t, m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng, ho&#7863;c xanh d&#432;&#417;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&amp;igrave; l&amp;agrave; m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c c&#7911;a s&#7921; &#7845;m c&amp;uacute;ng, n&#259;ng &#273;&#7897;ng n&amp;ecirc;n m&amp;agrave;u v&amp;agrave;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c d&amp;ugrave;ng &#273;&#7875; trang tr&amp;iacute; ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch. Khi trang ho&amp;agrave;ng cho ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch c&#7911;a b&#7841;n b&#7857;ng gam m&amp;agrave;u r&#7921;c r&#7905; n&amp;agrave;y s&#7869; khi&#7871;n cho kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian n&#417;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y to&amp;aacute;t l&amp;ecirc;n m&#7897;t v&#7867; th&amp;acirc;n thi&#7879;n, c&#7903;i m&#7903; nh&#432; mu&#7889;n t&#7887; l&amp;ograve;ng hi&#7871;u kh&amp;aacute;ch c&#7911;a b&#7841;n v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng v&#7883; kh&amp;aacute;ch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7921; hi&#7871;u kh&amp;aacute;ch c&#7911;a b&#7841;n c&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7899;i m&#7897;t kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian &#7845;m &amp;aacute;p, th&amp;acirc;n thi&#7879;n m&amp;agrave; s&#7855;c m&amp;agrave;u t&#432;&#417;i tr&#7867; n&amp;agrave;y mang l&#7841;i s&#7869; khi&#7871;n cho nh&#7919;ng v&#7883; kh&amp;aacute;ch d&amp;ugrave; ch&#7881; &#273;&#7871;n nh&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n m&#7897;t l&#7847;n s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng &#7845;n t&#432;&#7907;ng th&#7853;t &#273;&#7865;p v&#7873; b&#7841;n, v&#7873; ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; r&#7921;c r&#7905; s&#7855;c v&amp;agrave;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/mau-phong/mau-vang-am-cung2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;314&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/mau-phong/mau-vang-am-cung3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;375&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/mau-phong/mau-vang-am-cung4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/mau-phong/mau-vang-am-cung5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;391&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/mau-phong/mau-vang-am-cung6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','06/12/2011','06/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/mau-phong/mau-vang-am-cung.jpg',38,11,2173,'huyennt',1,'mau-vang-am-cung-cho-phong-khach-mua-dong',' M&agrave;u v&agrave;ng &#7845;m c&uacute;ng cho ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch m&ugrave;a &#273;&ocirc;ng',NULL,NULL,NULL,' M&agrave;u v&agrave;ng &#7845;m c&uacute;ng cho ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch m&ugrave;a &#273;&ocirc;ng',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(113,'G&#7847;n T&#7871;t, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng v&#7851;n &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m','Theo c&aacute;c c&#7917;a h&agrave;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng t&#7841;i TPHCM, th&ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng 3 th&aacute;ng cu&#7889;i n&#259;m l&agrave; m&ugrave;a cao &#273;i&#7875;m x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, tuy nhi&ecirc;n t&#7915; gi&#7919;a th&aacute;ng 10 &#273;&#7871;n nay, s&#7913;c mua v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng gi&#7843;m s&uacute;t m&#7841;nh, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng tr&#7847;m l&#7855;ng ch&#7913; kh&ocirc;ng s&ocirc;i &#273;&#7897;ng nh&#432; m&#7885;i n&#259;m.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo quan s&amp;aacute;t c&#7911;a Th&#7901;i b&amp;aacute;o Kinh t&#7871; S&amp;agrave;i G&amp;ograve;n Online s&amp;aacute;ng nay (30-11) tr&amp;ecirc;n tr&#7909;c &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng T&amp;ocirc; Hi&#7871;n Th&amp;agrave;nh, qu&#7853;n 10, n&#417;i t&#7853;p trung nhi&#7873;u c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng b&amp;aacute;n c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng nh&#432; g&#7841;ch &#7889;p t&#432;&#7901;ng, &#273;&amp;aacute; hoa c&#432;&#417;ng, b&#7891;n c&#7847;u, v&amp;ograve;i n&#432;&#7899;c, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u trang tr&amp;iacute; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t ... t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh giao d&#7883;ch kh&amp;aacute; bu&#7891;n t&#7867;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;377&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/01_011211DOOLThangTT018.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;agrave; Cao Th&#7883; Nhung, ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng Ph&amp;aacute;t Th&amp;agrave;nh C&amp;ocirc;ng, b&amp;aacute;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u trang tr&amp;iacute; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng T&amp;ocirc; Hi&#7871;n Th&amp;agrave;nh, qu&#7853;n 10, nh&#7853;n x&amp;eacute;t: nhi&#7873;u c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng n&#259;m nay b&#7883; &#273;&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7879;, b&#7887; d&#7903; dang do l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t cao, ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; thi&#7871;u v&#7889;n k&amp;eacute;o theo s&#7913;c mua v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng t&#7841;i c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng gi&#7843;m 20-30% so v&#7899;i n&#259;m ngo&amp;aacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;agrave; Nhung cho bi&#7871;t, ch&#7881; c&amp;ograve;n hy v&#7885;ng m&#7897;t th&amp;aacute;ng 12 t&#7899;i n&#7919;a th&amp;ocirc;i l&amp;agrave; h&#7871;t m&amp;ugrave;a cao &#273;i&#7875;m x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng khi h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o giai &#273;o&#7841;n ho&amp;agrave;n t&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, t&#7841;i c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&amp;aacute; hoa c&#432;&#417;ng Tu&#7845;n An c&#361;ng n&#7857;m tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng T&amp;ocirc; Hi&#7871;n Th&amp;agrave;nh, ch&#7883; Ph&#7841;m Th&#7883; Loan, nh&amp;acirc;n vi&amp;ecirc;n b&amp;aacute;n h&amp;agrave;ng c&#361;ng cho r&#7857;ng, s&#7913;c mua &#273;&amp;aacute; hoa c&#432;&#417;ng, g&#7841;ch men t&#7841;i &#273;&#7871;n th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y gi&#7843;m kho&#7843;ng 30% so v&#7899;i n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Ng&amp;agrave;nh &#273;&amp;aacute; hoa c&#432;&#417;ng nh&#432; t&#7909;i em ch&#7881; c&amp;ograve;n hy v&#7885;ng b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trong 1 &amp;ndash; 2 tu&#7847;n t&#7899;i, n&#7871;u t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh &#7871; &#7849;m ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i th&amp;igrave; coi nh&#432; kh&amp;oacute; c&#7843; n&#259;m&amp;rdquo;, ch&#7883; Loan than th&#7903;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, t&#7841;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng s&#7855;t th&amp;eacute;p tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng L&amp;yacute; Th&#432;&#7901;ng Ki&#7879;t qu&#7853;n 11, n&#7871;u nh&#432; gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng m&amp;ugrave;a cao &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7919;ng n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c li&amp;ecirc;n t&#7909;c bi&#7871;n &#273;&#7897;ng, nh&amp;iacute;ch l&amp;ecirc;n theo nhu c&#7847;u c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng th&amp;igrave; n&#259;m nay c&amp;ograve;n gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&#7913;ng &#7903; m&#7913;c 18,3 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n g&#7847;n m&#7897;t th&amp;aacute;ng nay b&#7903;i s&#7913;c mua v&#7851;n ch&#432;a t&#259;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng t&#7841;i TPHCM c&#361;ng cho bi&#7871;t, gi&amp;aacute; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u nh&#432; g&#7841;ch &#7889;ng, s&#7855;t th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng phi 6, phi 8, xi m&#259;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&#259;m nay t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#7889;i &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh h&#417;n m&#7897;t th&amp;aacute;ng qua, m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n do nhu c&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; c&amp;ograve;n th&#7845;p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#7909; th&#7875;, gi&amp;aacute; g&#7841;ch &#7889;ng v&#7851;n &#273;&#7913;ng m&#7913;c 750 &#273;&#7891;ng/vi&amp;ecirc;n, xi m&#259;ng Holcim 91 ng&amp;agrave;n &#273;&#7891;ng/bao (50 kg), xi m&#259;ng H&amp;agrave; Ti&amp;ecirc;n 91,5 ng&amp;agrave;n &#273;&#7891;ng/bao v&amp;agrave; th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng dao &#273;&#7897;ng 18,3 -18,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n t&amp;ugrave;y theo v&#7883; tr&amp;iacute; v&#7853;n chuy&#7875;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Ph&#7841;m &#272;i&#7879;u, Gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c C&amp;ocirc;ng ty TNHH X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Ki&#7871;n Minh C&amp;ocirc;ng &#7903; qu&#7853;n T&amp;acirc;n Ph&amp;uacute; cho bi&#7871;t, nh&amp;igrave;n chung &#273;&#7871;n th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7883;nh th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng n&#259;m nay gi&#7843;m kho&#7843;ng 20% so v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c. M&#7897;t s&#7889; nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u s&#7889;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&amp;agrave; nh&#7901; b&#7845;u v&amp;iacute;u v&amp;agrave;o c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng d&amp;acirc;n d&#7909;ng nh&#7887;, c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh l&#7899;n &#273;&#7871;n gi&#7901; v&#7851;n ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; g&amp;igrave; kh&#7903;i s&#7855;c.&lt;/p&gt;','06/12/2011','06/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/01_011211DOOLThangTT018.jpg',23,2,2926,'huyennt',1,'gan-tet-thi-truong-vat-lieu-xay-dung-van-am-dam','v&#7853;t li&#7879;u &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m, VLXD',NULL,NULL,NULL,'v&#7853;t li&#7879;u &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m, VLXD',0,0,0,'','','',3,'diaoconlien.vn',1,0,0,0),(114,'V&igrave; sao D&#7921; &aacute;n x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng Nh&agrave; m&aacute;y g&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung &ETH;&ocirc;ng H&#7891;i b&#7883; ng&#432;ng tr&#7879; ?','Qua ba l&#7847;n tri&#7875;n khai thi c&ocirc;ng g&oacute;i th&#7847;u &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng Nh&agrave; m&aacute;y K&#7871;t c&#7845;u b&ecirc;-t&ocirc;ng - v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng (KCBT-VLXD) kh&ocirc;ng nung, ph&iacute;a nh&agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&#7873;u g&#7863;p ph&#7843;i s&#7921; c&#7843;n tr&#7903; quy&#7871;t li&#7879;t do s&#7921; k&iacute;ch &#273;&#7897;ng c&#7911;a m&#7897;t s&#7889; ph&#7847;n t&#7917; qu&aacute; kh&iacute;ch.','\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/1312842435.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;Hi&#7879;n tr&#7841;ng khu &#273;&#7845;t d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y K&#7871;t c&#7845;u b&amp;ecirc;-t&amp;ocirc;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng H&#7891;i.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y KCBT-VLXD kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung &amp;ETH;&amp;ocirc;ng H&#7891;i, c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 400 tri&#7879;u vi&amp;ecirc;n/n&#259;m l&amp;agrave; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n kh&#7903;i c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n Khu c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p (KCN) &amp;ETH;&amp;ocirc;ng H&#7891;i thu&#7897;c huy&#7879;n Qu&#7923;nh L&#432;u (Ngh&#7879; An). &amp;ETH;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh h&#7907;p t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&#7911;a T&#7893;ng C&amp;ocirc;ng ty c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p xi-m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam (Vicem) t&#7841;i Ngh&#7879; An giai &#273;o&#7841;n 2011-2015 v&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng n&#259;m ti&#7871;p theo &#273;&#7871;n 2020. C&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7899;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y tr&amp;ecirc;n, c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng C&#7843;ng chuy&amp;ecirc;n d&amp;ugrave;ng Vicem - &amp;ETH;&amp;ocirc;ng H&#7891;i (bao g&#7891;m b&#7871;n c&#7843;ng s&#7889; 1, 2, 3, 4 v&amp;agrave; 5 theo Quy ho&#7841;ch chi ti&#7871;t Khu b&#7871;n c&#7843;ng &amp;ETH;&amp;ocirc;ng H&#7891;i &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c B&#7897; Giao th&amp;ocirc;ng v&#7853;n t&#7843;i ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t ng&amp;agrave;y 28-4-2011); Tr&#7841;m nghi&#7873;n v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i xi-m&#259;ng v&amp;agrave; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng h&#7841; t&#7847;ng v&#7853;n chuy&#7875;n &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u th&amp;ocirc;ng qua c&#7843;ng c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m xi-m&#259;ng khu v&#7921;c B&#7855;c Trung B&#7897;; Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi-m&#259;ng Ho&amp;agrave;ng Mai II, c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 4,5 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n/n&#259;m; D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; Vicem t&#7841;i x&amp;atilde; Nghi &amp;ETH;&#7913;c, TP Vinh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo b&amp;aacute;o c&amp;aacute;o c&#7911;a UBND huy&#7879;n Qu&#7923;nh L&#432;u v&#7873; c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng gi&#7843;i ph&amp;oacute;ng m&#7863;t b&#7857;ng (GPMB) d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y KCBT-VLXD kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung t&#7841;i KCN &amp;ETH;&amp;ocirc;ng H&#7891;i, d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&amp;oacute; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch 22,8 ha, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n l&amp;agrave; 19,8 ha. S&#7889; h&#7897; d&amp;acirc;n b&#7883; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng l&amp;agrave; 115 h&#7897;, 17 h&#7897; ph&#7843;i t&amp;aacute;i &#273;&#7883;nh c&#432; thu&#7897;c x&amp;atilde; Qu&#7923;nh L&#7853;p. Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y kh&#7903;i c&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&amp;acirc;y b&#7843;y th&amp;aacute;ng, t&#7893;ng hai l&#7847;n &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t chuy&#7875;n ti&#7873;n b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng h&#417;n 33 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng. H&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng GPMB &#273;&amp;atilde; ti&#7871;n h&amp;agrave;nh chi tr&#7843; cho d&amp;acirc;n b&#7889;n l&#7847;n h&#417;n 21,471 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng, c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i h&#417;n 11,829 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng c&amp;aacute;c h&#7897; ch&#432;a nh&#7853;n v&amp;igrave; l&amp;yacute; do &#273;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; ti&#7873;n b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7845;t &#7903; v&amp;agrave; nh&amp;agrave; &#7903;, c&amp;aacute;c t&amp;agrave;i s&#7843;n g&#7855;n li&#7873;n v&#7899;i &#273;&#7845;t &#7903;. C&amp;aacute;c h&#7897; y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u ph&#7843;i c&amp;oacute; khu t&amp;aacute;i &#273;&#7883;nh c&#432; th&amp;igrave; m&#7899;i nh&#7853;n ti&#7873;n b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng do s&#7907; khi nh&#7853;n ti&#7873;n r&#7891;i ph&#7843;i di chuy&#7875;n ngay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Qua tri&#7875;n khai thi c&amp;ocirc;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, Vicem &#273;&amp;atilde; g&#7863;p kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n do ph&amp;iacute;a ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n g&amp;acirc;y c&#7843;n tr&#7903;. M&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; H&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng GPMB huy&#7879;n, M&#7863;t tr&#7853;n v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c &#273;o&amp;agrave;n th&#7875; huy&#7879;n, x&amp;atilde; &#273;&amp;atilde; nhi&#7873;u l&#7847;n v&#7853;n &#273;&#7897;ng gi&#7843;i th&amp;iacute;ch cho ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n. L&#7847;n th&#7913; nh&#7845;t, ng&amp;agrave;y 27-4-2011 khi nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; tri&#7875;n khai g&amp;oacute;i th&#7847;u san l&#7845;p m&#7863;t b&#7857;ng  th&amp;igrave; m&#7897;t s&#7889; h&#7897; d&amp;acirc;n ng&#259;n c&#7843;n, c&amp;aacute;c h&#7897; n&amp;agrave;y t&#7893; ch&#7913;c h&#7885;p, k&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&#7897;ng, thu ti&#7873;n v&amp;agrave; t&#7893; ch&#7913;c khi&#7871;u n&#7841;i t&#7853;p th&#7875;. Ng&amp;agrave;y 8-6, UBND huy&#7879;n t&#7893; ch&#7913;c b&#7843;o v&#7879; thi c&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#432;ng c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng manh &#273;&#7897;ng, k&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&#7897;ng nh&amp;acirc;n d&amp;acirc;n, l&amp;ocirc;i k&amp;eacute;o ph&#7909; n&#7919; v&amp;agrave; tr&#7867; em ra ng&#259;n c&#7843;n, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i cao tu&#7893;i, n&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7843;i ng&#7915;ng thi c&amp;ocirc;ng. Sau khi ng&#7915;ng thi c&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng k&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&#7897;ng ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c t&#7893; ch&#7913;c h&#7885;p c&amp;aacute;c h&#7897; b&#7883; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng, ti&#7871;n h&amp;agrave;nh thu ti&#7873;n, vi&#7871;t &#273;&#417;n khi&#7871;u n&#7841;i. S&#7889; h&#7897; b&#7883; &amp;eacute;p bu&#7897;c &#273;i khi&#7871;u n&#7841;i l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i 55 h&#7897;, ch&#7911; y&#7871;u &#7903; x&amp;oacute;m &amp;ETH;&#7891;ng Thanh v&amp;agrave; &amp;ETH;&#7891;ng Minh. UBND huy&#7879;n &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7893; ch&#7913;c th&amp;agrave;nh l&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n thanh tra gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t khi&#7871;u n&#7841;i &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i 55 h&#7897; d&amp;acirc;n. Qua thanh tra 150 n&#7897;i dung khi&#7871;u n&#7841;i c&#7911;a 55 &#273;&#417;n, &#273;o&amp;agrave;n thanh tra x&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh 16 n&#7897;i dung khi&#7871;u n&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; c&#417; s&#7903;. C&amp;aacute;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; c&#417; s&#7903; do &#273;&#7845;t n&#7857;m ngo&amp;agrave;i quy ho&#7841;ch d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ho&#7863;c &#273;&#7845;t khai hoang nh&#432;ng n&#7857;m tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7845;t 64, &#273;&#7845;t c&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;iacute;ch c&#7911;a x&amp;atilde; &#273;&amp;atilde; b&#7887; hoang nhi&#7873;u n&#259;m n&amp;ecirc;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; c&#417; s&#7903; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7873;n b&amp;ugrave; theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Huy&#7879;n ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c c&#7917; c&amp;aacute;c t&#7893; c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c xu&#7889;ng tuy&amp;ecirc;n truy&#7873;n v&#7853;n &#273;&#7897;ng nh&amp;acirc;n d&amp;acirc;n, &#273;&#7871;n ng&amp;agrave;y 17-8, UBND huy&#7879;n t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;i&#7873;u &#273;&#7897;ng l&#7921;c l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c c&#417; quan xu&#7889;ng b&#7843;o v&#7879; thi c&amp;ocirc;ng. M&#7897;t s&#7889; ng&#432;&#7901;i qu&amp;aacute; kh&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&amp;atilde; d&amp;ugrave;ng &#273;&amp;aacute;, g&#7853;y g&#7897;c n&amp;eacute;m, &#273;&amp;aacute;nh l&amp;agrave;m m&#7897;t s&#7889; th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n trong l&#7921;c l&#432;&#7907;ng l&amp;agrave;m nhi&#7879;m v&#7909; b&#7883; th&#432;&#417;ng. Do t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh ph&#7913;c t&#7841;p x&#7843;y ra, l&#7921;c l&#432;&#7907;ng b&#7843;o v&#7879; &#273;&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7843;i r&amp;uacute;t v&amp;agrave; ng&#7915;ng thi c&amp;ocirc;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ng&amp;agrave;y 4-10, Ph&amp;oacute; Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch UBND t&#7881;nh Hu&#7923;nh Thanh &amp;ETH;i&#7873;n, &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; bu&#7893;i l&amp;agrave;m vi&#7879;c v&#7899;i huy&#7879;n Qu&#7923;nh L&#432;u. K&#7871;t lu&#7853;n t&#7841;i bu&#7893;i l&amp;agrave;m vi&#7879;c m&#7897;t l&#7847;n n&#7919;a n&amp;oacute;i r&amp;otilde;: D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y KCBT-VLXD kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung &amp;ETH;&amp;ocirc;ng H&#7891;i l&amp;agrave; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n kh&#7903;i c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n KCN &amp;ETH;&amp;ocirc;ng H&#7891;i. Ngo&amp;agrave;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n n&amp;agrave;y, Vicem c&amp;ograve;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; d&amp;acirc;y chuy&#7873;n Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y Xi-m&#259;ng Ho&amp;agrave;ng Mai II, C&#7843;ng xi-m&#259;ng &amp;ETH;&amp;ocirc;ng H&#7891;i. V&amp;igrave; th&#7871; vi&#7879;c nhanh ch&amp;oacute;ng b&amp;agrave;n giao m&#7863;t b&#7857;ng cho d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&amp;oacute; &amp;yacute; ngh&#297;a quan tr&#7885;ng trong vi&#7879;c thu h&amp;uacute;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&#7911;a t&#7881;nh, t&#7841;o ti&#7873;n &#273;&#7873; h&amp;igrave;nh th&amp;agrave;nh v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n KCN &amp;ETH;&amp;ocirc;ng H&#7891;i. UBND t&#7881;nh c&#361;ng giao huy&#7879;n Qu&#7923;nh L&#432;u ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c t&#7893; ch&#7913;c &#273;&#7889;i tho&#7841;i v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c h&#7897; d&amp;acirc;n c&amp;oacute; ki&#7871;n ngh&#7883;, gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t d&#7913;t &#273;i&#7875;m c&amp;aacute;c khi&#7871;u n&#7841;i c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c h&#7897; d&amp;acirc;n nh&#7857;m s&#7899;m &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; tri&#7875;n khai thi c&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng tuy&amp;ecirc;n truy&#7873;n ph&amp;aacute;p lu&#7853;t &#273;&#7875; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n hi&#7875;u r&amp;otilde; ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch, ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; v&#7873; b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng GPMB, l&#7907;i &amp;iacute;ch khi c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a b&amp;agrave;n...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong bi&amp;ecirc;n b&#7843;n l&amp;agrave;m vi&#7879;c gi&#7919;a l&amp;atilde;nh &#273;&#7841;o Vicem v&amp;agrave; l&amp;atilde;nh &#273;&#7841;o t&#7881;nh Ngh&#7879; An ng&amp;agrave;y 28-9-2011 v&#7873; h&#7907;p t&amp;aacute;c th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&amp;agrave; c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c h&#7895; tr&#7907; an sinh x&amp;atilde; h&#7897;i c&#7911;a Vicem tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a b&amp;agrave;n Ngh&#7879; An &#273;&amp;atilde; ghi: &amp;ETH;&#7889;i v&#7899;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y KCBT-&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;VLXD kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung: Vicem &#273;&amp;atilde; kh&#7903;i c&amp;ocirc;ng, &#273;&amp;atilde; chuy&#7875;n ti&#7873;n b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng h&#417;n 33 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng. T&#7881;nh Ngh&#7879; An ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;o x&#7917; l&amp;yacute; c&amp;aacute;c v&#432;&#7899;ng m&#7855;c v&#7873; b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng GPMB b&amp;agrave;n giao m&#7863;t b&#7857;ng cho Vicem tr&#432;&#7899;c ng&amp;agrave;y 31-11-2011 &#273;&#7875; Vicem tri&#7875;n khai th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n, ph&#7845;n &#273;&#7845;u &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2013 &#273;&#432;a nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t. Tuy v&#7853;y, &#273;&#7871;n nay vi&#7879;c tri&#7875;n khai thi c&amp;ocirc;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y v&#7851;n &#273;ang b&#7883; ng&#432;ng tr&#7879; do s&#7921; c&#7843;n tr&#7903; g&amp;acirc;y r&#7889;i tr&#7853;t t&#7921; c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng, c&#7889; &amp;yacute; &#273;&amp;aacute;nh ng&#432;&#7901;i g&amp;acirc;y th&#432;&#417;ng t&amp;iacute;ch v&amp;agrave; c&#7843;n tr&#7903; ng&#432;&#7901;i thi h&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng v&#7909; c&#7911;a m&#7897;t s&#7889; &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ETH;&#7875; kh&amp;ocirc;ng l&amp;agrave;m n&#7843;n l&amp;ograve;ng c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, t&#7881;nh Ngh&#7879; An c&#7847;n quy&#7871;t li&#7879;t ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;o huy&#7879;n Qu&#7923;nh L&#432;u ki&amp;ecirc;n quy&#7871;t x&#7917; l&amp;yacute; d&#7913;t &#273;i&#7875;m c&amp;aacute;c v&#432;&#7899;ng m&#7855;c &#273;&#7875; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y KCBT-VLXD kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung, m&amp;agrave; c&amp;ograve;n m&#7897;t s&#7889; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n kh&amp;aacute;c nh&#432; Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y s&#7855;t x&#7889;p Kobelco... c&amp;oacute; &amp;yacute; ngh&#297;a quan tr&#7885;ng trong thu h&amp;uacute;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&#7911;a t&#7881;nh, t&#7841;o ti&#7873;n &#273;&#7873; h&amp;igrave;nh th&amp;agrave;nh v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n KCN &amp;ETH;&amp;ocirc;ng H&#7891;i nh&#432; m&#7909;c ti&amp;ecirc;u &#273;&#7873; ra.&lt;/p&gt;','07/12/2011','07/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/1312842435.jpg',23,2,1880,'huyennt',1,'vi-sao-du-an-xay-dung-nha-may-gach-khong-nung-ðong-hoi-bi-ngung-tre-?','hi&#7879;n tr&#7841;ng, &#273;&#7845;t d&#7921; &aacute;n, c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh, VLXD, mikado',NULL,NULL,NULL,'hi&#7879;n tr&#7841;ng, &#273;&#7845;t d&#7921; &aacute;n, c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh, VLXD, mikado',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://www.nhandan.com.vn',1,0,0,0),(115,'Khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&ocirc;ng nung','Ph&oacute; Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ho&agrave;ng Trung H&#7843;i v&#7915;a giao B&#7897; X&acirc;y d&#7921;ng nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u, x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng d&#7921; th&#7843;o Ch&#7881; th&#7883; c&#7911;a Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch, &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&ocirc;ng nung, thay th&#7871; c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7845;t s&eacute;t &#273;ang d&#7847;n l&#7841;c h&#7853;u v&agrave; c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u h&#7879; qu&#7843; b&#7845;t l&#7907;i hi&#7879;n nay.','\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;500&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/gach-khong-nung.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m g&#7841;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung t&#7841;i H&#7897;i ch&#7907; Vietbuild 2011&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kh&#7855;c ph&#7909;c b&#7845;t c&#7853;p c&#7911;a s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, kinh doanh g&#7841;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo Th&#7913; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Nguy&#7877;n Tr&#7847;n Nam, m&#7895;i n&#259;m vi&#7879;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t nung l&amp;agrave;m m&#7845;t &#273;i m&#7897;t di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&#7845;t canh t&amp;aacute;c n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p c&#7911;a 1 x&amp;atilde;. Do &#273;&amp;oacute;, Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh 567/2010/Q&#272;-TTg c&#7911;a Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&#7873; vi&#7879;c ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2020 &#273;&amp;atilde; m&#7903; ra m&#7897;t h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;i m&#7899;i cho ng&amp;agrave;nh v&#7853;t li&#7879;u chi&#7871;m t&#7927; tr&#7885;ng l&#7899;n trong x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7915; v&amp;agrave;i ba d&amp;acirc;y chuy&#7873;n quy m&amp;ocirc; nh&#7887;, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t mang t&amp;iacute;nh th&amp;iacute; &#273;i&#7875;m, th&#259;m d&amp;ograve; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, &#273;&#7871;n nay, c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; h&#417;n 1.000 d&amp;acirc;y chuy&#7873;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch xi m&#259;ng c&#7889;t li&#7879;u c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t d&#432;&#7899;i 7 tri&#7879;u vi&amp;ecirc;n/n&#259;m, 50 d&amp;acirc;y chuy&#7873;n c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 7-40 tri&#7879;u vi&amp;ecirc;n/n&#259;m; 22 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; ch&#432;ng &amp;aacute;p v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 3,8 tri&#7879;u m3/n&#259;m; 17 d&amp;acirc;y chuy&#7873;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7885;t v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 190.000 m3/n&#259;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7871;n nay, v&#7899;i s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng 4,2 t&#7927; vi&amp;ecirc;n, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung &#273;&amp;atilde; ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c 6,15 tri&#7879;u m3 &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t, 615.000 t&#7845;n than v&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;m th&#7843;i v&amp;agrave;o kh&amp;iacute; quy&#7875;n 2,4 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n CO2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7881; t&amp;iacute;nh ri&amp;ecirc;ng 3 lo&#7841;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m n&amp;oacute;i tr&amp;ecirc;n, Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh 567 &#273;&amp;atilde; v&amp;agrave; s&#7869; &#273;&#7841;t v&amp;agrave; m&#7909;c ti&amp;ecirc;u &#273;&#7873; ra, hi&#7879;n t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; sau 1 n&#259;m th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n &#273;&amp;atilde; chi&#7871;m t&#7915; 16-17% t&#7893;ng s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y so v&#7899;i t&#7927; l&#7879; m&#7909;c ti&amp;ecirc;u &#273;&#7873; ra cho n&#259;m 2015 l&amp;agrave; 20-25%.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung &#273;ang cho th&#7845;y nh&#7919;ng b&#7845;t c&#7853;p, c&#7847;n nh&#7919;ng &#273;&amp;ograve;n b&#7849;y ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&#7875; &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;G&#7841;ch block xim&#259;ng c&#7889;t li&#7879;u c&amp;oacute; m&#7863;t tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7915; l&amp;acirc;u, thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i v&#7873; nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u v&#7899;i ngu&#7891;n &#273;&amp;aacute; m&#7841;t, x&#7881; l&amp;ograve;, tro bay,&amp;hellip; d&#7891;i d&amp;agrave;o, nh&#432;ng m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&#417;n &#273;i&#7879;u, v&#7915;a to v&#7915;a n&#7863;ng, gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh cao n&amp;ecirc;n kh&amp;oacute; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;G&#7841;ch b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7865; m&#7899;i &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, ch&#432;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng bi&#7871;t &#273;&#7871;n nhi&#7873;u v&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;&#7873;u, n&amp;ecirc;n ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; c&#361;ng r&#7845;t k&amp;eacute;m, h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&#7873;u ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;t 20-30% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871;, m&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; c&#361;ng ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;t 50-60% s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng, nhi&#7873;u &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&#7843;i d&#7915;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n cho g&#7841;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung khi kinh t&#7871; c&#361;ng nh&#432; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng tr&#7847;m l&#7855;ng, l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t vay &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#7903; m&#7913;c cao. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; ch&#432;ng &amp;aacute;p AAC hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i cao h&#417;n so v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t nung kho&#7843;ng 20-25% so chi ph&amp;iacute; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t cao h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ki&amp;ecirc;n quy&#7871;t d&#7847;n thay th&#7871; g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7889;t truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#432;&#7899;c t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh n&amp;agrave;y, B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; ki&#7871;n ngh&#7883; Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; t&amp;igrave;m c&amp;aacute;ch th&amp;aacute;o g&#7905; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, t&#7841;c &#273;&amp;ograve;n b&#7849;y &#273;&#7875; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m m&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; d&#7847;n thay th&#7871;, chi&#7871;m l&#297;nh th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7841;i cu&#7897;c h&#7885;p, Ph&amp;oacute; Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ho&amp;agrave;ng Trung H&#7843;i n&amp;ecirc;u r&amp;otilde; quan &#273;i&#7875;m khuy&#7871;n kh&amp;iacute;ch, ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung &#273;&#7875; thay th&#7871; g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t nung, ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m &#273;&#7845;t n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p, g&amp;oacute;p ph&#7847;n b&#7843;o &#273;&#7843;m an ninh l&#432;&#417;ng th&#7921;c qu&#7889;c gia, gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u kh&amp;iacute; ph&amp;aacute;t th&#7843;i g&amp;acirc;y hi&#7879;u &#7913;ng nh&amp;agrave; k&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;agrave; &amp;ocirc; nhi&#7877;m m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng, gi&#7843;m chi ph&amp;iacute; x&#7917; l&amp;yacute; ph&#7871; th&#7843;i c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c ng&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p, ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m nhi&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u than, &#273;em l&#7841;i hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; kinh t&#7871; chung cho to&amp;agrave;n x&amp;atilde; h&#7897;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;oacute; Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u, x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng m&#7897;t d&#7921; th&#7843;o Ch&#7881; th&#7883; c&#7911;a Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung trong th&#7901;i gian t&#7899;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &#273;&amp;oacute;, xem x&amp;eacute;t t&#7841;o c&#417; ch&#7871;, l&#7897; tr&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng cho v&#7853;t li&#7879;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung, t&#7841;o thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i cho nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7873; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, ngu&#7891;n nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u, t&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng thanh ki&#7875;m tra vi&#7879;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7845;t n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p l&amp;agrave;m g&#7841;ch &#273;&amp;atilde; b&#7883; c&#7845;m theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh t&#7841;i Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh 567, n&amp;acirc;ng ph&amp;iacute; b&#7843;o v&#7879; m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&amp;agrave; t&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng gi&amp;aacute;m s&amp;aacute;t &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&#417; s&#7903; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t nung.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng b&amp;aacute;m s&amp;aacute;t ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7845;t n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p, b&#7843;o v&#7879; &#273;&#7845;t l&amp;uacute;a &#273;&#7875; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o quy ho&#7841;ch ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng theo h&#432;&#7899;ng h&#7841;n ch&#7871; g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t nung, c&amp;oacute; l&#7897; tr&amp;igrave;nh ch&#7845;m d&#7921;t vi&#7879;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch b&#7857;ng l&amp;ograve; th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong d&#7921; th&#7843;o Ch&#7881; th&#7883; c&#361;ng b&#7893; sung c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m t&#7845;m 3D v&amp;agrave; t&#7845;m t&#432;&#7901;ng th&#7841;ch cao &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&#432;&#7903;ng c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7871; &#273;&#7897; &#432;u &#273;&amp;atilde;i nh&#432; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; ch&#432;ng &amp;aacute;p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, b&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, c&amp;aacute;c c&#417; quan li&amp;ecirc;n quan s&#7869; xem x&amp;eacute;t vi&#7879;c t&#7841;o c&#417; ch&#7871; thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i v&#7873; t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave; t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u c&#7911;a Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c cho c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; g&#7841;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung, &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh thu&#7871; t&amp;agrave;i nguy&amp;ecirc;n, ph&amp;iacute; m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&amp;oacute; li&amp;ecirc;n quan.&lt;/p&gt;','07/12/2011','07/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/gach-khong-nung.jpg',23,2,1948,'huyennt',1,'khuyen-khich-phat-trien-vat-lieu-xay-dung-khong-nung',' Khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&ocirc;ng nung',NULL,NULL,NULL,' Khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&ocirc;ng nung',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://www.xaydungvietnam.vn',1,0,0,0),(116,'T&#259;ng &#273;&#7897; cao c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh &#7903; khu Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m','H&#7841;n ch&#7871; t&#259;ng m&#7853;t &#273;&#7897; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, d&agrave;nh qu&#7929; &#273;&#7845;t &#273;&#7875; b&#7889; tr&iacute; c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh c&ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng. Ng&agrave;y 6-12, BQL Khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m t&#7893; ch&#7913;c h&#7897;i th&#7843;o g&oacute;p &yacute; nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh c&#7909;c b&#7897; quy ho&#7841;ch ph&acirc;n khu t&#7881; l&#7879; 1/2.000 Khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m &#273;&#7875; ho&agrave;n ch&#7881;nh thi&#7871;t k&#7871;, tr&igrave;nh UBND TP.HCM ph&ecirc; duy&#7879;t.','&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;Thi&#7871;t k&#7871; quy ho&#7841;ch Khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m l&#7847;n n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u thay &#273;&#7893;i so v&#7899;i &#273;&#7891; &amp;aacute;n quy ho&#7841;ch &#273;&#432;&#7907;c UBND TP ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t n&#259;m 2005. C&#7909; th&#7875;, t&#259;ng di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch s&amp;agrave;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng t&#7915; 5,6 tri&#7879;u l&amp;ecirc;n 7,5 tri&#7879;u m2; t&#259;ng t&#7847;ng cao c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh ki&#7871;n tr&amp;uacute;c m&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n l&amp;agrave; Th&amp;aacute;p quan s&amp;aacute;t 86 t&#7847;ng; t&#259;ng m&#7853;t &#273;&#7897; d&amp;acirc;n c&#432; t&#7915; 120.000 l&amp;ecirc;n h&#417;n 137.000 ng&#432;&#7901;i (v&#7851;n d&#432;&#7899;i m&#7913;c TP &#273;&amp;atilde; duy&#7879;t l&amp;agrave; 160.000 d&amp;acirc;n). L&#432;&#7907;ng c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; t&#259;ng th&amp;ecirc;m ch&#7911; y&#7871;u t&#7915; khu t&amp;aacute;i &#273;&#7883;nh c&#432; v&amp;agrave; chuy&#7875;n c&amp;ocirc;ng n&#259;ng khu d&#7885;c &#273;&#7841;i l&#7897; &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng T&amp;acirc;y. C&amp;ocirc;ng ty t&#432; v&#7845;n Sasaki Associates (Hoa K&#7923;) cho r&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7881; ti&amp;ecirc;u &#273;&#432;a ra trong quy ho&#7841;ch l&#7847;n n&amp;agrave;y th&#7845;p h&#417;n con s&#7889; UBND TP &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o bi&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7897; uy&#7875;n chuy&#7875;n cho thi&#7871;t k&#7871; chi ti&#7871;t t&#7915;ng &amp;ocirc; ph&#7889; sau n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; &quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/thu-thiem.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;Khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;&amp;Yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng ch&#7911; &#273;&#7841;o l&amp;agrave; h&amp;igrave;nh th&amp;agrave;nh khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; c&amp;oacute; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian m&#7903;, g&#7847;n g&#361;i thi&amp;ecirc;n nhi&amp;ecirc;n v&#7899;i t&#7847;m nh&amp;igrave;n c&#7843;nh quan h&#432;&#7899;ng ra s&amp;ocirc;ng S&amp;agrave;i G&amp;ograve;n. Gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n l&amp;agrave; t&#259;ng &#273;&#7897; cao c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch s&amp;agrave;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, ph&#7909;c v&#7909; nhu c&#7847;u nh&amp;agrave; &#7903; cho l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n t&#259;ng th&amp;ecirc;m nh&#432;ng h&#7841;n ch&#7871; t&#259;ng m&#7853;t &#273;&#7897; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, d&amp;agrave;nh qu&#7929; &#273;&#7845;t &#273;&#7875; b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh giao th&amp;ocirc;ng, c&amp;acirc;y xanh, c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n... C&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng, d&#7883;ch v&#7909;, th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; r&#7843;i r&amp;aacute;c theo t&#7915;ng c&#7909;m &#273;&#7875; k&#7871;t n&#7889;i v&#7899;i khu d&amp;acirc;n c&#432;&amp;rdquo; - &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; t&#432; v&#7845;n ph&amp;acirc;n t&amp;iacute;ch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Thi&#7871;t k&#7871; quy ho&#7841;ch Khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m l&#7847;n n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u thay &#273;&#7893;i so v&#7899;i &#273;&#7891; &amp;aacute;n quy ho&#7841;ch &#273;&#432;&#7907;c UBND TP ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t n&#259;m 2005.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, &amp;ocirc;ng Trang B&#7843;o S&#417;n, Ph&amp;oacute; Tr&#432;&#7903;ng BQL Khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n UBND qu&#7853;n 2 kh&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;n th&amp;agrave;nh thi&#7871;t k&#7871; &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7847;m &#273;i b&#7897; d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&#7841;i l&#7897; V&amp;ograve;ng cung. L&amp;yacute; do l&amp;agrave; ch&#432;a ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p nhu c&#7847;u ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n th&#7921;c t&#7871;. &amp;ldquo;Hi&#7879;n tuy&#7871;n &#273;&#7841;i l&#7897; V&amp;ograve;ng cung &#273;&amp;atilde; kh&#7903;i &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#7875; k&#7871;t n&#7889;i khai th&amp;aacute;c khu l&amp;otilde;i sau khi h&amp;igrave;nh th&amp;agrave;nh. V&#7853;y gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p thi&#7871;t k&#7871; h&#7847;m &#273;i b&#7897; v&amp;agrave; kh&#7889;i th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i d&#7883;ch v&#7909; n&#7857;m d&#432;&#7899;i tuy&#7871;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;oacute; c&amp;ograve;n kh&#7843; thi kh&amp;ocirc;ng? C&amp;oacute; th&#7875; thay b&#7857;ng gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng n&#7889;i v&amp;agrave; t&#259;ng kh&#7889;i th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i d&#7883;ch v&#7909; &#7903; c&amp;aacute;c t&#7847;ng &amp;ocirc; ph&#7889; kh&amp;aacute;c&amp;rdquo; - &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n BQL v&amp;agrave; UBND qu&#7853;n 2 c&amp;ugrave;ng ph&amp;acirc;n t&amp;iacute;ch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n Anh Tu&#7845;n, Tr&#432;&#7903;ng BQL Khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m, c&#361;ng y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u nh&amp;agrave; t&#432; v&#7845;n &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh quy ho&#7841;ch theo h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7919; nguy&amp;ecirc;n hai ch&#7881; ti&amp;ecirc;u &amp;ldquo;c&#7913;ng&amp;rdquo; UBND TP &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t. &#272;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng d&amp;acirc;n c&#432; 160.000 ng&#432;&#7901;i v&amp;agrave; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch s&amp;agrave;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng 8 tri&#7879;u m2 &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o chu&#7849;n thi&#7871;t k&#7871; chung v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; trong t&#432;&#417;ng lai. &amp;ldquo;N&#7871;u &#273;&#7875; bi&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7897; dao &#273;&#7897;ng nhi&#7873;u s&#7869; t&#7841;o s&#7921; ph&amp;acirc;n b&amp;igrave; gi&#7919;a c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; khi &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t quy ho&#7841;ch chi ti&#7871;t, t&#7915; &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; n&#7843;y sinh kh&amp;uacute;c m&#7855;c, nghi ng&#7841;i &amp;ldquo;c&amp;oacute; ti&amp;ecirc;u c&#7921;c&amp;rdquo; trong vi&#7879;c ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t, c&#7845;p ph&amp;eacute;p&amp;rdquo; - &amp;ocirc;ng Tu&#7845;n n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - theo: diaoconline.vn&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;','07/12/2011','07/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/thu-thiem.jpg',28,8,2013,'huyennt',1,'tang-do-cao-cong-trinh-o-khu-thu-thiem','khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m',NULL,NULL,NULL,'khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m',0,0,0,'','','',3,'diaoconlien.vn',1,0,0,0),(117,'Th&eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;ang h&#7841; gi&aacute; &#273;&#7875; tr&aacute;nh t&#7891;n kho','Nh&#7919;ng th&aacute;ng cu&#7889;i n&#259;m 2011, c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng ph&#7845;n &#273;&#7845;u ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch c&#7897;ng v&#7899;i nhu c&#7847;u s&#7917;a ch&#7919;a nh&agrave; m&#7899;i &#273;&oacute;n T&#7871;t &#273;&atilde; kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;m s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&eacute;p t&#259;ng m&agrave; ng&#432;&#7907;c l&#7841;i, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&agrave; nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u c&#361;ng gi&#7843;m d&#7847;n do ti&ecirc;u th&#7909; kh&oacute; kh&#259;n.','\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p trong ng&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&#7847;m ch&#7915;ng tr&amp;aacute;nh t&#7891;n kho c&#361;ng nh&#432; &#273;&#7885;ng v&#7889;n n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7871;n h&#7871;t th&amp;aacute;ng 11/2012 &#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7841;t 6,44 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c gi&#7843;m 1,5% so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;365&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/hagia.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHai th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u ch&amp;iacute;nh c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam l&amp;agrave; Nh&#7853;t B&#7843;n v&amp;agrave; Trung Qu&#7889;c &#273;&#7873;u ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng n&amp;ecirc;n trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;atilde; x&#7843;y ra hi&#7879;n t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7841;nh tranh kh&amp;ocirc;ng l&amp;agrave;nh m&#7841;nh b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; v&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;m l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7891;n kho. Hi&#7879;n nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;ang ch&amp;agrave;o gi&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p h&#417;n gi&amp;aacute; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7915; 200 - 300 ngh&amp;igrave;n &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; g&amp;oacute;p ph&#7847;n b&#7843;o &#273;&#7843;m ngu&#7891;n cung, b&amp;igrave;nh &#7893;n gi&amp;aacute; c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng thi&#7871;t y&#7871;u trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam &#273;ang ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c r&amp;agrave; so&amp;aacute;t c&amp;aacute;c kho&#7843;n chi ph&amp;iacute; c&#7845;u th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t nh&#7857;m minh b&#7841;ch gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng. H&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&#7873;u th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n nghi&amp;ecirc;m t&amp;uacute;c ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;o c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng v&amp;agrave; c&#7911;a Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911;, ni&amp;ecirc;m y&#7871;t, ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i gi&amp;aacute; nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7849;m &#7903; t&#7915;ng &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute; ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i theo t&#7915;ng ng&amp;agrave;y.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;','08/12/2011','09/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/hagia.jpg',23,2,1831,'huyennt',1,'thep-trong-nuoc-dang-ha-gia-de-tranh-ton-kho','th&eacute;p h&#7841; gi&aacute; &#273;&#7875; tr&aacute;nh t&#7891;n kho',NULL,NULL,NULL,'th&eacute;p h&#7841; gi&aacute; &#273;&#7875; tr&aacute;nh t&#7891;n kho',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - theo:http://www.xaydungvietnam.vn',1,0,0,0),(118,'Khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Ho&agrave;ng &#272;&igrave;nh Villa &#272;&agrave; l&#7841;t','Ho&agrave;ng &#272;&igrave;nh Villa l&agrave; d&#7921; &aacute;n khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; quy m&ocirc; l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t &#272;&agrave; L&#7841;t, kho&#7843;ng 76 ha, c&oacute; quy ho&#7841;ch t&#7893;ng th&#7875; v&#7899;i &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; c&aacute;c ph&acirc;n khu ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh ti&#7879;n &iacute;ch c&#7911;a m&#7897;t khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&#7903;i c&amp;ocirc;ng cu&amp;ocirc;&#769;i n&#259;m 2010 do C&amp;ocirc;ng ty TNHH &#272;&#7847;u t&#432; &amp;amp; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Ki&amp;ecirc;n Trung l&amp;agrave;m ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng v&#7889;n kho&#7843;ng 500 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng. D&#7921; &aacute;n c&amp;oacute; v&#7883; tr&iacute; &#273;&#7855;c &#273;&#7883;a, li&amp;ecirc;n k&#7871;t v&amp;ugrave;ng thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i, n&#7857;m trong quy ho&#7841;ch ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&#7911;a th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; &#272;&amp;agrave; L&#7841;t, g&#7847;n c&amp;aacute;c danh lam th&#7855;ng c&#7843;nh. Theo &#273;&amp;oacute;, Ho&agrave;ng &#272;&igrave;nh Villa n&#7857;m &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n ch&#7907; N&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7843;n &#272;&amp;agrave; L&#7841;t, g&#7847;n ch&amp;ugrave;a Linh Ph&#432;&#7899;c (ch&amp;ugrave;a Ve Chai), c&amp;aacute;ch &#7911;y ban nh&amp;acirc;n d&amp;acirc;n ph&#432;&#7901;ng 11 kho&#7843;ng 500 m, c&aacute;ch tr&#432;&#7901;ng ti&#7875;u h&#7885;c Tr&#7841;i M&amp;aacute;t kho&#7843;ng 1 km v&agrave; Trung t&amp;acirc;m &#272;&agrave; L&#7841;t kho&#7843;ng 5-6 km.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;352&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/Minh-Hoa-1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;D&#7921; &aacute;n c&oacute; m&amp;acirc;&#803;t &#273;&amp;ocirc;&#803; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng ch&#432;a &#273;&amp;ecirc;&#769;n 28%, khai th&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian c&amp;acirc;y xanh, r&#7915;ng c&#7843;nh quan, k&#7871;t h&#7907;p su&#7889;i c&amp;oacute; s&#7861;n &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o m&#7897;t khu v&#7921;c xanh bao quanh khu &#7903;, &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o t&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng ti&#7879;n nghi cho khu &#7903; v&#7873; m&#7863;t m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng c&#361;ng nh&#432; th&#7849;m m&#7929; ki&#7871;n tr&amp;uacute;c c&#7843;nh quan. Khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chia l&amp;agrave;m nhi&#7873;u ph&amp;acirc;n khu ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng, g&#7891;m c&amp;oacute; 130 l&amp;ocirc; &#273;&#7845;t nh&amp;agrave; li&amp;ecirc;n k&#7871; s&amp;acirc;n v&#432;&#7901;n, 276 l&amp;ocirc; nh&amp;agrave; bi&#7879;t l&#7853;p, 170 l&amp;ocirc; bi&#7879;t th&#7921; v&amp;agrave; 2,37 ha &#273;&#7845;t ch&#7881;nh trang.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nKhu th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i - D&#7883;ch v&#7909; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; t&#7841;i trung t&amp;acirc;m khu &#7903; t&#7841;o &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n tr&amp;ecirc;n tr&#7909;c ch&amp;iacute;nh c&#361;ng nh&#432; l&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n c&#7911;a to&amp;agrave;n b&#7897; khu &#7903;. T&#7893;ng di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch s&amp;agrave;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kho&#7843;ng 13.000 m2 bao g&amp;ocirc;&#768;m: kh&amp;aacute;ch s&#7841;n 5 t&#7847;ng, trung t&amp;acirc;m th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i, ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng, v&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng cho thu&amp;ecirc;, c&amp;aacute;c c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng b&amp;aacute;n l&#7867; .C&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng bao g&amp;ocirc;&#768;m: khu c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;acirc;y xanh kho&#7843;ng 12,3 ha, tr&#432;&#7901;ng m&#7847;m non, tr&#432;&#7901;ng c&#7845;p 1, tr&#7841;m y t&#7871;, khu th&#7875; d&#7909;c th&#7875; thao, khu vui ch&#417;i gi&#7843;i tr&amp;iacute; c&amp;oacute; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch t&#7899;i 17.000 m2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ho&agrave;ng &#272;&igrave;nh Villa &#272;&agrave; L&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&#7903;i c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave;o ng&amp;agrave;y 20/12. D&#7921; ki&#7871;n d&#7921; &aacute;n s&#7869; ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2016. Hi&amp;ecirc;&#803;n &#273;&amp;acirc;&#769;t n&amp;ecirc;&#768;n c&#7911;a d&#7921; &aacute;n &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&agrave;o b&aacute;n v&#7899;i gi&aacute; t&#7915; 3,8 &#273;&#7871;n 5,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng m&#7897;t m2. Ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&#361;ng cam k&#7871;t cao trong vi&#7879;c ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;aacute;p l&amp;yacute; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n r&amp;otilde; r&amp;agrave;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','08/12/2011','08/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/Minh-Hoa-1.jpg',28,8,2162,'huyennt',1,'khu-do-thi-moi-hoang-dinh-villa-da-lat','Khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Ho&agrave;ng &#272;&igrave;nh Villa &#272;&agrave; l&#7841;t',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Ho&agrave;ng &#272;&igrave;nh Villa &#272;&agrave; l&#7841;t',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://vnexpress.net',1,0,0,0),(119,'Las Vegas Sands d&#7921; t&iacute;nh x&acirc;y khu du l&#7883;ch 2 t&#7927; USD','Las Vegas Sands, khu ngh&#7881; d&#432;&#7905;ng, Marina Bay Sands, kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n, nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng, khu t&#7893; ch&#7913;c tri&#7875;n l&atilde;m, h&#7897;i ngh&#7883;, h&#7897;i ch&#7907;, khu mua s&#7855;m, spa, khu t&#7853;p th&#7875; thao, nh&agrave; h&aacute;t, b&#7843;o t&agrave;ng','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nChi&#7873;u 7/12, trong cu&#7897;c g&#7863;p B&amp;iacute; th&#432; Th&amp;agrave;nh &#7911;y Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; H&#7891; Ch&amp;iacute; Minh L&amp;ecirc; Thanh H&#7843;i, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch t&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n Las Vegas Sands, Sheldon Adelson, cho bi&#7871;t t&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n d&#7921; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7869; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng m&#7897;t khu du l&#7883;ch ph&#7913;c h&#7907;p t&#7841;i Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889;, v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng m&#7913;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i h&#417;n 2 t&#7927; USD.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTo&amp;agrave;n c&#7843;nh b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; khu ph&#7913;c h&#7907;p Marina Bay Sands c&#7911;a T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n Las Vegas Sands t&#7841;i Singapore. D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; quy m&amp;ocirc; v&amp;agrave; t&amp;iacute;nh ch&#7845;t t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; nh&#432; khu ngh&#7881; d&#432;&#7905;ng Marina Bay Sands c&#7911;a T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n Las Vegas Sands t&#7841;i Singapore, g&#7891;m khu kh&amp;aacute;ch s&#7841;n, nh&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;ng, khu t&#7893; ch&#7913;c tri&#7875;n l&amp;atilde;m, h&#7897;i ngh&#7883;, h&#7897;i ch&#7907;, khu mua s&#7855;m, spa, khu t&#7853;p th&#7875; thao, nh&amp;agrave; h&amp;aacute;t, b&#7843;o t&amp;agrave;ng v&amp;agrave; nhi&#7873;u lo&#7841;i h&amp;igrave;nh vui ch&#417;i, gi&#7843;i tr&amp;iacute; kh&amp;aacute;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;Ocirc;ng Adelson cho r&#7857;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam c&amp;oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u ti&#7873;m n&#259;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng nh&#7919;ng c&#417; s&#7903; du l&#7883;ch, ngh&#7881; d&#432;&#7905;ng ph&#7913;c h&#7907;p, kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; &#273;&#7875; thu h&amp;uacute;t kh&amp;aacute;ch du l&#7883;ch m&amp;agrave; c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; gi&amp;uacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam l&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7875;m &#273;&#7871;n cho c&amp;aacute;c h&#7897;i ngh&#7883;, h&#7897;i ch&#7907;, tri&#7875;n l&amp;atilde;m qu&#7889;c t&#7871;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch t&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n c&#361;ng cho bi&#7871;t Las Vegas Sands (nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng nh&#7919;ng khu du l&#7883;ch ph&#7913;c h&#7907;p l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t th&#7871; gi&#7899;i) mong mu&#7889;n h&#7907;p t&amp;aacute;c v&#7899;i Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; H&#7891; Ch&amp;iacute; Minh &#273;&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n m&amp;agrave; khi ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7869; mang t&amp;iacute;nh bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng cho Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889;, t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; nh&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh Marina Bay Sands t&#7841;i Singapore.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/thi-truong.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n t&#7841;i Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; H&#7891; Ch&amp;iacute; Minh hi&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; s&#417; b&#7897; v&#7899;i h&amp;igrave;nh m&#7851;u 2 t&amp;ograve;a nh&amp;agrave; h&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;aacute;nh bu&#7891;m tr&amp;ecirc;n n&#7873;n m&#7897;t hoa sen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;iacute; th&#432; Th&amp;agrave;nh &#7911;y Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; H&#7891; Ch&amp;iacute; Minh &#273;&amp;aacute;nh gi&amp;aacute; cao chuy&#7871;n th&#259;m Vi&#7879;t Nam v&amp;agrave; Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; H&#7891; Ch&amp;iacute; Minh &#273;&#7875; t&amp;igrave;m hi&#7875;u m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave; c&#417; h&#7897;i h&#7907;p t&amp;aacute;c c&#7911;a T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n Las Vegas Sands.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng L&amp;ecirc; Thanh H&#7843;i hoan ngh&amp;ecirc;nh &amp;yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng v&amp;agrave; d&#7921; t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave;o l&#297;nh v&#7921;c du l&#7883;ch, d&#7883;ch v&#7909; c&#7911;a Las Vegas Sands, b&#7903;i Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; H&#7891; Ch&amp;iacute; Minh l&amp;agrave; trung t&amp;acirc;m kinh t&#7871; l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; d&#7883;ch v&#7909; chi&#7871;m t&#7881; tr&#7885;ng l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t trong c&#417; c&#7845;u kinh t&#7871; th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889;, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; c&#7917;a ng&amp;otilde; giao th&#432;&#417;ng c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam v&#7899;i qu&#7889;c t&#7871;, nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; v&#7899;i khu v&#7921;c &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng Nam &amp;Aacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;L&amp;atilde;nh &#273;&#7841;o Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; H&#7891; Ch&amp;iacute; Minh c&#361;ng cho bi&#7871;t Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; mong mu&#7889;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&#7907;p t&amp;aacute;c v&#7899;i T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n Las Vegas Sands &#7903; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;oacute; quy m&amp;ocirc; l&#7899;n n&amp;agrave;y./.&lt;/p&gt;','08/12/2011','08/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/thi-truong.jpg',36,8,1945,'huyennt',1,'las-vegas-sands-du-tinh-xay-khu-du-lich-2-ty-usd',' Las Vegas Sands d&#7921; t&iacute;nh x&acirc;y khu du l&#7883;ch 2 t&#7927; USD',NULL,NULL,NULL,' Las Vegas Sands d&#7921; t&iacute;nh x&acirc;y khu du l&#7883;ch 2 t&#7927; USD',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(120,'Khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m: Ch&#7881; ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n nh&agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; l&#7899;n','D&#7921; &aacute;n x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m &#273;&#7871;n nay &#273;&atilde; ho&agrave;n t&#7845;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c 96% kh&#7889;i l&#432;&#7907;ng gi&#7843;i ph&oacute;ng m&#7863;t b&#7857;ng, sang n&#259;m 2012 s&#7869; b&#432;&#7899;c v&agrave;o giai &#273;o&#7841;n x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897; c&#417; s&#7903; h&#7841; t&#7847;ng &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n k&ecirc;u g&#7885;i nh&agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;; nh&#432;ng TPHCM ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng ch&#7881; ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n nh&agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; l&#7899;n.','\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/tuyen-duong-do-thi.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;Tuy&#7871;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&#7851;n t&#7915; &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7847;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;m Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m v&amp;agrave;o qu&#7853;n 2, TPHCM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;aacute;t bi&#7875;u tr&#432;&#7899;c phi&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7845;t v&#7845;n k&#7923; h&#7885;p th&#7913; 3 H&#272;ND th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; kh&amp;oacute;a VIII s&amp;aacute;ng nay (8-12), &amp;ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n H&#7919;u T&amp;iacute;n, Ph&amp;oacute; ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch UBND TPHCM cho bi&#7871;t nh&#432; v&#7853;y v&amp;agrave; kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh trong n&#259;m 2012, th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; s&#7869; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c 4 tuy&#7871;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ch&amp;iacute;nh t&#7841;i khu n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#7875; k&amp;ecirc;u g&#7885;i &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &amp;ocirc;ng T&amp;iacute;n, &#273;&#7871;n nay c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;m hi&#7875;u c&#417; h&#7897;i, nh&#432;ng th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng ch&#7881; ch&#7845;p thu&#7853;n c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; l&#7899;n, uy t&amp;iacute;n &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o l&#7921;c h&amp;uacute;t c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; l&#7899;n kh&amp;aacute;c tham gia ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n Anh Tu&#7845;n, Tr&#432;&#7903;ng ban Qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; Khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m, cho bi&#7871;t khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quy ho&#7841;ch th&amp;agrave;nh trung t&amp;acirc;m d&#7883;ch v&#7909;, th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i, ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7847;m c&#7905; qu&#7889;c t&#7871;. &#272;&#7871;n nay, &#273;&amp;atilde; di d&#7901;i h&#417;n 12.500 h&#7897; d&amp;acirc;n, ch&#432;a k&#7875; c&amp;aacute;c c&#417; s&#7903; t&amp;ocirc;n gi&amp;aacute;o, tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7885;c, ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n, hi&#7879;n c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i kho&#7843;ng 11 h&amp;eacute;c ta v&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&#417; s&#7903; t&amp;ocirc;n gi&amp;aacute;o ch&#432;a di d&#7901;i. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, c&amp;ograve;n 1.300 h&#7891; s&#417; c&#7847;n b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; nh&amp;agrave; t&amp;aacute;i &#273;&#7883;nh c&#432;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#432;&#7899;c m&#7855;t, theo &amp;ocirc;ng Tu&#7845;n, th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; s&#7869; k&amp;ecirc;u g&#7885;i &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; 3 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ch&amp;iacute;nh g&#7891;m: Khu trung t&amp;acirc;m t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;aacute;nh ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng; Khu d&amp;acirc;n c&#432; h&#7841; t&#7847;ng s&#7889; 3 v&amp;agrave; Khu ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m. Trong th&amp;aacute;ng 7-2012 s&#7869; ti&#7871;n h&amp;agrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng 3 tuy&#7871;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ch&amp;iacute;nh t&#7841;i khu v&#7921;c n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;T&#7915; nay &#273;&#7871;n 2015, ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i s&#7869; k&amp;ecirc;u g&#7885;i to&amp;agrave;n b&#7897; c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n trong khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m. T&#7915; 2008 &#273;&#7871;n nay, do suy tho&amp;aacute;i kinh t&#7871; n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7885;n ch&#432;a tri&#7875;n khai &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&amp;igrave; nhi&#7873;u. Ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i v&#7853;n &#273;&#7897;ng nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; l&#7899;n, c&amp;oacute; ngu&#7891;n v&#7889;n m&#7841;nh &#273;&#7875; tri&#7875;n khai c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n, hy v&#7885;ng trong v&amp;ograve;ng 5 n&#259;m t&#7899;i s&#7869; k&amp;ecirc;u g&#7885;i &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave;o khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ocirc;ng Tu&#7845;n n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;','09/12/2011','09/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/tuyen-duong-do-thi.jpg',28,8,1856,'huyennt',1,'khu-do-thi-moi-thu-thiem-chi-chap-nhan-nha-dau-tu-lon','nh&agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m',NULL,NULL,NULL,'nh&agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'http://www.diaoconline.vn',1,0,0,0),(121,'B&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u cho thu&ecirc; m&#7863;t b&#7857;ng Vincom Center A','C&ocirc;ng ty CP Vincom v&#7915;a ch&iacute;nh th&#7913;c c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; th&ocirc;ng tin d&#7921; &aacute;n Vincom Center A - khu t&#7913; gi&aacute;c Eden.','\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7899;i quy m&amp;ocirc; 6 t&#7847;ng ng&#7847;m v&amp;agrave; 9 t&#7847;ng n&#7893;i, d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n n&amp;agrave;y s&#7869; bao g&#7891;m: trung t&amp;acirc;m th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i &#273;&#7859;ng c&#7845;p qu&#7889;c t&#7871; c&amp;oacute; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch kho&#7843;ng 38.000 m2, kh&amp;aacute;ch s&#7841;n Vinpearl Luxury TP.HCM v&#432;&#7907;t chu&#7849;n 5 sao v&#7899;i g&#7847;n 300 ph&amp;ograve;ng v&amp;agrave; b&amp;atilde;i &#273;&#7853;u xe ng&#7847;m tr&amp;ecirc;n 25.000 m2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/eden.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nD&#7883;p n&amp;agrave;y, Vincom c&#361;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u cho thu&amp;ecirc; m&#7863;t b&#7857;ng TTTM n&#7857;m trong khu ph&#7913;c h&#7907;p c&#7911;a d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n k&#7875; t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u th&amp;aacute;ng 12.2011.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7901;i gian d&#7921; ki&#7871;n khai tr&#432;&#417;ng Vincom Center A TP.HCM l&amp;agrave; ng&amp;agrave;y 10.10.2012.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trao &#273;&#7893;i v&#7873; ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n, &amp;Ocirc;ng L&amp;ecirc; Kh&#7855;c Hi&#7879;p, Ph&amp;oacute; Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n Vingroup cho bi&#7871;t: &amp;ldquo;Vi&#7879;c Vingroup &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o t&#7889;t v&#7873; c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; v&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o &#273;&amp;uacute;ng cam k&#7871;t v&#7899;i kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng; gi&#7919; v&#7919;ng uy t&amp;iacute;n th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u &amp;ndash; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; m&amp;agrave; Vingroup lu&amp;ocirc;n &#273;&#7873; cao.Vi&#7879;c &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh thi c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave;o th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng g&#7863;p nhi&#7873;u thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i v&amp;igrave; ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i huy &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7889;i &#273;a ngu&#7891;n m&amp;aacute;y m&amp;oacute;c, c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i; nguy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u t&#7889;t v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; c&#7841;nh tranh v&amp;agrave; nh&amp;acirc;n l&#7921;c thi c&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cao c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u&amp;hellip;. Vi&#7879;c n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng gi&amp;uacute;p ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i chu&#7849;n b&#7883; s&#7861;n v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m, d&#7883;ch v&#7909; &#273;