#273;&#7875; vi&#7879;c x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p h&#417;n v&#7899;i &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n th&#7921;c t&#7871; v&amp;agrave; h&#7845;p d&#7851;n h&#417;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, Ban Qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m &#273;&amp;atilde; cho nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh c&#7909;c b&#7897; quy ho&#7841;ch chi ti&#7871;t 1/2000.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;MARGIN-RIGHT: 10px&quot; height=&quot;291&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/dothithuthiem.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; &quot;&gt;D&#7921; ki&#7871;n, quy ho&#7841;ch &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh theo h&#432;&#7899;ng t&#259;ng di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch s&amp;agrave;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng l&amp;ecirc;n kho&#7843;ng 40% so v&#7899;i d&amp;acirc;n s&#7889; t&#259;ng t&#7915; 120.000 ng&#432;&#7901;i l&amp;ecirc;n 160.000 ng&#432;&#7901;i. Trong qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh quy ho&#7841;ch, nh&#7919;ng d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p ph&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng nh&#432; khu t&amp;aacute;i &#273;&#7883;nh c&#432;, khu c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh c&#7911;a T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n GS&amp;hellip; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p v&amp;agrave;o quy ho&#7841;ch. Nguy&amp;ecirc;n t&#7855;c c&#417; b&#7843;n trong &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh quy ho&#7841;ch l&#7847;n n&amp;agrave;y: kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&amp;agrave;m thay &#273;&#7893;i t&amp;iacute;nh ch&#7845;t c&#7911;a &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#78