INSERT INTO `tblarticle` VALUES (127,'N&#259;m 2016 H&agrave; N&#7897;i m&#7899;i kh&eacute;p k&iacute;n c&aacute;c &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng v&agrave;nh &#273;ai','Theo Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch H&agrave; N&#7897;i Nguy&#7877;n Th&#7871; Th&#7843;o, n&#259;m t&#7899;i H&agrave; N&#7897;i s&#7869; &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; c&aacute;c d&#7921; &aacute;n &#273;&#7875; kh&eacute;p k&iacute;n v&agrave;nh &#273;ai 2 v&agrave; m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n v&agrave;nh &#273;ai 3. &#272;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2016, 3 tuy&#7871;n v&agrave;nh &#273;ai m&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ho&agrave;n ch&#7881;nh.','\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;236&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/vanh-dai3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;Thi c&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n cao t&#7841;i v&amp;agrave;nh &#273;ai 3.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#7843; l&#7901;i ch&#7845;t v&#7845;n c&#7917; tri v&#7873; c&amp;aacute;c tuy&#7871;n v&amp;agrave;nh &#273;ai &#273;ang ch&#7853;m ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897;, UBND th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;a ra l&#7897; tr&amp;igrave;nh tri&#7875;n khai.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &#273;&amp;oacute;, v&amp;agrave;nh &#273;ai 1 c&amp;oacute; chi&#7873;u d&amp;agrave;i 23 km, hi&#7879;n &#273;&amp;atilde; tri&#7875;n khai &#273;o&#7841;n &amp;Ocirc; &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng M&amp;aacute;c - Nguy&#7877;n Kho&amp;aacute;i d&amp;agrave;i 548 m, &#273;o&#7841;n &amp;Ocirc; Ch&#7907; D&#7915;a - Ho&amp;agrave;ng C&#7847;u d&amp;agrave;i 547 m v&amp;agrave; l&#7853;p d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;o&#7841;n Ho&amp;agrave;ng C&#7847;u - Voi Ph&#7909;c d&amp;agrave;i kho&#7843;ng 2,2 km.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;o&#7841;n &amp;Ocirc; &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng M&amp;aacute;c - Nguy&#7877;n Kho&amp;aacute;i b&#7883; ch&#7853;m ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; do quy ho&#7841;ch chi ti&#7871;t hai b&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ch&#7853;m, c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c gi&#7843;i ph&amp;oacute;ng m&#7863;t b&#7857;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n do c&#417; ch&#7871;, th&#7911; t&#7909;c &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n, &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh thi&#7871;t k&#7871; c&#7911;a ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;. Tuy&#7871;n n&amp;agrave;y &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7853;p quy ho&#7841;ch 1/500 &#273;&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897; tuy&#7871;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7899;i tuy&#7871;n ph&#7889; v&amp;agrave; tri&#7875;n khai gi&#7843;i ph&amp;oacute;ng m&#7863;t b&#7857;ng &#273;&#7875; thi c&amp;ocirc;ng n&#259;m 2012, ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh n&#259;m 2014.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;o&#7841;n &amp;Ocirc; Ch&#7907; D&#7915;a - Ho&amp;agrave;ng C&#7847;u &#273;&amp;atilde; ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh 80 m &#273;&#7847;u tuy&#7871;n ph&amp;iacute;a Ho&amp;agrave;ng C&#7847;u. Ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;ang thu h&#7891;i &#273;&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n b&#7891;i th&#432;&#7901;ng gi&#7843;i ph&amp;oacute;ng &#273;o&#7841;n c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i, d&#7921; ki&#7871;n ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh tr&#432;&#7899;c th&amp;aacute;ng 8/2012, x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh xong trong n&#259;m 2013.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;o&#7841;n Ho&amp;agrave;ng C&#7847;u - Voi Ph&#7909;c d&amp;agrave;i kho&#7843;ng 2,2 km &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c UBND th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; ch&#7845;p thu&#7853;n b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; v&#7889;n chu&#7849;n b&#7883; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;; d&#7921; ki&#7871;n ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n v&amp;agrave; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n thu h&#7891;i &#273;&#7845;t, c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh n&#259;m 2016.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy&#7871;n v&amp;agrave;nh &#273;ai 2 d&amp;agrave;i 43 km, t&#7915; &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng Nguy&#7877;n V&#259;n Linh - c&#7847;u V&#297;nh Tuy - Minh Khai - ph&#7889; &#272;&#7841;i La - Ng&amp;atilde; T&#432; V&#7885;ng - &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng Tr&#432;&#7901;ng Chinh - Ng&amp;atilde; T&#432; S&#7903; - &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng L&amp;aacute;ng - C&#7847;u Gi&#7845;y - B&#432;&#7903;i - L&#7841;c Long Qu&amp;acirc;n - C&#7847;u Nh&#7853;t T&amp;acirc;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; &#273;&amp;atilde; c&#7843;i t&#7841;o, m&#7903; r&#7897;ng ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;aacute;c &#273;o&#7841;n t&#7915; Ng&amp;atilde; T&#432; S&#7903; &#273;&#7871;n C&#7847;u Gi&#7845;y d&amp;agrave;i 4,5 km, &#273;o&#7841;n C&#7847;u Chui - V&#297;nh Tuy d&amp;agrave;i kho&#7843;ng 8,8 km.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c &#273;o&#7841;n c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i nh&#432; V&#297;nh Tuy - Ng&amp;atilde; t&#432; V&#7885;ng d&amp;agrave;i kho&#7843;ng 3,2 km, &#273;ang th&#7849;m &#273;&#7883;nh ch&#7881; gi&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7887;, d&#7921; ki&#7871;n ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n trong n&#259;m 2012, d&#7921; ki&#7871;n ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh n&#259;m 2016. T&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921;, &#273;o&#7841;n Ng&amp;atilde; T&#432; V&#7885;ng - Ng&amp;atilde; T&#432; S&#7903; c&#361;ng &#273;&#7863;t k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch to&amp;agrave;n t&#7845;t n&#259;m 2016.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;o&#7841;n Nh&#7853;t T&amp;acirc;n - Xu&amp;acirc;n La - B&#432;&#7903;i - C&#7847;u Gi&#7845;y d&amp;agrave;i 6,4 km &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ngu&#7891;n v&#7889;n vay c&#7911;a Ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng th&#7871; gi&#7899;i, &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; thi c&amp;ocirc;ng, &#273;&#7875; kh&#7903;i c&amp;ocirc;ng trong qu&amp;yacute; I/2012, ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh n&#259;m 2015.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong v&amp;agrave;nh &#273;ai 2 c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n cao &#273;o&#7841;n V&#297;nh Tuy - Ng&amp;atilde; T&#432; V&#7885;ng d&amp;agrave;i 3,2 km, d&#7921; ki&#7871;n kh&#7903;i c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave;o qu&amp;yacute; 4 n&#259;m sau v&amp;agrave; ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh n&#259;m 2014.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy&#7871;n v&amp;agrave;nh &#273;ai 3 d&amp;agrave;i kho&#7843;ng 65 km, t&#7915; c&#7847;u Th&#259;ng Long - Mai D&#7883;ch - Thanh Xu&amp;acirc;n - Ph&amp;aacute;p V&amp;acirc;n - c&#7847;u Thanh Tr&amp;igrave; - S&amp;agrave;i &#272;&#7891;ng - c&#7847;u Ph&amp;ugrave; &#272;&#7893;ng 2 (v&#432;&#7907;t s&amp;ocirc;ng &#272;u&#7889;ng) - giao v&#7899;i qu&#7889;c l&#7897; 1 c&#361; - giao &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng 18 v&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng B&#7855;c Th&#259;ng Long - N&#7897;i B&amp;agrave;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&amp;ecirc;n tuy&#7871;n n&amp;agrave;y &#273;ang tri&#7875;n khai d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n cao Mai D&#7883;ch - b&#7855;c h&#7891; Linh &#272;&amp;agrave;m do &#273;&#432;&#7907;c B&#7897; Giao th&amp;ocirc;ng V&#7853;n t&#7843;i ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t, d&#7921; ki&#7871;n ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh n&#259;m 2012.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, &#273;o&#7841;n Mai D&#7883;ch - c&#7847;u Th&#259;ng Long s&#7869; tri&#7875;n khai &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; n&#259;m 2013 v&amp;agrave; &#273;o&#7841;n Ninh Hi&#7879;p &#273;&#7871;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng B&#7855;c Th&#259;ng Long - N&#7897;i B&amp;agrave;i &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, d&#7921; ki&#7871;n tri&#7875;n khai t&#7915; n&#259;m 2013, ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh n&#259;m 2016.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c tuy&#7871;n v&amp;agrave;nh &#273;ai ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7869; gi&amp;uacute;p ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#787