h&amp;ograve;a h&#7907;p v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng th&#7875; trang tr&amp;iacute; c&#7911;a Parkson.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/hinh-anh/giovani3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nShowroom s&#7889; 193 Ph&#7889; Hu&#7871; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c khai tr&#432;&#417;ng v&amp;agrave;o ng&amp;agrave;y 6/12. &#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; tuy&#7871;n ph&#7889; trung t&amp;acirc;m c&#7911;a th&#7911; &#273;&amp;ocirc; H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i, &#273;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m thu&#7853;n ti&#7879;n n&amp;agrave;y s&#7869; thay th&#7871; cho showroom t&#7841;i s&#7889; 45 Tu&#7879; T&#297;nh c&#7911;a Giovanni tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;oacute;. L&#7847;n &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;oacute; m&#7863;t t&#7841;i c&#7917;a ng&amp;otilde; ph&amp;iacute;a &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7911;a H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i, gian h&amp;agrave;ng Giovanni t&#7841;i trung t&amp;acirc;m th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i Savico Mega Mall b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u &#273;&amp;oacute;n kh&amp;aacute;ch t&#7915; ng&amp;agrave;y 1/12 v&amp;agrave; khai tr&#432;&#417;ng ng&amp;agrave;y 16/12.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/hinh-anh/giovani2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nM&#7915;ng khai tr&#432;&#417;ng, h&amp;atilde;ng c&amp;oacute; ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh khuy&#7871;n m&#7841;i d&amp;agrave;nh cho kh&amp;aacute;ch. Theo &#273;&amp;oacute;, t&#7841;i Parkson Landmark, ng&amp;agrave;y 2/12, Giovanni gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; 10% c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m nguy&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;aacute; d&amp;agrave;nh cho &#273;&#7891; nam v&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;m 20% c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m nguy&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;aacute; d&amp;agrave;nh cho &#273;&#7891; n&#7919;. T&#7841;i s&#7889; 193 Ph&#7889; Hu&#7871;, ng&amp;agrave;y 6/12, h&amp;atilde;ng gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; 20% cho t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m nguy&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;aacute;; t&#7915; ng&amp;agrave;y 7 &#273;&#7871;n 31/12, h&amp;atilde;ng gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; 10% t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m nguy&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;aacute;. T&#7841;i Savico Mega Mall, t&#7915; ng&amp;agrave;y 1 &#273;&#7871;n 31/12, Giovanni gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; 10% t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m nguy&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;aacute;. Ri&amp;ecirc;ng trong ng&amp;agrave;y khai tr&#432;&#417;ng 16/12, h&amp;atilde;ng gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; 20% t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;677&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/hinh-anh/giovani1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNh&amp;acirc;n s&#7921; ki&#7879;n n&amp;agrave;y, Giovanni gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u t&#7899;i kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng nh&#7919;ng b&#7897; s&#432;u t&#7853;p th&#7901;i trang thu &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng m&#7899;i nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a h&amp;atilde;ng: sang tr&#7885;ng v&#7899;i &amp;aacute;o len, tr&#7867; trung n&#259;ng &#273;&#7897;ng c&amp;ugrave;ng &amp;aacute;o kho&amp;aacute;c, l&#7883;ch l&amp;atilde;m v&#7899;i &amp;aacute;o vest v&amp;agrave; &amp;aacute;o d&#7841;. H&#417;n 4 n&#259;m k&#7875; t&#7915; ng&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;oacute; m&#7863;t t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam, Giovanni c&amp;oacute; m&#7863;t &#7903; nhi&#7873;u t&#7881;nh th&amp;agrave;nh trong c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c (H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i, TP HCM, H&#7843;i Ph&amp;ograve;ng, Qu&#7843;ng Ninh, Thanh H&amp;oacute;a, Vinh, Nha Trang...).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','13/12/2011','13/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/hinh-anh/giovani3.jpg',48,11,193,'huyennt',1,'giovanni-khai-truong-3-showroom-moi-tai-ha-noi',' Giovanni khai tr&#432;&#417;ng 3 showroom m&#7899;i t&#7841;i H&agrave; N&#7897;i, showroom',NULL,NULL,NULL,' Giovanni khai tr&#432;&#417;ng 3 showroom m&#7899;i t&#7841;i H&agrave; N&#7897;i, showroom',0,0,1,'18/01/2012','','',3,'http://vnexpress.net',1,0,0,0),(129,'&#272;&oacute;n Gi&aacute;ng Sinh c&ugrave;ng tone m&agrave;u &#273;&#7887;','Trang tr&iacute; Gi&aacute;ng Sinh v&#7899;i ph&#7909; ki&#7879;n m&agrave;u &#273;&#7887; l&agrave; c&aacute;ch hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; nh&#7845;t &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m n&#7893;i b&#7853;t kh&ocirc;ng gian s&#7889;ng gia &#273;&igrave;nh b&#7841;n trong ng&agrave;y l&#7877; n&agrave;y.','&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c t&#432;&#417;i t&#7855;n v&#7899;i h&amp;igrave;nh d&#7841;ng d&#7877; th&#432;&#417;ng c&#7911;a &#273;&#7891; trang tr&amp;iacute; Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh , c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7875; trang tr&amp;iacute; c&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng Noel, trang tr&amp;iacute; ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n, ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch, v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; &#273;&#7875; ch&amp;agrave;o &#273;&amp;oacute;n Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh s&#7855;p t&#7899;i. &#272;&#7891; d&amp;ugrave;ng trang tr&amp;iacute; th&#432;&#7901;ng l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng qu&#7843; b&amp;oacute;ng nh&#7887;, &#273;&#7891; ch&#417;i, tay c&#7847;m &amp;ocirc;, tranh v&#7869;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7899;i tone m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;agrave;y, c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng s&#7869; tr&#7903; n&amp;ecirc;n n&amp;oacute;ng b&#7887;ng, quy&#7871;n r&#361; v&amp;agrave; sang tr&#7885;ng h&#417;n bao gi&#7901; h&#7871;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; bi&#7871;t r&amp;otilde; h&#417;n, c&amp;aacute;c b&#7841;n h&amp;atilde;y xem c&amp;aacute;c &amp;yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng sau &#273;&amp;acirc;y v&amp