5; ch&uacute;ng th&#7853;t th&uacute; v&#7883;, &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&aacute;o v&agrave; kh&aacute;c bi&#7879;t?','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng s&#7855;c m&amp;agrave;u&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;490&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/can-bep.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t c&#259;n b&#7871;p v&#7899;i b&#7879; b&#7871;p l&amp;agrave;m b&#7857;ng th&amp;eacute;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng g&#7881;, m&#7897;t chi&#7871;c tivi treo t&#432;&#7901;ng hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng m&amp;agrave;u xanh t&#7887;a t&#7915; ph&amp;iacute;a b&#7891;n r&#7917;a ra b&#7871;p n&#7845;u; chi&#7871;c b&amp;agrave;n &#259;n v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c ph&#7909; ki&#7879;n nhi&#7873;u m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c... T&#7845;t c&#7843; khi&#7871;n cho gian b&#7871;p ki&amp;ecirc;m ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n tr&#7903; n&amp;ecirc;n th&#7853;t &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng linh ho&#7841;t&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/nha-dep-1_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&#7841;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &amp;quot;c&#417;i n&#7899;i&amp;quot; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian cho ph&amp;ograve;ng b&#7871;p - ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n th&amp;ecirc;m tho&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&amp;atilde;ng v&#7899;i m&amp;agrave;u s&amp;aacute;ng, b&amp;oacute;ng. B&amp;agrave;n gh&#7871;, &#273;&amp;egrave;n, &#273;&#7891; d&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7853;t d&#7909;ng kh&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7873;u &amp;quot;&#432;u &amp;aacute;i&amp;quot; m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t chi&#7871;c b&amp;agrave;n &#259;n c&amp;oacute; g&#7855;n b&amp;aacute;nh xe s&#7869; l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;ch tuy&#7879;t v&#7901;i &#273;&#7875; b&#7841;n d&#7877; d&amp;agrave;ng s&#7855;p x&#7871;p c&#259;n b&#7871;p - ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n m&#7897;t c&amp;aacute;ch linh &#273;&#7897;ng t&amp;ugrave;y th&amp;iacute;ch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng nam t&amp;iacute;nh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/nha-dep-2_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;ograve;ng b&#7871;p n&amp;agrave;y mang d&amp;aacute;ng d&#7845;p m&#7897;t qu&#7847;y bar. &#272;&#7891; &#273;&#7841;c s&#7855;p x&#7871;p r&#7845;t &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n, kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; t&#7911; b&#7871;p hay nhi&#7873;u v&#7853;t d&#7909;ng xung quanh. &amp;Aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng t&#7921; nhi&amp;ecirc;n v&amp;agrave; &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&amp;egrave;n h&amp;agrave;i h&amp;ograve;a khi&#7871;n c&#259;n b&#7871;p - ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n n&amp;agrave;y r&#7845;t c&amp;aacute; t&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;oacute;ng kho&amp;aacute;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng nh&amp;igrave;n ra v&#432;&#7901;n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;476&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/nha-dep-3_4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u nh&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t khu v&#432;&#7901;n th&amp;igrave; c&amp;ograve;n g&amp;igrave; th&amp;uacute; v&#7883; b&#7857;ng vi&#7879;c ng&#7891;i &#259;n v&amp;agrave; ng&#7855;m nh&amp;igrave;n tr&#7901;i &#273;&#7845;t c&amp;acirc;y c&#7887;. M&#7897;t c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng b&#7871;p, ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n v&#7899;i r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; t&#7921; nhi&amp;ecirc;n s&#7869; gi&amp;uacute;p b&#7919;a &#259;n tr&#7903; n&amp;ecirc;n ngon l&amp;agrave;nh, th&amp;uacute; v&#7883;. V&#7899;i m&#7897;t ph&amp;ograve;ng th&#7871; n&amp;agrave;y, m&amp;agrave;u xanh tr&#7855;ng lu&amp;ocirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#432;u ti&amp;ecirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng tr&#7855;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;505&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/nha-dep-4_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&amp;iacute;ch b&#7871;p n&#7889;i li&#7873;n v&#7899;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian &#259;n u&#7889;ng, b&#7841;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&#7897;t b&#7913;c t&#432;&#7901;ng tr&#7855;ng nh&#7887; ch&#7855;n qua nh&#432; trong h&amp;igrave;nh. Ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n - b&#7871;p m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng nh&#432; th&#7871; n&amp;agrave;y th&#7921;c s&#7921; khi&#7871;n m&#7885;i th&#7913; tr&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7841;ch s&#7869; v&amp;agrave; d&#7877; ch&#7883;u. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, c&amp;aacute;c th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n trong gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh c&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; t&#7853;n d&#7909;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#7875; h&#7885;c h&amp;agrave;nh, vui ch&#417;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng g&#7895;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/nha-dep-5_6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7891; b&#7857;ng g&#7895; lu&amp;ocirc;n mang l&#7841;i v&#7867; sang tr&#7885;ng m&amp;agrave; c&#7893; &#273;i&#7875;n. G&#7895; t&#7921; nhi&amp;ecirc;n k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i th&amp;eacute;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng g&#7881; trong c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n m&#7897;t c&amp;aacute;i nh&amp;igrave;n d&#7877; ch&#7883;u cho c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng retro&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/nha-dep-6_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng v&#7853;t d&#7909;ng trang tr&amp;iacute;, &#273;&#7891; d&amp;ugrave;ng ki&#7875;u vintage s&#7869; khi&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;c th&#7921;c kh&amp;aacute;ch gh&amp;eacute; qua c&#7843;m th&#7845;y &#7845;m c&amp;uacute;ng v&amp;agrave; th&amp;iacute;ch th&amp;uacute;. N&amp;oacute; t&#7841;o cho kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian b&#7871;p v&amp;agrave; &#259;n u&#7889;ng s&#7921; y&amp;ecirc;n b&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng &#273;&#417;n s&#7855;c&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;522&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/nha-dep-7_4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng nhi&#7873;u m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c, m&#7897;t c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; 2 m&amp;agrave;u &#273;en tr&#7855;ng c&#361;ng r&#7845;t th&amp;uacute; v&#7883;. T&#7915; b&amp;agrave;n gh&#7871;, th&#7843;m t&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c b&#7913;c &#7843;nh treo t&#432;&#7901;ng, t&#7845;t c&#7843; &#273;&#7873;u ton sur ton.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&#272;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n v&#7899;i m&amp;agrave;u xanh l&amp;aacute;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/nha-dep-8_4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng ch&#7911; y&#7871;u m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng c&amp;oacute; &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n m&amp;agrave;u xanh l&amp;aacute; s&#7869; g&#7907;i l&amp;ecirc;n s&#7921; t&#432;&#417;i m&amp;aacute;t cho c&#259;n b&#7871;p c&#7911;a gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng chi&#7871;t trung&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;551&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/nha-dep-9_3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng theo khu&amp;ocirc;n ph&amp;eacute;p &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7861;n n&amp;agrave;o, h&amp;agrave;i h&amp;ograve;a gi&#7919;a c&#7893; &#273;i&#7875;n, hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, duy t&amp;acirc;m, duy v&#7853;t s&#7869; t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n b&#7845;t ng&#7901; hi&#7871;m th&#7845;y. H&amp;atilde;y th&#7917; xem c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng trong h&amp;igrave;nh v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;c b&#7843;n &#273;&#7891;, khung &#7843;nh, &#273;&#7891; v&#7853;t, gi&amp;aacute; treo... c&amp;oacute; ai ngh&#297; r&#7857;ng &#273;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian b&#7871;p v&amp;agrave; &#259;n u&#7889;ng?&lt;/p&gt;','13/12/2011','13/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/can-bep.jpg',38,11,2357,'huyennt',1,'nhung-can-bep-dep-lung-linh','phong bep, phong an, khong gian, b&#7843;n &#273;&#7891;, khung &#7843;nh, &#273;&#7891; v&#7853;t, gi&aacute; treo, kh&ocirc;ng gian &#273;&#7865;p, khong gian',NULL,NULL,NULL,'phong bep, phong an, khong gian, b&#7843;n &#273;&#7891;, khung &#7843;nh, &#273;&#7891; v&#7853;t, gi&aacute; treo, kh&ocirc;ng gian &#273;&#7865;p, khong gian',0,0,0,'','','',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - theo: http://dothi.net/',1,0,0,0),(131,'Gi&aacute; tr&#7883; sinh th&aacute;i trong ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c nh&agrave; v&#432;&#7901;n','Phong c&aacute;ch ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c nh&agrave; v&#432;&#7901;n l&agrave; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&#7911;a ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c nh&agrave; v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng gian v&#432;&#7901;n sao cho hai kh&ocirc;ng gian &#273;&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;an xen l&#7851;n nhau &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c g&#7847;n g&#361;i v&#7899;i thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;Bi&#7879;t th&#7921; nh&amp;agrave; v&#432;&#7901;n m&#7897;t v&amp;agrave;i n&#259;m tr&#7903; l&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y tr&#7903; th&amp;agrave;nh xu h&#432;&#7899;ng ngh&#7881; ng&#417;i t&#297;nh d&#432;&#7905;ng c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;oacute; &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n, phong c&amp;aacute;ch chung c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng c&#259;n bi&#7879;t th&#7921; v&#432;&#7901;n n&amp;agrave;y th&#432;&#7901;ng nghi&amp;ecirc;ng v&#7873; t&amp;iacute;nh ch&#7845;t d&amp;acirc;n gi&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7875; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; c&#7843;m nh&#7853;n h&#7871;t nh&#7919;ng d&#7921; v&#7883; m&#7897;c m&#7841;c c&#7911;a th&amp;ocirc;n qu&amp;ecirc;. C&#7909; th&#7875; l&amp;agrave; nh&amp;agrave; g&#7895;, ho&#7863;c x&amp;acirc;y m&#7897;t t&#7847;ng chia khu ri&amp;ecirc;ng bi&#7879;t nh&#432;ng v&#7851;n c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; k&#7871;t n&#7889;i t&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian v&#7899;i nhau.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i y&amp;ecirc;u th&amp;iacute;ch cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng ti&#7879;n nghi, hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i th&amp;igrave; vi&#7879;c &#273;&#432;a ra m&#7897;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871; ki&#7871;n tr&amp;uacute;c nh&amp;agrave; v&#432;&#7901;n &#273;i theo h&#432;&#7899;ng n&amp;agrave;y m&amp;agrave; v&#7851;n t&#7841;o c&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;c nh&#7865; nh&amp;agrave;ng, tho&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&amp;atilde;ng l&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; g&amp;igrave; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n. &#272;&#417;n gi&#7843;n nh&#432; m&#7851;u ki&#7871;n tr&amp;uacute;c nh&amp;agrave; v&#432;&#7901;n d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/biet-thu-vuon1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nKh&amp;aacute;c v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ng&amp;ocirc;i bi&#7879;t th&#7921; mang phong c&amp;aacute;ch th&amp;ocirc;n qu&amp;ecirc; kh&amp;aacute;c, bi&#7879;t th&#7921; v&#432;&#7901;n tr&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;oacute; c&amp;aacute;ch thi&#7871;t k&#7871; kh&amp;aacute; &#7845;n t&#432;&#7907;ng, m&#7897;t ch&amp;uacute;t g&amp;igrave; &#273;&amp;oacute; &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n, sang tr&#7885;ng pha l&#7851;n v&#7899;i n&amp;eacute;t m&#7897;c m&#7841;c c&#7911;a c&#7887; c&amp;acirc;y, non n&#432;&#7899;c. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; trong l&amp;agrave;nh, tho&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&amp;atilde;ng c&#7911;a m&#7897;t v&amp;ugrave;ng qu&amp;ecirc; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i thi&#7871;t k&#7871; v&#7919;ng ch&amp;atilde;i, ti&#7879;n nghi khi&#7871;n cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng c&#7911;a con ng&#432;&#7901;i gi&#7889;ng nh&#432; tr&amp;ecirc;n thi&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ngo&amp;agrave;i s&#7921; kh&amp;aacute;c nhau v&#7873; c&amp;aacute;ch th&#7875; hi&#7879;n (h&amp;igrave;nh th&#7913;c, ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u), bi&#7879;t th&#7921; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; c&amp;aacute;ch b&amp;agrave;i tr&amp;iacute;, b&#7889; c&#7909;c ho&amp;agrave;n to&amp;agrave;n kh&amp;aacute;c so v&#7899;i bi&#7879;t th&#7921; v&#432;&#7901;n d&amp;acirc;n d&amp;atilde;. T&#7893; h&#7907;p n&amp;agrave;y bao g&#7891;m ph&amp;ograve;ng sinh ho&#7841;t chung, 3 ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; v&amp;agrave; b&#7871;p &#259;n k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i khu v&#7921;c ph&#7909; kh&amp;aacute;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/biet-thu-vuon2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nC&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian s&#7917; d&#7909;ng trong nh&amp;agrave; ph&amp;acirc;n chia ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng r&amp;otilde; r&amp;agrave;ng nh&#432;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng t&#7841;o c&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;c t&amp;aacute;ch bi&#7879;t nhi&#7873;u. &#7902; &#273;&amp;acirc;y ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch v&amp;agrave; b&#7871;p &#259;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; trong c&amp;ugrave;ng m&#7897;t kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian m&amp;agrave; k&#7871;t n&#7889;i v&#7899;i nhau b&#7857;ng hi&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;agrave; v&amp;agrave; l&#7889;i s&#7843;nh nh&#7887;. Ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c coi l&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian ri&amp;ecirc;ng t&#432; k&amp;iacute;n &#273;&amp;aacute;o nh&#432;ng v&#7899;i ki&#7875;u bi&#7879;t th&#7921; v&#432;&#7901;n th&amp;igrave; ch&amp;uacute;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; m&#7903; v&#7899;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian b&amp;ecirc;n ngo&amp;agrave;i, t&#7915; c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng m&#7903; nhi&#7873;u g&amp;oacute;c view ra c&amp;aacute;c khu v&#7921;c xung quanh nh&#432; s&amp;acirc;n v&#432;&#7901;n, h&#7891; n&#432;&#7899;c&amp;hellip;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/biet-thu-vuon3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nH&amp;igrave;nh kh&#7889;i ki&#7871;n tr&amp;uacute;c, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; ph&#432;&#417;ng ti&#7879;n th&#7875; hi&#7879;n n&amp;eacute;t l&#7883;ch l&amp;atilde;m, sang tr&#7885;ng v&amp;agrave; ti&#7879;n nghi cho bi&#7879;t th&#7921;. Bi&#7879;t th&#7921; n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng thi&amp;ecirc;n v&#7873; nhi&#7873;u chi ti&#7871;t m&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&#7843;ng mi&#7871;ng t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n n&amp;eacute;t &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&amp;aacute;o cho kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian ki&#7871;n tr&amp;uacute;c. Kh&#7889;i nh&amp;agrave; vu&amp;ocirc;ng v&#7855;n k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i m&amp;aacute;i ngang l&#7899;n, c&#7917;a k&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng &amp;ocirc; c&#7917;a s&#7893; nh&#7887; t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;i nh&amp;igrave;n &#7845;n t&#432;&#7907;ng, r&#7845;t &amp;ldquo;t&amp;acirc;y&amp;rdquo; m&amp;agrave; v&#7851;n h&amp;agrave;i ho&amp;agrave; v&#7899;i khung c&#7843;nh xung quanh c&#7911;a ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/biet-thu-vuon4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nHi&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;agrave; r&#7897;ng l&#7899;n m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n n&#7857;m tr&amp;ecirc;n m&#7863;t n&#432;&#7899;c, l&#7889;i v&amp;agrave;o nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; u&#7889;n l&#432;&#7907;n d&#7851;n v&amp;agrave;o trong nh&amp;agrave;. C&amp;aacute;c gam m&amp;agrave;u t&#432;&#417;i s&#7863;c s&#7905; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; d&#7909;ng b&#7903;i ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;atilde; n&#7857;m gi&#7919;a kho&#7843;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng xanh ng&amp;aacute;t, mu&amp;ocirc;n m&amp;agrave;u mu&amp;ocirc;n v&#7867; c&#7911;a thi&amp;ecirc;n nhi&amp;ecirc;n.&lt;/p&gt;','14/12/2011','14/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/biet-thu-vuon1.jpg',38,11,2519,'huyennt',1,'gia-tri-sinh-thai-trong-kien-truc-nha-vuon',' nh&agrave; v&#432;&#7901;n, sinh th&aacute;i, n&#7897;i th&#7845;t, hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i',NULL,NULL,NULL,' nh&agrave; v&#432;&#7901;n, sinh th&aacute;i, n&#7897;i th&#7845;t, hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - theo: http://dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(132,'Mang kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; gi&aacute;ng sinh v&agrave;o nh&agrave;','Gi&aacute;ng sinh v&agrave; T&#7871;t &#273;ang t&#7899;i g&#7847;n, mang theo h&#417;i &#7845;m t&#7915; &aacute;nh &#273;&egrave;n lung linh, c&#7911;a m&agrave;u &#273;&#7887; r&#7921;c r&#7905;, c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng t&#7845;m thi&#7879;p tr&agrave;n &#273;&#7847;y l&#7901;i y&ecirc;u th&#432;&#417;ng... H&atilde;y mang kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; &#7845;m &aacute;p c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng ng&agrave;y l&#7877; v&agrave;o trong ng&ocirc;i nh&agrave; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n nh&eacute;.','\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; &quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. L&amp;agrave;m c&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng Noel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng d&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#432; l&amp;agrave; linh h&#7891;n c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;y l&#7877; Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh. Sau khi ch&#7885;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t c&amp;acirc;y &#432;ng &amp;yacute;, b&#7841;n h&amp;atilde;y trang tr&amp;iacute; v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ch&amp;uacute; chim b&#7891; c&amp;acirc;u b&#7857;ng v&#7843;i, h&amp;igrave;nh tr&amp;aacute;i tim, ng&amp;ocirc;i sao, ... cho th&#7853;t r&#7921;c r&#7905;. H&amp;atilde;y &#273;&#7875; m&#7885;i th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n trong gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh v&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&amp;aacute;ch c&#7843;m nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; &#7845;m &amp;aacute;p trong ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch, b&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;ch b&#7885;c v&#7843;i gh&#7871; sofa, gh&#7871; b&amp;agrave;nh b&#7857;ng nh&#7919;ng m&amp;agrave;u vui v&#7867; nh&#432; &#273;&#7887;, v&amp;agrave;ng, ... v&amp;agrave; th&amp;ecirc;m nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;c g&#7889;i &amp;ocirc;m b&#7857;ng v&#7843;i &#7845;m &amp;aacute;p n&#7919;a.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;500&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/tao-kkhi-am-ap-giang-sinh.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/tao-kkhi-am-ap-giang-sinh-1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Trang tr&amp;iacute; t&#432;&#7901;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&#7841;n ch&#7881; c&#7847;n trang tr&amp;iacute; t&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n b&#7857;ng gi&#7845;y d&amp;aacute;n t&#432;&#7901;ng ho&#7863;c c&amp;aacute;c sticker c&amp;oacute; h&amp;igrave;nh in hoa v&#259;n vui nh&#7897;n, hay h&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng, vv... nh&#7919;ng th&#7913; li&amp;ecirc;n quan t&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/tao-kkhi-am-ap-giang-sinh2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;3. Treo thi&#7879;p c&#7855;t lazer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Thi&#7879;p c&#7855;t lazer r&#7845;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c y&amp;ecirc;u th&amp;iacute;ch trong Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh n&#259;m nay. B&#7841;n ch&#7881; c&#7847;n m&amp;oacute;c v&amp;agrave;o s&#7907;i d&amp;acirc;y treo l&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;aacute; s&amp;aacute;ch, xen k&#7869; c&amp;ugrave;ng nh&#7919;ng h&amp;igrave;nh tr&amp;aacute;i tim.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/tao-kkhi-am-ap-giang-sinh-3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. Trang tr&amp;iacute; b&#7857;ng chim gi&#7845;y&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7921; l&amp;agrave;m chim gi&#7845;y handmade r&#7845;t nhanh v&amp;agrave; th&amp;uacute; v&#7883;. B&#7841;n h&amp;atilde;y t&amp;ugrave;y ch&#7881;nh m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c h&#7885;a ti&#7871;t trang tr&amp;iacute; cho ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7875; treo l&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng nh&amp;eacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/tao-kkhi-am-ap-giang-sinh-4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. Trang tr&amp;iacute; b&#7857;ng nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;c t&#7845;t&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;H&amp;atilde;y l&amp;agrave;m &amp;quot;&#7845;m&amp;quot; kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; Noel b&#7857;ng nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;c t&#7845;t r&#7921;c r&#7905; n&amp;agrave;y nh&amp;eacute;. B&#7841;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; mua, ho&#7863;c t&#7921; l&amp;agrave;m, c&#361;ng r&#7845;t &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/tao-kkhi-am-ap-giang-sinh5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/tao-kkhi-am-ap-giang-sinh-6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. Trang tr&amp;iacute; trong ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911;, h&amp;atilde;y k&#7871;t 1 v&amp;ograve;ng hoa t&#7915; t&#7921; nhi&amp;ecirc;n nh&#432; hoa, l&amp;aacute;, v&amp;agrave; xen k&#7869; l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;c b&amp;iacute;t t&#7845;t m&amp;agrave;u &#273;&#7887;, &#273;&amp;ocirc;i tu&#7847;n l&#7897;c. Tr&#7843;i nh&#7919;ng t&#7845;m ch&#259;n, ga b&#7857;ng v&#7843;i len &#273;&#7887;, th&amp;ecirc;m nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;c g&#7889;i m&amp;agrave;u &#273;&#7887; &#7845;m &amp;aacute;p. Ho&#7863;c b&#7841;n c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; treo &#273;&amp;egrave;n trong ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; n&#7919;a.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/tao-kkhi-am-ap-giang-sinh-7.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n7. &amp;quot;May &amp;aacute;o&amp;quot; cho c&#7917;a s&#7893;, b&amp;agrave;n &#259;n v&amp;agrave; ch&#7909;p &#273;&amp;egrave;n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Thay cho c&#7917;a s&#7893; t&#7845;m r&amp;egrave;m m&#7899;i b&#7857;ng m&amp;agrave;u &#273;&#7887; v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng h&amp;igrave;nh tr&amp;aacute;i tim m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng theo phong c&amp;aacute;ch d&amp;acirc;n gian. Chi&#7871;c r&amp;egrave;m c&#7917;a n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; thay cho t&#7899;i T&#7871;t, mang l&#7841;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; th&#7853;t &#7845;m &amp;aacute;p v&amp;agrave; may m&#7855;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/tao-kkhi-am-ap-giang-sinh-8.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCh&#7885;n gi&#7845;y d&amp;aacute;n t&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7857;ng l&#7909;a c&amp;oacute; h&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&amp;ocirc;i tu&#7847;n l&#7897;c, h&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng Noel &#273;&#7875; ph&#7911; ngo&amp;agrave;i ch&#7909;p &#273;&amp;egrave;n, b&#7841;n s&#7869; th&#7845;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; b&amp;agrave;n &#259;n kh&amp;aacute;c h&#7859;n. T&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; v&#7899;i chi&#7871;c b&amp;agrave;n &#259;n, h&amp;atilde;y thay kh&#259;n tr&#7843;i b&amp;agrave;n th&amp;ecirc;u nh&#7919;ng h&amp;igrave;nh hoa v&#259;n &#273;&#7865;p m&#7855;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/tao-kkhi-am-ap-giang-sinh-9.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n','14/12/2011','14/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/tao-kkhi-am-ap-giang-sinh-1.jpg',38,11,2350,'huyennt',1,'mang-khong-khi-giang-sinh-vao-nha','kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; gi&aacute;ng sinh, mang kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; gi&aacute;ng sinh v&agrave; t&#7871;t v&agrave;o nh&agrave;, kh&ocirc;ng gian &#273;&#7865;p, gi&aacute;ng sinh',NULL,NULL,NULL,'kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; gi&aacute;ng sinh, mang kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; gi&aacute;ng sinh v&agrave; t&#7871;t v&agrave;o nh&agrave;, kh&ocirc;ng gian &#273;&#7865;p, gi&aacute;ng sinh',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - theo: http://dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(133,'Khu d&acirc;n c&#432; trung t&acirc;m th&#7883; tr&#7845;n Duc Hoa Residence','D&#7921; &aacute;n khu d&acirc;n c&#432; trung t&acirc;m th&#7883; tr&#7845;n v&#7899;i quy m&ocirc; 34,5 ha, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897;, n&#7857;m ngay trung t&acirc;m th&#7883; tr&#7845;n &#272;&#7913;c H&ograve;a, t&#7881;nh Long An, v&#7899;i &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; c&aacute;c ti&#7879;n &iacute;ch d&#7883;ch v&#7909; do C&ocirc;ng ty CP To&agrave;n Gia Th&#7883;nh l&agrave;m ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;.','\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; &quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nDuc Hoa Residence c&amp;oacute; v&#7883; tr&amp;iacute; thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i n&#7857;m ngay trung t&amp;acirc;m th&#7883; tr&#7845;n &#272;&#7913;c H&amp;ograve;a li&#7873;n k&#7873; khu d&amp;acirc;n c&#432; hi&#7879;n h&#7919;u v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng d&#7883;ch v&#7909; ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch s&#7861;n c&amp;oacute; nh&#432; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#272;H qu&#7889;c t&#7871; T&amp;acirc;n T&#7841;o, tr&#432;&#7901;ng c&#7845;p 3 T&amp;acirc;n &#272;&#7913;c. D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ti&#7871;p gi&amp;aacute;p tr&#7909;c T&#7881;nh l&#7897; 825 hi&#7879;n h&#7919;u, n&#7857;m trong v&amp;ugrave;ng quy ho&#7841;ch giao th&amp;ocirc;ng thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i nh&#432; c&amp;aacute;ch v&amp;agrave;nh &#273;ai 4 kho&#7843;ng 2 km, v&amp;agrave;nh &#273;ai 3 kho&#7843;ng 4 km...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/PhoiCanh.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ph&#7889;i c&#7843;nh t&#7893;ng th&#7875; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nD&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Khu d&amp;acirc;n c&#432; trung t&amp;acirc;m th&#7883; tr&#7845;n Duc Hoa Residence c&amp;oacute; quy m&amp;ocirc; 34,5 ha v&#7899;i &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; c&amp;aacute;c ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch d&#7883;ch v&#7909; nh&#7857;m &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u s&#7889;ng, h&#7885;c t&#7853;p v&amp;agrave; l&amp;agrave;m vi&#7879;c nh&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;acirc;y xanh, tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7885;c, tr&#7841;m y t&#7871;, khu th&#7875; d&#7909;c th&#7875; thao&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Khu d&amp;acirc;n c&#432; trung t&amp;acirc;m th&#7883; tr&#7845;n Duc Hoa Residence do C&amp;ocirc;ng ty CP B&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n Danh Kh&amp;ocirc;i &amp;Aacute; Ch&amp;acirc;u (DKRA) l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; t&#432; v&#7845;n v&amp;agrave; ti&#7871;p th&#7883; &#273;&#7897;c quy&#7873;n, v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n trung b&amp;igrave;nh ch&#7881; 2,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng m&#7897;t m2, di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute; t&#7915; 125 m2 &#273;&#7871;n 222 m2. Thanh to&amp;aacute;n chia th&amp;agrave;nh 6 &#273;&#7907;t, m&#7895;i &#273;&#7907;t c&amp;aacute;ch nhau 3 th&amp;aacute;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;219&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/Minh-Hoa-2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ph&#7889;i c&#7843;nh nh&amp;agrave; m&#7851;u v&amp;agrave; tr&#432;&#7901;ng m&#7847;m non.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;','14/12/2011','14/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/Minh-Hoa-2.jpg',28,8,1966,'huyennt',1,'khu-dan-cu-trung-tam-thi-tran-duc-hoa-residence','khu d&acirc;n c&#432; trung t&acirc;m, d&#7921; &aacute;n, khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883;, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;',NULL,NULL,NULL,'khu d&acirc;n c&#432; trung t&acirc;m, d&#7921; &aacute;n, khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883;, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://vnexpress.net',1,0,0,0),(134,'Ph&acirc;n v&ugrave;ng th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng: H&#7885; Vicem m&#7845;t ph&#7847;n','Vi&#7879;c &aacute;p d&#7909;ng chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c ph&acirc;n v&ugrave;ng th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng cho c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a Vicem &#273;ang khi&#7871;n cho c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a t&#7893;ng c&ocirc;ng ty n&agrave;y m&#7845;t th&#7883; ph&#7847;n.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;L&amp;agrave; nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t xi m&#259;ng s&#7889; 1 Vi&#7879;t Nam v&#7899;i 36,03% th&#7883; ph&#7847;n, T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty C&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p Xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam (Vicem) &#273;ang &amp;aacute;p d&#7909;ng chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;acirc;n v&amp;ugrave;ng th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng cho c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n. Song, kh&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;iacute;t c&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7843;n &#7913;ng v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;ch l&amp;agrave;m n&amp;agrave;y, b&#7903;i sau khi nh&#432;&#7907;ng l&#7841;i &#273;&#7883;a b&amp;agrave;n, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p &amp;ldquo;anh em&amp;rdquo; ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n &#273;&amp;atilde; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gi&#7919; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7883; ph&#7847;n nh&#432; tr&#432;&#7899;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&amp;acirc;y g&#7847;n 4 n&#259;m, Vicem b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u tri&#7875;n khai chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;acirc;n v&amp;ugrave;ng l&#7841;i cho c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n. Theo &#273;&amp;oacute;, Ho&amp;agrave;ng Th&#7841;ch &#273;&#432;&#7907;c y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u ph&#7843;i r&amp;uacute;t kh&#7887;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ph&amp;iacute;a Nam &#273;&#7875; nh&#432;&#7907;ng l&#7841;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;agrave;y cho c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p &amp;ldquo;anh em&amp;rdquo; trong h&#7885; Vicem l&amp;agrave; Ho&amp;agrave;ng Mai, H&amp;agrave; Ti&amp;ecirc;n 1, 2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7909;c &#273;&amp;iacute;ch c&#7911;a vi&#7879;c ph&amp;acirc;n v&amp;ugrave;ng n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m b&#7899;t chi ph&amp;iacute; v&#7853;n chuy&#7875;n, v&amp;igrave; Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng Ho&amp;agrave;ng Th&#7841;ch &#273;&#7863;t t&#7841;i H&#7843;i D&#432;&#417;ng, trong khi Ho&amp;agrave;ng Mai, H&amp;agrave; Ti&amp;ecirc;n 1, 2 g&#7847;n ph&amp;iacute;a Nam h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n Ng&#7885;c Anh, T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c C&amp;ocirc;ng ty TNHH m&#7897;t th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n Xi m&#259;ng Vicem Ho&amp;agrave;ng Th&#7841;ch cho bi&#7871;t, &amp;ocirc;ng t&#7915;ng ph&#7843;n &#273;&#7889;i k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch r&amp;uacute;t th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u xi m&#259;ng Ho&amp;agrave;ng Th&#7841;ch kh&#7887;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ph&amp;iacute;a Nam, v&amp;igrave; Ho&amp;agrave;ng Th&#7841;ch &#273;&amp;atilde; kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u t&#7841;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;agrave;y v&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;atilde; chi&#7871;m m&#7897;t th&#7883; ph&#7847;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7887; t&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;N&#7871;u T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh khi Ho&amp;agrave;ng Th&#7841;ch r&amp;uacute;t ra to&amp;agrave;n b&#7897; th&#7883; ph&#7847;n s&#7869; thu&#7897;c v&#7873; m&#7897;t th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u kh&amp;aacute;c c&#7911;a Vicem th&amp;igrave; Ho&amp;agrave;ng Th&#7841;ch r&#7845;t s&#7861;n s&amp;agrave;ng. C&amp;ograve;n tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p ng&#432;&#7907;c l&#7841;i, th&#7883; ph&#7847;n &#273;&amp;oacute; b&#7883; th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u xi m&#259;ng kh&amp;aacute;c ngo&amp;agrave;i Vicem chi&#7871;m gi&#7919;, n&amp;ecirc;n ch&#259;ng c&#7847;n c&amp;acirc;n nh&#7855;c l&#7841;i&amp;rdquo;, &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n Ho&amp;agrave;ng Th&#7841;ch b&#259;n kho&#259;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;316&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/PHAN-VUNG.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, l&amp;agrave; &amp;ldquo;con&amp;rdquo; kh&amp;ocirc;ng d&amp;aacute;m c&amp;atilde;i l&#7901;i &amp;ldquo;m&#7865;&amp;rdquo;, trong v&amp;ograve;ng ch&#432;a &#273;&#7847;y 4 n&#259;m, Xi m&#259;ng Ho&amp;agrave;ng Th&#7841;ch &#273;&amp;atilde; r&amp;uacute;t kh&#7887;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ph&amp;iacute;a Nam v&amp;agrave; c&amp;acirc;u chuy&#7879;n gi&#7919; th&#7883; ph&#7847;n b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u g&amp;acirc;y tranh c&amp;atilde;i khi c&amp;aacute;c th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u kh&amp;aacute;c thu&#7897;c h&#7885; Vicem kh&amp;oacute; c&#7841;nh tranh t&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nV&#7899;i vi&#7879;c d&#432; cung, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng xi m&#259;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; b&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave;o giai &#273;o&#7841;n c&#7841;nh tranh kh&#7889;c li&#7879;t v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u t&amp;ecirc;n tu&#7893;i l&#7899;n, nh&#7887;. C&amp;oacute; th&#7875; k&#7875; &#273;&#7871;n h&amp;agrave;ng lo&#7841;t th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u c&#7911;a Vicem nh&#432; Ho&amp;agrave;ng Th&#7841;ch, H&amp;agrave; Ti&amp;ecirc;n, H&#7843;i Ph&amp;ograve;ng, B&amp;uacute;t S&#417;n, B&#7881;m S&#417;n, Ho&amp;agrave;ng Mai, Tam &#272;i&#7879;p, c&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u kh&amp;aacute;c l&amp;agrave; Chinfon, Nghi S&#417;n, Ph&amp;uacute;c S&#417;n, Holcim, FICO,&amp;hellip; Th&amp;ecirc;m v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&amp;oacute;, m&#7895;i v&amp;ugrave;ng l&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t lo&#7841;i xi m&#259;ng &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng &amp;ldquo;&amp;aacute;n ng&#7919;&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hai &#273;&#7883;a b&amp;agrave;n ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; xi m&#259;ng nhi&#7873;u nh&#7845;t c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c l&amp;agrave; TP. HCM v&amp;agrave; H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u m&#7899;i r&#7845;t kh&amp;oacute; chen ch&amp;acirc;n v&amp;agrave;o. B&#7903;i &#7903; nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7883;a b&amp;agrave;n n&amp;agrave;y, d&amp;ugrave; l&amp;agrave; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; xi m&#259;ng l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c, nh&#432;ng v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u &amp;ocirc;ng l&#7899;n, mi&#7871;ng b&amp;aacute;nh n&amp;agrave;y xem ra qu&amp;aacute; nh&#7887;. &#272;&#417;n c&#7917;, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i m&#7895;i n&#259;m ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; kho&#7843;ng 5 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, trong khi c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t to&amp;agrave;n ng&amp;agrave;nh v&amp;agrave;o kho&#7843;ng 55 - 60 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n (trong &#273;&amp;oacute; xi m&#259;ng l&amp;ograve; &#273;&#7913;ng v&amp;agrave;o kho&#7843;ng 10 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, vi&#7879;c c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng, c&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7899;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n tr&#7847;m l&#7855;ng c&#361;ng k&amp;eacute;o theo s&#7921; s&#7909;t gi&#7843;m ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; xi m&#259;ng. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7841;y h&#7871;t c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; n&#7895;i ni&#7873;m c&#7911;a &#273;a ph&#7847;n c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t xi m&#259;ng trong th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng l&amp;ograve; &#273;&#7913;ng &amp;ldquo;bi&#7871;t th&amp;acirc;n, bi&#7871;t ph&#7853;n&amp;rdquo; n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7921; &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t t&#7915; m&#7897;t v&amp;agrave;i n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c b&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;ch s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung nh&#432; g&#7841;ch Block.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;H&#417;n n&#7919;a, c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng l&amp;ograve; &#273;&#7913;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; b&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave;o th&#7901;i k&#7923; kh&#7845;u hao xong ho&#7863;c kh&#7845;u hao g&#7847;n h&#7871;t n&amp;ecirc;n b&amp;agrave;i to&amp;aacute;n cho s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t s&#7869; &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n h&#417;n nhi&#7873;u. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng l&amp;ograve; quay, do &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; l&#7899;n, l&#7841;i ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n m&#7899;i n&amp;ecirc;n ngo&amp;agrave;i v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, c&amp;ograve;n ph&#7843;i tr&#7843; n&#7907; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; m&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; n&#7907; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; b&#7857;ng v&#7889;n n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&amp;agrave;i, n&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7843;i t&amp;iacute;nh th&amp;ecirc;m b&amp;agrave;i to&amp;aacute;n tr&#432;&#7907;t gi&amp;aacute; ngo&#7841;i t&#7879;. V&amp;igrave; th&#7871;, kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n c&amp;agrave;ng th&amp;ecirc;m ch&#7891;ng ch&#7845;t &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;agrave;y xi m&#259;ng m&#7899;i, c&amp;oacute; su&#7845;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; l&#7899;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Vi&#7879;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng duy tr&amp;igrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng v&#7873; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&amp;atilde; khi&#7871;n nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p g&#7863;p kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n l&#7899;n trong kh&amp;acirc;u tr&#7843; n&#7907;. B&#7857;ng ch&#7913;ng l&amp;agrave; n&#259;m 2011, B&#7897; T&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7843;i tr&#7843; n&#7907; thay cho Xi m&#259;ng Tam &#272;i&#7879;p, Th&amp;aacute;i Nguy&amp;ecirc;n, &#272;&#7891;ng B&amp;agrave;nh v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;atilde;n n&#7907; cho Xi m&#259;ng Ho&amp;agrave;ng Mai do &#273;&#7871;n k&#7923; tr&#7843; n&#7907; m&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng tr&#7843; n&#7907;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;acirc;u h&#7887;i &#273;&#7863;t ra l&amp;agrave; trong &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n hi&#7879;n nay, li&#7879;u Vicem c&amp;oacute; gi&#7919; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7883; ph&#7847;n v&amp;agrave; ph&#432;&#417;ng &amp;aacute;n &amp;ldquo;ph&amp;acirc;n v&amp;ugrave;ng&amp;rdquo; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng c&#7911;a Vicem c&amp;oacute; ph&#7843;i l&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p t&#7889;i &#432;u?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nguy&#7877;n&amp;nbsp;Huy&#7873;n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','14/12/2011','14/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/PHAN-VUNG.jpg',23,2,1834,'huyennt',1,'phan-vung-thi-truong-ho-vicem-mat-phan',' Ph&acirc;n v&ugrave;ng th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng: H&#7885; Vicem m&#7845;t ph&#7847;n, phan vung',NULL,NULL,NULL,' Ph&acirc;n v&ugrave;ng th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng: H&#7885; Vicem m&#7845;t ph&#7847;n, phan vung',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://www.diaoconline.vn',1,0,0,1),(135,'Chung c&#432; cao c&#7845;p v&#7873; ... t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p','Nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i d&acirc;n H&agrave; N&#7897;i &#273;&atilde; kh&ocirc;ng ti&#7871;c ti&#7873;n b&#7887; c&#7843; ch&#7909;c t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;&#7875; mua m&#7897;t c&#259;n h&#7897; chung c&#432; cao c&#7845;p nh&#7919;ng mong &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7853;n h&#432;&#7903;ng cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng ti&#7879;n nghi hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, tr&aacute;i v&#7899;i mong &#273;&#7907;i, nhi&#7873;u chung c&#432; &#273;&atilde; xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p','\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;N&#7895;i l&amp;ograve;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i mua chung c&#432; cao c&#7845;p&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/chungcu_TH-NC.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&amp;agrave;i n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c, chung c&#432; The Manor (M&#7929; &#272;&amp;igrave;nh, H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i) l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng t&#7893; h&#7907;p chung c&#432; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i nh&#7845;t H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i. C&#7843;nh quan &#273;&#7865;p, c&amp;aacute;c khu v&#7921;c d&#7883;ch v&#7909; ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch nh&#432; b&#7875; b&#417;i, khu vui ch&#417;i, si&amp;ecirc;u th&#7883;, nh&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quy ho&#7841;ch h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute;. &#272;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7903; h&#7919;u c&#259;n h&#7897; trong khu chung c&#432; n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7915;ng l&amp;agrave; ni&#7873;m m&#417; &#432;&#7899;c c&#7911;a nhi&#7873;u gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Sau 5 n&#259;m &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7899;i th&#7901;i gian khu chung c&#432; n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p. &#272;i&#7873;u &#273;&amp;aacute;ng n&amp;oacute;i, do x&#7843;y ra nhi&#7873;u tranh ch&#7845;p c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n v&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; vi&#7879;c b&#7843;o tr&amp;igrave;, b&#7843;o d&#432;&#7905;ng c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh, h&#7841;ng m&#7909;c c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng g&#7847;n nh&#432; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quan t&amp;acirc;m. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y, &#273;&#7859;ng c&#7845;p khu chung c&#432; n&amp;agrave;y &#273;ang d&#7847;n b&#7883; m&#7845;t &#273;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n The Manor cho bi&#7871;t, sau khi ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n chung c&#432; n&amp;agrave;y nh&#7845;t quy&#7871;t ph&#7843;n &#273;&#7889;i vi&#7879;c thu nhi&#7873;u kho&#7843;n ph&amp;iacute; b&#7845;t h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; bu&#7897;c ph&#7843;i d&#7915;ng thu ph&amp;iacute;. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, &#273;&#7891;ng ngh&#297; vi&#7879;c gi&#7843;m ph&amp;iacute; th&amp;igrave; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng. B&#7875; b&#417;i g&#7847;n nh&#432; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, &#273;&amp;egrave;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng c&#7843; khu v&#7921;c chung c&#432; c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m b&#7899;t, c&amp;aacute;c khu v&#7921;c chung kh&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7841;ch s&#7869; &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t vi&#7879;c tu d&#432;&#7905;ng c&amp;aacute;c khu v&#7921;c c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ograve;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c coi tr&#7885;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;N&#259;m 2007, gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh t&amp;ocirc;i &#273;&amp;atilde; mua c&#259;n h&#7897; v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; 5 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng/c&#259;n. So v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c khu chung c&#432; kh&amp;aacute;c th&amp;igrave; vi&#7879;c sinh s&#7889;ng chung c&#432; The Manor r&#7845;t t&#7889;t b&#7903;i ch&#432;a chung c&#432; n&amp;agrave;o c&amp;oacute; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian s&#7889;ng tuy&#7879;t v&#7901;i nh&#432; The Manor, c&#7843;nh quan c&amp;acirc;y c&#7889;i, s&amp;acirc;n ch&#417;i cho tr&#7867; con r&#7845;t l&amp;yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng... Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, sau d&#7883;ch v&#7909; c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t l&amp;agrave; b&#7875; b&#417;i khi&#7871;n cho chung c&#432; m&#7845;t d&#7847;n gi&amp;aacute; tr&#7883;. Th&amp;ecirc;m v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&amp;oacute;, vi&#7879;c &#273;&#7845;u tranh v&#7899;i ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; trong m&#7897;t th&#7901;i gian d&amp;agrave;i &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;agrave;m cho m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i th&#7921;c s&#7921; m&#7879;t m&#7887;i v&amp;agrave; c&#259;ng th&#7859;ng&amp;rdquo; v&#7883; n&amp;agrave;y cho bi&#7871;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/be-boi.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;C&#432; d&amp;acirc;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&amp;oacute;ng ph&amp;iacute; v&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; kh&amp;ocirc;ng chi ph&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7875; v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh b&#7875; b&#417;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; x&#7843;y ra t&#7841;i chung c&#432; b&#7853;c nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i m&amp;agrave; m&#7899;i &#273;&#7845;y ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n s&#7889;ng chung c&#432; Keangnam Vina c&#361;ng ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c &#273;&#7889;i m&#7863;t v&#7899;i nguy c&#417; n&amp;agrave;y do b&#7845;t &#273;&#7891;ng v&#7899;i ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;H&amp;atilde;y khoan b&amp;igrave;nh lu&#7853;n vi&#7879;c &amp;ldquo;ai kh&amp;ocirc;ng x&#7913;ng v&#7899;i ai&amp;rdquo; m&amp;agrave; nh&amp;igrave;n nh&#7853;n &#7903; g&amp;oacute;c &#273;&#7897; kh&amp;aacute;ch quan nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i cho r&#7857;ng, m&#7897;t c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u k&#7927; l&#7909;c, hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i nh&#7845;t Vi&#7879;t Nam nh&#432; Keangnam Vina r&#7891;i c&#361;ng s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; k&#7871;t c&#7909;c ch&#7859;ng kh&amp;aacute;c g&amp;igrave; The Manor khi m&amp;agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n v&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; kh&amp;ocirc;ng h&#7907;p t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;a ra ph&#432;&#417;ng &amp;aacute;n v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh t&amp;ograve;a nh&amp;agrave; cao nh&#7845;t Vi&#7879;t Nam.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Anh Nguy&#7877;n H&#7843;i Thanh &amp;ndash; c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n s&#7889;ng t&#7841;i chung c&#432; Keangnam cho bi&#7871;t, c&amp;aacute;c chung c&#432; Vi&#7879;t Nam &#273;a ph&#7847;n sau khi b&amp;agrave;n giao cho ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; h&#7847;u nh&#432; kh&amp;ocirc;ng quan t&amp;acirc;m m&amp;agrave; ph&amp;oacute; m&#7863;c cho ban qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute;. V&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y vi&#7879;c xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p di&#7877;n ra r&#7845;t nhanh ch&amp;oacute;ng. C&amp;aacute;c chung c&#432; cao c&#7845;p c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t ngo&#7841;i l&#7879;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n khu chung c&#432; Keangnam c&amp;oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u h&#7841;ng m&#7909;c c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng nh&#432; &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng x&amp;aacute;, c&amp;acirc;y xanh, chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng, ph&amp;ograve;ng t&#7853;p, s&amp;acirc;n ch&#417;i, b&#7875; b&#7903;i, s&amp;acirc;n tennis&amp;hellip; v&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh, b&#7843;o tr&amp;igrave;, b&#7843;o d&#432;&#7905;ng ph&#7843;i th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n. N&#7871;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng l&amp;agrave;m &#273;&#7873;u &#273;&#7863;n, ch&#7881; v&amp;agrave;i n&#259;m n&#7919;a c&amp;aacute;c h&#7841;ng m&#7909;c xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p th&amp;igrave; gi&amp;aacute; tr&#7883; chung c&#432; m&#7845;t d&#7847;n v&amp;agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i nhi&#7873;u nh&#7845;t v&#7851;n l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo anh Thanh, k&#7875; c&#7843; trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7843; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n v&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&#7891;ng thu&#7853;n thay ban qu&#7843;n tr&#7883; m&#7899;i th&amp;igrave; li&#7879;u v&#7899;i s&#7921; c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m ph&amp;iacute; d&#7883;ch v&#7909; Ban qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; t&amp;ograve;a nh&amp;agrave; m&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7843;m &#273;&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nhi&#7879;m v&#7909; v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh t&amp;ograve;a nh&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t c&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&amp;uacute;ng quy chu&#7849;n. Li&#7879;u r&#7857;ng sau 5 hay 10 n&#259;m n&#7919;a, c&amp;aacute;c c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n Keangnam c&amp;oacute; ph&#7843;i nh&amp;igrave;n th&#7845;y b&#7875; b&#417;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p n&#432;&#7899;c, c&amp;acirc;y c&#7889;i h&amp;eacute;o do kh&amp;ocirc;ng suy tr&amp;igrave; ch&#259;m s&amp;oacute;c, thang m&amp;aacute;y tr&#7909;c tr&#7863;c...&#272;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u m&amp;agrave; nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n s&#7889;ng &#7903; Keangnam lo ng&#7841;i h&#417;n c&#7843;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;M&#7845;t 1 &#273;&#7891;ng c&amp;ograve;n h&#417;n ph&#7843;i t&#7889;n 20 &#273;&#7891;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;a ph&#7847;n nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n Vi&#7879;t Nam sinh s&#7889;ng t&#7841;i c&amp;aacute;c khu chung c&#432; &amp;iacute;t quan t&amp;acirc;m &#273;&#7871;n v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh b&#7843;o tr&amp;igrave; t&amp;ograve;a nh&amp;agrave; b&#7903;i h&#7885; cho r&#7857;ng &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; tr&amp;aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m c&#7911;a ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave; Ban qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute;. Th&#7853;m ch&amp;iacute;, khi t&amp;ograve;a nh&amp;agrave; xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng h&#432; h&#7887;ng vi&#7879;c h&amp;ocirc; h&amp;agrave;o ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n &#273;&amp;oacute;ng ti&#7873;n &#273;&#7875; s&#7917;a ch&#7919;a l&amp;agrave; kh&amp;aacute; v&#7845;t v&#7843; v&#7899;i ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&amp;iacute; nh&#432; m&#7897;t con &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng xong n&#7871;u ch&#7881; khai th&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7843;o tr&amp;igrave;, b&#7843;o d&#432;&#7905;ng th&amp;igrave; &#273;&#432;&#417;ng nhi&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh b&#7883; xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p. Nhi&#7873;u chuy&amp;ecirc;n gia khuy&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;o, n&#7871;u b&#7887; 1 &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7843;o tr&amp;igrave; &#273;&amp;uacute;ng l&amp;uacute;c th&amp;igrave; sau n&amp;agrave;y tr&amp;aacute;nh ph&#7843;i m&#7845;y 20 &#273;&#7891;ng. T&#7915; &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; th&#7845;y x&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh vi&#7879;c b&#7843;o tr&amp;igrave; cho c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh, t&amp;ograve;a nh&amp;agrave; l&amp;agrave; r&#7845;t quan tr&#7885;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7915; th&#7921;c t&#7871; di&#7877;n ra t&#7841;i chung c&#432; The Manor, Keangnam Vina cho th&#7845;y, &#273;&#7875; c&amp;aacute;c t&amp;ograve;a chung c&#432; cao c&#7845;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7883; xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p, m&#7845;t gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;igrave; &#273;i&#7873;u c&#7847;n nh&#7845;t &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng c&amp;aacute;i b&#7855;t tay t&#7915; nhi&#7873;u ph&amp;iacute;a.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; l&amp;agrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y c&#7843; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, Ban qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; v&amp;agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n &#273;&#7873;u c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i th&#7889;ng nh&#7845;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7913;c ph&amp;iacute; h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute; m&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7841;i b&#7897; ph&#7853;n ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, m&#7913;c ph&amp;iacute; c&#361;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7911; &#273;&#7875; cho ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; b&amp;ugrave; &#273;&#7855;p c&amp;aacute;c chi ph&amp;iacute; cho vi&#7879;c v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh t&amp;ograve;a nh&amp;agrave; tr&amp;aacute;nh vi&#7879;c ph&#7843;i c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m b&#7899;t c&amp;aacute;c d&#7883;ch v&#7909; c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng c&#7911;a t&amp;ograve;a nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&#7903;i vi&#7879;c c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m d&#7883;ch v&#7909; ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch s&#7869; &#273;&#7891;ng ngh&#297;a vi&#7879;c &#273;&#7859;ng c&#7845;p chung c&#432; m&#7845;t d&#7847;n v&amp;agrave; ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n ch&#7859;ng c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n n&amp;agrave;o mong mu&#7889;n b&#7887; c&#7843; ch&#7909;c t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng ra mua c&#259;n h&#7897; nh&#432;ng &#273;&#7859;ng c&#7845;p v&amp;agrave; m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng s&#7889;ng l&#7841;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#432; k&#7923; v&#7885;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','14/12/2011','14/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/chungcu_TH-NC.jpg',29,8,1819,'huyennt',1,'chung-cu-cao-cap-ve-toc-do-xuong-cap','chung c&#432;, chung c&#432; xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p, t&#7889;c d&#7897; xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p',NULL,NULL,NULL,'chung c&#432;, chung c&#432; xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p, t&#7889;c d&#7897; xu&#7889;ng c&#7845;p',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'http://www.diaoconline.vn',1,0,0,0),(136,'Xi Riverview Palace ch&agrave;o &#273;&oacute;n nh&#7919;ng c&#432; d&acirc;n &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n','Sau th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng t&#7841;i H&agrave;n Qu&#7889;c, th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u nh&agrave; th&ocirc;ng minh cao c&#7845;p &quot;Xi&quot; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n b&#7903;i ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; GS E&amp;C c&#361;ng &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch mua c&#259;n h&#7897; cao c&#7845;p t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam ch&agrave;o &#273;&oacute;n khi ra m&#7855;t d&#7921; &aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n t&#7841;i Th&#7843;o &#272;i&#7873;n, Q.2, Tp.H&#7891; Ch&iacute; Minh-Xi Riverview Palace. &#272;&#7871;n nay, d&#7921; &aacute;n &#273;&atilde; ho&agrave;n t&#7845;t vi&#7879;c x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng v&agrave; s&#7869; ti&#7871;n h&agrave;nh b&agrave;n giao nh&agrave; t&#7915; ng&agrave;y 23/12/2011.','\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; &quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&#259;n h&#7897; cao c&#7845;p c&#7911;a t&#432;&#417;ng lai: An to&amp;agrave;n v&amp;agrave; th&amp;ocirc;ng minh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&amp;uacute;ng nh&#432; t&amp;ecirc;n g&#7885;i &amp;ldquo;L&amp;acirc;u &#273;&amp;agrave;i b&amp;ecirc;n s&amp;ocirc;ng&amp;rdquo;, t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c c&#259;n h&#7897; &#273;&#7873;uh&#432;&#7899;ng ra kh&amp;uacute;c quanh &#273;&#7865;p nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a s&amp;ocirc;ng S&amp;agrave;i G&amp;ograve;n. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, m&#7895;i c&#259;n h&#7897; c&#7911;a Xi &#273;&#7873;u c&amp;oacute; t&#432;&#7901;ng ri&amp;ecirc;ng bi&#7879;t v&#7899;i kh&#7843; n&#259;ng c&amp;aacute;ch &amp;acirc;m v&amp;agrave; th&amp;ocirc;ng gi&amp;oacute; t&#7889;t nh&#7845;t. M&#7895;i t&#7847;ng ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; 04 c&#259;n h&#7897; t&#7841;o t&amp;iacute;nh bi&#7879;t l&#7853;p cao gi&#7919;a c&amp;aacute;c h&#7897; gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/xii-reverview-palace.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nXi Riverview Palace ch&amp;agrave;o &#273;&amp;oacute;n nh&#7919;ng c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nT&#7847;ng 1 v&amp;agrave; 2 &#273;&#432;&#7907;c d&amp;ugrave;ng l&amp;agrave;m b&amp;atilde;i &#273;&#7853;u xe, t&#7847;ng 3 l&amp;agrave; khu ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch cao c&#7845;p, t&#7915; t&#7847;ng 4 tr&#7903; l&amp;ecirc;n l&amp;agrave; n&#417;i an c&#432; c&#7911;a c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng v&#7899;i t&#7847;m nh&amp;igrave;n ra s&amp;ocirc;ng r&#7897;ng m&#7903;, kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; tho&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&amp;atilde;ng m&amp;aacute;t m&#7867; v&amp;agrave; h&#7841;n ch&#7871; m&#7885;i ti&#7871;ng &#7891;n. D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p Gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh (&#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o an to&amp;agrave;n v&#7873; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng ch&#7883;u l&#7921;c, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng, khai th&amp;aacute;c v&amp;agrave; v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh l&amp;acirc;u d&amp;agrave;i) b&#7903;i C&amp;ocirc;ng ty CP t&#432; v&#7845;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng t&#7893;ng h&#7907;p v&amp;agrave;o ng&amp;agrave;y 9/12/2011.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7841;i H&amp;agrave;n Qu&#7889;c, GS E&amp;amp;C l&amp;agrave; t&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng h&#7879; th&#7889;ng Home Network t&#7889;i t&amp;acirc;n v&amp;agrave;o lo&#7841;i b&#7853;c nh&#7845;t so v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n nh&amp;agrave; &#7903; kh&amp;aacute;c. C&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7899;i h&#7879; th&#7889;ng ki&#7875;m so&amp;aacute;t an ninh nghi&amp;ecirc;m ng&#7863;t qua b&#7889;n c&#7917;a, c&#259;n h&#7897; th&amp;ocirc;ng minh v&#432;&#7907;t tr&#7897;i c&#7911;a Xi Riverview Palace b&#7843;o v&#7879; s&#7921; an to&amp;agrave;n cao nh&#7845;t cho c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n sinh s&#7889;ng t&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch chung &#273;&#7841;t ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n qu&#7889;c t&#7871;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Xi Riverview Palace &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; GS E&amp;amp;C v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i t&amp;aacute;c c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute; ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n &#273;&#7871;n t&#7915;ng chi ti&#7871;t nh&#7857;m &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n mong mu&#7889;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7889;ng trong m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng trong l&amp;agrave;nh v&amp;agrave; ti&#7879;n nghi v&#432;&#7907;t tr&#7897;i v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ch&#259;m s&amp;oacute;c to&amp;agrave;n di&#7879;n t&#7893; &#7845;m c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh &#7903; m&#7885;i n&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o m&#7885;i th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m. &#272;&#7843;m b&#7843;o ch&#259;m s&amp;oacute;c s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e v&amp;agrave; m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng s&#7889;ng c&#7911;a c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n trong khu c&#259;n h&#7897; l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng &#273;i&#7873;u quan tr&#7885;ng nh&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;342&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/beboi.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;Xi Riverview Palace cung c&#7845;p cho c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n nh&#7919;ng d&#7883;ch v&#7909; ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch cao c&#7845;p ti&amp;ecirc;n ti&#7871;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nXi Riverview Palace cung c&#7845;p cho c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n nh&#7919;ng d&#7883;ch v&#7909; ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch cao c&#7845;p ti&amp;ecirc;n ti&#7871;n nh&#432; h&#7891; b&#417;i, ph&amp;ograve;ng t&#7853;p th&#7875; d&#7909;c, ph&amp;ograve;ng x&amp;ocirc;ng h&#417;i, yoga, s&amp;acirc;n golf mini trong nh&amp;agrave; v&amp;agrave; ngo&amp;agrave;i tr&#7901;i, s&amp;acirc;n ch&#417;i tr&#7867; em, s&amp;acirc;n tennis, nh&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;ng m&#7903;, nh&amp;agrave; kh&amp;aacute;ch, ph&amp;ograve;ng h&#7885;p&amp;hellip; Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng 2 t&#7847;ng gi&amp;agrave;nh ri&amp;ecirc;ng cho b&amp;atilde;i &#273;&#7895; xe th&amp;ocirc;ng minh, &#432;&#7899;c t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7911; r&#7897;ng &#273;&#7875; m&#7895;i c&#259;n h&#7897; c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t ch&#7895; &#273;&#7895; xe &amp;ocirc;t&amp;ocirc; v&amp;agrave; 2 ch&#7895; &#273;&#7895; xe m&amp;aacute;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;M&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng s&#7889;ng th&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p cho c&#7843; th&#7871; h&#7879; t&#432;&#417;ng lai&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Xi Riverview Palace c&amp;oacute; l&#7907;i th&#7871; n&#7857;m trong khu Th&#7843;o &#272;i&#7873;n Qu&#7853;n 2 v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch trong khu v&#7921;c nh&#432; si&amp;ecirc;u th&#7883; Metro, b&#7879;nh vi&#7879;n, ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;m qu&#7889;c t&#7871;, BIS, AIS&amp;hellip; &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#259;m s&amp;oacute;c v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n th&#7871; h&#7879; tr&#7867; t&amp;agrave;i n&#259;ng trong t&#432;&#417;ng lai. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, trong khu&amp;ocirc;n vi&amp;ecirc;n d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; c&#7843; Tr&#432;&#7901;ng m&#7847;m non qu&#7889;c t&#7871; AIS, gi&amp;uacute;p &amp;iacute;ch r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u cho qu&amp;yacute; c&#432; d&amp;acirc;n n&amp;agrave;o &#273;ang c&amp;oacute; con em tu&#7893;i &#273;i h&#7885;c m&#7851;u gi&amp;aacute;o. Tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng v&amp;agrave; thi&#7871;t k&#7871; &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&amp;aacute;o sinh &#273;&#7897;ng ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p cho vi&#7879;c gi&amp;aacute;o d&#7909;c c&amp;aacute;c em nh&#7887; &#7903; l&#7913;a tu&#7893;i m&#7847;m non c&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7899;i m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng sinh s&#7889;ng th&amp;acirc;n thi&#7879;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S&#7921; an t&amp;acirc;m &#273;&#7871;n t&#7915; cam k&#7871;t v&amp;agrave; uy t&amp;iacute;n c&#7911;a ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n th&#7901;i gian v&#7915;a qua tr&#7847;m l&#7855;ng b&#7903;i nhi&#7873;u y&#7871;u t&#7889; v&#297; m&amp;ocirc;, GS v&#7851;n cam k&#7871;t ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&amp;uacute;ng ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; nh&#432; &#273;&amp;atilde; cam k&#7871;t v&#7899;i kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong nh&#7919;ng ng&amp;agrave;y cu&#7889;i n&#259;m r&#7897;n r&amp;atilde; m&#7915;ng Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh v&amp;agrave; ch&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m m&#7899;i 2012, Ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; GS v&amp;agrave; Savills Vi&#7879;t Nam s&#7869; ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p t&#7893; ch&#7913;c bu&#7893;i ti&#7879;c g&#7863;p g&#7905; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng, v&#7915;a t&#7841;o c&#417; h&#7897;i cho qu&amp;iacute; kh&amp;aacute;ch c&amp;ugrave;ng gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh ngh&#7881; ng&#417;i th&#432; gi&amp;atilde;n v&amp;agrave; tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m c&amp;aacute;c ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch, v&#7915;a l&amp;agrave; d&#7883;p &#273;&#7875; l&#7855;ng nghe t&amp;acirc;m t&#432; nguy&#7879;n v&#7885;ng c&#7911;a kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng v&amp;agrave; cu&#7889;i c&amp;ugrave;ng l&amp;agrave; ch&amp;iacute;nh th&#7913;c c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; trao ch&amp;igrave;a kh&amp;oacute;a c&#259;n h&#7897; cho nh&#7919;ng ch&#7911; nh&amp;acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng lai.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;','15/12/2011','15/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/xii-reverview-palace.jpg',29,8,1812,'huyennt',1,'xi-riverview-palace-chao-don-nhung-cu-dan-dau-tien',' Xi Riverview Palace ch&agrave;o &#273;&oacute;n nh&#7919;ng c&#432; d&acirc;n &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n, chung c&#432;, &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883;, d&#7921; &aacute;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,' Xi Riverview Palace ch&agrave;o &#273;&oacute;n nh&#7919;ng c&#432; d&acirc;n &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n, chung c&#432;, &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883;, d&#7921; &aacute;n',0,0,0,'','','',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - theo: http://dothi.net/',1,0,0,0),(137,'C&aacute;c DN th&eacute;p n&#7895; l&#7921;c v&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute;','Tr&#432;&#7899;c t&igrave;nh c&#7843;nh kh&oacute; kh&#259;n ch&#7891;ng ch&#7845;t c&#7911;a ng&agrave;nh th&eacute;p, nhi&#7873;u DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&eacute;p tr&ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a b&agrave;n t&#7881;nh B&agrave; R&#7883;a-V&#361;ng T&agrave;u &#273;&atilde; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c bi&#7879;n ph&aacute;p t&iacute;ch c&#7921;c &#273;&#7875; &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, &#273;&#432;a DN v&#432;&#7907;t qua th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m kh&oacute; kh&#259;n.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng &#272;&#7863;ng Huy Hi&#7879;p - Gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c Cty Th&amp;eacute;p Vina Kyoei (VKS) cho bi&#7871;t, nh&#7919;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n chung c&#7911;a n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871; th&#7871; gi&#7899;i v&amp;agrave; ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t ti&#7873;n t&#7879;, gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7875; ki&#7875;m so&amp;aacute;t l&#7841;m ph&amp;aacute;t theo Ngh&#7883; quy&#7871;t 11 c&#7911;a Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7887; t&#7899;i ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t kinh doanh c&#7911;a DN.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; gi&#7843;m&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;L&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng lu&amp;ocirc;n &#7903; m&#7913;c cao, c&amp;oacute; khi l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i 20% &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;agrave;m &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng m&#7841;nh &#273;&#7871;n k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&#7911;a VSK, Cty ph&#7843;i c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m c&amp;aacute;c chi ph&amp;iacute; v&amp;agrave; h&#7841; c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7881; ti&amp;ecirc;u xu&#7889;ng &#273;&#7875; b&#7843;o &#273;&#7843;m s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t&amp;rdquo; - &amp;ocirc;ng Hi&#7879;p chia s&#7867;. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, t&#7881; gi&amp;aacute; VN&#272;/USD t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m &#273;&#7871;n nay kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh v&amp;agrave; t&#259;ng m&#7841;nh, t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh l&#7841;m ph&amp;aacute;t lu&amp;ocirc;n &#7903; m&#7913;c cao c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave;m cho DN nhi&#7873;u phen &amp;ldquo;lao &#273;ao&amp;rdquo;. Nhi&#7873;u l&amp;uacute;c Cty ph&#7843;i &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t do nguy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c ph&#7909; t&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7851;n ph&#7843;i nh&#7853;p t&#7915; n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&amp;agrave;i. Trong n&#259;m 2011, VSK &#273;&amp;atilde; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7847;n 376 t&#7845;n th&amp;eacute;p, gi&#7843;m h&#417;n 7% so v&#7899;i n&#259;m 2010, l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#361;ng gi&#7843;m g&#7847;n 15%. Theo nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a &amp;ocirc;ng Hi&#7879;p, v&#7899;i k&#7871;t qu&#7843; n&amp;agrave;y, VKS tuy gi&#7919; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7913;c &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh, nh&#432;ng hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; th&#7845;p, l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho t&#259;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/500.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;S&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;acirc;y t&#7841;i Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nT&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; nh&#432; VKS, ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t kinh doanh c&#7911;a Cty Posco VN c&#361;ng r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n khi ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7889;i m&#7863;t v&#7899;i l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho l&#7899;n. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, v&#7899;i s&#7921; c&#7841;nh tranh m&#7841;nh m&#7869; c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;eacute;p nh&#7853;p ngo&#7841;i t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c, Malaysia... c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave;m cho kh&#7843; n&#259;ng b&amp;aacute;n h&amp;agrave;ng c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c g&#7863;p kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n. Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; ch&#432;a thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;agrave;ng r&amp;agrave;o k&#7929; thu&#7853;t &#273;&#7875; ng&#259;n ch&#7863;n c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;eacute;p k&amp;eacute;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng v&amp;agrave;o th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng trong n&#432;&#7899;c, v&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y s&#7921; c&#7841;nh tranh v&#7873; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; c&#361;ng gay g&#7855;t &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &#273;&amp;aacute;nh gi&amp;aacute; c&#7911;a S&#7903; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng, trong n&#259;m 2011, nhi&#7873;u s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p ch&#7911; l&#7921;c c&#7911;a t&#7881;nh gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; th&amp;eacute;p. S&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#259;m 2011 &#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7841;t 2,5 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, ri&amp;ecirc;ng trong th&amp;aacute;ng 11, s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng th&amp;eacute;p gi&#7843;m t&#7899;i g&#7847;n 8,5%. &#272;&#7871;n nay, tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a b&amp;agrave;n t&#7881;nh ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p n&amp;agrave;o ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n, nh&#432;ng c&amp;aacute;c DN ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng h&#7871;t s&#7913;c kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&#7847;m ch&#7915;ng, c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m lao &#273;&#7897;ng...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; c&amp;aacute;c DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p g&#7863;p kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n m&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;eacute;p c&#361;ng r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o ho&amp;agrave;n c&#7843;nh t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921;. B&amp;agrave; Nguy&#7877;n Th&#7883; Hu&#7923;nh Nga - ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng Hu&#7923;nh Nga chuy&amp;ecirc;n ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;eacute;p Nh&#7853;t &#7903; &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng Huy&#7873;n Tr&amp;acirc;n C&amp;ocirc;ng Ch&amp;uacute;a (TP V&#361;ng T&amp;agrave;u) cho bi&#7871;t, trong n&#259;m 2011, t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p ch&#7881; kh&#7903;i s&#7855;c trong 3 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m, c&amp;ograve;n t&#7915; th&amp;aacute;ng 4 tr&#7903; l&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y th&amp;igrave; s&#7913;c mua c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ch&#7853;m ch&#7841;p. T&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m &#273;&#7871;n nay gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&amp;atilde; h&#417;n 10 l&#7847;n &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh, c&amp;oacute; khi trong 1 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh &#273;&#7871;n 2-3 l&#7847;n; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;agrave;m &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n m&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909;. B&amp;agrave; Nga d&#7851;n ch&#7913;ng c&#7909; th&#7875;, trong n&#259;m 2010, b&amp;igrave;nh qu&amp;acirc;n c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng Hu&#7923;nh Nga b&amp;aacute;n kho&#7843;ng 250 &amp;ndash; 300 t&#7845;n th&amp;eacute;p/th&amp;aacute;ng, ri&amp;ecirc;ng n&#259;m nay kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n l&#7855;m m&#7899;i &#273;&#7841;t kho&#7843;ng 50 &amp;ndash; 60 t&#7845;n/th&amp;aacute;ng. &amp;ldquo;S&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; n&#259;m nay gi&#7843;m g&#7847;n nh&#432; 50% so v&#7899;i n&#259;m 2010&amp;rdquo; - b&amp;agrave; Nga cho bi&#7871;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;T&#7921; xoay s&#7903;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Nam Sik - &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n Cty Posco VN cho bi&#7871;t, tr&#432;&#7899;c nh&#7919;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n do l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p &#7903; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng trong n&#432;&#7899;c gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh, xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u ra n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&amp;agrave;i l&amp;agrave; h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;i t&#7845;t y&#7871;u m&amp;agrave; Posco VN &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;agrave;m trong su&#7889;t th&#7901;i gian qua. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, vi&#7879;c xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u c&#7911;a DN c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng d&#7877; g&amp;igrave; do c&amp;aacute;c ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch b&#7843;o h&#7897; ng&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&#432;&#7899;c ngo&amp;agrave;i nh&#432; h&amp;agrave;ng r&amp;agrave;o ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng, ch&#7889;ng b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute;... g&amp;acirc;y cho DN nhi&#7873;u tr&#7903; ng&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7893;i m&#7899;i c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879;, ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m ti&amp;ecirc;u hao n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng l&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p h&#7919;u hi&#7879;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c VKS th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i ph&amp;oacute; v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c th&amp;aacute;ch th&#7913;c hi&#7879;n nay nh&#7857;m h&#7841; gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m v&amp;agrave; n&amp;acirc;ng cao n&#259;ng l&#7921;c c&#7841;nh tranh. &amp;Ocirc;ng &#272;&#7863;ng Huy Hi&#7879;p cho bi&#7871;t, trong n&#259;m 2011, VKS &#273;&amp;atilde; &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng th&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng m&amp;ocirc; h&amp;igrave;nh &amp;ldquo;M&#7887; &#273;&#7889;t t&amp;aacute;i sinh&amp;rdquo; cho l&amp;ograve; nung c&amp;aacute;m th&amp;eacute;p, nh&#7901; v&#7853;y &#273;&amp;atilde; gi&#7843;m ti&amp;ecirc;u hao nhi&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u &#273;&#7871;n h&#417;n 11%. C&#361;ng trong n&#259;m 2011, VKS &#273;&amp;atilde; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&#7917; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;eacute;p n&#7889;i ren nh&#7857;m &#273;a d&#7841;ng h&amp;oacute;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m, &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u cao c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng. V&#7899;i t&amp;iacute;nh n&#259;ng v&#432;&#7907;t tr&#7897;i nh&#432; ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m th&#7901;i gian v&amp;agrave; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u th&amp;eacute;p trong x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;eacute;p n&#7889;i ren c&#7911;a VSK &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&amp;aacute;nh gi&amp;aacute; cao.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;H&#7841; th&#7845;p c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7881; ti&amp;ecirc;u k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch, gi&#7843;m s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng, gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u c&amp;aacute;c chi ph&amp;iacute; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t nh&#432; &#273;i&#7879;n, n&#432;&#7899;c, nguy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u v&amp;agrave; huy &#273;&#7897;ng v&#7889;n t&#7841;i ch&#7895; b&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;ch b&amp;aacute;n c&#7893; phi&#7871;u c&amp;ocirc;ng ty cho c&amp;aacute;n b&#7897;, c&amp;ocirc;ng nh&amp;acirc;n vi&amp;ecirc;n l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;ch m&amp;agrave; Cty Th&amp;eacute;p Mi&#7873;n Nam s&#7917; d&amp;ugrave;ng &#273;&#7875; v&#432;&#7907;t qua &amp;ldquo;v&#7853;n b&#297;&amp;rdquo; hi&#7879;n nay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo nh&amp;igrave;n nh&#7853;n c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c chuy&amp;ecirc;n gia kinh t&#7871;, t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh suy gi&#7843;m kinh t&#7871; hi&#7879;n nay khi&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;c DN ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, nh&#432;ng &#273;&amp;acirc;y c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; c&#417; h&#7897;i &#273;&#7875; ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p s&amp;agrave;ng l&#7885;c v&amp;agrave; c&#7845;u tr&amp;uacute;c l&#7841;i. Nh&#7919;ng DN kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7911; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng s&#7869; b&#7883; lo&#7841;i kh&#7887;i ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p, nh&#7919;ng nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y quy m&amp;ocirc; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t nh&#7887;, c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; l&#7841;c h&#7853;u s&#7869; b&#7883; &#273;&amp;agrave;o th&#7843;i ho&#7863;c c&amp;aacute;c DN s&#7869; ph&#7843;i li&amp;ecirc;n k&#7871;t v&#7899;i nhau &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o th&amp;agrave;nh m&#7897;t th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u m&#7841;nh, chuy&#7875;n h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave;o c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;eacute;p m&amp;agrave; trong n&#432;&#7899;c ch&#432;a s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, &#273;&#7875; l&amp;agrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y, c&amp;aacute;c c&#417; quan qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; c&#7847;n nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u, &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t c&amp;aacute;c c&#417; ch&#7871;, ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch h&#7895; tr&#7907; DN th&amp;eacute;p v&#432;&#7907;t qua kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','15/12/2011','15/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/500.jpg',23,2,1782,'huyennt',1,'cac-dn-thep-no-luc-vuot-kho','s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&eacute;p, th&eacute;p, nh&agrave; m&aacute;y th&eacute;p, nguy&ecirc;n li&#7879;u, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, vat lieu xay dung, VLXD, c&aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p n&#7895; l&#7921;c v&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute;',NULL,NULL,NULL,'s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&eacute;p, th&eacute;p, nh&agrave; m&aacute;y th&eacute;p, nguy&ecirc;n li&#7879;u, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, vat lieu xay dung, VLXD, c&aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p n&#7895; l&#7921;c v&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute;',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://www.xaydungvietnam.vn',1,0,0,0),(138,'S&#7869; c&oacute; cu&#7897;c chi&#7871;n v&#7873; gi&aacute; c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i chung c&#432;','&#272;&aacute;nh &#273;&uacute;ng ph&acirc;n kh&uacute;c th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;ang thi&#7871;u h&#7909;t, nhi&#7873;u ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&atilde; chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i sang x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng nh&agrave; chung c&#432; gi&aacute; trung b&igrave;nh 14-18 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2.','\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; &quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n nh&amp;agrave; thu nh&#7853;p th&#7845;p &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&amp;agrave;o b&amp;aacute;n v&#7899;i m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p h&#417;n 1-2 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2. Nhi&#7873;u &amp;yacute; ki&#7871;n cho r&#7857;ng, s&#7855;p t&#7899;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ch&#7913;ng khi&#7871;n s&#7921; c&#7841;nh tranh kh&#7889;c li&#7879;t ph&amp;acirc;n kh&amp;uacute;c n&amp;agrave;y khi ngu&#7891;n cung ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c pha lo&amp;atilde;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;375&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/139095_500.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;B&#7897;i th&#7921;c ngu&#7891;n cung&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Chung c&#432; cao c&#7845;p &#7871; &#7845;m, s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m l&amp;agrave;m ra kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i mua. C&#7921;c ch&#7859;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; nhi&#7873;u ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&#7893;i h&#432;&#7899;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&amp;aacute;c chung c&#432; c&amp;oacute; m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;igrave;nh d&amp;acirc;n t&#7915; 14-18 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2, v&#7899;i di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch nh&#7887; &#273;&#7875; ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i ngu&#7891;n c&#7847;u th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7889;n &#273;ang b&#7883; b&#7887; ng&#7887;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7921; chuy&#7875;n h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#432; t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n l&amp;agrave;n s&amp;oacute;ng khi ch&#7881; trong v&amp;ograve;ng 2 th&amp;aacute;ng nay, h&#417;n 10 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n gi&amp;aacute; r&#7867; li&amp;ecirc;n ti&#7871;p ch&amp;agrave;o h&amp;agrave;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&#272;&#417;n c&#7917; nh&#432; D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Dream Town (T&amp;acirc;y M&#7895;, T&#7915; Li&amp;ecirc;m, H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i) &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&amp;agrave;o b&amp;aacute;n v&#7899;i m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; l&amp;agrave; 17,8 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2, ch&#432;a g&#7891;m VAT. D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n An B&amp;igrave;nh Tower do C&amp;ocirc;ng ty TNHH MTV &#272;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave; Ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i tung ra th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7899;i m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; &amp;ldquo;s&#7889;c&amp;rdquo;, 1,3 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng/c&#259;n h&#7897;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng L&#297;nh Nam (Ho&amp;agrave;ng Mai - H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i) v&#7915;a g&amp;acirc;y s&#7889;c tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng khi h&#7841; gi&amp;aacute; xu&#7889;ng ch&#7881; c&amp;ograve;n h&#417;n 12 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2. D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n chung c&#432; Sails Tower &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&amp;agrave;o b&amp;aacute;n v&#7899;i m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; d&#432;&#7899;i 18 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2, di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch c&#259;n h&#7897; t&#7915; 77,2 - 107,8m2&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo t&amp;igrave;m hi&#7875;u ri&amp;ecirc;ng ph&amp;oacute;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n, m&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n chung c&#432; gi&amp;aacute; r&#7867; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7903; b&amp;aacute;n nh&#432;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng h&#7845;p th&#7909; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n r&#7845;t khi&amp;ecirc;m t&#7889;n b&#7903;i nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n chung c&#432; c&amp;oacute; v&#7883; tr&amp;iacute; c&amp;aacute;ch xa trung t&amp;acirc;m. Th&amp;ecirc;m v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&amp;oacute;, h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n m&#7899;i &#273;ang trong giai &#273;o&#7841;n tri&#7875;n khai m&amp;oacute;ng v&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y kh&amp;oacute; thu h&amp;uacute;t kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng trong b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh n&amp;agrave;y b&#7903;i s&#7921; ch&#7853;m ch&#7877; trong vi&#7879;c th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&#7911;a nhi&#7873;u ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&amp;atilde; khi&#7871;n cho kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng m&#7845;t ni&#7873;m tin v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;aacute; th&#7853;n tr&#7885;ng khi l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n nh&#432;ng d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;ang tri&#7875;n khai.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&amp;ecirc;m v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&amp;oacute;, ph&amp;acirc;n kh&amp;uacute;c chung c&#432; gi&amp;aacute; m&#7873;m &#273;ang &#273;&#7889;i m&#7863;t v&#7899;i s&#7921; c&#7841;nh tranh c&#7911;a nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n nh&amp;agrave; thu nh&#7853;p th&#7845;p &#273;ang r&#7847;m r&#7897; tri&#7875;n khai v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;iacute;t ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;ang lo ng&#7841;i c&#259;n h&#7897; thu nh&#7853;p th&#7845;p r&#7891;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y c&#361;ng ph&#7843;i &amp;ldquo;b&amp;aacute;n th&amp;aacute;o&amp;rdquo; gi&#7889;ng nh&#432; m&#7897;t s&#7889; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n chung c&#432; th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i v&#7915;a qua.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7921;c t&#7871; cho th&#7845;y, c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n nh&amp;agrave; thu nh&#7853;p th&#7845;p &#273;ang b&#7883; r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh c&#7843;nh th&#7845;t b&#7841;i khi l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng &#7871;, t&#7891;n kho l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n c&#7843; ngh&amp;igrave;n c&#259;n h&#7897;. M&amp;agrave; nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n ch&amp;iacute;nh c&#7911;a s&#7921; &#7871; &#7849;m n&amp;agrave;y v&#7851;n l&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&amp;agrave;o b&amp;aacute;n m&#7913;c cao 11-13 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#417;n c&#7917;, d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n nh&amp;agrave; thu nh&#7853;p th&#7845;p S&amp;agrave;i &#272;&#7891;ng c&#7911;a C&amp;ocirc;ng ty X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng s&#7889; 3 m&#7903; b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7907;t 2 nh&#432;ng ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; 30 ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#259;ng k&amp;yacute; tham gia b&#7889;c th&#259;m, tr&amp;ecirc;n t&#7893;ng s&#7889; h&#417;n 100 c&#259;n h&#7897; doanh nghi&#7879;p n&amp;agrave;y m&#7903; b&amp;aacute;n nh&#432;ng v&#7851;n ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#259;ng k&amp;yacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7841;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n nh&amp;agrave; thu nh&#7853;p th&#7845;p &#272;&#7863;ng X&amp;aacute; c&#7911;a Viglacera, t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh th&#7853;m ch&amp;iacute; c&amp;ograve;n t&#7891;i t&#7879; h&#417;n, khi ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; 15 ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#7871;n k&amp;yacute; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng mua c&#259;n h&#7897; trong s&#7889; h&amp;agrave;ng tr&#259;m c&#259;n h&#7897; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c doanh nghi&#7879;p n&amp;agrave;y ch&amp;agrave;o b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7907;t 2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; ch&#432;a k&#7875; &#273;&#7871;n h&amp;agrave;ng lo&#7841;t c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n chung c&#432; mini &#273;&amp;atilde; m&#7885;c l&amp;ecirc;n nh&#432; n&#7845;m sau khi c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; c&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n v&#7873; m&#7863;t ph&amp;aacute;p l&amp;yacute;. &#272;a ph&#7847;n c&amp;aacute;c c&#259;n h&#7897; chung c&#432; mini t&#7841;i c&amp;aacute;c qu&#7853;n, huy&#7879;n H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&amp;agrave;o b&amp;aacute;n m&#7913;c 600-1,2 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng/c&#259;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;Aacute;p l&#7921;c c&#7841;nh tranh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#432;&#7899;c s&#7921; b&amp;ugrave;ng n&#7893; ngu&#7891;n cung, nhi&#7873;u &amp;yacute; ki&#7871;n lo ng&#7841;i &#273;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y s&#7869; t&#7841;o &amp;aacute;p l&#7921;c c&#7841;nh tranh quy&#7871;t li&#7879;t gi&#7919;a nh&#7919;ng d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n trong ph&amp;acirc;n kh&amp;uacute;c n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7841;i di&#7879;n m&#7897;t ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n cho r&#7857;ng, c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;ang c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i v&amp;agrave; c&amp;acirc;n nh&#7855;c &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m sao cho ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i &#273;&#7841;i b&#7897; ph&#7853;n ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, do s&#7921; thay &#273;&#7893;i di&#7877;n ra c&amp;ugrave;ng v&amp;agrave;o th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m v&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y &#273;&#7875; d&amp;agrave;nh th&#7855;ng l&#7907;i c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; s&#7869; bu&#7897;c ph&#7843;i c&#7841;nh tranh quy&#7871;t li&#7879;t &#273;&#7875; d&amp;agrave;nh th&#7883; ph&#7847;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;M&#7863;t b&#7857;ng thu nh&#7853;p c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n c&amp;ograve;n th&#7845;p n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n kh&amp;aacute; y&#7871;u. Khi mua nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7845;t, kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng lu&amp;ocirc;n ph&#7843;i nh&#7901; &#273;&#7871;n s&#7921; h&#7895; tr&#7907; t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh c&#7911;a ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng, nh&#432;ng vi&#7879;c vay &#273;&#432;&#7907;c v&#7889;n ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng hi&#7879;n &#273;ang r&#7845;t kh&amp;oacute;. V&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y, ph&amp;acirc;n kh&amp;uacute;c n&amp;agrave;y v&#7851;n ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7889;i m&#7863;t v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u ch&#432;&#7899;ng ng&#7841;i v&#7853;t&amp;rdquo; v&#7883; n&amp;agrave;y cho bi&#7871;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Peter Ryder - CEO Indochina Capital cho r&#7857;ng, th&#7901;i gian v&#7915;a qua kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; ri&amp;ecirc;ng v&#7873; ph&amp;acirc;n kh&amp;uacute;c b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n cao c&#7845;p m&amp;agrave; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c ph&amp;acirc;n kh&amp;uacute;c b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n kh&amp;aacute;c c&#361;ng &#273;ang trong t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; v&#432;&#7907;t c&#7847;u.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, c&amp;oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u y&#7871;u t&#7889; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#432; l&#7841;m ph&amp;aacute;t, ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng t&#259;ng l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t hay kh&#7843; n&#259;ng t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng c&#7911;a t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, c&amp;aacute; nh&amp;acirc;n. Nh&#7919;ng y&#7871;u t&#7889; n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;atilde; t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng l&amp;agrave;m th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n nh&#432; v&#7853;y, nh&#432;ng &#273;i&#7875;m m&#7845;u ch&#7889;t hi&#7879;n nay l&amp;agrave; t&amp;iacute;nh c&#7841;nh tranh c&#7911;a ch&amp;iacute;nh s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#7911;a d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n. N&#7871;u s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&amp;oacute; v&#7883; tr&amp;iacute; t&#7889;t, thi&#7871;t k&#7871; t&#7889;t, gi&amp;aacute; ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p th&amp;igrave; v&#7851;n c&amp;oacute; ch&#7895; &#273;&#7913;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7