0px; &quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. S&#7917; d&#7909;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian c&#7911;a c&#7847;u thang&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;500&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&#272;&#7863;t m&#7897;t chi&#7871;c b&amp;agrave;n nh&#7887; d&#432;&#7899;i ch&amp;acirc;n c&#7847;u thang, n&#7893;i b&#7853;t tr&amp;ecirc;n n&#7873;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian tr&#7855;ng l&amp;agrave; c&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng mini &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trang tr&amp;iacute; v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c ph&#7909; ki&#7879;n nhi&#7873;u m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c b&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh l&amp;agrave; l&amp;acirc;u &#273;&amp;agrave;i c&#7911;a Santa Claus nh&#7887; xinh. V&#7915;a b&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave;o nh&amp;agrave;, kh&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&amp;atilde; th&#7845;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh tr&amp;agrave;n ng&#7853;p r&#7891;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;2. T&#7853;n d&#7909;ng c&#7917;a s&#7893;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giang-sinh11.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nT&#7847;m nh&amp;igrave;n ra ngo&amp;agrave;i tr&#7901;i l&#7841;nh gi&amp;aacute; b&#7883; c&#7843;n b&#7903;i h&amp;igrave;nh trang tr&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7865;p m&#7855;t tr&amp;ecirc;n t&#7845;m k&amp;iacute;nh c&#7917;a s&#7893;. &#272;&amp;ecirc;m &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7859;ng th&#7875; n&amp;agrave;o c&amp;oacute; c&#417; h&#7897;i len l&#7887;i v&amp;agrave;o kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian &#7845;m &amp;aacute;p c&#7911;a gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh b&#7841;n. C&amp;aacute;ch l&amp;agrave;m c&#361;ng r&#7845;t &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n, treo nh&#7919;ng qu&#7843; b&amp;oacute;ng v&amp;agrave;o d&amp;acirc;y ruy b&#259;ng r&#7891;i treo v&amp;agrave;o khung c&#7917;a.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. S&#7917; d&#7909;ng t&#432;&#7901;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;0&quot; height=&quot;0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giang-sinh1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;600&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giang-sinh1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nB&#7913;c tranh &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n v&#7899;i h&amp;igrave;nh &#7843;nh m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c xinh x&#7855;n &#7903; gi&#7919;a, l&#7845;y l&amp;aacute; th&amp;ocirc;ng gi&#7843; trang tr&amp;iacute; l&amp;ecirc;n tr&amp;ecirc;n b&#7913;c tranh. &#272;&#417;n gi&#7843;n, d&#7877; l&amp;agrave;m v&amp;agrave; ch&#7859;ng t&#7889;n k&amp;egrave;m g&amp;igrave; c&#7843;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Nh&#7919;ng v&amp;ograve;ng tr&amp;ograve;n nh&#7887;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;500&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7853;n d&#7909;ng b&#7913;c t&#432;&#7901;ng tr&#7889;ng l&amp;agrave;m khu v&#7921;c trang tr&amp;iacute; cho Noel. Nh&#7919;ng v&amp;ograve;ng hoa nho nh&#7887; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i qu&#7843; &#273;&#7887;, chu&amp;ocirc;ng, ruy b&#259;ng, t&amp;ugrave;y nh&#7919;ng ph&#7909; ki&#7879;n b&#7841;n th&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&#7875; trang tr&amp;iacute; sao cho &#273;&#7865;p m&#7855;t nh&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. B&amp;ecirc;n ngo&amp;agrave;i c&#7917;a ra v&amp;agrave;o&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;500&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t c&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;ocirc;ng gi&#7843; ho&#7863;c m&#7897;t c&amp;agrave;nh b&amp;aacute;ch t&amp;aacute;n th&#7853;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trang tr&amp;iacute; b&#7857;ng nh&#7919;ng ph&#7909; ki&#7879;n Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh d&#7877; mua &#7903; b&#7845;t c&#7913; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng n&amp;agrave;o. B&#7841;n treo ch&amp;uacute;ng ngo&amp;agrave;i c&#7917;a ra v&amp;agrave;o, v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c v&#7883; kh&amp;aacute;ch bi&#7871;t r&#7857;ng, nh&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n s&#7861;n s&amp;agrave;ng cho Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh r&#7891;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. T&#7853;n d&#7909;ng c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&amp;egrave;n ch&amp;ugrave;m&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;700&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giang-sinh2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch nh&#7887; n&amp;agrave;o b&amp;agrave;y bi&#7879;n c&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng th&amp;igrave; n&amp;ecirc;n t&#7853;n d&#7909;ng nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;c &#273;&amp;egrave;n ch&amp;ugrave;m nh&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n. Treo nh&#7919;ng qu&#7843; b&amp;oacute;ng b&#7841;c nh&#7887; l&#7845;p l&amp;aacute;nh d&#432;&#7899;i &amp;aacute;nh &#273;i&#7879;n c&amp;agrave;ng khi&#7871;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian nh&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n tr&#7903; n&amp;ecirc;n lung linh h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7. T&#7853;n d&#7909;ng n&amp;oacute;c t&#7911;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;600&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giang-sinh.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&#7919;ng k&#7879; s&amp;aacute;ch, n&amp;oacute;c t&#7911;, k&#7869; h&#7903; c&amp;aacute;c b&#7913;c t&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7873;u c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7875; trang tr&amp;iacute; cho ng&amp;agrave;y Noel th&#7853;t t&#432;ng b&#7915;ng. Ch&#7885;n nh&#7919;ng c&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7887; xinh, c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7891; trang tr&amp;iacute; c&#361;ng nho nh&#7887; theo, b&#7841;n &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; g&amp;oacute;c Noel &#273;&amp;aacute;ng y&amp;ecirc;u r&#7891;i &#273;&amp;oacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8. Nh&#7919;ng v&amp;ograve;ng hoa nh&#7887; tr&amp;ecirc;n t&#7911; b&#7871;p&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#417;i th&#7875; hi&#7879;n s&#7921; &#273;&#7847;m &#7845;m c&#7911;a gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; thi&#7871;u m&#7897;t ch&amp;uacute;t g&amp;igrave; &#273;&amp;oacute; &#273;i&#7875;m t&amp;ocirc; cho Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh. B&#7841;n treo c&amp;aacute;c v&amp;ograve;ng hoa l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7911; b&#7871;p, trang tr&amp;iacute; b&#7857;ng ruy b&#259;ng satin.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9. S&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&amp;agrave;nh b&amp;aacute;ch t&amp;aacute;n, ruy b&#259;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBu&#7897;c ch&amp;uacute;ng l&#7841;i v&#7899;i nhau v&amp;agrave; treo l&amp;ecirc;n t&#432;&#7901;ng. &#272;&amp;acirc;y c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; bi&#7879;n ph&amp;aacute;p t&#259;ng m&amp;agrave;u xanh cho nh&amp;agrave;, gi&amp;uacute;p nh&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; c&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;c r&#7897;ng h&#417;n v&amp;igrave; d&amp;acirc;y tr&#7843;i d&amp;agrave;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh trong nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; n&#417;i b&#7841;n c&#7847;n mang kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7847;m &#7845;m, vui v&#7867; t&#7899;i. B&#7903;i v&amp;igrave; &#273;&amp;oacute; ch&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;agrave; n&#417;i m&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n x&#7843; stress, n&#417;i b&#7841;n th&#432; th&amp;aacute;i, h&amp;ograve;a m&amp;igrave;nh v&amp;agrave;o l&amp;agrave;n n&#432;&#7899;c n&amp;oacute;ng, xua &#273;i bao m&#7879;t m&#7887;i, &#432;u phi&#7873;n. M&#7897;t c&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7887; xinh trang tr&amp;iacute; v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c ph&#7909; ki&#7879;n, b&amp;oacute;ng th&#7911;y tinh v&amp;agrave; d&amp;agrave;n &#273;&amp;egrave;n nh&#7845;p nh&amp;aacute;y s&#7869; gi&amp;uacute;p c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng &#273;&#7865;p xinh h&#417;n r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;11. C&#7917;a s&#7893;, n&#7871;n, th&amp;ocirc;ng, b&#7897; ba ho&amp;agrave;n h&#7843;o&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;700&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giang-sinh6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7881; c&#7847;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng b&#7853;u c&#7917;a s&#7893; nh&#432; l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t thung l&#361;ng tuy&#7871;t tr&#7855;ng, n&#417;i c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng c&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng m&#7885;c ng&amp;uacute;t t&#7847;m m&#7855;t, kho&amp;aacute;c l&amp;ecirc;n m&amp;igrave;nh nh&#7919;ng d&#7843;i tuy&#7871;t s&amp;aacute;ng b&#7841;c, th&amp;ecirc;m &amp;aacute;nh n&#7871;n t&#7841;o hi&#7879;u &#7913;ng lung linh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;12. S&#7917; d&#7909;ng gh&#7871; &#7903; l&#7889;i v&amp;agrave;o&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;500&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel7.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&amp;agrave; ai c&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t l&#7889;i &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o th&amp;ocirc;ng tho&amp;aacute;ng, b&#7841;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; t&#7853;n d&#7909;ng nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;c gh&#7871; ch&#7901; &#273;&#7875; trang tr&amp;iacute; nh&#7919;ng m&amp;oacute;n &#273;&#7891; Noel l&amp;ecirc;n tr&amp;ecirc;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;13. Qu&#7843; b&amp;oacute;ng Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh l&amp;agrave;m b&amp;igrave;nh hoa&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel8.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&#7919;ng qu&#7843; b&amp;oacute;ng th&#7911;y tinh ho&#7863;c b&#7857;ng nh&#7921;a s&#7855;c m&amp;agrave;u r&#7921;c r&#7905; gi&amp;uacute;p b&amp;agrave;n &#259;n s&amp;aacute;ng h&#417;n. C&#7855;m hoa trang tr&amp;iacute; l&amp;ecirc;n. B&amp;agrave;n &#259;n v&#7915;a s&#7889;ng &#273;&#7897;ng l&#7841;i v&#7915;a ng&#7853;p tr&amp;agrave;n m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;14. S&#7917; d&#7909;ng tr&#7855;ng &amp;ndash; &#273;&#7887; truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;700&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giang-sinh10.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;700&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giang-sinh13.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nS&#7855;c &#273;&#7887; truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng lu&amp;ocirc;n l&amp;agrave;m m&amp;agrave;u c&#7911;a Gi&amp;aacute;ng sinh. C&amp;acirc;y gi&#7843; m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng, trang tr&amp;iacute; b&amp;oacute;ng &#273;&#7887;, ruy b&#259;ng &#273;&#7887; n&#7893;i b&#7853;t. D&#432;&#7899;i ch&amp;acirc;n c&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng h&#7897;p qu&amp;agrave; nh&#7887; v&#7899;i n&#417; voan xinh x&#7855;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;15. T&#7853;n d&#7909;ng c&#7917;a s&#7893; b&#7871;p&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel9.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#7917;a s&#7893; b&#7871;p c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; n&#417;i l&amp;iacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7875; trang tr&amp;iacute; cho Noel th&amp;ecirc;m n&#7891;ng n&amp;agrave;n. D&amp;aacute;n h&amp;igrave;nh b&amp;ocirc;ng tuy&#7871;t l&amp;ecirc;n c&#7917;a s&#7893;, l&#7873; c&#7917;a s&#7893; trang tr&amp;iacute; b&#7857;ng nh&#7919;ng c&amp;agrave;nh b&amp;aacute;ch t&amp;aacute;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;16. S&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7853;t trang tr&amp;iacute; nh&#7887;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel10.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel11.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nKh&amp;ocirc;ng gian nh&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng cho ph&amp;eacute;p &#273;&#7875; c&amp;acirc;y to v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7891; trang tr&amp;iacute; to v&amp;igrave; n&amp;oacute; chi&#7871;m h&#7871;t th&#7901;i gian. N&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c store ch&#7885;n c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7891; trang tr&amp;iacute; nh&#7887; nh&#7887;, xinh xinh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;17. &#272;&#417;n gi&#7843;n m&amp;agrave; ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel12.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i t&#7889;n c&amp;ocirc;ng l&#7841;m d&#7909;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian trong nh&amp;agrave;, ch&#7881; c&#7847;n 3 c&amp;acirc;y th&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7887; trang tr&amp;iacute; nh&#432; trong &#7843;nh, nh&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n c&#361;ng &#273;&#7911; kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&amp;oacute;n Gi&amp;aacute;ng&amp;nbsp;sinh r&#7891;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/div&gt;','16/12/2011','16/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noel12.jpg',38,11,2212,'huyennt',1,'dem-khong-khi-noel-vao-nha','Gi&aacute;ng sinh, kh&ocirc;ng gian nh&agrave;, Noel, Santa Claus, c&acirc;y th&ocirc;ng, giang sinh, qu&agrave; gi&aacute;ng sinh, kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; gi&aacute;ng sinh, khong khi giang sinh',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Gi&aacute;ng sinh, kh&ocirc;ng gian nh&agrave;, Noel, Santa Claus, c&acirc;y th&ocirc;ng, giang sinh, qu&agrave; gi&aacute;ng sinh, kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; gi&aacute;ng sinh, khong khi giang sinh',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - theo: http://dothi.net/',1,0,0,0),(142,'Khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m - T&#7853;p trung thu h&uacute;t nh&agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c','T&#7841;i bu&#7893;i h&#7885;p b&aacute;o c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh v&agrave; k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch tri&#7875;n khai &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng Khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m ng&agrave;y 16-12, &ocirc;ng Trang B&#7843;o S&#417;n, Ph&oacute; Tr&#432;&#7903;ng ban Qu&#7843;n l&yacute; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; - x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m (BQL Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m) cho bi&#7871;t, n&#259;m 2012 TPHCM s&#7869; &#273;&#7849;y nhanh vi&#7879;c x&uacute;c ti&#7871;n m&#7901;i g&#7885;i c&aacute;c nh&agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&agrave;o m&#7897;t s&#7889; d&#7921; &aacute;n h&#7841; t&#7847;ng, c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh tr&#7885;ng &#273;i&#7875;m c&#7911;a khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m, trong &#273;&oacute; t&#7853;p trung thu h&uacute;t c&aacute;c nh&agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c c&oacute; th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u v&agrave; &#273;&#7859;ng c&#7845;p qu&#7889;c t&#7871; &#273;&#7875; tri&#7875;n khai c&aacute;c d&#7921; &aacute;n t&#7841;i &#273;&acirc;y.','&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; &quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S&#7869; l&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; &#273;&#7865;p nh&#7845;t &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng Nam &amp;Aacute;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo BQL Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m, m&#7897;t trong c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n h&#7841; t&#7847;ng tr&#7885;ng &#273;i&#7875;m s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c tri&#7875;n khai trong n&#259;m 2012 l&amp;agrave; 4 tuy&#7871;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ch&amp;iacute;nh t&#7841;i khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m. &#272;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7841;i l&#7897; v&amp;ograve;ng cung, &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ven h&#7891; trung t&amp;acirc;m, &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ven s&amp;ocirc;ng S&amp;agrave;i G&amp;ograve;n v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n cao.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;400&quot; height=&quot;296&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/thu-thiem(1).jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&#7889;n tuy&#7871;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;agrave; tr&#7909;c ch&amp;iacute;nh c&#7911;a h&#7841; t&#7847;ng k&#7929; thu&#7853;t, qua &#273;&amp;oacute; s&#7869; t&#7841;o &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n k&#7871;t n&#7889;i cho c&amp;aacute;c tuy&#7871;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng kh&amp;aacute;c. Hi&#7879;n 4 tuy&#7871;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;agrave;y TP &#273;&amp;atilde; giao cho T&#7893;ng C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n h&#7841; t&#7847;ng v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh Vi&#7879;t Nam (VIDIFI) l&amp;agrave;m ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;. D&#7921; ki&#7871;n, kho&#7843;ng qu&amp;yacute; 3-2012 ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; s&#7869; kh&#7903;i c&amp;ocirc;ng v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng v&#7889;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; d&#7921; ki&#7871;n kho&#7843;ng 10.000 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Khu l&amp;otilde;i trung t&amp;acirc;m - trung t&amp;acirc;m ch&amp;iacute;nh c&#7911;a Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m s&#7869; l&amp;agrave; khu v&#7921;c t&#7853;p trung c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n tr&#7885;ng &#273;i&#7875;m c&#7911;a TP nh&#432; Trung t&amp;acirc;m h&#7897;i ngh&#7883; qu&#7889;c t&#7871;, qu&#7843;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng trung t&amp;acirc;m v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t l&amp;agrave; Trung t&amp;acirc;m t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh qu&#7889;c t&#7871; v&amp;agrave; giao d&#7883;ch th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i. Trong &#273;&amp;oacute;, &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Trung t&amp;acirc;m t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh qu&#7889;c t&#7871; v&amp;agrave; giao d&#7883;ch th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i, TP &#273;&amp;atilde; thu&#7853;n ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng giao cho VietinBank l&amp;agrave;m nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, hi&#7879;n &#273;ang ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh &amp;yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng v&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p &#273;&#7875; tr&amp;igrave;nh UBND TP. &amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;&#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&amp;oacute; &amp;yacute; ngh&#297;a r&#7845;t quan tr&#7885;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; v&#7899;i c&#417; c&#7845;u ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng c&#7911;a khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m m&amp;agrave; c&amp;ograve;n l&amp;agrave; ch&amp;igrave;a kh&amp;oacute;a m&#7903; ra kh&#7843; n&#259;ng v&amp;agrave; tri&#7875;n v&#7885;ng m&#7899;i cho TP trong qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh h&#7897;i nh&#7853;p&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;- &amp;ocirc;ng Trang B&#7843;o S&#417;n cho hay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, m&#7897;t s&#7889; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n tr&#7885;ng &#273;i&#7875;m t&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; ch&#7885;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; nh&#432; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n th&amp;aacute;p &#273;a ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng v&#7899;i di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch 8,7ha, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; th&amp;aacute;p quan s&amp;aacute;t v&#7899;i chi&#7873;u cao t&#7889;i &#273;a l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 86 t&#7847;ng. D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thu&#7853;n ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng giao cho li&amp;ecirc;n doanh Ki&#7871;n Ph&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave; Capital Land, hi&#7879;n &#273;ang l&amp;agrave;m th&#7911; t&#7909;c &#273;&#7875; c&#7845;p gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &amp;ocirc;ng S&#417;n, t&amp;ograve;a th&amp;aacute;p n&amp;agrave;y s&#7869; l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n c&#7911;a Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; t&amp;iacute;nh &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng cao. C&amp;ograve;n c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n nh&#432; qu&#7843;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng trung t&amp;acirc;m, c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n b&#7901; s&amp;ocirc;ng, c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng th&amp;igrave; TP s&#7869; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; khi quy ho&#7841;ch chi ti&#7871;t 1/500 ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh, d&#7921; ki&#7871;n v&amp;agrave;o cu&#7889;i n&#259;m 2012. Theo &#273;&amp;oacute;, h&#7841; t&#7847;ng c&#7911;a to&amp;agrave;n b&#7897; khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#7847;m h&amp;oacute;a, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian ng&#7847;m &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; &#7903; khu v&#7921;c l&amp;otilde;i trung t&amp;acirc;m. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m s&#7869; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng truy&#7873;n m&#7841;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng d&amp;acirc;y v&#7899;i t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; cao, h&#7841; t&#7847;ng vi&#7877;n th&amp;ocirc;ng t&#7889;t nh&#7845;t &#273;&#7875; ph&#7909;c v&#7909; c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&#7873; t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh t&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;Khi ti&#7871;p x&amp;uacute;c v&#7899;i ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i, c&amp;aacute;c chuy&amp;ecirc;n gia, c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; t&#432; v&#7845;n qu&#7889;c t&#7871; c&#361;ng nh&#432; c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&amp;aacute;nh gi&amp;aacute; r&#7845;t cao v&#7873; khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m. N&#7871;u l&amp;agrave;m t&#7889;t th&amp;igrave; v&#7873; l&amp;acirc;u d&amp;agrave;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y s&#7869; l&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; &#273;&#7865;p nh&#7845;t &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng Nam &amp;Aacute; v&amp;agrave; s&#7869; thu h&amp;uacute;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;- &amp;ocirc;ng S&#417;n nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7883;nh. &amp;Ocirc;ng S&#417;n c&#361;ng cho bi&#7871;t, theo k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch c&#7911;a TP, n&#259;m 2015 ph&#7843;i ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh c&#417; b&#7843;n &#273;&#7875; c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;agrave;i c&#7911;a Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thu h&#7891;i th&amp;ecirc;m 1 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n h&#7841; t&#7847;ng, TP s&#7869; d&amp;agrave;nh m&#7897;t s&#7889; khu &#273;&#7845;t &#273;&#7875; &#273;em b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7845;u gi&amp;aacute; ho&#7863;c giao cho c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;. Hi&#7879;n c&amp;oacute; 2 khu &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a ra &#273;&#7845;u th&#7847;u l&amp;agrave; khu nh&amp;agrave; th&#7845;p t&#7847;ng c&amp;oacute; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch kho&#7843;ng 11,8ha v&amp;agrave; khu tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7885;c c&amp;oacute; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch 11,3ha. &amp;Ocirc;ng Trang B&#7843;o S&#417;n th&#7915;a nh&#7853;n, trong t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh &#273;ang kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n th&amp;igrave; vi&#7879;c &#273;&#432;a ra &#273;&#7845;u th&#7847;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i v&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&#361;ng g&#7863;p nhi&#7873;u th&amp;aacute;ch th&#7913;c trong vi&#7879;c s&#7855;p x&#7871;p t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, theo &amp;ocirc;ng S&#417;n, khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n kinh doanh m&amp;agrave; l&amp;agrave; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; n&amp;ecirc;n c&#361;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; r&#7845;t k&#7929;. H&#417;n n&#7919;a, hi&#7879;n qu&#7929; &#273;&#7845;t c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng nhi&#7873;u do &#273;&amp;oacute; BQL Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m s&#7869; ch&#7855;t l&#7885;c c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; l&#7899;n c&amp;oacute; th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u, uy t&amp;iacute;n v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7859;ng c&#7845;p qu&#7889;c t&#7871; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n tr&#7885;ng &#273;i&#7875;m t&#7841;i khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y, m&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; xin tham gia v&amp;agrave;o khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m nh&#432;ng TP v&#7851;n ch&#432;a &amp;ldquo;g&#7853;t &#273;&#7847;u&amp;rdquo;. &amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;&#272;&#7875; chu&#7849;n b&#7883; cho c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c k&amp;ecirc;u g&#7885;i &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, TP &#273;&amp;atilde; giao cho c&amp;aacute;c s&#7903;, ng&amp;agrave;nh li&amp;ecirc;n quan chu&#7849;n b&#7883; m&#7897;t s&#7889; ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch &#432;u &#273;&amp;atilde;i cho c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, d&#7921; ki&#7871;n s&#7869; ban h&amp;agrave;nh trong n&#259;m 2012&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo; - &amp;ocirc;ng S&#417;n cho hay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Li&amp;ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n 2 d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m t&#7841;i khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m, BQL Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m cho bi&#7871;t, ngo&amp;agrave;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n C&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m c&amp;oacute; v&#7889;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; 1,2 t&#7927; USD v&#7915;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c TP ch&#7845;p thu&#7853;n thu h&#7891;i gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, hi&#7879;n BQL Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m &#273;ang ki&#7871;n ngh&#7883; thu h&#7891;i m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch c&#7911;a d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n C&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n tri th&#7913;c Vi&#7879;t - Nh&#7853;t do C&amp;ocirc;ng ty c&#7893; ph&#7847;n Ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n ngu&#7891;n l&#7921;c Vi&#7879;t - Nh&#7853;t (VIJA) l&amp;agrave;m ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;. D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&#7903;i c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave;o th&amp;aacute;ng 12-2008 v&#7899;i di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch 10,3ha, c&amp;oacute; t&#7893;ng v&#7889;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; kho&#7843;ng 610 tri&#7879;u USD. Do &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7911;a suy tho&amp;aacute;i kinh t&#7871; to&amp;agrave;n c&#7847;u, ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n n&amp;ecirc;n xin &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh quy m&amp;ocirc; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n xu&#7889;ng c&amp;ograve;n 3,3ha.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;7ha m&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; xin &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh sau khi TP thu h&#7891;i s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quy ho&#7841;ch x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng khu b&#7879;nh vi&#7879;n &#273;a khoa qu&#7889;c t&#7871; nh&#432; &#273;&amp;atilde; quy ho&#7841;ch tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;acirc;y&amp;rdquo; - &amp;ocirc;ng D&#432;&#417;ng C&amp;ocirc;ng Lu&#7853;n, Tr&#432;&#7903;ng ph&amp;ograve;ng k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; BQL Th&#7911; Thi&amp;ecirc;m cho bi&#7871;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;','17/12/2011','17/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/thu-thiem(1).jpg',28,8,2026,'huyennt',1,'khu-do-thi-moi-thu-thiem-tap-trung-thu-hut-nha-dau-tu-chien-luoc',' Khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m - T&#7853;p trung thu h&uacute;t nh&agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c, khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883;, do thi, thu hut d&#432; an, thu h&uacute;t,&#273;&#7847;u t&#432;',NULL,NULL,NULL,' Khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i Th&#7911; Thi&ecirc;m - T&#7853;p trung thu h&uacute;t nh&agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c, khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883;, do thi, thu hut d&#432; an, thu h&uacute;t,&#273;&#7847;u t&#432;',0,0,0,'','','',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - Theo: http://www.diaoconline.vn',1,0,0,0),(143,'Ch&#7845;m d&#7913;t m&#7901;i g&#7885;i &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&aacute;c d&#7921; &aacute;n th&eacute;p, xim&#259;ng','Ng&agrave;y 14-12, t&#7841;i H&#7897;i ngh&#7883; ngo&#7841;i giao l&#7847;n th&#7913; 27, Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Nguy&#7877;n T&#7845;n D&#361;ng &#273;&atilde; y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u ch&#7845;m d&#7913;t m&#7901;i g&#7885;i &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&#7899;i c&aacute;c d&#7921; &aacute;n th&eacute;p, xim&#259;ng, may m&#7863;c...','\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/thep-cay---gia-thep---VNE.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTh&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Nguy&#7877;n T&#7845;n D&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;a ra nh&#7919;ng vi&#7879;c r&#7845;t c&#7909; th&#7875;. &amp;Ocirc;ng cho r&#7857;ng nhi&#7879;m v&#7909; c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7841;i s&#7913;, tham t&amp;aacute;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i s&#7855;p t&#7899;i ph&#7843;i v&#7853;n &#273;&#7897;ng quy&#7871;t li&#7879;t &#273;&#7875; c&amp;aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c c&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n VN l&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c c&amp;oacute; n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng (hi&#7879;n nay m&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; 29 n&#432;&#7899;c c&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ph&#7843;i b&#7843;o v&#7879; &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7857;ng s&amp;ocirc;ng C&#7917;u Long&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7863;t kh&amp;aacute;c, Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng giao nhi&#7879;m v&#7909; ng&amp;agrave;nh ngo&#7841;i giao ph&#7843;i g&amp;oacute;p ph&#7847;n m&#7903; r&#7897;ng th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7875; thu h&amp;uacute;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave; xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u h&amp;agrave;ng h&amp;oacute;a. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng thu h&amp;uacute;t c&amp;aacute;c ng&amp;agrave;nh nh&#432; xim&#259;ng, th&amp;eacute;p, da gi&amp;agrave;y, may m&#7863;c... n&#7919;a m&amp;agrave; t&#7853;p trung v&amp;agrave;o c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n, t&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n c&amp;oacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; cao.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;&#272;&#417;n c&#7917; T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n Intel, n&#259;m nay xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u 1,5 t&#7881; USD, d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o ph&#7845;n &#273;&#7845;u n&#259;m 2015 s&#7869; xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u 5 t&#7881; USD&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo; - Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng cho bi&#7871;t ch&#7881; nh&#432; v&#7853;y m&#7899;i thay &#273;&#7893;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#417; c&#7845;u kinh t&#7871;. B&#7843;n th&amp;acirc;n ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch trong n&#432;&#7899;c, Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh c&#361;ng s&#7869; &#273;&#7893;i m&#7899;i theo h&#432;&#7899;ng &#432;u &#273;&amp;atilde;i h&#7871;t m&#7913;c c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7875; thu h&amp;uacute;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7873; ngo&#7841;i giao ch&amp;iacute;nh tr&#7883;, Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;o m&#7909;c ti&amp;ecirc;u cao nh&#7845;t trong &#273;&#7889;i tho&#7841;i qu&#7889;c t&#7871; l&amp;agrave; l&#7907;i &amp;iacute;ch qu&#7889;c gia - d&amp;acirc;n t&#7897;c ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t l&amp;ecirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u. V&amp;iacute; d&#7909; n&#7871;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng 11 th&#7911;y &#273;i&#7879;n tr&amp;ecirc;n s&amp;ocirc;ng Mekong s&#7869; m&#7845;t &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7857;ng s&amp;ocirc;ng C&#7917;u Long. Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng h&#7887;i v&#7853;y 21 tri&#7879;u ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n &#7903; &#273;&amp;acirc;y s&#7869; sinh s&#7889;ng ra sao v&amp;agrave; nh&#7845;n m&#7841;nh &amp;ldquo;&#273;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; l&#7907;i &amp;iacute;ch r&#7845;t ch&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&amp;aacute;ng, ch&amp;uacute;ng ta ph&#7843;i b&#7843;o v&#7879;&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Doanh nghi&#7879;p c&#7847;n ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;aacute;t bi&#7875;u v&#7873; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng M&#7929;, &amp;ocirc;ng &#272;&amp;agrave;o Tr&#7847;n Nh&amp;acirc;n - ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#7913;ng &#273;&#7847;u th&#432;&#417;ng v&#7909; t&#7841;i M&#7929; - cho bi&#7871;t &#7903; th&#7911; &#273;&amp;ocirc; M&#7929; &#273;ang c&amp;oacute; t&#7899;i h&#417;n 12.000 ng&#432;&#7901;i v&#7853;n &#273;&#7897;ng h&amp;agrave;nh lang v&amp;agrave; v&#7873; v&#7909; c&amp;aacute; da tr&#417;n, h&#7885; &#273;ang l&amp;agrave;m nhi&#7873;u vi&#7879;c n&#7921;c c&#432;&#7901;i, nh&#432; t&#7915; ch&#7895; y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; coi c&amp;aacute; tra, ba sa c&#7911;a VN l&amp;agrave; catfish r&#7891;i l&#7841;i y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u ph&#7843;i coi &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; catfish.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&amp;ecirc;u kinh nghi&#7879;m doanh nghi&#7879;p M&#7929; th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;i c&amp;ugrave;ng c&amp;aacute;c &#273;o&amp;agrave;n &#273;&amp;agrave;m ph&amp;aacute;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i, l&#7921;c l&#432;&#7907;ng c&amp;ograve;n &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng h&#417;n c&#7843; &#273;o&amp;agrave;n &#273;&amp;agrave;m ph&amp;aacute;n, &amp;ocirc;ng Nh&amp;acirc;n khuy&#7871;n ngh&#7883; doanh nghi&#7879;p VN c&#361;ng c&#7847;n ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng B&amp;ugrave;i Thanh S&#417;n, th&#7913; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; Ngo&#7841;i giao, n&amp;ecirc;u th&#7921;c t&#7871;: &amp;ldquo;T&amp;ocirc;i &#273;&#7871;n m&#7897;t s&#7889; n&#432;&#7899;c, h&#7887;i tham t&amp;aacute;n, ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#7913;ng &#273;&#7847;u c&#417; quan ngo&#7841;i giao th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng bi&#7871;t doanh nghi&#7879;p ta &#273;&amp;atilde; h&#7907;p t&amp;aacute;c l&amp;agrave;m &#259;n &#7903; n&#432;&#7899;c b&#7841;n r&#7891;i&amp;rdquo;. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, &amp;ocirc;ng S&#417;n cho r&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p c&#7847;n ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u tham t&amp;aacute;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i gi&amp;uacute;p &#273;&#7905; v&amp;igrave; &amp;ldquo;khi tr&#7909;c tr&#7863;c doanh nghi&#7879;p m&#7899;i quay l&#7841;i c&#417; quan ngo&#7841;i giao, l&amp;uacute;c &#273;&amp;oacute; th&amp;igrave; &#273;&amp;atilde; h&#7887;ng r&#7891;i&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Tr&#7847;n Trung Th&#7921;c, tham t&amp;aacute;n c&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7913; t&#7841;i B&#7881; v&amp;agrave; EU, th&amp;ocirc;ng tin khu v&#7921;c ch&amp;acirc;u &amp;Acirc;u &#273;ang kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n v&amp;agrave; h&#7885; s&#7869; thay &#273;&#7893;i n&amp;ecirc;n m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&#417; c&#7845;u xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u c&#7911;a VN c&#361;ng ph&#7843;i thay &#273;&#7893;i. Trong kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, &amp;ocirc;ng Th&#7921;c n&amp;ecirc;u c&#417; h&#7897;i &amp;ldquo;h&#7879; th&#7889;ng ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i c&#7911;a ch&amp;acirc;u &amp;Acirc;u kh&amp;aacute; gi&amp;agrave; c&#7895;i, b&amp;igrave;nh th&#432;&#7901;ng r&#7845;t kh&amp;oacute; chen v&amp;agrave;o nh&#432;ng khi kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n h&#7885; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; nh&#432;&#7907;ng b&#7897;, h&amp;agrave;ng VN c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; th&amp;acirc;m nh&#7853;p&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tham t&amp;aacute;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i VN t&#7841;i Trung Qu&#7889;c Nguy&#7877;n Duy Ph&amp;uacute; th&amp;igrave; kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh h&#7871;t th&amp;aacute;ng 11-2011, nh&#7853;p si&amp;ecirc;u c&#7911;a VN v&#7899;i Trung Qu&#7889;c &#273;&amp;atilde; l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i 12,36 t&#7881; USD, t&#259;ng 6,1% so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923; n&#259;m 2010 v&amp;agrave; cho r&#7857;ng m&#7913;c &#273;&#7897; ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c c&#7911;a VN v&amp;agrave;o h&amp;agrave;ng Trung Qu&#7889;c l&amp;agrave; r&#7845;t cao.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;p &#273;&#7883;nh th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i t&#7921; do ASEAN - Trung Qu&#7889;c m&amp;agrave; VN tham gia, theo &amp;ocirc;ng Ph&amp;uacute;, th&amp;uacute;c &#273;&#7849;y xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u c&#7843; hai b&amp;ecirc;n, nh&#432;ng h&amp;agrave;ng Trung Qu&#7889;c c&amp;oacute; s&#7913;c c&#7841;nh tranh t&#7889;t h&#417;n n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&amp;atilde; xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u cao h&#417;n. &#272;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2015, VN s&#7869; ph&#7843;i c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m thu&#7871; quan theo&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;p &#273;&#7883;nh th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i t&#7921; do ASEAN - Trung Qu&#7889;c n&amp;ecirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u Trung Qu&#7889;c c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c t&#259;ng...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Ph&amp;uacute; ki&#7871;n ngh&#7883; c&#7847;n t&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7853;p hu&#7845;n doanh nghi&#7879;p v&#7873; c&amp;aacute;c &#432;u &#273;&amp;atilde;i v&#7873; thu&#7871; c&#7911;a Trung Qu&#7889;c c&#361;ng nh&#432; nh&#7919;ng quy &#273;&#7883;nh m&#7899;i c&#7911;a h&#7885; v&#7873; h&amp;agrave;ng th&#7921;c ph&#7849;m, h&#7843;i s&#7843;n..., n&#7871;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng doanh nghi&#7879;p VN c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ch&#7883;u thi&#7879;t h&#7841;i l&#7899;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nhi&#7873;u th&#432;&#417;ng v&#7909; c&#7911;a VN thi&#7871;u t&amp;iacute;ch c&#7921;c&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7913; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng Nguy&#7877;n Th&amp;agrave;nh Bi&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&amp;aacute;n b&#7897; tham t&amp;aacute;n th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i, c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;aacute;n b&#7897; t&#7841;i th&#432;&#417;ng v&#7909; c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; th&amp;aacute;i &#273;&#7897; nhi&#7879;m k&#7923;, thi&#7871;u t&amp;iacute;ch c&#7921;c. &amp;Ocirc;ng Bi&amp;ecirc;n v&amp;iacute; d&#7909; chuy&#7879;n m&#7899;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y n&amp;oacute;i gi&amp;aacute; g&#7841;o cao, s&#7869; thi&#7871;u g&#7841;o nh&#432;ng ch&#432;a &#273;&#7847;y m&#7897;t th&amp;aacute;ng gi&amp;aacute; xu&#7889;ng r&#7845;t th&#7845;p. &lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;&#272;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#7863;t ra nhi&#7879;m v&#7909; &#7913;ng ph&amp;oacute; nhanh nh&#7841;y v&amp;agrave; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng th&#432;&#417;ng v&#7909; c&#7847;n n&#7855;m b&#7855;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xu h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7875; th&amp;ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; trong n&#432;&#7899;c&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em&gt; - &amp;ocirc;ng Bi&amp;ecirc;n n&amp;oacute;i v&amp;agrave; cho r&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;c th&#432;&#417;ng v&#7909; c&#7847;n &#273;&#7893;i m&#7899;i nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; n&amp;acirc;ng hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c th&#432;&#417;ng v&#7909;, B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; th&#7859;ng th&#7855;n ki&#7871;n ngh&#7883; c&#7847;n c&amp;oacute; quy &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&#7875; tr&amp;aacute;nh ch&#7891;ng ch&amp;eacute;o, m&amp;acirc;u thu&#7851;n trong ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;o c&#7911;a b&#7897; v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7841;i s&#7913; qu&amp;aacute;n. Ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng chuy&amp;ecirc;n m&amp;ocirc;n c&#7911;a th&#432;&#417;ng v&#7909;, theo B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng, c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7897;c l&#7853;p t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#7889;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#432;&#7899;c nhi&#7873;u &amp;yacute; ki&#7871;n cho r&#7857;ng th&#432;&#417;ng v&#7909; &#273;&#7871;n b&amp;aacute;o c&amp;aacute;o v&#7873; t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh c&#361;ng ph&#7843;i tr&amp;igrave;nh, xin &amp;yacute; ki&#7871;n &#273;&#7841;i s&#7913;, B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng l&#7847;n n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;atilde; th&#7859;ng th&#7855;n y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u: c&amp;aacute;c nhi&#7879;m v&#7909; mang t&amp;iacute;nh chuy&amp;ecirc;n m&amp;ocirc;n c&#7911;a th&#432;&#417;ng v&#7909; c&#7847;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p t&#7915; B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng v&amp;agrave; th&#432;&#417;ng v&#7909; ch&#7881; c&#7847;n th&amp;ocirc;ng b&amp;aacute;o &#273;&#7875; ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#7913;ng &#273;&#7847;u c&#417; quan &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n bi&#7871;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t &#273;i&#7875;m &#273;&#7897;t ph&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7875; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; gi&amp;uacute;p doanh nghi&#7879;p l&amp;agrave; B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; t&#7841;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; n&#417;i c&#7847;n cho ph&amp;eacute;p thu&amp;ecirc; c&amp;aacute;n b&#7897;, t&#432; v&#7845;n n&#432;&#7899;c s&#7903; t&#7841;i. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u cho th&amp;iacute; &#273;i&#7875;m c&#417; ch&#7871; th&#432;&#417;ng v&#7909; nh&#7853;n &#7911;y th&amp;aacute;c c&#7911;a doanh nghi&#7879;p theo h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o ngu&#