 nghi&#7879;p trong ng&amp;agrave;nh ch&#7881; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&#7847;m ch&#7915;ng &#273;&#7875; tr&amp;aacute;nh t&#7891;n kho c&#361;ng nh&#432; &#273;&#7885;ng v&#7889;n, n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7871;n h&#7871;t th&amp;aacute;ng 11/2012 &#273;&#7841;t 6,44 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c gi&#7843;m 1,5% so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923; n&#259;m ngo&amp;aacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, hai th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u ch&amp;iacute;nh c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam l&amp;agrave; Nh&#7853;t B&#7843;n v&amp;agrave; Trung Qu&#7889;c &#273;&#7873;u ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng n&amp;ecirc;n trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;atilde; x&#7843;y ra hi&#7879;n t&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7841;nh tranh kh&amp;ocirc;ng l&amp;agrave;nh m&#7841;nh, b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7849;y l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; v&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;m l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7891;n kho. Hi&#7879;n nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;ang ch&amp;agrave;o gi&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p h&#417;n gi&amp;aacute; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7915; 200.000-300.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;D&#7851;n ch&#7913;ng v&#7873; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh th&#7901;i gian g&#7847;n &#273;&amp;acirc;y, Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam cho bi&#7871;t s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh nh&#7845;t r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o th&amp;aacute;ng S&amp;aacute;u, ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;t 298.000 t&#7845;n, b&#432;&#7899;c sang th&amp;aacute;ng B&#7843;y v&amp;agrave; th&amp;aacute;ng T&amp;aacute;m, nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&#7843;i gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n th&amp;eacute;p t&#7915; 100.000-300.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n th&amp;igrave; l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; m&#7899;i kh&amp;aacute; l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kho&#7843;ng 483.000 t&#7845;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, b&#432;&#7899;c sang th&amp;aacute;ng Ch&amp;iacute;n n&#259;m nay, khi th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;agrave;y b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u kh&#7903;i s&#7855;c, gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#259;ng th&amp;ecirc;m t&#7915; 200.000-400.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n so v&#7899;i th&amp;aacute;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;oacute; th&amp;igrave; l&#432;&#7907;ng th&amp;eacute;p b&amp;aacute;n ra l&#7841;i gi&#7843;m c&amp;ograve;n 380.000 t&#7845;n; th&amp;aacute;ng 10, l&#432;&#7907;ng th&amp;eacute;p b&amp;aacute;n ra ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c gi&#7843;m, ch&#7881; c&amp;ograve;n 326.000 t&#7845;n v&amp;agrave; sang th&amp;aacute;ng 11 - th&amp;aacute;ng cao &#273;i&#7875;m trong m&amp;ugrave;a x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng cu&#7889;i n&#259;m c&#361;ng ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;t 350.000 t&#7845;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;300&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/gia-thep.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Do s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p y&#7871;u n&amp;ecirc;n l&#432;&#7907;ng th&amp;eacute;p t&#7891;n kho &#7903; c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7871;n h&#7871;t th&amp;aacute;ng 11 l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n 365.000 t&#7845;n, trong khi m&#7913;c t&#7891;n kho b&amp;igrave;nh qu&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng n&#259;m ch&#7881; kho&#7843;ng 250.000 t&#7845;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i c&#361;ng cho hay m&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7891;n kho ch&#432;a &#273;&#7871;n m&#7913;c b&amp;aacute;o &#273;&#7897;ng, nh&#432;ng &#273;i&#7873;u &#273;&amp;aacute;ng lo ng&#7841;i l&amp;agrave; t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng n&amp;agrave;y di&#7877;n ra t&#7915; th&amp;aacute;ng S&amp;aacute;u &#273;&#7871;n nay. &#272;&amp;aacute;ng ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute;, v&#7899;i l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t cao nh&#432; hi&#7879;n nay, m&#7895;i t&#7845;n th&amp;eacute;p t&#7891;n kho, doanh nghi&#7879;p ph&#7843;i tr&#7843; l&amp;atilde;i vay ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7915; 200.000-300.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n c&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c kho&#7843;n chi ph&amp;iacute; kh&amp;aacute;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p cu&#7897;n b&amp;aacute;n ra t&#7841;i nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y, ch&#432;a tr&#7915; chi&#7871;t kh&#7845;u v&amp;agrave; thu&#7871; gi&amp;aacute; tr&#7883; gia t&#259;ng ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n &#7903; m&#7913;c 15,7-15,95 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n t&#7841;i ph&amp;iacute;a B&#7855;c v&amp;agrave; t&#7915; 16,32-17,4 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n &#7903; ph&amp;iacute;a Nam; gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n l&#7867; th&amp;eacute;p ngo&amp;agrave;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n &#7903; m&#7913;c 18-18,7 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo m&#7897;t s&#7889; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, th&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng, khi s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng gi&#7843;m s&amp;uacute;t v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7875; k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7847;u, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t l&amp;agrave; trong b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m nh&#432; hi&#7879;n nay, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p ph&#7843;i chia s&#7867; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, ph&#7843;i gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7875; c&amp;ugrave;ng nhau &amp;ldquo;s&#432;&#7903;i &#7845;m&amp;rdquo; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, nh&#432;ng c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p l&#7841;i gi&#7919; nguy&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n, ch&#7881; t&#259;ng chi&#7871;t kh&#7845;u b&amp;aacute;n h&amp;agrave;ng cho c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute; t&#7915; 1-1,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. Ch&amp;iacute;nh &#273;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&amp;atilde; kh&amp;ocirc;ng k&amp;iacute;ch th&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7913;c mua tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n m&#7913;c t&#7891;n kho l&#7899;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p l&#7841;i cho r&#7857;ng, m&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave;, l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7891;n kho l&#7899;n, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; ch&#7853;m, nh&#432;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n do hi&#7879;n nay c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ngu&#7891;n nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;oacute; v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; cao, n&#7871;u gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n s&#7869; b&#7883; l&#7895; n&#7863;ng. C&amp;ograve;n c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i cho r&#7857;ng, s&#7903; d&#297; c&amp;aacute;c h&amp;atilde;ng th&amp;eacute;p ch&#432;a ch&#7883;u gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; l&amp;agrave; do s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;ang qu&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p, n&#7871;u gi&#7843;m l&amp;uacute;c n&amp;agrave;y r&#7845;t d&#7877; t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng t&amp;acirc;m l&amp;yacute; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng mu&#7889;n ch&#7901; gi&amp;aacute; xu&#7889;ng n&#7919;a m&#7899;i mua, l&amp;uacute;c &#273;&amp;oacute; s&#7869; g&amp;acirc;y b&#7845;t l&#7907;i cho nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, &#273;&#7875; g&amp;oacute;p ph&#7847;n b&#7843;o &#273;&#7843;m ngu&#7891;n cung, b&amp;igrave;nh &#7893;n gi&amp;aacute; c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng thi&#7871;t y&#7871;u trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, T&#7893;ng C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam &#273;ang ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c r&amp;agrave; so&amp;aacute;t c&amp;aacute;c kho&#7843;n chi ph&amp;iacute; c&#7845;u th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t nh&#7857;m minh b&#7841;ch gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng. H&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i th&amp;eacute;p thu&#7897;c T&#7893;ng C&amp;ocirc;ng ty &#273;&#7873;u th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n nghi&amp;ecirc;m t&amp;uacute;c ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;o c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng v&amp;agrave; c&#7911;a Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911;, ni&amp;ecirc;m y&#7871;t, ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i gi&amp;aacute; nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7849;m &#7903; t&#7915;ng &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute; ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i theo t&#7915;ng ng&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam c&#361;ng cho hay c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;aacute;n c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c trong n&#259;m 2011 &#273;&#7841;t kho&#7843;ng 9 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, s&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; d&#7921; ki&#7871;n ch&#7881; &#7903; m&#7913;c 5,6 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, gi&#7843;m kho&#7843;ng 10% so v&#7899;i n&#259;m 2010. B&#432;&#7899;c sang n&#259;m 2012, kinh t&#7871; trong n&#432;&#7899;c v&#7851;n ch&#432;a h&#7871;t kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n v&amp;agrave; n&amp;ecirc;n ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c ch&#7881; &#273;&#7863;t k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t kho&#7843;ng 9,8 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, t&#259;ng 4% so v&#7899;i 2011 v&amp;agrave; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p d&#7921; ki&#7871;n ch&#7881; t&#259;ng &#7903; m&#7913;c 4% so v&#7899;i n&#259;m 2011.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','17/12/2011','17/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/gia-thep.jpg',23,2,1842,'huyennt',1,'gia-thep-xay-dung-giam-manh-muc-ton-kho-tang-cao',' Gi&aacute; th&eacute;p x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh, m&#7913;c t&#7891;n kho t&#259;ng cao, gi&aacute; th&eacute;p, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, Th&eacute;p , k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t',NULL,NULL,NULL,' Gi&aacute; th&eacute;p x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng gi&#7843;m m&#7841;nh, m&#7913;c t&#7891;n kho t&#259;ng cao, gi&aacute; th&eacute;p, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, Th&eacute;p , k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t',0,0,0,'','','',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - theo:http://www.xaydungvietnam.vn',1,0,0,0),(146,'V&#7853;t li&#7879;u ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n h&uacute;t h&agrave;ng','V&agrave;o th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m cu&#7889;i n&#259;m n&agrave;y, khi c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh nh&agrave; &#7903; &#273;ang &#273;i v&agrave;o giai &#273;o&#7841;n ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&oacute;n T&#7871;t th&igrave; s&#7913;c mua VLXD c&#361;ng t&#259;ng l&ecirc;n &iacute;t nhi&#7873;u, nh&#7845;t l&agrave; VLXD ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n. Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; th&#7871;, gi&aacute; c&#7843; c&aacute;c m&#7863;t h&agrave;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n c&oacute; c&#417; h&#7897;i nh&iacute;ch gi&aacute;.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mua b&amp;aacute;n nh&#7897;n nh&#7883;p&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;i d&#7885;c con ph&#7889; Nguy&#7877;n Khuy&#7871;n chuy&amp;ecirc;n cung c&#7845;p c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i s&#417;n t&#432;&#7901;ng trong v&amp;agrave; ngo&amp;agrave;i tr&#7901;i, s&#417;n ch&#7889;ng th&#7845;m, b&#7897;t b&#7843; ma tit&amp;hellip; m&#7899;i th&#7845;y s&#7913;c mua &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#259;ng nhi&#7879;t. C&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i s&#417;n th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&amp;agrave;o th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;agrave; s&#417;n ch&#7889;ng th&#7845;m, s&#417;n trong nh&amp;agrave;, s&#417;n ngo&amp;agrave;i nh&amp;agrave;&amp;hellip; c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c h&amp;atilde;ng quen thu&#7897;c nh&#432; Dulux, My kolor, Rosa, Toa, Jotun, Spec. Ch&#7883; Lan - ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng s&#417;n tr&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7889; n&amp;agrave;y cho bi&#7871;t: &amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;V&amp;igrave; &#273;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng ph&#7909;c v&#7909; cho nhu c&#7847;u s&#7917;a sang ho&#7863;c x&amp;acirc;y m&#7899;i cho c&#259;n h&#7897; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&amp;oacute;n T&#7871;t n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7913;c mua th&#7901;i gian n&amp;agrave;y t&#259;ng h&#417;n h&#7859;n so v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng th&amp;aacute;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c, v&amp;agrave; t&#7845;t nhi&amp;ecirc;n, gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; c&#361;ng s&#7869; ph&#7843;i t&#259;ng h&#417;n 1 ch&amp;uacute;t, nh&#432;ng n&#7871;u kh&amp;aacute;ch mua nhi&#7873;u, ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i v&#7851;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; chi&#7871;t kh&#7845;u ph&#7847;n tr&#259;m. Ng&#432;&#7901;i mua l&#7867; l&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; y&#7871;u th&amp;ocirc;i, ch&#7913; c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh l&#7899;n m&amp;agrave; ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n v&amp;agrave;o cu&#7889;i n&#259;m n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u. Nh&#432;ng d&#7851;u sao, c&#7913; c&amp;oacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i mua l&amp;agrave; ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i vui r&#7891;i, ch&#7913; &#7871; &#7849;m m&amp;atilde;i th&amp;igrave; ch&amp;aacute;n l&#7855;m&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/vat-lieu.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;D&#7841;o quanh th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i, v&amp;agrave;o th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y, ngo&amp;agrave;i s&#417;n th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;aacute;c c&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; s&#7913;c mua t&#259;ng l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&amp;aacute;ng k&#7875;. C&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#273;i&#7875;m t&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng nh&#432;: G&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;t n&#7873;n, thi&#7871;t b&#7883; nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m, v&#7879; sinh, c&#7847;u thang, lan can, b&amp;igrave;nh n&#432;&#7899;c n&amp;oacute;ng&amp;hellip; Gi&amp;aacute; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh nh&#7853;p ngo&#7841;i t&#259;ng nh&#7865;, trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, gi&amp;aacute; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u cho ph&#7847;n ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n v&amp;agrave; trang tr&amp;iacute; t&#259;ng m&#7841;nh t&#7915; 10 - 20%. Nhi&#7873;u &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute; g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t cho bi&#7871;t r&#7857;ng: Hi&#7879;n nay, ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n th&#432;&#7901;ng ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch ceramic hay granite kh&#7893; 40x40, 60x60 &#273;&#7875; l&amp;aacute;t n&#7873;n l&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; y&#7871;u. Gi&amp;aacute; c&amp;oacute; t&#259;ng l&amp;ecirc;n 1 ch&amp;uacute;t c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; quy lu&#7853;t c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, nh&#432;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n c&#361;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch n&amp;agrave;o v&#7915;a t&#7889;t m&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; c&#361;ng v&#7915;a ph&#7843;i. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; th&#7871;, c&amp;aacute;c th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u &#272;&#7891;ng T&amp;acirc;m, Th&#7841;ch B&amp;agrave;n, VIGLACERA&amp;hellip; v&#7851;n l&amp;agrave; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, nhi&#7873;u kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng c&#361;ng ch&#7885;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m g&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;t c&#7911;a Trung Qu&#7889;c v&amp;igrave; m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7865;p, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#361;ng t&#7889;t m&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; l&#7841;i c&#7841;nh tranh. C&amp;ograve;n c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i s&amp;agrave;n g&#7895; c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p hay t&#7921; nhi&amp;ecirc;n v&#7851;n c&amp;oacute; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh, nh&#432;ng s&#7913;c mua kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; b&#7857;ng g&#7841;ch men.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#361;ng gi&#7889;ng nh&#432; g&#7841;ch, thi&#7871;t b&#7883; nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m v&amp;agrave; v&#7879; sinh c&amp;oacute; s&#7913;c mua r&#7845;t m&#7841;nh. Tr&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c con ph&#7889; chuy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7873; VLXD c&#7911;a H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i nh&#432; C&amp;aacute;t Linh, Tr&#432;&#7901;ng Chinh, Ho&amp;agrave;ng Qu&#7889;c Vi&#7879;t th&amp;igrave; s&#7921; hi&#7879;n di&#7879;n c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u ho&#7863;c li&amp;ecirc;n doanh c&#7911;a M&#7929;, H&amp;agrave;n Qu&#7889;c, &amp;Yacute;, T&amp;acirc;y Ban Nha, Nh&#7853;t B&#7843;n&amp;hellip; v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u nh&#432;: Toto, Ceasar, American Standard, Inax, Ariston, Picenza&amp;hellip; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute; h&#417;n c&#7843;, v&amp;igrave; h&amp;agrave;ng ngo&#7841;i lu&amp;ocirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&amp;ograve;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&amp;ecirc;u d&amp;ugrave;ng trong n&#432;&#7899;c b&#7903;i s&#7921; phong ph&amp;uacute; v&#7873; m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde;, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m. Anh Long - ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng VLXD tr&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7889; Tr&#432;&#7901;ng Chinh cho hay: &amp;ldquo;S&#7913;c mua th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng t&#259;ng h&#417;n h&#7859;n nh&#7919;ng th&amp;aacute;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c b&#7903;i thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t nh&#7845;t cho m&#7897;t c&#259;n h&#7897; m&#7899;i. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; s&#7913;c mua t&#259;ng m&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng b&amp;aacute;n ra c&#361;ng ch&#7841;y h&#417;n&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&amp;ecirc;u d&amp;ugrave;ng quan t&amp;acirc;m gi&amp;aacute; ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n cho c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; khi T&#7871;t &#273;&#7871;n, xu&amp;acirc;n v&#7873; th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng VLXD thi&#7871;t y&#7871;u nh&#432; g&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;t n&#7873;n, thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh, nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m, c&#7917;a s&#7893;, lan can&amp;hellip; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#432;u ti&amp;ecirc;n l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i v&amp;igrave; th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m kinh t&#7871; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n m&amp;agrave; vi&#7879;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u cho c&#259;n h&#7897; m&#7899;i l&#7841;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute;. Nh&#432; &amp;yacute; ki&#7871;n c&#7911;a anh Tr&#7845;n, m&#7897;t kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;ang l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n cho r&#7857;ng: Ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; nh&amp;agrave; cho thu&amp;ecirc;, chung c&#432; mini cho thu&amp;ecirc;&amp;hellip; th&amp;igrave; ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; m&#7899;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n r&#7867; m&#7897;t ch&amp;uacute;t th&amp;ocirc;i, ch&#7913; nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;igrave;nh &#7903; l&amp;acirc;u d&amp;agrave;i th&amp;igrave; ch&#7885;n lo&#7841;i n&amp;agrave;o b&#7873;n v&amp;agrave; t&#7889;t m&#7899;i &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; th&#7871;, ch&#7881; tr&#7915; m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng n&amp;agrave;o qu&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7855;t kho&#7843;ng v&amp;agrave;i ch&#7909;c tri&#7879;u/s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;igrave; t&amp;ocirc;i s&#7869; ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7855;n &#273;o, ch&#7913; t&amp;ocirc;i s&#7869; &#432;u ti&amp;ecirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng n&#7897;i, ngo&#7841;i ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7889;t v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t l&amp;yacute; do &#273;&#7875; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh mua lo&#7841;i n&amp;agrave;o nh&#432;ng nh&#7919;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u li&amp;ecirc;n doanh c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; ph&#7843;i ch&#259;ng, b&#7843;o h&amp;agrave;nh d&amp;agrave;i h&#7841;n v&#7851;n l&amp;agrave; s&#7921; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n. Nh&#7919;ng m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng c&amp;oacute; th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m n&amp;agrave;o c&#361;ng qu&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7855;t, c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u lo&#7841;i gi&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7875; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n. N&#7855;m b&#7855;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&amp;acirc;m l&amp;yacute; &#7845;y c&#7911;a kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng, n&amp;ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; cung c&#7845;p &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;a ra s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n cho c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; v&#7899;i m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7865;p, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7889;t v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u gi&amp;aacute; cho kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n, nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng g&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;t, thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh, nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m, c&#7917;a&amp;hellip; &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh, nh&#7919;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; tr&amp;ecirc;n 10 tri&#7879;u/b&#7897;, c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; chi&amp;ecirc;u h&amp;uacute;t kh&amp;aacute;ch b&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;ch gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;. T&#7841;i &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute; c&#7911;a Cty TBVS To&amp;agrave;n Qu&#7889;c B&#7897; th&amp;igrave; b&amp;aacute;o gi&amp;aacute; b&#7897; sen v&amp;ograve;i nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u t&#7841;i M&#7929; c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; 12,5 tri&#7879;u gi&#7843;m xu&#7889;ng c&amp;ograve;n 8,4 tri&#7879;u, b&#7897; sen v&amp;ograve;i c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; 13,6 tri&#7879;u gi&#7843;m xu&#7889;ng c&amp;ograve;n 8,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#7847;u thang c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; kh&amp;aacute; l&#7899;n, do &#273;&amp;oacute;, kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng ch&#7885;n c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i c&#7847;u thang m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7865;p nh&#432;ng gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; ph&#7843;i h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute;. C&#7847;u thang g&#7895; th&amp;igrave; lu&amp;ocirc;n t&#7841;o &#273;&#432;&#7907;c v&#7867; &#273;&#7865;p sang tr&#7885;ng cho c&#259;n h&#7897;, nh&#432;ng gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; c&#7911;a ch&amp;uacute;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng h&#7873; &amp;ldquo;m&#7873;m&amp;rdquo; n&amp;ecirc;n kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n sang c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i c&#7847;u thang kh&amp;aacute;c nh&#432; inox, h&#7879; k&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;aacute;ch d&#7921;ng, d&amp;acirc;y c&amp;aacute;p, s&#7855;t m&#7929; thu&#7853;t, c&#7847;u thang k&amp;iacute;nh. Cty TNHH C&#7847;u thang Vi&#7879;t &#273;&#432;a ra m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacu