e;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; ch&#7853;m ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897;, bao g&#7891;m:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Khu bi&#7879;t th&#7921; ngh&#7881; d&#432;&#7905;ng qu&#7889;c t&#7871; H&amp;ograve;a; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Khu du l&#7883;ch ngh&#7881; m&amp;aacute;t sinh th&amp;aacute;i bi&#7875;n Diana; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Khu du l&#7883;ch sinh th&amp;aacute;i bi&#7875;n L&#259;ng C&amp;ocirc;; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Khu ngh&#7881; d&#432;&#7905;ng ven bi&#7875;n L&#259;ng C&amp;ocirc;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;C&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n n&amp;agrave;y b&#7883; thu h&#7891;i do ch&#7853;m ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; so v&#7899;i quy &#273;&#7883;nh t&#7841;i gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n b&#7843;o &#273;&#7843;m &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&#272;&#432;&#7907;c bi&#7871;t trong th&amp;aacute;ng 7-2011, Thanh tra B&#7897; KH&amp;amp;&#272;T &#273;&amp;atilde; ti&#7871;n h&amp;agrave;nh thanh tra c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n du l&#7883;ch, ngh&#7881; d&#432;&#7905;ng t&#7841;i t&#7881;nh Th&#7915;a Thi&amp;ecirc;n-Hu&#7871;. T&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y, thanh tra &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&amp;aacute;t hi&#7879;n nhi&#7873;u d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c giao &#273;&#7845;t tr&amp;ecirc;n ba n&#259;m nh&#432;ng v&#7851;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng tri&#7875;n khai d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;','19/12/2011','19/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/du-an-500.jpg',36,8,1794,'huyennt',1,'thua-thien-hue-thu-hoi-bon-du-an-du-lich-cham-tien-do','d&#7921; &aacute;n, gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, d&#7921; &aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n, b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n du l&#7883;ch, ngh&#7881; d&#432;&#7905;ng',NULL,NULL,NULL,'d&#7921; &aacute;n, gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, d&#7921; &aacute;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n, b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n du l&#7883;ch, ngh&#7881; d&#432;&#7905;ng',0,0,0,'','','',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - theo: http://dothi.net/',1,0,0,0),(149,'Tri&#7875;n v&#7885;ng ng&agrave;nh th&eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam n&#259;m 2012','N&#259;m 2011 l&agrave; giai &#273;o&#7841;n kh&oacute; kh&#259;n c&#7911;a ng&agrave;nh th&eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c khi chi ph&iacute; nguy&ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u &#7903; m&#7913;c cao, s&#7921; gi&#7843;m gi&aacute; c&#7911;a &#273;&#7891;ng n&#7897;i t&#7879; v&agrave; chi ph&iacute; l&atilde;i vay t&#259;ng cao.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&amp;ecirc;m v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&amp;oacute;, ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch t&amp;agrave;i kh&amp;oacute;a v&amp;agrave; ti&#7873;n t&#7879; th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t &#273;&amp;atilde; d&#7851;n t&#7899;i s&#7921; s&#7909;t gi&#7843;m c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p v&amp;agrave; d&amp;acirc;n d&#7909;ng - v&#7889;n chi&#7871;m kho&#7843;ng 34% t&#7893;ng nhu c&#7847;u c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p. L&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c n&#259;m 2011 &#432;&#7899;c t&amp;iacute;nh gi&#7843;m kho&#7843;ng 8% so v&#7899;i n&#259;m tr&#432;&#7899;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, y&#7871;u t&#7889; thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i l&amp;agrave; ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n theo chi&#7873;u s&amp;acirc;u. Th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&amp;atilde;, &#273;ang v&amp;agrave; s&#7869; l&amp;agrave; nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u c&#417; b&#7843;n cho s&#7921; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n kinh t&#7871;. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, t&#7927; l&#7879; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p b&amp;igrave;nh qu&amp;acirc;n c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam v&#7851;n &#7903; m&#7913;c r&#7845;t th&#7845;p, 128 kg th&amp;eacute;p/ng&#432;&#7901;i n&#259;m 2010 so v&#7899;i m&#7913;c b&amp;igrave;nh qu&amp;acirc;n 193 kg c&#7911;a th&#7871; gi&#7899;i v&amp;agrave; 275 kg c&#7911;a khu v&#7921;c ASEAN.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y, ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i v&#7851;n l&#7841;c quan v&#7873; tri&#7875;n v&#7885;ng d&amp;agrave;i h&#7841;n cho ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c, m&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; nh&#7919;ng th&amp;aacute;ch th&#7913;c v&#7873; nhu c&#7847;u th&#7845;p v&amp;agrave; chi ph&amp;iacute; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t cao m&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;eacute;p n&#7897;i &#273;&#7883;a ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7889;i m&#7863;t c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c trong n&#259;m 2012.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nh&#7919;ng y&#7871;u t&#7889; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p th&#7871; gi&#7899;i&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trung Qu&#7889;c l&amp;agrave; qu&#7889;c gia ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i. Trong 11 th&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2011, Trung Qu&#7889;c chi&#7871;m 46% t&#7893;ng s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng th&amp;eacute;p th&#7871; gi&#7899;i v&amp;agrave; d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o s&#7869; t&#259;ng 58% &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2015.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&#7919;ng lo ng&#7841;i v&#7873; s&#7921; ch&#7853;m l&#7841;i c&#7911;a kinh t&#7871; Trung Qu&#7889;c, v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; n&#7907; c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ch&amp;acirc;u &amp;Acirc;u v&amp;agrave; s&#7921; h&#7891;i ph&#7909;c ch&#432;a b&#7873;n v&#7919;ng c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng M&#7929; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u c&#7921;c l&amp;ecirc;n gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch ti&#7873;n t&#7879; th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t c&#7911;a Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; Trung Qu&#7889;c &#273;&#7875; ki&#7873;m ch&#7871; l&#7841;m ph&amp;aacute;t &#273;&amp;atilde; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u c&amp;oacute; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2011. Th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, hai &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng ch&amp;iacute;nh c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng. S&#7889; li&#7879;u th&#7889;ng k&amp;ecirc; h&amp;agrave;ng th&amp;aacute;ng v&#7873; ch&#7881; s&#7889; qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; thu mua (PMI) v&amp;agrave; b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n Trung Qu&#7889;c &#273;&amp;atilde; s&#7909;t gi&#7843;m k&#7875; t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2011. PMI xu&#7889;ng m&#7913;c th&#7845;p nh&#7845;t trong 32 th&amp;aacute;ng v&amp;agrave;o th&amp;aacute;ng 10 v&#7915;a qua &#7903; m&#7913;c 50,4, gi&#7843;m g&#7847;n 50% so v&#7899;i m&#7913;c &#273;&#7881;nh. Trong d&amp;agrave;i h&#7841;n, k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch 5 n&#259;m l&#7847;n th&#7913; 12 c&#7911;a Trung Qu&#7889;c (2011 - 2015) d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o t&#7927; l&#7879; t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng g&#7897;p h&amp;agrave;ng n&#259;m c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p s&#7869; &#273;&#7841;t t&#7915; 5 - 6%/n&#259;m so v&#7899;i m&#7913;c t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng 10% c&#7911;a k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch 5 n&#259;m l&#7847;n tr&#432;&#7899;c (2006 - 2010).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i, gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p th&#7871; gi&#7899;i trong n&#259;m 2012 kh&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng t&#259;ng m&#7841;nh v&#7899;i nhu c&#7847;u y&#7871;u t&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871; ch&#7911; ch&#7889;t. Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p x&#7845;u nh&#7845;t, gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p b&amp;igrave;nh qu&amp;acirc;n trong n&#259;m 2012 c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7869; s&#7909;t gi&#7843;m, n&#7871;u nh&#432; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; n&#7907; c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7911;a ch&amp;acirc;u &amp;Acirc;u ch&#432;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t v&amp;agrave; bong b&amp;oacute;ng b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n c&#7911;a Trung Qu&#7889;c &amp;ldquo;v&#7905;&amp;rdquo;. Theo gi&#7843; &#273;&#7883;nh c&#417; s&#7903;, ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i &#432;&#7899;c t&amp;iacute;nh, gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p th&#7871; gi&#7899;i n&#259;m 2012 s&#7869; dao &#273;&#7897;ng trong kho&#7843;ng t&#7915; gi&#7843;m 15% &#273;&#7871;n t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng 5%.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTri&#7875;n v&#7885;ng ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong n&#259;m 2011, ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch th&#7863;t ch&#7863;t t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng m&#7841;nh &#273;&#7871;n nhu c&#7847;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng th&amp;eacute;p. T&#7927; l&#7879; t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng trong n&#259;m 2011 &#432;&#7899;c t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7841;t 12%, t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng 75% so v&#7899;i k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m l&amp;agrave; 15 - 17%. M&#7909;c ti&amp;ecirc;u t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng trong n&#259;m 2012 ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t ra &#7903; m&#7913;c 15 - 17%, nh&#432;ng &#432;u ti&amp;ecirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u c&#7911;a Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&#7851;n l&amp;agrave; ki&#7873;m ch&#7871; l&#7841;m ph&amp;aacute;t. Ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i cho r&#7857;ng, ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p c&#361;ng nh&#432; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng s&#7869; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c ch&#7883;u t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t n&amp;agrave;y trong n&#259;m 2012 (xem &#273;&#7891; th&#7883;).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong n&#259;m 2011, Ngh&#7883; quy&#7871;t 11 v&amp;agrave; Ch&#7881; th&#7883; 01 c&#7911;a Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&amp;agrave; NHNN &#273;&#432;a ra nh&#7857;m c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; h&#7841;n ch&#7871; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng cho vay phi s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#7841;o ra nh&#7919;ng &amp;aacute;p l&#7921;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7887; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i nhu c&#7847;u th&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng. Nhu c&#7847;u th&#7845;p khi&#7871;n hi&#7879;u su&#7845;t ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng c&#7911;a nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y ch&#7881; c&amp;ograve;n kho&#7843;ng 40 - 45% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871;, l&amp;agrave;m t&#259;ng chi ph&amp;iacute; c&#7889; &#273;&#7883;nh tr&amp;ecirc;n m&#7895;i &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, s&#7921; gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; c&#7911;a VND c&#361;ng t&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;ng m&#7841;nh &#273;&#7871;n l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n, khi ph&#7847;n l&#7899;n kho&#7843;n n&#7907; c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&amp;agrave;i tr&#7907; b&#7857;ng ngo&#7841;i t&#7879;. Chi ph&amp;iacute; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7889;n vay v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c y&#7871;u t&#7889; &#273;&#7847;u v&amp;agrave;o nh&#432; nguy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, &#273;i&#7879;n, l&#432;&#417;ng nh&amp;acirc;n c&amp;ocirc;ng... t&#259;ng, c&#361;ng g&amp;oacute;p ph&#7847;n &#273;&#7849;y gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m l&amp;ecirc;n cao.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i cho r&#7857;ng, trong ng&#7855;n h&#7841;n, gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c s&#7869; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gi&#7843;m &#273;&amp;aacute;ng k&#7875; ngay khi gi&amp;aacute; nguy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u &#273;ang gi&#7843;m, v&amp;igrave; nh&#7919;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p v&#7851;n &#273;ang g&amp;aacute;nh ch&#7883;u l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho gi&amp;aacute; cao v&amp;agrave; chi ph&amp;iacute; v&#7889;n ch&#432;a gi&#7843;m. N&#7871;u xu h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7843;m c&#7911;a gi&amp;aacute; nguy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c trong n&#259;m 2012, c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n khi l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho gi&amp;aacute; cao &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i ph&amp;oacute;ng b&#7899;t. Nh&#432; v&#7853;y, gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c s&#7869; dao &#273;&#7897;ng trong kho&#7843;ng 14,5 - 17 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong d&amp;agrave;i h&#7841;n, qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p ho&amp;aacute;, &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; ho&amp;aacute; v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&#417; s&#7903; h&#7841; t&#7847;ng ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c l&amp;agrave; y&#7871;u t&#7889; th&amp;uacute;c &#273;&#7849;y nhu c&#7847;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng th&amp;eacute;p. T&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; ho&amp;aacute; trung b&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;agrave;ng n&#259;m c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam trong 10 n&#259;m qua v&amp;agrave;o kho&#7843;ng 3,4%; t&#7927; l&#7879; &#432;&#7899;c t&amp;iacute;nh trong 10 n&#259;m t&#7899;i v&amp;agrave;o kho&#7843;ng 3%. Theo k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch, t&#7927; l&#7879; &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; ho&amp;aacute; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7841;t 50% v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2025.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: right; &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','20/12/2011','20/12/2011','',23,2,1842,'huyennt',1,'trien-vong-nganh-thep-viet-nam-nam-2012',' Tri&#7875;n v&#7885;ng ng&agrave;nh th&eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam n&#259;m 2012 , v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, vat lieu, gi&aacute; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u',NULL,NULL,NULL,' Tri&#7875;n v&#7885;ng ng&agrave;nh th&eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam n&#259;m 2012 , v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, vat lieu, gi&aacute; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u',0,0,0,'','','',3,'http://tinnhanhchungkhoan.vn',1,0,0,0),(150,'Mua nh&agrave; x&acirc;y kh&ocirc;ng ph&eacute;p b&#7857;ng gi&#7845;y tay','N&#259;m 2010, &ocirc;ng A c&oacute; mua m&#7897;t th&#7917;a &#273;&#7845;t 37m2 t&#7915; &ocirc;ng B v&agrave; b&#7857;ng gi&#7845;y tay. Th&#7917;a &#273;&#7845;t n&agrave;y &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n quy&#7873;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7845;t chung trong th&#7917;a &#273;&#7845;t l&#7899;n c&#7911;a &ocirc;ng B. Sau &#273;&oacute;, &ocirc;ng A x&acirc;y nh&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng ph&eacute;p tr&ecirc;n ph&#7847;n &#273;&#7845;t n&agrave;y v&agrave; &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c UBND qu&#7853;n Th&#7911; &#272;&#7913;c c&#7845;p s&#7889; nh&agrave;.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTh&#7913; Hai, 19/12/2011, 13:42 GMT+7&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nc&#259;n nh&amp;agrave;, gi&#7845;y ph&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, quy&#7873;n s&#7903; h&#7919;u, di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&#7845;t, tranh ch&#7845;p, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p, s&#7893; &#273;&#7887;, B&#7897; lu&#7853;t d&amp;acirc;n s&#7921;, t&amp;aacute;ch th&#7917;a, h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng chuy&#7875;n nh&#432;&#7907;ng&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&amp;aacute;ng 10-2011, t&amp;ocirc;i mua l&#7841;i c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; tr&amp;ecirc;n t&#7915; &amp;ocirc;ng A c&#361;ng b&#7857;ng gi&#7845;y tay. Trong gi&#7845;y t&#7901; mua b&amp;aacute;n nh&amp;agrave; vi&#7871;t tay c&amp;oacute; ph&#7847;n cam k&#7871;t nh&#432; sau:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&amp;ocirc;i (t&#7913;c &amp;ocirc;ng B) cam &#273;oan ph&#7847;n di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&#7845;t c&#7911;a c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; tr&amp;ecirc;n (kho&#7843;ng 37m2) &#273;&amp;atilde; b&amp;aacute;n cho v&#7907; ch&#7891;ng &amp;ocirc;ng A &#273;&#7875; l&amp;agrave;m nh&amp;agrave; v&amp;agrave; sinh s&#7889;ng. Th&amp;aacute;ng 10-2011, &amp;ocirc;ng A b&amp;aacute;n c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; s&#7889; tr&amp;ecirc;n cho &amp;ocirc;ng C (t&#7913;c l&amp;agrave; t&amp;ocirc;i) l&amp;agrave; ho&amp;agrave;n to&amp;agrave;n thu&#7897;c quy&#7873;n v&amp;agrave; ngh&#297;a v&#7909; c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c b&amp;ecirc;n. T&amp;ocirc;i l&amp;agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#7913;ng ki&#7871;n v&amp;agrave; cam &#273;oan kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u b&#7845;t c&#7913; tr&amp;aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m, ngh&#297;a v&#7909; hay khi&#7871;u n&#7841;i, tranh ch&#7845;p g&amp;igrave; li&amp;ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch &#273;&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; n&amp;oacute;i tr&amp;ecirc;n trong th&#7901;i gian sau n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Gi&#7901; t&amp;ocirc;i mu&#7889;n t&amp;aacute;ch th&#7917;a th&amp;igrave; th&#7911; t&#7909;c th&#7871; n&amp;agrave;o?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#7843; l&#7901;i:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a ph&amp;aacute;p lu&#7853;t v&#7873; &#273;&#7845;t &#273;ai hi&#7879;n h&amp;agrave;nh, &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i vi&#7879;c chuy&#7875;n nh&#432;&#7907;ng quy&#7873;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7845;t t&#7915; ng&amp;agrave;y 1-7-2004 tr&#7903; v&#7873; sau, c&amp;aacute;c b&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7843;i l&#7853;p h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng chuy&#7875;n nh&#432;&#7907;ng c&amp;oacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7913;ng theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh th&amp;igrave; giao d&#7883;ch m&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;aacute;p lu&#7853;t c&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n. Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&amp;aacute;c b&amp;ecirc;n chuy&#7875;n nh&#432;&#7907;ng b&#7857;ng gi&#7845;y tay, giao d&#7883;ch s&#7869; b&#7883; v&amp;ocirc; hi&#7879;u do kh&amp;ocirc;ng tu&amp;acirc;n th&#7911; quy &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7873; h&amp;igrave;nh th&#7913;c theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh t&#7841;i &#273;i&#7873;u 134 B&#7897; lu&#7853;t d&amp;acirc;n s&#7921;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nC&#259;n c&#7913; quy &#273;&#7883;nh n&amp;oacute;i tr&amp;ecirc;n, vi&#7879;c chuy&#7875;n nh&#432;&#7907;ng quy&#7873;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7845;t t&#7915; &amp;ocirc;ng B sang cho &amp;ocirc;ng A v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2010 l&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c ph&amp;aacute;p lu&#7853;t v&amp;agrave; vi&#7879;c b&#7841;n mua nh&amp;agrave; t&#7915; &amp;ocirc;ng A c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng nhi&amp;ecirc;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p nh&#432; th&#7871;, &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7913;ng t&amp;ecirc;n quy&#7873;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7845;t, b&#7841;n n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; &amp;ocirc;ng B l&#7853;p h&#7907;p &#273;&#7891;ng chuy&#7875;n nh&#432;&#7907;ng cho b&#7841;n v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7913;ng theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh (v&amp;igrave; &amp;ocirc;ng B l&amp;agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;ang &#273;&#7913;ng t&amp;ecirc;n tr&amp;ecirc;n s&#7893; &#273;&#7887;). Sau &#273;&amp;oacute;, &amp;ocirc;ng B s&#7869; l&amp;agrave;m th&#7911; t&#7909;c t&amp;aacute;ch th&#7917;a v&amp;agrave; sang t&amp;ecirc;n quy&#7873;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7845;t cho b&#7841;n. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, tr&#432;&#7899;c khi ti&#7871;n h&amp;agrave;nh th&#7911; t&#7909;c n&amp;agrave;y, b&#7841;n c&#7847;n l&#432;u &amp;yacute; v&#7873; m&#7909;c &#273;&amp;iacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch t&#7889;i thi&#7875;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;eacute;p t&amp;aacute;ch th&#7917;a.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p m&#7909;c &#273;&amp;iacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&#7911;a th&#7917;a &#273;&#7845;t theo ghi nh&#7853;n tr&amp;ecirc;n s&#7893; &#273;&#7887; &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p cho &amp;ocirc;ng B l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7845;t n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p th&amp;igrave; &amp;ocirc;ng B kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; l&amp;agrave;m th&#7911; t&#7909;c t&amp;aacute;ch th&#7917;a cho b&#7841;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c. V&amp;igrave; theo kho&#7843;n 2 &#273;i&#7873;u 3 quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh 19/2009/Q&#272;-UBND, vi&#7879;c t&amp;aacute;ch th&#7917;a &#273;&#7845;t n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o di&amp;ecirc;%3&#7685;n t&amp;iacute;ch t&amp;ocirc;&#769;i thi&amp;ecirc;&#777;u l&amp;agrave; 1.000m2 &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i &#273;&#7845;t n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c quy ho&#7841;ch &#273;&#7875; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p v&amp;agrave; 500m2 &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i &#273;&#7845;t n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p kh&amp;aacute;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p th&#7917;a &#273;&#7845;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7845;t &#7903;, theo kho&#7843;n 1 &#273;i&#7873;u 3 quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh 19/2009/Q&#272;-UBND c&#7911;a UBND TP.HCM, &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;eacute;p t&amp;aacute;ch th&#7917;a &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i &#273;&#7845;t &#7903; &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; nh&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;n h&#7919;u t&#7841;i qu&#7853;n Th&#7911; &#272;&#7913;c l&amp;agrave; 50m2 v&amp;agrave; chi&#7873;u r&#7897;ng m&#7863;t ti&#7873;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7887; h&#417;n 4m. Do th&#7917;a &#273;&#7845;t c&#7911;a b&#7841;n ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; 37m2 n&amp;ecirc;n vi&#7879;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;eacute;p t&amp;aacute;ch th&#7917;a hay kh&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7869; t&amp;ugrave;y thu&#7897;c s&#7921; xem x&amp;eacute;t c&#7911;a UBND qu&#7853;n Th&#7911; &#272;&#7913;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7873; ph&#7847;n c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave;, theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a ph&amp;aacute;p lu&#7853;t v&#7873; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng hi&#7879;n h&amp;agrave;nh, nh&amp;agrave; &#7903; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;igrave;nh th&amp;agrave;nh t&#7915; ng&amp;agrave;y 1-7-2006 tr&#7903; v&#7873; sau v&amp;agrave; thu&#7897;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p ph&#7843;i xin gi&#7845;y ph&amp;eacute;p x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng m&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng xin ph&amp;eacute;p theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh th&amp;igrave; s&#7869; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n quy&#7873;n s&#7903; h&#7919;u. Do c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n &#273;&amp;atilde; mua &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&amp;eacute;p sau ng&amp;agrave;y 1-7-2006 n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7869; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n quy&#7873;n s&#7903; h&#7919;u, song b&#7841;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng theo hi&#7879;n tr&#7841;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;ograve;n vi&#7879;c UBND qu&#7853;n Th&#7911; &#272;&#7913;c c&#7845;p s&#7889; nh&amp;agrave; ch&#7881; l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7875; thu&#7853;n ti&#7879;n trong c&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;aacute;c qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a b&amp;agrave;n, kh&amp;ocirc;ng mang &amp;yacute; ngh&#297;a c&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n quy&#7873;n s&#7903; h&#7919;u c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&amp;acirc;n tr&#7885;ng.&lt;/p&gt;','20/12/2011','20/12/2011','',23,2,0,'huyennt',1,'mua-nha-xay-khong-phep-bang-giay-tay','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'',0,0,1,'20/12/2011','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(151,'G&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung, sao ch&#7853;m th&#7871;?','T&#7915; th&aacute;ng 4.2010, Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; &#273;&atilde; k&yacute; quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh ph&ecirc; duy&#7879;t ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&ocirc;ng nung &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2020. Theo &#273;&oacute;, m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u l&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u n&agrave;y thay th&#7871; g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7845;t s&eacute;t nung &#273;&#7841;t t&#7881; l&#7879; 20-25% v&agrave;o n&#259;m 2015 v&agrave; 30-40% v&agrave;o n&#259;m 2020.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTr&#432;&#7899;c m&#7855;t  quy &#273;&#7883;nh t&#7915; n&#259;m 2011, c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh nh&amp;agrave; cao t&#7847;ng (t&#7915; 9 t&#7847;ng tr&#7903; l&amp;ecirc;n) ph&#7843;i  s&#7917; d&#7909;ng t&#7889;i thi&#7875;u 30% v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung lo&#7841;i nh&#7865; (kh&#7889;i l&#432;&#7907;ng th&#7875; t&amp;iacute;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng l&#7899;n h&#417;n 1.000kg/m3) trong t&#7893;ng s&#7889; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y. Song cho &#273;&#7871;n nay &#273;&amp;atilde; g&#7847;n h&#7871;t n&#259;m, quy &#273;&#7883;nh n&amp;agrave;y v&#7851;n ch&#432;a &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;436&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/1301978483_184679036_1-Hinh-anh-ca--Gach-khong-nung-hai-phong.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7881; &#273;&#417;n c&#7917; m&#7897;t con s&#7889;: C&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c hi&#7879;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&amp;agrave;o kho&#7843;ng 20 tri&#7879;u vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch nung quy chu&#7849;n /n&#259;m l&amp;agrave; m&#7845;t 150ha &#273;&#7845;t t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng m&#7897;t x&amp;atilde;. V&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7875; nung 20 tri&#7879;u vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch tr&amp;ecirc;n s&#7869; m&#7845;t 3 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n than v&amp;agrave; th&#7843;i v&amp;agrave;o kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; 9 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n c&amp;aacute;cbon. Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;  Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; v&#7915;a  ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c &#7913;ng ph&amp;oacute; v&#7899;i bi&#7871;n &#273;&#7893;i kh&amp;iacute; h&#7853;u trong &#273;&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; m&#7909;c ti&amp;ecirc;u  ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871; th&#7845;p cacbon, ngh&#297;a l&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;m th&#7843;i kh&amp;iacute; c&amp;aacute;cbon ra m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng.  V&amp;igrave; th&#7871; vi&#7879;c ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung &#273;&#7875; thay th&#7871; g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t nung c&amp;oacute; t&amp;aacute;c d&#7909;ng ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m &#273;&#7845;t n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p, gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u kh&amp;iacute; ph&amp;aacute;t th&#7843;i g&amp;acirc;y &amp;ocirc; nhi&#7877;m m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng, ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m nhi&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u than, &#273;em l&#7841;i hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; kinh t&#7871; chung cho to&amp;agrave;n x&amp;atilde; h&#7897;i. M&#7897;t s&#7889; DN &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&amp;oacute;n tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7883;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng n&amp;agrave;y v&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung &#273;&#7875; &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Song &#273;i&#7873;u &#273;&amp;aacute;ng bu&#7891;n l&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;n nay, quy &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung  v&#7851;n &#273;ang &amp;ldquo;treo&amp;rdquo;. C&amp;aacute;c l&amp;ograve; nung g&#7841;ch v&#7851;n nghi ng&amp;uacute;t nh&#7843; kh&amp;oacute;i v&amp;agrave;  c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng v&#7851;n v&amp;ocirc; t&#432; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch nung b&#7845;t ch&#7845;p l&#7907;i &amp;iacute;ch c&#7911;a to&amp;agrave;n th&#7875; c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng. Th&#7921;c tr&#7841;ng n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng bi&#7871;t c&amp;oacute; khi&#7871;n  c&amp;aacute;c  nh&amp;agrave; qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; gi&#7853;t m&amp;igrave;nh(?!).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','22/12/2011','22/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/1301978483_184679036_1-Hinh-anh-ca--Gach-khong-nung-hai-phong.jpg',23,2,1930,'huyennt',1,'gach-khong-nung-sao-cham-the?','g&#7841;ch, g&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung, ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u',NULL,NULL,NULL,'g&#7841;ch, g&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung, ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - theo: http://laodong.com.vn',1,0,0,0),(152,'V&#7853;t li&#7879;u ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n h&uacute;t h&agrave;ng','V&agrave;o th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m cu&#7889;i n&#259;m n&agrave;y, khi c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng tr&igrave;nh nh&agrave; &#7903; &#273;ang &#273;i v&agrave;o giai &#273;o&#7841;n ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&oacute;n T&#7871;t th&igrave; s&#7913;c mua VLXD c&#361;ng t&#259;ng l&ecirc;n &iacute;t nhi&#7873;u, nh&#7845;t l&agrave; VLXD ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n. Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; th&#7871;, gi&aacute; c&#7843; c&aacute;c m&#7863;t h&agrave;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n c&oacute; c&#417; h&#7897;i nh&iacute;ch gi&aacute;.','\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/mua-ban.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mua b&amp;aacute;n nh&#7897;n nh&#7883;p&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;i d&#7885;c con ph&#7889; Nguy&#7877;n Khuy&#7871;n chuy&amp;ecirc;n cung c&#7845;p c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i s&#417;n t&#432;&#7901;ng trong v&amp;agrave; ngo&amp;agrave;i tr&#7901;i, s&#417;n ch&#7889;ng th&#7845;m, b&#7897;t b&#7843; ma tit&amp;hellip; m&#7899;i th&#7845;y s&#7913;c mua &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#259;ng nhi&#7879;t. C&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i s&#417;n th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&amp;agrave;o th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;agrave; s&#417;n ch&#7889;ng th&#7845;m, s&#417;n trong nh&amp;agrave;, s&#417;n ngo&amp;agrave;i nh&amp;agrave;&amp;hellip; c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c h&amp;atilde;ng quen thu&#7897;c nh&#432; Dulux, My kolor, Rosa, Toa, Jotun, Spec. Ch&#7883; Lan - ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng s&#417;n tr&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7889; n&amp;agrave;y cho bi&#7871;t: &amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;V&amp;igrave; &#273;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng ph&#7909;c v&#7909; cho nhu c&#7847;u s&#7917;a sang ho&#7863;c x&amp;acirc;y m&#7899;i cho c&#259;n h&#7897; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&amp;oacute;n T&#7871;t n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7913;c mua th&#7901;i gian n&amp;agrave;y t&#259;ng h&#417;n h&#7859;n so v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng th&amp;aacute;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c, v&amp;agrave; t&#7845;t nhi&amp;ecirc;n, gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; c&#361;ng s&#7869; ph&#7843;i t&#259;ng h&#417;n 1 ch&amp;uacute;t, nh&#432;ng n&#7871;u kh&amp;aacute;ch mua nhi&#7873;u, ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i v&#7851;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; chi&#7871;t kh&#7845;u ph&#7847;n tr&#259;m. Ng&#432;&#7901;i mua l&#7867; l&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; y&#7871;u th&amp;ocirc;i, ch&#7913; c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh l&#7899;n m&amp;agrave; ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n v&amp;agrave;o cu&#7889;i n&#259;m n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u. Nh&#432;ng d&#7851;u sao, c&#7913; c&amp;oacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i mua l&amp;agrave; ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i vui r&#7891;i, ch&#7913; &#7871; &#7849;m m&amp;atilde;i th&amp;igrave; ch&amp;aacute;n l&#7855;m&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;D&#7841;o quanh th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i, v&amp;agrave;o th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y, ngo&amp;agrave;i s&#417;n th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;aacute;c c&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; s&#7913;c mua t&#259;ng l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&amp;aacute;ng k&#7875;. C&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#273;i&#7875;m t&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng nh&#432;: G&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;t n&#7873;n, thi&#7871;t b&#7883; nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m, v&#7879; sinh, c&#7847;u thang, lan can, b&amp;igrave;nh n&#432;&#7899;c n&amp;oacute;ng&amp;hellip; Gi&amp;aacute; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh nh&#7853;p ngo&#7841;i t&#259;ng nh&#7865;, trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, gi&amp;aacute; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u cho ph&#7847;n ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n v&amp;agrave; trang tr&amp;iacute; t&#259;ng m&#7841;nh t&#7915; 10 - 20%. Nhi&#7873;u &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute; g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t cho bi&#7871;t r&#7857;ng: Hi&#7879;n nay, ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n th&#432;&#7901;ng ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch ceramic hay granite kh&#7893; 40x40, 60x60 &#273;&#7875; l&amp;aacute;t n&#7873;n l&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; y&#7871;u. Gi&amp;aacute; c&amp;oacute; t&#259;ng l&amp;ecirc;n 1 ch&amp;uacute;t c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; quy lu&#7853;t c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, nh&#432;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n c&#361;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch n&amp;agrave;o v&#7915;a t&#7889;t m&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; c&#361;ng v&#7915;a ph&#7843;i. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; th&#7871;, c&amp;aacute;c th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u &#272;&#7891;ng T&amp;acirc;m, Th&#7841;ch B&amp;agrave;n, VIGLACERA&amp;hellip; v&#7851;n l&amp;agrave; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, nhi&#7873;u kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng c&#361;ng ch&#7885;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m g&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;t c&#7911;a Trung Qu&#7889;c v&amp;igrave; m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7865;p, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#361;ng t&#7889;t m&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; l&#7841;i c&#7841;nh tranh. C&amp;ograve;n c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i s&amp;agrave;n g&#7895; c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p hay t&#7921; nhi&amp;ecirc;n v&#7851;n c&amp;oacute; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh, nh&#432;ng s&#7913;c mua kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; b&#7857;ng g&#7841;ch men.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#361;ng gi&#7889;ng nh&#432; g&#7841;ch, thi&#7871;t b&#7883; nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m v&amp;agrave; v&#7879; sinh c&amp;oacute; s&#7913;c mua r&#7845;t m&#7841;nh. Tr&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c con ph&#7889; chuy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7873; VLXD c&#7911;a H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i nh&#432; C&amp;aacute;t Linh, Tr&#432;&#7901;ng Chinh, Ho&amp;agrave;ng Qu&#7889;c Vi&#7879;t th&amp;igrave; s&#7921; hi&#7879;n di&#7879;n c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u ho&#7863;c li&amp;ecirc;n doanh c&#7911;a M&#7929;, H&amp;agrave;n Qu&#7889;c, &amp;Yacute;, T&amp;acirc;y Ban Nha, Nh&#7853;t B&#7843;n&amp;hellip; v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u nh&#432;: Toto, Ceasar, American Standard, Inax, Ariston, Picenza&amp;hellip; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute; h&#417;n c&#7843;, v&amp;igrave; h&amp;agrave;ng ngo&#7841;i lu&amp;ocirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&amp;ograve;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&amp;ecirc;u d&amp;ugrave;ng trong n&#432;&#7899;c b&#7903;i s&#7921; phong ph&amp;uacute; v&#7873; m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde;, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m. Anh Long - ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng VLXD tr&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7889; Tr&#432;&#7901;ng Chinh cho hay: &amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;S&#7913;c mua th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng t&#259;ng h&#417;n h&#7859;n nh&#7919;ng th&amp;aacute;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c b&#7903;i thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t nh&#7845;t cho m&#7897;t c&#259;n h&#7897; m&#7899;i. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; s&#7913;c mua t&#259;ng m&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng b&amp;aacute;n ra c&#361;ng ch&#7841;y h&#417;n&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&amp;ecirc;u d&amp;ugrave;ng quan t&amp;acirc;m gi&amp;aacute; ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n cho c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; khi T&#7871;t &#273;&#7871;n, xu&amp;acirc;n v&#7873; th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng VLXD thi&#7871;t y&#7871;u nh&#432; g&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;t n&#7873;n, thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh, nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m, c&#7917;a s&#7893;, lan can&amp;hellip; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#432;u ti&amp;ecirc;n l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i v&amp;igrave; th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m kinh t&#7871; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n m&amp;agrave; vi&#7879;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u cho c&#259;n h&#7897; m&#7899;i l&#7841;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute;. Nh&#432; &amp;yacute; ki&#7871;n c&#7911;a anh Tr&#7845;n, m&#7897;t kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;ang l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n cho r&#7857;ng: Ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; nh&amp;agrave; cho thu&amp;ecirc;, chung c&#432; mini cho thu&amp;ecirc;&amp;hellip; th&amp;igrave; ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; m&#7899;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n r&#7867; m&#7897;t ch&amp;uacute;t th&amp;ocirc;i, ch&#7913; nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;igrave;nh &#7903; l&amp;acirc;u d&amp;agrave;i th&amp;igrave; ch&#7885;n lo&#7841;i n&amp;agrave;o b&#7873;n v&amp;agrave; t&#7889;t m&#7899;i &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; th&#7871;, ch&#7881; tr&#7915; m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng n&amp;agrave;o qu&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7855;t kho&#7843;ng v&amp;agrave;i ch&#7909;c tri&#7879;u/s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;igrave; t&amp;ocirc;i s&#7869; ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7855;n &#273;o, ch&#7913; t&amp;ocirc;i s&#7869; &#432;u ti&amp;ecirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng n&#7897;i, ngo&#7841;i ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7889;t v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/mua-ban1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nGi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t l&amp;yacute; do &#273;&#7875; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh mua lo&#7841;i n&amp;agrave;o nh&#432;ng nh&#7919;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u li&amp;ecirc;n doanh c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; ph&#7843;i ch&#259;ng, b&#7843;o h&amp;agrave;nh d&amp;agrave;i h&#7841;n v&#7851;n l&amp;agrave; s&#7921; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n. Nh&#7919;ng m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng c&amp;oacute; th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m n&amp;agrave;o c&#361;ng qu&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7855;t, c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u lo&#7841;i gi&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7875; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n. N&#7855;m b&#7855;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&amp;acirc;m l&amp;yacute; &#7845;y c&#7911;a kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng, n&amp;ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u nh&amp;agrave; cung c&#7845;p &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;a ra s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n cho c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; v&#7899;i m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7865;p, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7889;t v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u gi&amp;aacute; cho kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n, nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng g&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;t, thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh, nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m, c&#7917;a&amp;hellip; &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh, nh&#7919;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; tr&amp;ecirc;n 10 tri&#7879;u/b&#7897;, c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; chi&amp;ecirc;u h&amp;uacute;t kh&amp;aacute;ch b&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;ch gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;. T&#7841;i &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute; c&#7911;a Cty TBVS To&amp;agrave;n Qu&#7889;c B&#7897; th&amp;igrave; b&amp;aacute;o gi&amp;aacute; b&#7897; sen v&amp;ograve;i nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u t&#7841;i M&#7929; c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; 12,5 tri&#7879;u gi&#7843;m xu&#7889;ng c&amp;ograve;n 8,4 tri&#7879;u, b&#7897; sen v&amp;ograve;i c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; 13,6 tri&#7879;u gi&#7843;m xu&#7889;ng c&amp;ograve;n 8,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#7847;u thang c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; kh&amp;aacute; l&#7899;n, do &#273;&amp;oacute;, kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng ch&#7885;n c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i c&#7847;u thang m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; &#273;&#7865;p nh&#432;ng gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; ph&#7843;i h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute;. C&#7847;u thang g&#7895; th&amp;igrave; lu&amp;ocirc;n t&#7841;o &#273;&#432;&#7907;c v&#7867; &#273;&#7865;p sang tr&#7885;ng cho c&#259;n h&#7897;, nh&#432;ng gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; c&#7911;a ch&amp;uacute;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng h&#7873; &amp;ldquo;m&#7873;m&amp;rdquo; n&amp;ecirc;n kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n sang c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i c&#7847;u thang kh&amp;aacute;c nh&#432; inox, h&#7879; k&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;aacute;ch d&#7921;ng, d&amp;acirc;y c&amp;aacute;p, s&#7855;t m&#7929; thu&#7853;t, c&#7847;u thang k&amp;iacute;nh. Cty TNHH C&#7847;u thang Vi&#7879;t &#273;&#432;a ra m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; c&#7847;u thang nh&#432; sau: V&#7899;i m&#7851;u tay v&#7883;n V-inox1 c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; 1,3 tri&#7879;u &#273;/m, tay v&#7883;n V-inox2 c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; 1,45 tri&#7879;u &#273;/m, tay v&#7883;n V-inox3 c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; 1,3 4 tri&#7879;u &#273;/m (ph&#7909; ki&#7879;n Inox 304, tay v&#7883;n D60 v&amp;agrave; n&#7865;p g&#7895; lim Nam Phi, su&#7889;t Inox 12,7mm); m&#7851;u tay v&#7883;n V-k&amp;iacute;nh4 (k&amp;iacute;nh c&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7921;c d&amp;agrave;y 10mm) c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; 2,55 tri&#7879;u &#273;/m, m&#7851;u tay v&#7883;n V-k&amp;iacute;nh5 (k&amp;iacute;nh c&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7921;c d&amp;agrave;y 10mm, cao 1,1m) c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; 2,55 tri&#7879;u &#273;/m; m&#7851;u tay v&#7883;n V-k&amp;iacute;nh6 (k&amp;iacute;nh c&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7921;c d&amp;agrave;y 12mm, cao 1,1m) c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; 2,7 tri&#7879;u &#273;/m&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; l&amp;agrave;m m&#7899;i, l&amp;agrave;m &#273;&#7865;p cho c&#259;n h&#7897; ch&amp;agrave;o &#273;&amp;oacute;n n&#259;m m&#7899;i, kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; ch&#7883;u m&#7903; h&#7847;u bao &#273;&#7875; mua v&#7873; nh&#7919;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u v&#7899;i ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7889;t v&amp;agrave; m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; phong ph&amp;uacute;. V&amp;igrave; th&#7871; m&amp;agrave; s&#7913;c mua cu&#7889;i n&#259;m cho v&#7853;t li&#7879;u ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#259;ng h&#417;n h&#7859;n, v&amp;agrave; c&#361;ng theo &#273;&amp;oacute;, gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng nh&amp;iacute;ch l&amp;ecirc;n ch&amp;uacute;t &amp;iacute;t. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, ti&#7873;n n&amp;agrave;o c&#7911;a &#7845;y, n&amp;ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng v&#7851;n &#432;u ti&amp;ecirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng, gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; v&#7915;a ph&#7843;i ch&#7913; kh&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;igrave; tham c&#7911;a r&#7867; m&amp;agrave; &amp;ldquo;ti&#7873;n m&#7845;t t&#7853;t mang&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n','22/12/2011','22/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/mua-ban.jpg',23,2,2249,'huyennt',1,'vat-lieu-hoan-thien-hut-hang',' V&#7853;t li&#7879;u ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n h&uacute;t h&agrave;ng, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, VLXD, x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng',NULL,NULL,NULL,' V&#7853;t li&#7879;u ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n h&uacute;t h&agrave;ng, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, VLXD, x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng',0,0,0,'','','',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - Theo: http://www.diaoconline.vn',1,0,0,0),(153,'Nh&#7919;ng m&#7851;u ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch &#273;&#7865;p &#273;&oacute;n n&#259;m m&#7899;i','Ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch lu&ocirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem l&agrave; t&acirc;m &#273;i&#7875;m c&#7911;a ng&ocirc;i nh&agrave;, kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7919;ng &#273;&oacute; l&agrave; n&#417;i &#273;&#7875; th&#7875; hi&#7879;n phong c&aacute;ch v&agrave; con ng&#432;&#7901;i c&#7911;a ch&iacute;nh gia ch&#7911; m&agrave; c&ograve;n l&agrave; n&#417;i d&agrave;nh cho c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n trong gia &#273;&igrave;nh th&#432; gi&atilde;n v&agrave; gi&#7843;i tr&iacute; sau m&#7897;t ng&agrave;y m&#7879;t m&#7887;i. Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; th&#7871;, b&#7841;n n&ecirc;n ch&#7885;n cho ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch nh&agrave; m&igrave;nh m&#7897;t phong c&aacute;ch th&#7853;t ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;ch b&amp;agrave;i tr&amp;iacute; &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n, m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p kh&amp;eacute;o l&amp;eacute;o v&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;i ho&amp;agrave; nh&#432;ng nh&#7919;ng m&#7851;u ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u sau &#273;&amp;acirc;y &#273;&#7873;u to&amp;aacute;t l&amp;ecirc;n v&#7867; sang tr&#7885;ng, hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&amp;aacute;o, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; cung c&#7845;p m&#7897;t s&#7889; &amp;yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n m&#7897;t kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian s&#7889;ng t&#7889;t nh&#7845;t cho gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh b&#7841;n:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mau-phong-khach.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch s&#7855;p x&#7871;p h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute; v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng b&#7913;c t&#432;&#7901;ng &#7889;p g&#7895; v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7891; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t m&amp;agrave;u t&#7889;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mau-phong-khach1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;agrave; s&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p h&amp;agrave;i h&amp;ograve;a gi&#7919;a &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng v&amp;agrave; m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c, t&#7841;o c&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;c nh&#7865; nh&amp;agrave;ng, th&#432; gi&amp;atilde;n, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n l&amp;agrave; t&#7845;m th&#7843;m tr&#7843;i m&amp;agrave;u&amp;nbsp;&#273;&#7887; tr&#7855;ng s&#7869; khi&#7871;n ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch c&#7911;a b&#7841;n th&amp;ecirc;m ph&#7847;n c&amp;aacute; t&amp;iacute;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mau-phong-khach3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;agrave;n gh&#7871; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7885;c da m&amp;agrave;u s&amp;ocirc;-c&amp;ocirc;-la k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i m&amp;agrave;u t&#432;&#7901;ng c&amp;ugrave;ng t&amp;ocirc;ng t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7921; tinh t&amp;uacute;y , v&amp;agrave; sang tr&#7885;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mau-phong-khach4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong m&#7897;t kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian nh&#7887; v&#7851;n th&#7875; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&amp;aacute;o b&#7857;ng t&amp;ocirc;ng m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng c&#7911;a gh&#7871; sofa &#273;i&#7875;m xuy&#7871;t v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c ph&#7909; ki&#7879;n kh&amp;aacute;c m&amp;agrave;u th&#7875; hi&#7879;n s&#7921; kh&amp;ocirc;n ngoan v&amp;agrave; tinh t&#7871; c&#7911;a gia ch&#7911; trong thi&#7871;t k&#7871; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian ki&#7871;n tr&amp;uacute;c&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mau-phong-khach5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#259;n h&#7897; penthouse sang tr&#7885;ng, quy&#7871;n r&#361; v&#7899;i &#273;&amp;aacute; c&#7849;m th&#7841;ch tr&#7855;ng v&amp;agrave; c&#7917;a s&#7893; nh&amp;igrave;n ra khung c&#7843;nh tuy&#7879;t v&#7901;i c&amp;ugrave;ng n&#7897;i th&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, sang tr&#7885;ng, v&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t t&#7845;m th&#7843;m &amp;ecirc;m &amp;aacute;i t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7921; m&#7873;m m&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mau-phong-khach6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&#7911;a cement v&amp;agrave; g&#7895; trong thi&#7871;t k&#7871; n&amp;agrave;y b&#7893; sung cho nhau m&#7897;t c&amp;aacute;ch r&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&amp;aacute;o.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mau-phong-khach7.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mau-phong-khach8.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mau-phong-khach9.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u b&#7841;n th&amp;iacute;ch s&#7921; &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n, nh&#7865; nh&amp;agrave;ng nh&#432;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng k&amp;eacute;m ph&#7847;n hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i th&amp;igrave; ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ho&amp;agrave;n h&#7843;o cho b&#7841;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mau-phong-khach10.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7921; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p gi&#7919;a truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng v&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i trong ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch v&#7899;i ba m&amp;agrave;u &#273;en, tr&#7855;ng v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7887;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mau-phong-khach11.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&amp;agrave;u &#273;&#7887; mang &#273;&#7871;n cho ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch s&#7921; quy&#7871;n r&#361; v&amp;agrave; n&#259;ng &#273;&#7897;ng, s&amp;agrave;n nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&amp;aacute;t g&#7841;ch men m&amp;agrave;u &#273;en xen k&#7869; tr&#7855;ng theo ki&#7875;u &amp;ocirc; c&#7901; t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7921; kh&amp;aacute;c bi&#7879;t v&amp;agrave; v&amp;ocirc; c&amp;ugrave;ng tr&#7867; trung, n&#259;ng &#273;&#7897;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','22/12/2011','22/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mau-phong-khach.jpg',38,11,3586,'huyennt',1,'nhung-mau-phong-khach-dep-don-nam-moi','thiet ke phong khach, phong khach dep, khong gian dep, khong gian song, m&#7851;u ph&ograve;ng  &#273;&#7865;p, kh&ocirc;ng gian &#273;&#7865;p.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'thiet ke phong khach, phong khach dep, khong gian dep, khong gian song, m&#7851;u ph&ograve;ng  &#273;&#7865;p, kh&ocirc;ng gian &#273;&#7865;p.',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - Theo: http://www.dothi.net',1,0,0,0),(154,'&ldquo;Nh&#7853;n d&#7841;ng&rdquo; xu h&#432;&#7899;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t theo phong c&aacute;ch hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i','Xu h&#432;&#7899;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t nh&agrave; &#7903; theo phong c&aacute;ch hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i &#273;ang r&#7845;t ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t trong gi&#7899;i tr&#7867;. Phong c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y d&#7877; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n b&#7903;i s&#7921; h&#7907;p l&yacute; v&#7873; c&ocirc;ng n&#259;ng v&agrave; th&#7849;m m&#7929;.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;  Kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng li&amp;ecirc;n th&amp;ocirc;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong thi&#7871;t k&#7871; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, c&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian th&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; xen l&#7851;n v&#7899;i nhau, kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; trong c&amp;aacute;c c&#259;n h&#7897; chung c&#432; ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; ng&#259;n c&amp;aacute;ch m&amp;agrave; c&#7843; v&#7899;i nh&amp;agrave; ph&#7889; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch h&#7865;p hay bi&#7879;t th&#7921; r&#7897;ng l&#7899;n c&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; c&amp;aacute;ch ph&amp;acirc;n chia t&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921; t&#7841;o th&amp;agrave;nh m&#7897;t kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian li&amp;ecirc;n ho&amp;agrave;n, v&#7915;a thu&#7853;n ti&#7879;n trong sinh ho&#7841;t l&#7841;i m&#7903; r&#7897;ng t&#7889;i &#273;a di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noi-that-hien-dai-1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Thi&#7871;t k&#7871; li&amp;ecirc;n th&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; tr&#7903; th&amp;agrave;nh xu h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u ti&#7879;n nghi ho&amp;aacute; v&amp;agrave; t&#7889;i &#273;a ho&amp;aacute; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng c&#7911;a ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;. S&#7921; ph&amp;acirc;n chia kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian m&#7897;t c&amp;aacute;ch v&amp;ocirc; h&amp;igrave;nh qua s&#7855;p x&#7871;p &#273;&#7891; d&amp;ugrave;ng cho ph&amp;eacute;p c&amp;aacute;c th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n trong gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; giao ti&#7871;p v&amp;agrave; tr&amp;ograve; chuy&#7879;n v&#7899;i nhau khi &#7903; trong c&amp;aacute;c ph&amp;ograve;ng ri&amp;ecirc;ng bi&#7879;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng m&#7863;t l&#7907;i c&#7911;a kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian li&amp;ecirc;n th&amp;ocirc;ng l&amp;agrave; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng k&#7871;t n&#7889;i tr&#7921;c quan c&amp;aacute;c khu v&#7921;c, ph&amp;ocirc; di&#7877;n t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng n&amp;eacute;t &#273;&#7865;p c&#7911;a trang tr&amp;iacute; v&amp;agrave; s&#7855;p x&#7871;p n&#7897;i th&#7845;t. T&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7891; d&amp;ugrave;ng trong c&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian m&#7903; &#273;&#7873;u &amp;ldquo;l&#7897; thi&amp;ecirc;n&amp;rdquo; n&amp;ecirc;n vi&#7879;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&amp;agrave; s&#7855;p x&#7871;p &#273;&#7891; d&amp;ugrave;ng n&#7897;i th&#7845;t &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o t&amp;iacute;nh th&#7849;m m&#7929; l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n v&amp;ocirc; c&amp;ugrave;ng quan tr&#7885;ng trong vi&#7879;c t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n v&#7867; &#273;&#7865;p v&amp;agrave; t&amp;iacute;nh ti&#7879;n nghi c&#7911;a ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noi-that-hien-dai-2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n nay nh&#7919;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian ch&#7911; y&#7871;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; li&amp;ecirc;n th&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;a ph&#7847;n l&amp;agrave; n&#417;i sinh ho&#7841;t mang t&amp;iacute;nh ch&#7845;t t&#7853;p trung nh&#432; ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch v&amp;agrave; b&#7871;p &#259;n, ph&amp;ograve;ng sinh ho&#7841;t chung v&amp;agrave; ti&#7873;n s&#7843;nh. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng n&#417;i mang t&amp;iacute;nh ch&#7845;t c&amp;aacute; nh&amp;acirc;n nh&#432; ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; ho&#7863;c ph&amp;ograve;ng t&#7855;m c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; ph&amp;acirc;n chia k&amp;iacute;n &#273;&amp;aacute;o nh&#7857;m&#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o s&#7921; ri&amp;ecirc;ng t&#432; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;D&amp;ugrave;ng v&amp;aacute;ch ng&#259;n nh&#7865; thay t&#432;&#7901;ng c&#7889; &#273;&#7883;nh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; nhi&#7873;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian m&#7903; m&amp;agrave; gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh v&#7851;n mu&#7889;n c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; r&amp;otilde; r&amp;agrave;ng trong vi&#7879;c ph&amp;acirc;n chia ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng th&amp;igrave; v&amp;aacute;ch ng&#259;n nh&#7865; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c coi l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p t&#7889;i &#432;u v&#7915;a ng&#259;n c&amp;aacute;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; l&#7841;i v&#7851;n &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o s&#7921; th&amp;ocirc;ng tho&amp;aacute;ng c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t cho ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noi-that-hien-dai-3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNh&#7919;ng v&amp;aacute;ch ng&#259;n n&amp;agrave;y th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; gi&#7919;a ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n ho&#7863;c ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch v&amp;agrave; c&#7847;u thang... Ngay c&#7843; gi&#7919;a ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;ograve;ng l&amp;agrave;m vi&#7879;c li&#7873;n k&#7873; v&#7851;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t v&amp;aacute;ch ng&#259;n &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n b&#7857;ng m&#7897;t chi&#7871;c k&#7879; trang tr&amp;iacute;. C&#7847;u thang c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7847;n x&amp;acirc;y v&amp;aacute;ch m&amp;agrave; thay b&#7857;ng v&amp;aacute;ch ng&#259;n g&#7895; v&#7915;a &#273;&#7875; trang tr&amp;iacute;, v&#7915;a kh&amp;ocirc;ng h&#7841;n ch&#7871; t&#7847;m nh&amp;igrave;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noi-that-hien-dai-4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7873; ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;aacute; &#273;a d&#7841;ng, v&amp;aacute;ch ng&#259;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; b&#7857;ng g&#7895;, lam, k&amp;iacute;nh ho&#7863;c nh&#7921;a&amp;hellip;.v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u hoa ti&#7871;t b&#7855;t m&#7855;t. C&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; t&#7853;n d&#7909;ng lu&amp;ocirc;n &#273;&#7891; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t nh&#432; t&#7911;, k&#7879;, ti&#7875;u c&#7843;nh&amp;hellip;c&amp;oacute; s&#7861;n trong nh&amp;agrave; &#7903;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch &amp;ldquo;m&#7903;&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Xu h&#432;&#7899;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871; ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch m&#7903; &#273;&amp;atilde; v&amp;agrave; &#273;ang r&#7845;t ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t trong nh&#7919;ng gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7867; y&amp;ecirc;u th&amp;iacute;ch phong c&amp;aacute;ch hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i. Phong c&amp;aacute;ch n&amp;agrave;y d&#7877; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n b&#7903;i s&#7921; h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute; v&#7873; c&amp;ocirc;ng n&#259;ng v&amp;agrave; th&#7849;m m&#7929;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noi-that-hien-dai-5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7897;t &#273;i&#7873;u d&#7877; nh&#7853;n th&#7845;y l&amp;agrave; ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch m&#7903; th&#432;&#7901;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&amp;aacute;ch k&amp;iacute;nh l&#7899;n gi&amp;uacute;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian c&amp;oacute; ph&#7847;n r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i v&amp;agrave; d&#7877; trang tr&amp;iacute; h&#417;n b&#7903;i KTS v&amp;agrave; gia ch&#7911; th&#432;&#7901;ng t&amp;igrave;m nh&#7919;ng g&amp;oacute;c view &#273;&#7865;p m&#7855;t nh&#7845;t trong ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; cho kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian n&amp;agrave;y, &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; n&#417;i giao ho&amp;agrave; gi&#7919;a trong v&amp;agrave; ngo&amp;agrave;i, gi&#7919;a kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian s&#7889;ng v&#7899;i thi&amp;ecirc;n nhi&amp;ecirc;n thay cho nh&#7919;ng kh&#7889;i b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng d&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#7863;c nh&#432; tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;acirc;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;eacute;t ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch m&#7903; th&#432;&#7901;ng mang t&amp;iacute;nh ch&#7845;t kh&#7887;e kho&#7855;n, t&#7921; do v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;aacute; c&amp;aacute;ch th&#7875; hi&#7879;n s&#7921; kho&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7841;t v&amp;agrave; t&amp;acirc;m h&#7891;n r&#7897;ng m&#7903;. M&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c cho c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng gam m&amp;agrave;u nh&#7865; nh&amp;agrave;ng, sang tr&#7885;ng. &#272;&amp;ocirc;i khi l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t v&amp;agrave;i &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n b&#7857;ng m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;oacute;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noi-that-hien-dai-6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Khi b&#7841;n l&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; nh&amp;acirc;n c&#7911;a m&#7897;t ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch &amp;ldquo;m&#7903;&amp;rdquo; th&amp;igrave; c&#361;ng &#273;&#7891;ng ngh&#297;a v&#7899;i vi&#7879;c b&#7841;n s&#7903; h&#7919;u ho&amp;agrave;n to&amp;agrave;n &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng &amp;ldquo;tr&#7901;i cho&amp;rdquo;, ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y &#273;&#7875; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng b&#7841;n n&amp;ecirc;n l&#7855;p th&amp;ecirc;m r&amp;egrave;m cho nh&#7919;ng &amp;ocirc; c&#7917;a.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;N&#7899;i r&#7897;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian b&#7857;ng g&amp;aacute;c l&#7917;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;G&amp;aacute;c l&#7917;ng ngo&amp;agrave;i c&amp;ocirc;ng n&#259;ng l&amp;agrave; t&#259;ng th&amp;ecirc;m di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch sinh ho&#7841;t, c&amp;ograve;n t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c g&amp;oacute;c nh&amp;igrave;n &#273;&#7865;p v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;uacute;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian trong nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chuy&#7875;n ti&#7871;p, th&amp;ocirc;ng tho&amp;aacute;ng, t&#259;ng l&#432;u l&#432;&#7907;ng chuy&#7875;n kh&amp;iacute; cho n&#7897;i th&#7845;t nh&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noi-that-hien-dai-7.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&#7911;a t&#7847;ng l&#7917;ng kh&amp;aacute; &#273;a d&#7841;ng. C&amp;oacute; th&#7875; x&amp;acirc;y l&#7879;ch t&#7847;ng v&amp;agrave; &#7903; &#273;&amp;oacute; d&amp;ugrave;ng l&amp;agrave;m n&#417;i sinh ho&#7841;t chung hay ph&amp;ograve;ng l&amp;agrave;m vi&#7879;c ho&#7863;c &#273;&#432;a ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch, ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911;, ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n, sinh ho&#7841;t chung&amp;hellip;.l&amp;ecirc;n khu v&#7921;c n&amp;agrave;y. Nh&#7901; v&#7883; tr&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&amp;aacute;o, t&#7847;ng l&#7917;ng c&amp;oacute; t&#7847;m view &#273;&#7865;p xu&#7889;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian ph&amp;iacute;a d&#432;&#7899;i. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, do s&#7921; th&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7889;t v&amp;agrave; t&amp;iacute;nh ch&#7845;t m&#7903; c&#7911;a t&#7847;ng l&#7917;ng n&amp;ecirc;n khi thi&#7871;t k&#7871; v&amp;agrave; trang tr&amp;iacute;, b&#7841;n n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o s&#7921; h&amp;agrave;i h&amp;ograve;a v&#7899;i di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch, kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian, n&#7897;i th&#7845;t c&#7911;a t&#7847;ng l&#7917;ng n&amp;oacute;i ri&amp;ecirc;ng v&amp;agrave; ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; n&amp;oacute;i chung.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7873; m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c, n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c cho t&#7847;ng l&#7917;ng h&amp;agrave;i h&amp;ograve;a v&#7899;i n&#7897;i th&#7845;t c&#7911;a ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;. Nh&#7919;ng m&amp;agrave;u qu&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7889;i l&#7853;p s&#7869; g&amp;acirc;y ph&#7843;n c&#7843;m, m&#7845;t c&amp;acirc;n b&#7857;ng trong t&#7893;ng th&#7875; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian, t&#7841;o c&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;c n&#7863;ng n&#7873;. Mu&#7889;n t&#7841;o &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n, gia ch&#7911; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; d&amp;ugrave;ng gam m&amp;agrave;u chuy&#7875;n ti&#7871;p theo t&amp;ocirc;ng m&amp;agrave;u chung c&#7911;a t&#7847;ng m&#7897;t nh&#432;ng thh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng, c&amp;aacute;c gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n t&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7841;t &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o c&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;c nh&#7865; nh&amp;agrave;ng, th&#432; th&amp;aacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noi-that-hien-dai-8.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7873; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t, tu&#7923; theo ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7875; c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n, b&amp;agrave;i tr&amp;iacute; h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute; nh&#7845;t. N&#7871;u t&#7847;ng l&#7917;ng l&amp;agrave;m ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; b&amp;agrave;i tr&amp;iacute; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t th&#7845;p s&amp;agrave;n ho&#7863;c b&#7879;t s&amp;agrave;n ki&#7875;u Nh&#7853;t v&amp;igrave; chi&#7873;u cao c&#7911;a kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian n&amp;agrave;y ch&#7881; dao &#273;&#7897;ng t&#7915; 2,2 &amp;ndash; 2,5m n&#7871;u b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t cao s&#7869; b&#7883; m&#7845;t c&amp;acirc;n &#273;&#7889;i. T&#432;&#417;ng t&#7921;, n&#7871;u t&#7847;ng l&#7917;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng cho ph&amp;ograve;ng l&amp;agrave;m vi&#7879;c, ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; c&#361;ng n&amp;ecirc;n b&amp;agrave;i tr&amp;iacute; &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n, ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; t&#7841;o &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; th&amp;ocirc;ng tho&amp;aacute;ng, r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#7847;u thang d&#7851;n l&amp;ecirc;n g&amp;aacute;c l&#7917;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; &#7903; v&#7883; tr&amp;iacute; g&amp;oacute;c nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7875; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian b&amp;ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i r&#7897;ng v&amp;agrave; tho&amp;aacute;ng h&#417;n. &#272;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, n&amp;ecirc;n thi&#7871;t k&#7871; c&#7847;u thang c&amp;oacute; ki&#7875;u d&amp;aacute;ng nh&#7865; nh&amp;agrave;ng, m&#7873;m m&#7841;i, &amp;iacute;t chi ti&#7871;t v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i n&#7897;i th&#7845;t chung c&#7911;a ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;. &#272;&#7875; g&amp;aacute;c l&#7917;ng th&amp;ocirc;ng tho&amp;aacute;ng h&#417;n, c&amp;aacute;c v&amp;aacute;ch ng&#259;n tr&amp;ecirc;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian n&amp;agrave;y n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; th&amp;ecirc;m nh&#7919;ng m&#7843;ng s&amp;aacute;ng ho&#7863;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&amp;egrave;n h&#7855;t s&amp;aacute;ng lo&#7841;i nh&#7887;, h&#7855;t t&#7915; d&#432;&#7899;i l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7841;o nh&#7919;ng &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n xinh x&#7855;n cho ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n','24/12/2011','24/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/noi-that-hien-dai-6.jpg',38,11,3126,'huyennt',1,'“nhan-dang”-xu-huong-thiet-ke-noi-that-theo-phong-cach-hien-dai','&ldquo;Nh&#7853;n d&#7841;ng&rdquo; xu h&#432;&#7899;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t theo phong c&aacute;ch hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i',NULL,NULL,NULL,'&ldquo;Nh&#7853;n d&#7841;ng&rdquo; xu h&#432;&#7899;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t theo phong c&aacute;ch hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i',0,0,0,'','','',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - theo: http://dothi.net/',1,0,0,0),(155,'C&#7917;a cu&#7889;n b&aacute;o &#273;&#7897;ng h&#7887;a ho&#7841;n: &Aacute;p d&#7909;ng c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; truy&#7873;n &#273;&#7897;ng Austmatic','C&#7917;a l&agrave; m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; thi&#7871;u c&#7911;a m&#7895;i ng&ocirc;i nh&agrave;, n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; mang t&iacute;nh th&#7849;m m&#7929;, ti&#7879;n l&#7907;i m&agrave; c&ograve;n c&oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng b&#7843;o v&#7879; cao.','&lt;p&gt;Cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng ng&amp;agrave;y c&amp;agrave;ng ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n, ngo&amp;agrave;i c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i c&#7917;a g&#7895;, th&amp;eacute;p s&#417;n t&#297;nh &#273;i&#7879;n, h&#7907;p kim... nhi&#7873;u gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;ograve;n trang b&#7883; th&amp;ecirc;m cho m&#7863;t ti&#7873;n ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i c&#7917;a cu&#7889;n hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i mang th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u trong n&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave; th&#7871; gi&#7899;i. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, m&#7897;t v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; m&amp;agrave; nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#432;a quan t&amp;acirc;m &#273;&#7871;n l&amp;agrave; l&amp;agrave;m th&#7871; n&amp;agrave;o &#273;&#7875; x&#7917; l&amp;yacute; nh&#7919;ng lo&#7841;i c&#7917;a n&amp;agrave;y n&#7871;u nh&#432; c&amp;oacute; ho&#7843; ho&#7841;n x&#7843;y ra.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/cua-cuon.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7901;i gian qua, tr&amp;ecirc;n b&amp;aacute;o, &#273;&amp;agrave;i &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;a tin nhi&#7873;u v&#7909; tai n&#7841;n hy h&#7919;u x&#7843;y ra b&#7903;i c&#7917;a cu&#7889;n. Nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i b&#7883; c&#7917;a &#273;&amp;egrave; v&amp;agrave;o ng&#432;&#7901;i khi c&#7917;a &#273;&amp;oacute;ng xu&#7889;ng, g&amp;acirc;y ra th&#432;&#417;ng t&amp;iacute;ch ho&#7863;c khi c&amp;oacute; h&#7887;a ho&#7841;n, nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i trong nh&amp;agrave; kh&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; tho&amp;aacute;t ra ngo&amp;agrave;i do c&#7917;a kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; t&amp;iacute;nh n&#259;ng tho&amp;aacute;t hi&#7875;m trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p kh&#7849;n c&#7845;p. C&amp;aacute;c ki&#7875;u c&#7917;a cu&#7889;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a ra th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;em &#273;&#7871;n cho kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng nhi&#7873;u s&#7921; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&#7873; ch&#7911;ng lo&#7841;i, m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; nh&#432; c&#7917;a cu&#7889;n si&amp;ecirc;u tr&#432;&#7901;ng, ch&#7889;ng ch&amp;aacute;y, t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; cao, c&amp;aacute;ch &amp;acirc;m c&amp;aacute;ch nhi&#7879;t&amp;hellip; nh&#432;ng &#273;a ph&#7847;n c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i c&#7917;a n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#7873;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trang b&#7883; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng b&amp;aacute;o &#273;&#7897;ng khi c&amp;oacute; ch&amp;aacute;y x&#7843;y ra.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng th&amp;ocirc;ng d&#7909;ng, c&#7917;a cu&#7889;n &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7871; t&#7841;o, trang b&#7883; th&amp;ecirc;m t&amp;iacute;nh n&#259;ng t&#7921; d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i khi g&#7863;p v&#7853;t c&#7843;n b&#7857;ng c&amp;aacute;ch l&#7855;p &#273;&#7863;t th&amp;ecirc;m b&#7897; ph&#7853;n &amp;ldquo;m&#7855;t th&#7847;n&amp;rdquo; &#273;&#7875; c&#7843;m &#7913;ng khi g&#7863;p v&#7853;t c&#7843;n. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p n&amp;agrave;y l&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7889; h&#7841;n ch&#7871; nh&#432; c&#7917;a ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i ch&#7913; kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; &#273;&#7843;o chi&#7873;u v&amp;agrave; ch&#7881; t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i khi g&#7863;p v&#7853;t c&#7843;n &#7903; m&#7897;t &#273;&#7897; cao nh&#7845;t &#273;&#7883;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; kh&#7855;c ph&#7909;c th&#7921;c tr&#7841;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n, m&#7897;t s&#7889; h&amp;atilde;ng chuy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7873; thi&#7871;t k&#7871; c&#7917;a cu&#7889;n &#273;&amp;atilde; &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; truy&#7873;n &#273;&#7897;ng m&#7899;i gi&amp;uacute;p c&#7917;a t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#7843;o chi&#7873;u khi g&#7863;p ch&#432;&#7899;ng ng&#7841;i v&#7853;t v&amp;agrave; b&amp;aacute;o &#273;&#7897;ng khi c&amp;oacute; h&#7887;a ho&#7841;n hay khi b&#7883; x&amp;acirc;m nh&#7853;p. C&amp;oacute; th&#7875; k&#7875; &#273;&#7871;n T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n Austdoor, &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; ti&amp;ecirc;n phong trong vi&#7879;c gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; truy&#7873;n &#273;&#7897;ng cho c&#7917;a cu&#7889;n mang t&amp;ecirc;n Austmatic. C&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; n&amp;agrave;y cho ph&amp;eacute;p c&#7917;a c&amp;oacute; th&amp;ecirc;m t&amp;iacute;nh n&#259;ng &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o an to&amp;agrave;n cho ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng nh&#432; t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#7843;o chi&#7873;u khi g&#7863;p v&#7853;t c&#7843;n, t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng b&amp;aacute;o tr&#7897;m v&amp;agrave; b&amp;aacute;o ch&amp;aacute;y, tho&amp;aacute;t hi&#7875;m trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p kh&#7849;n c&#7845;p&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7899;i c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; c&#7843;i ti&#7871;n Austmatic, khi c&#7917;a v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh ch&#7841;y xu&#7889;ng g&#7863;p ph&#7843;i ch&#432;&#7899;ng ng&#7841;i v&#7853;t &#273;&#7897;t ng&#7897;t, motor &#273;i&#7879;n m&#7897;t chi&#7873;u chuy&#7875;n t&amp;iacute;n hi&#7879;u cho b&#7897; h&#7897;p &#273;i&#7873;u khi&#7875;n, b&#7897; h&#7897;p &#273;i&#7873;u khi&#7875;n v&#7899;i h&#7879; th&#7889;ng ch&#7889;ng ch&amp;aacute;y t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trang b&#7883; m&#7841;ch &#273;&#7871;m th&#7901;i gian &#273;&#7875; &#273;i&#7873;u khi&#7875;n h&amp;agrave;nh tr&amp;igrave;nh c&#7911;a c&#7917;a. C&#417; c&#7845;u gi&#7843;m t&#7889;c t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&amp;iacute;ch ho&#7841;t t&#7915; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng b&amp;aacute;o ch&amp;aacute;y, b&#7897; d&amp;ograve; t&amp;iacute;n hi&#7879;u nhi&#7879;t hay kh&amp;oacute;i khi nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&amp;iacute;n hi&#7879;u b&amp;aacute;o ch&amp;aacute;y, motor s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p ngu&#7891;n &#273;i&#7879;n &#273;&#7875; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng. &#272;i&#7873;u khi&#7875;n m&#7913;c c&#7917;a gi&#7843;m d&#7847;n trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p kh&#7849;n c&#7845;p, c&#7917;a ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;i xu&#7889;ng v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c d&#7915;ng l&#7841;i &#7903; m&#7913;c &#273;&#7897; &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&amp;agrave;i &#273;&#7863;t tr&#432;&#7899;c. Sau m&#7897;t th&#7901;i gian &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7845;n &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7917;a ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c h&amp;agrave;nh tr&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;ng l&#7841;i, c&amp;aacute;ch ly l&#7917;a v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;oacute;i lan sang c&amp;aacute;c khu v&#7921;c kh&amp;aacute;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng D&#432;&#417;ng Th&#7841;ch Nguy&amp;ecirc;n - Ph&amp;oacute; t&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c Austdoor, Tr&#432;&#7903;ng d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; Austmatic cho bi&#7871;t, c&#7917;a cu&#7889;n theo c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; m&#7899;i n&amp;agrave;y s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ngu&#7891;n &#273;i&#7879;n m&#7897;t chi&#7873;u, c&amp;oacute; t&amp;aacute;c d&#7909;ng ph&amp;ograve;ng tr&amp;aacute;nh nh&#7919;ng tai n&#7841;n do c&#7917;a cu&#7889;n b&#7883; r&amp;ograve; r&#7881; &#273;i&#7879;n n&amp;ecirc;n r&#7845;t an to&amp;agrave;n cho ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng. Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p &#273;i&#7879;n b&#7883; r&amp;ograve;, c&#361;ng s&#7869; kh&amp;ocirc;ng x&#7843;y ra tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p b&#7883; &#273;i&#7879;n gi&#7853;t. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; truy&#7873;n &#273;&#7897;ng Austmatic c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; mang &#273;&#7871;n cho chi&#7871;c c&#7917;a cu&#7889;n nh&#7919;ng t&amp;iacute;nh n&#259;ng kh&amp;aacute;c nh&#432; ch&#7889;ng copy m&amp;atilde; s&#7889; m&#7903; c&#7917;a, t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng b&#7853;t &#273;&amp;egrave;n khi v&#7853;n h&amp;agrave;nh trong &#273;&amp;ecirc;m t&#7889;i&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;','24/12/2011','24/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/cua-cuon.jpg',23,2,1859,'huyennt',1,'cua-cuon-bao-dong-hoa-hoan-ap-dung-cong-nghe-truyen-dong-austmatic','C&#7917;a cu&#7889;n b&aacute;o &#273;&#7897;ng h&#7887;a ho&#7841;n: &Aacute;p d&#7909;ng c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; truy&#7873;n &#273;&#7897;ng Austmatic, c&#7917;a cu&#7889;n, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng',NULL,NULL,NULL,'C&#7917;a cu&#7889;n b&aacute;o &#273;&#7897;ng h&#7887;a ho&#7841;n: &Aacute;p d&#7909;ng c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; truy&#7873;n &#273;&#7897;ng Austmatic, c&#7917;a cu&#7889;n, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng',0,0,0,'','','',3,'Nguy&#7877;n Huy&#7873;n - theo:http://www.xaydungvietnam.vn',1,0,0,0),(156,'Khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch x&acirc;y kh&ocirc;ng nung thay th&#7871; g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7845;t s&eacute;t nung','Ng&agrave;y 23/12, S&#7903; X&acirc;y d&#7921;ng t&#7893; ch&#7913;c h&#7897;i th&#7843;o l&#7845;y &yacute; ki&#7871;n v&#7873; &#273;&#7873; t&agrave;i &ldquo;Nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng chuy&#7875;n giao c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&agrave; khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&ocirc;ng nung thay th&#7871; cho v&#7853;t li&#7879;u nung tr&ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a b&agrave;n t&#7881;nh&rdquo; do th&#7841;c s&#297; Hu&#7923;nh L&#7919; T&acirc;n, Ph&oacute; gi&aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c S&#7903; l&agrave;m ch&#7911; nhi&#7879;m &#273;&#7873; t&agrave;i.','\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/58861_013284.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7873; t&amp;agrave;i nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung (th&#432;&#7901;ng g&#7885;i g&#7841;ch block b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng) &#273;&#7875; &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng v&amp;agrave;o thi c&amp;ocirc;ng trong c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh theo quy ho&#7841;ch t&#7893;ng th&#7875; ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2020 do Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ng&amp;agrave;y c&amp;agrave;ng cao c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng trong t&#7881;nh. G&#7841;ch x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung l&amp;agrave; g&#7841;ch b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t t&#7915; xi m&#259;ng, c&amp;aacute;t v&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;n nh&#432; &#273;&amp;aacute; d&#259;m, s&#7887;i,&amp;hellip;. V&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch n&amp;agrave;y ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m &#273;&#7845;t n&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p, nhi&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u &#273;&#7889;t, t&#7853;n d&#7909;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&#7871; ph&#7849;m trong c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng,&amp;hellip; g&amp;oacute;p ph&#7847;n b&#7843;o v&#7879; m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng; &#273;&amp;aacute;p &#7913;ng c&amp;aacute;c ti&amp;ecirc;u ch&amp;iacute; v&#7873; k&#7929; thu&#7853;t, k&#7871;t c&#7845;u, ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&amp;aacute;p thi c&amp;ocirc;ng. M&#7863;t kh&amp;aacute;c, gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh c&#361;ng nh&#432; c&amp;aacute;c &#432;u &#273;i&#7875;m c&#7911;a lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch n&amp;agrave;y khi s&#7917; d&#7909;ng s&#7869; ti&#7871;t ki&#7879;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi ph&amp;iacute; thi c&amp;ocirc;ng t&#7915; 10-20% so v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch th&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng.&lt;/p&gt;','24/12/2011','24/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/58861_013284.jpg',23,2,1850,'huyennt',1,'khuyen-khich-su-dung-gach-xay-khong-nung-thay-the-gach-dat-set-nung','khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung thay cho &#273;&#7845;t s&eacute;t, khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n, g&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung, &#273;&#7845;t s&eacute;t',NULL,NULL,NULL,'khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung thay cho &#273;&#7845;t s&eacute;t, khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n, g&#7841;ch kh&ocirc;ng nung, &#273;&#7845;t s&eacute;t',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(157,'Thu h&#7891;i D&#7921; &aacute;n c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n B&atilde;i D&#432;&#417;ng','V&#7915;a qua, th&ocirc;ng tin t&#7915; S&#7903; K&#7871; ho&#7841;ch v&agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; t&#7881;nh Ki&ecirc;n Giang cho bi&#7871;t: Ph&oacute; ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch UBND t&#7881;nh Ki&ecirc;n Giang L&acirc;m Ho&agrave;ng Sa &#273;&atilde; th&#7889;ng nh&#7845;t v&#7899;i &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t c&#7911;a s&#7903; l&agrave; thu h&#7891;i ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; d&#7921; &aacute;n c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n B&atilde;i D&#432;&#417;ng 2.','&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/du-an_18.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n B&amp;atilde;i D&#432;&#417;ng 2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n B&amp;atilde;i D&#432;&#417;ng 2 (&#273;o&#7841;n t&#7915; &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng L&#7841;c H&#7891;ng &#273;&#7871;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng Tr&#7847;n Quang Kh&#7843;i, khu l&#7845;n bi&#7875;n TP R&#7841;ch Gi&amp;aacute;) do C&amp;ocirc;ng ty c&#7893; ph&#7847;n Du l&#7883;ch Ki&amp;ecirc;n Giang.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo S&#7903; K&#7871; ho&#7841;ch v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; t&#7881;nh Ki&amp;ecirc;n Giang, nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n thu h&#7891;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n l&amp;agrave; do nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; ch&#7853;m tri&#7875;n khai. T&#7915; khi c&amp;oacute; ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng giao cho C&amp;ocirc;ng ty c&#7893; ph&#7847;n Du l&#7883;ch Ki&amp;ecirc;n Giang qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; v&amp;agrave; khai th&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n B&amp;atilde;i D&#432;&#417;ng 2 (n&#259;m 2008) nh&#432;ng &#273;&#7871;n nay c&amp;ocirc;ng ty kh&amp;ocirc;ng tri&#7875;n khai &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n theo quy &#273;&#7883;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;o c&#7911;a UBND t&#7881;nh Ki&amp;ecirc;n Giang, sau khi thu h&#7891;i s&#7869; giao l&#7841;i c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n B&amp;atilde;i D&#432;&#417;ng 2 cho UBND TP R&#7841;ch Gi&amp;aacute; qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute;, k&amp;ecirc;u g&#7885;i &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave; khai th&amp;aacute;c.&lt;/p&gt;','26/12/2011','26/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/du-an_18.jpg',36,8,1922,'huyennt',1,'thu-hoi-du-an-cong-vien-bai-duong','d&#7921; &aacute;n, c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n B&atilde;i D&#432;&#417;ng, &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng Tr&#7847;n Quang Kh&#7843;i, &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng L&#7841;c H&#7891;ng, TP R&#7841;ch Gi&aacute;, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, Ki&ecirc;n Giang, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;',NULL,NULL,NULL,'d&#7921; &aacute;n, c&ocirc;ng vi&ecirc;n B&atilde;i D&#432;&#417;ng, &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng Tr&#7847;n Quang Kh&#7843;i, &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng L&#7841;c H&#7891;ng, TP R&#7841;ch Gi&aacute;, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng, Ki&ecirc;n Giang, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(158,'Viglacera tr&#7847;n t&igrave;nh vi&#7879;c t&#259;ng gi&aacute; d&#7921; &aacute;n K&#272;T Xu&acirc;n Ph&#432;&#417;ng','D&#7921; &aacute;n ch&#7853;m tri&#7875;n khai do v&#432;&#7899;ng m&#7855;c v&#7873; ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch c&#361;ng nh&#432; quy ho&#7841;ch, gi&aacute; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng t&#259;ng cao, bi&#7871;n &#273;&#7897;ng th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng,&hellip; l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n khi&#7871;n ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; t&#259;ng gi&aacute;.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;Chi&#7873;u 23/12, &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n l&amp;atilde;nh &#273;&#7841;o T&#7893;ng C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&#7911;y tinh v&amp;agrave; G&#7889;m x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng (Viglacera) &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; cu&#7897;c &#273;&#7889;i tho&#7841;i v&#7899;i b&amp;aacute;o gi&#7899;i tr&#432;&#7899;c nh&#7919;ng ph&#7843;n h&#7891;i c&#7911;a kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7841;i D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n khu ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng K&#272;T Xu&amp;acirc;n Ph&#432;&#417;ng (T&#7915; Li&amp;ecirc;m, H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;477&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/Viglacera.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPh&amp;oacute; T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c Viglacera &amp;ocirc;ng &#272;&amp;agrave;o &#272;&amp;igrave;nh Thi kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh, nh&#7919;ng quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; Xu&amp;acirc;n Ph&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;a ra trong th&#7901;i gian qua l&amp;agrave; ho&amp;agrave;n to&amp;agrave;n ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng c&#7911;a T&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ty v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;aacute;p lu&#7853;t c&#7911;a nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Gi&#7843;i th&amp;iacute;ch cho l&amp;yacute; do v&amp;igrave; sao d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ch&#7853;m ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; t&#7899;i h&#417;n 4 n&#259;m, &amp;ocirc;ng Thi cho bi&#7871;t, qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh tri&#7875;n khai d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n t&#7915; n&#259;m 2007 &#273;&#7871;n nay g&#7863;p nhi&#7873;u kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n kh&amp;aacute;ch quan li&amp;ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng, ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch c&#7911;a &#272;&#7843;ng v&amp;agrave; Nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c c&#361;ng nh&#432; c&#7911;a th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;ldquo;D&amp;ugrave; r&#7857;ng, quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t quy ho&#7841;ch chi ti&#7871;t 1/500 khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i ban h&amp;agrave;nh t&#7915; th&amp;aacute;ng 6/2007, song ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7871;n th&amp;aacute;ng 10/2009, th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889; m&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; v&#259;n b&#7843;n ch&#7845;p thu&#7853;n cho ph&amp;eacute;p tri&#7875;n khai &#273;&#7907;t 1, v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7871;n 23/8/2011, H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i m&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh ch&amp;iacute;nh th&#7913;c giao &#273;&#7845;t cho ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; Xu&amp;acirc;n Ph&#432;&#417;ng. Nh&#432; v&#7853;y, ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; c&#361;ng nh&#432; qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh chu&#7849;n b&#7883; th&#7911; t&#7909;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n b&#7883; ch&#7853;m, &#273;&amp;atilde; d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;c chi ph&amp;iacute; ph&amp;aacute;t sinh t&#259;ng cao so v&#7899;i th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m 2007&amp;rdquo; &amp;ndash; &amp;ocirc;ng Thi kh&#7859;ng &#273;&#7883;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Khu &#273;&amp;ocirc; th&#7883; Xu&amp;acirc;n Ph&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; ch&#7845;p thu&#7853;n c&#7911;a UBND TP.H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i v&#7873; vi&#7879;c di chuy&#7875;n c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&amp;acirc;y &amp;ocirc; nhi&#7877;m m&amp;ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ograve;n ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i quy ho&#7841;ch ra kh&#7887;i trung t&amp;acirc;m th&amp;agrave;nh ph&#7889;, Nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y g&#7841;ch T&#7915; Li&amp;ecirc;m tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a b&amp;agrave;n x&amp;atilde; Xu&amp;acirc;n Ph&#432;&#417;ng, huy&#7879;n T&#7915; Li&amp;ecirc;m &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c di d&#7901;i v&amp;agrave; chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i m&#7909;c &#273;&amp;iacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7845;t sang nh&amp;agrave; &#7903; &#273;&#7875; b&amp;aacute;n theo c&amp;ocirc;ng v&#259;n s&#7889; 2348/UBND-XD&#272;T - ng&amp;agrave;y 2.6.2006 c&#7911;a UBND TP.H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&#7843;i chi 70 t&#7881; &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;&#7875; di d&#7901;i c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y, l&amp;agrave;m th&#7911; t&#7909;c chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i m&#7909;c &#273;&amp;iacute;ch s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&#7911;a khu &#273;&#7845;t tr&amp;ecirc;n, &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; ch&#432;a t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7871;n m&#7895;i n&#259;m ph&#7843;i n&#7897;p 10 t&#7881; &#273;&#7891;ng c&amp;aacute;c chi ph&amp;iacute; ph&amp;aacute;t sinh v&amp;agrave; ti&#7873;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7845;t. Ri&amp;ecirc;ng chi ph&amp;iacute; l&amp;atilde;i vay ph&#7843;i tr&#7843; cho CBCNV trong h&#417;n 4 n&#259;m qua l&amp;agrave; kho&#7843;ng 75 t&#7881; &#273;&#7891;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ttheo quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a TP.H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i v&#7873; &#273;&#417;n gi&amp;aacute; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7845;t th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m 2007 &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Xu&amp;acirc;n Ph&#432;&#417;ng ch&#7881; l&amp;agrave; 3 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, &#273;&#7871;n ng&amp;agrave;y 2.12.2011, H&amp;agrave; N&#7897;i &#273;&amp;atilde; ban h&amp;agrave;nh quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh 5639/UBND ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t gi&amp;aacute; thu ti&#7873;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7845;t t&#7841;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n n&amp;agrave;y l&amp;ecirc;n t&#7899;i tr&amp;ecirc;n 15 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2 (15.173.483 &#273;&#7891;ng/m2), t&#7913;c t&#259;ng 5,1 l&#7847;n so v&#7899;i quy &#273;&#7883;nh tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;oacute;. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, theo &amp;ocirc;ng Thi, t&#7915; n&#259;m 2007 &amp;ndash; 2011 gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng bi&#7871;n &#273;&#7897;ng m&#7841;nh, &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#259;ng kho&#7843;ng 1,64 l&#7847;n, gi&amp;aacute; ti&#7873;n l&#432;&#417;ng, chi ph&amp;iacute; nh&amp;acirc;n c&amp;ocirc;ng t&#259;ng kho&#7843;ng 1,96 l&#7847;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Do nh&#7919;ng y&#7871;u t&#7889; kh&amp;aacute;ch quan n&amp;oacute;i tr&amp;ecirc;n, ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&amp;atilde; quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;i&#7873;u ch&#7881;nh gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n trung b&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i &#273;&#7845;t c&amp;oacute; h&#7841; t&#7847;ng t&#7841;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n l&amp;agrave; 34,9 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2 (&#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; VAT).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#361;ng theo &amp;ocirc;ng Thi, m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; tr&amp;ecirc;n ho&amp;agrave;n to&amp;agrave;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng cao h&#417;n so v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n xung quanh khu v&#7921;c c&#361;ng nh&#432; &#273;&#7845;t th&#7893; c&#432; trong x&amp;atilde; Xu&amp;acirc;n Ph&#432;&#417;ng nh&#432; gi&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7845;t li&#7873;n k&#7873; d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n V&amp;acirc;n Canh t&#7915; 42- 45 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2, d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Coma6 T&amp;acirc;y M&#7895; l&amp;agrave; 60 - 65 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; chia s&#7867; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n v&#7899;i kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng, &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n c&#7911;a Viglacera ti&#7871;t l&#7897; cho bi&#7871;t, n&#7871;u c&amp;aacute;n b&#7897;, nh&amp;acirc;n vi&amp;ecirc;n n&amp;agrave;o kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; nhu c&#7847;u mua nh&amp;agrave; t&#7841;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n ho&#7863;c t&#7915; ch&#7889;i &#273;&#259;ng k&amp;yacute; mua nh&amp;agrave; t&#7841;i th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m n&amp;agrave;y, c&amp;ocirc;ng ty s&#7869; ho&amp;agrave;n tr&#7843; l&#7841;i s&#7889; ti&#7873;n c&#7897;ng l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t nh&#432; hai b&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&amp;atilde; th&#7887;a thu&#7853;n. V&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n, ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; s&#7869; xem x&amp;eacute;t gi&amp;atilde;n ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; thu ti&#7873;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng v&amp;agrave; s&#7869; ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n nh&amp;agrave; &#7903; tr&#432;&#7899;c cho c&amp;aacute;n b&#7897;, nh&amp;acirc;n vi&amp;ecirc;n n&amp;agrave;o c&amp;oacute; nhu c&#7847;u.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;oacute;, h&amp;agrave;ng ch&#7909;c kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng mua &#273;&amp;atilde; k&amp;eacute;o &#273;&#7871;n d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n gi&#259;ng b&#259;ng r&amp;ocirc;n, bi&#7875;u ng&#7919; ph&#7843;n &amp;aacute;nh ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; t&#259;ng gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n.&lt;/p&gt;','26/12/2011','26/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/Viglacera.jpg',28,8,1938,'huyennt',1,'viglacera-tran-tinh-viec-tang-gia-du-an-kdt-xuan-phuong','Viglacera, T&#7893;ng c&ocirc;ng ty Viglacera, khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i xu&acirc;n ph&#432;&#417;ng, ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, d&#7921; &aacute;n, tin d&#7921; &aacute;n,',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Viglacera, T&#7893;ng c&ocirc;ng ty Viglacera, khu &#273;&ocirc; th&#7883; m&#7899;i xu&acirc;n ph&#432;&#417;ng, ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, d&#7921; &aacute;n, tin d&#7921; &aacute;n,',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(159,'Ph&ograve;ng ng&#7911; quy&#7871;n r&#361; v&#7899;i gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&ograve;n','Gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&ograve;n l&agrave; m&#7897;t xu th&#7871; m&#7899;i, tuy nhi&ecirc;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u kh&aacute;ch s&#7841;n h&#7841;ng sang &#273;&#432;a v&agrave;o, v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&ocirc;ng &iacute;t nh&#7919;ng ng&ocirc;i sao Holywood y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch. S&#7921; quy&#7871;n r&#361; c&#7911;a n&oacute; n&#7857;m &#7903; s&#7921; m&#7899;i l&#7841;, l&atilde;ng m&#7841;n v&agrave; th&#7875; hi&#7879;n nh&#7919;ng n&eacute;t tinh t&#7871; m&agrave; m&#7897;t chi&#7871;c gi&#432;&#7901;ng th&ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u &#273;&amp;atilde; qu&amp;aacute; quen m&#7855;t v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;c gi&#432;&#7901;ng h&amp;igrave;nh ch&#7919; nh&#7853;t nh&amp;agrave;m ch&amp;aacute;n, t&#7841;i sao b&#7841;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&amp;aacute; c&amp;aacute;ch cho ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; v&#7899;i m&#7897;t chi&#7871;c gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ograve;n &#273;&#7847;y &#7845;n t&#432;&#7907;ng m&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng k&amp;eacute;m tho&#7843;i m&amp;aacute;i n&amp;agrave;y?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ograve;n v&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871; &#273;a n&#259;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ograve;n g&amp;acirc;y &#7845;n t&#432;&#7907;ng m&#7841;nh m&#7869; v&#7899;i b&#7845;t k&#7923; ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; n&amp;agrave;o. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, n&amp;oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; r&#7845;t &#273;a d&#7841;ng v&amp;agrave; th&amp;ocirc;ng minh. Khi th&amp;igrave; l&amp;agrave; chi&#7871;c gi&#432;&#7901;ng th&#7853;t s&#7921; &amp;ecirc;m &amp;aacute;i, d&#7877; ch&#7883;u, khi b&#7841;n b&amp;egrave; &#273;&#7871;n ch&#417;i, ph&#7847;n sau gi&#432;&#7901;ng s&#7869; tr&#7903; th&amp;agrave;nh b&#7897; gh&#7871; sofa th&#7853;t l&amp;yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng, v&amp;agrave; ph&#7847;n tr&#432;&#7899;c tr&#7903; th&amp;agrave;nh b&amp;agrave;n tr&amp;agrave;. M&#7897;t s&#7889; thi&#7871;t k&#7871; kh&amp;aacute;c, c&amp;oacute; ph&#7847;n l&#432;u tr&#7919; ph&amp;iacute;a sau, gi&amp;uacute;p b&#7841;n c&#7845;t ch&#259;n, ga g&#7889;i, vv&amp;hellip; Nhi&#7873;u ki&#7875;u gi&#432;&#7901;ng c&amp;ograve;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p &#273;&amp;egrave;n chi&#7871;u s&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7885;c s&amp;aacute;ch, hay chu&amp;ocirc;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;331&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giuong-tron.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng xoay 360 &#273;&#7897; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i y&amp;ecirc;u th&amp;iacute;ch, v&amp;igrave; b&#7841;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i di chuy&#7875;n c&#417; th&#7875;, m&amp;agrave; v&#7851;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; xoay gi&#432;&#7901;ng v&#7873; ph&amp;iacute;a c&#7917;a s&#7893; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&amp;oacute;n &amp;aacute;nh b&amp;igrave;nh minh khi m&#7863;t tr&#7901;i m&#7885;c, l&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; xoay v&#7873; ph&amp;iacute;a m&amp;agrave;n h&amp;igrave;nh tivi &#273;&#7875; c&amp;ugrave;ng th&#432; gi&amp;atilde;n, vv&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S&#7903; h&#7919;u m&#7897;t chi&#7871;c gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ograve;n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n nay gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ograve;n ch&#432;a ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n &#7903; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&#7897;i th&#7845;t Vi&#7879;t Nam, v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; tr&#7883; c&#7911;a n&amp;oacute; c&#361;ng &#273;&#7855;t h&#417;n so v&#7899;i chi&#7871;c gi&#432;&#7901;ng th&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng. Gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ograve;n &#273;a s&#7889; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&amp;agrave;m t&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i g&#7895; t&#7889;t nh&#432; g&#7895; th&amp;ocirc;ng r&#7855;n, ho&#7863;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&amp;agrave;m b&#7857;ng da. Nh&#7919;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871; n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c &#273;&#7875; b&#7841;n l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n B&#7841;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n trong b&#7897; s&#432;u t&#7853;p gi&#432;&#7901;ng ng&#7911; c&#7911;a IKEA, v&amp;igrave; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; c&#7911;a n&amp;oacute; kh&amp;aacute; ph&#7843;i ch&#259;ng. M&#7895;i chi&#7871;c gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ograve;n, t&amp;ugrave;y t&#7915;ng ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u m&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; kh&amp;aacute;c nhau, kho&#7843;ng 900 USD.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giuong-tron1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ho&#7863;c, n&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n t&#7921; thi&#7871;t k&#7871; theo &amp;yacute; m&amp;igrave;nh, hay m&#417; &#432;&#7899;c s&#7903; h&#7919;u m&#7897;t chi&#7871;c gi&#432;&#7901;ng nh&#432; b&#7841;n &#273;&amp;atilde; th&#7845;y qua phim &#7843;nh, internet th&amp;igrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; g&#7917;i m&#7851;u &#273;&#7875; nh&#7901; KTS ho&#7863;c c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng n&#7897;i th&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&#272;&#7875; c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; lung linh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ograve;n th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t &#7903; trung t&amp;acirc;m c&#7911;a c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng, nh&#432; m&#7897;t &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t. &#272;&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng n&amp;oacute;, b&#7841;n c&#7847;n c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng &#273;&#7911; l&#7899;n, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; d&#7877; d&amp;agrave;ng xoay khi c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t. V&#7899;i chi&#7871;c gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ograve;n, b&#7841;n s&#7869; m&#7845;t kho&#7843;n ti&#7873;n l&#7899;n h&#417;n &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o ra phong c&amp;aacute;ch cho ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giuong-tron3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&#7841;n n&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7885;n k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905; gi&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7899;n, c&#7843; nh&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; th&#7843; m&amp;igrave;nh tr&amp;ecirc;n chi&#7871;c gi&#432;&#7901;ng &amp;ecirc;m &amp;aacute;i v&amp;agrave;o ng&amp;agrave;y ch&#7911; nh&#7853;t nh&amp;agrave;n r&#7895;i. Th&amp;ecirc;m n&#7919;a, n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; cho ch&#259;n g&#7889;i l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng lo&#7841;i th&#7853;t t&#7889;t v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7855;t ti&#7873;n. S&#7921; m&amp;ecirc; ho&#7863;c c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;c gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ograve;n n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; thi&#7871;u nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;c g&#7889;i nhi&#7873;u k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905;, h&amp;igrave;nh d&amp;aacute;ng v&amp;agrave; m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c. &#272;&#7875; l&amp;agrave;m gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ograve;n lu&amp;ocirc;n n&#7893;i b&#7853;t trong ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911;, h&amp;atilde;y kh&amp;aacute;m ph&amp;aacute; m&#7897;t s&#7889; &amp;yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng trang tr&amp;iacute; ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; v&#7899;i gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&amp;ograve;n d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y nh&amp;eacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Phong c&amp;aacute;ch vintage&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giuong-tron4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u b&#7841;n y&amp;ecirc;u th&amp;iacute;ch s&#7921; tinh t&#7871;, c&#7847;u k&amp;igrave; v&amp;agrave; sang tr&#7885;ng trong phong c&amp;aacute;ch c&#7893; &#273;i&#7875;n, th&amp;igrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t chi&#7871;c gi&#432;&#7901;ng theo ki&#7875;u n&amp;agrave;y. &#272;i k&amp;egrave;m v&#7899;i n&amp;oacute;, h&amp;atilde;y ch&#7885;n nh&#7919;ng chi ti&#7871;t c&#7893; x&#432;a nh&#432; nh&#7919;ng khung &#7843;nh c&#361; gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh, nh&#7919;ng b&#7913;c &#7843;nh thi&amp;ecirc;n nhi&amp;ecirc;n, vv&amp;hellip; &#273;&#7875; trang tr&amp;iacute; cho c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng. M&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; y&#7871;u t&#7889; r&#7845;t quan tr&#7885;ng. Nh&#7919;ng m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng, &#273;en, &#273;&#7887;, t&amp;iacute;m, vv&amp;hellip; l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c &#273;&#7853;m ch&#7845;t c&#7893; &#273;i&#7875;n v&amp;agrave; mang &#273;&#7847;y n&amp;eacute;t quy&#7871;n r&#361;, sang tr&#7885;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giuong-tron5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Phong c&amp;aacute;ch Retro&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Phong c&amp;aacute;ch Retro mang h&#417;i th&#7903; &#273;&#7863;c tr&#432;ng c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng n&#259;m 60, t&#7853;p trung th&#7883; gi&amp;aacute;c m&#7841;nh m&#7869; trong ph&amp;ograve;ng, b&#7893; sung kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; vui t&#432;&#417;i cho ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;. Phong c&amp;aacute;ch retro th&#432;&#7901;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p nh&#7919;ng m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c th&amp;uacute; v&#7883;, nh&#432; &#273;&#7887; cam v&amp;agrave; n&amp;acirc;u, ho&#7863;c c&amp;aacute;c s&#7855;c th&amp;aacute;i kh&amp;aacute;c nhau c&#7911;a xanh v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p cho nhi&#7873;u l&#7913;a tu&#7893;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giuong-tron6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Khi ch&#7885;n c&amp;aacute;c h&#7885;a ti&#7871;t h&amp;igrave;nh h&#7885;c, hoa v&#259;n trang tr&amp;iacute;, n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;i&#7879;u gi&#7889;ng nhau &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o s&#7921; g&#7855;n k&#7871;t trong thi&#7871;t k&#7871;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giuong-tron7.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Phong c&amp;aacute;ch l&amp;atilde;ng m&#7841;n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; t&#7841;o ra kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; l&amp;atilde;ng m&#7841;n, b&#7841;n h&amp;atilde;y ch&#7885;n nh&#7919;ng lo&#7841;i ga, g&#7889;i, ch&#259;n th&#7853;t m&#7873;m m&#7841;i, nh&#432; ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u satin hay l&#7909;a. Th&amp;ecirc;m v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&amp;oacute;, l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng chi&#7871;c g&#7889;i v&#7899;i ki&#7875;u d&amp;aacute;ng b&#7855;t m&#7855;t. &amp;Aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng g&amp;oacute;p ph&#7847;n quan tr&#7885;ng &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o ra v&#7867; &#273;&#7865;p lung ling cho ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911;, do v&#7853;y h&amp;atilde;y ch&#7885;n lo&#7841;i &#273;&amp;egrave;n c&amp;oacute; &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng m&#7873;m m&#7841;i, d&#7883;u d&amp;agrave;ng. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng kh&amp;aacute;c c&#361;ng n&amp;ecirc;n b&#7893; sung &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng hi&#7879;u &#7913;ng. M&#7897;t b&#7897; s&#432;u t&#7853;p n&#7871;n s&#7855;c m&amp;agrave;u l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t c&amp;aacute;ch tuy&#7879;t v&#7901;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giuong-tron8.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nN&#7897;i th&#7845;t trong ph&amp;ograve;ng n&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7885;n &#273;&#7891; thanh l&#7883;ch nh&#432; m&#7897;t chi&#7871;c t&#7911; qu&#7847;n &amp;aacute;o th&#7853;t &#273;&#7865;p, m&#7897;t chi&#7871;c b&amp;agrave;n tr&amp;agrave; nh&#7887; xinh, vv&amp;hellip;, h&amp;ograve;a v&amp;agrave;o s&#7921; &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;i&#7879;u c&#7911;a c&#7843; c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng.&lt;/p&gt;','26/12/2011','26/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/giuong-tron7.jpg',38,11,2525,'huyennt',1,'phong-ngu-quyen-ru-voi-giuong-tron','gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&ograve;n, ph&ograve;ng ng&#7911; quy&#7871;n r&#361; v&#7899;i gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&ograve;n, trang tr&iacute; ph&ograve;ng ng&#7911; v&#7899;i gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&ograve;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&ograve;n, ph&ograve;ng ng&#7911; quy&#7871;n r&#361; v&#7899;i gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&ograve;n, trang tr&iacute; ph&ograve;ng ng&#7911; v&#7899;i gi&#432;&#7901;ng tr&ograve;n',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(160,'Ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng ngo&#7843;nh m&#7863;t v&#7899;i doanh nghi&#7879;p th&eacute;p','Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&eacute;p Vi&#7879;t Nam cho bi&#7871;t, s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t kinh doanh th&eacute;p n&#259;m 2011 c&oacute; m&#7913;c t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng &acirc;m t&#7915; 10-12% so v&#7899;i n&#259;m 2010. Trong khi &#273;&oacute;, h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&aacute;c ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7873;u c&#7843;nh gi&aacute;c kh&ocirc;ng mu&#7889;n cho ng&agrave;nh th&eacute;p vay v&#7889;n.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n nay l&#432;&#7907;ng th&amp;eacute;p t&#7891;n kho c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i th&amp;eacute;p l&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7871;n tr&amp;ecirc;n 500.000 t&#7845;n v&amp;agrave; ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; r&#7845;t ch&#7853;m. Th&amp;aacute;ng 10 v&#7915;a qua m&#7913;c ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&#7845;p nh&#7845;t, ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;t x&#7845;p x&#7881; 300.000 t&#7845;n. Sang th&amp;aacute;ng 11 ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#259;ng l&amp;ecirc;n 397.000 t&#7845;n, nh&#432;ng v&#7851;n gi&#7843;m t&#7899;i 23% so v&#7899;i th&amp;aacute;ng 11/2010.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/doanh-nghie-thep.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;H&#432;&#7899;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u th&amp;eacute;p th&#7901;i gian qua c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nhi&#7873;u DN &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTheo &amp;ocirc;ng &#272;inh Huy Tam, Ph&amp;oacute; Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p VN, 2011 l&amp;agrave; n&#259;m kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n ch&#7891;ng ch&#7845;t v&#7899;i ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p. C&amp;aacute;c ng&amp;agrave;nh ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; nhi&#7873;u th&amp;eacute;p nh&#432; &#273;&amp;oacute;ng t&amp;agrave;u, x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, c&#417; kh&amp;iacute; ch&#7871; t&#7841;o, b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n b&#7883; suy gi&#7843;m, khi&#7871;n cho th&amp;eacute;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7847;u ra. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; ch&amp;ecirc;nh l&#7879;ch t&#7927; gi&amp;aacute; gi&#7919;a &#273;&#7891;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7891;ng ng&#7885;ai t&#7879; m&#7841;nh nh&#432; USD, Y&amp;ecirc;n, Nh&amp;acirc;n d&amp;acirc;n t&#7879;, Euro... t&#259;ng cao, thi&#7871;u ngo&#7841;i t&#7879; &#273;&#7875; nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u nguy&amp;ecirc;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u v&amp;agrave; l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t ti&#7873;n &#273;&#7891;ng qu&amp;aacute; cao, l&amp;agrave;m t&#259;ng chi ph&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7847;u v&amp;agrave;o, khi&#7871;n nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng g&amp;aacute;nh ch&#7883;u n&#7893;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&#7863;c d&amp;ugrave; cho t&#7899;i th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; DN n&amp;agrave;o ch&amp;iacute;nh th&#7913;c c&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7889; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n, song th&#7901;i gian qua C&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;eacute;p &#272;&amp;igrave;nh V&#361; (H&#7843;i Ph&amp;ograve;ng) &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&#7843;i b&amp;aacute;n nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&#7875; tr&#7843; n&#7907;. C&amp;ocirc;ng ty th&amp;eacute;p V&#7841;n L&#7907;i, m&#7899;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y c&#361;ng ti&#7871;p b&#432;&#7899;c. H&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng c&#7893; &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; h&#7885;p v&amp;agrave; quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh b&amp;aacute;n t&amp;agrave;i s&#7843;n &#273;&#7875; tr&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c kho&#7843;n n&#7907; vay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&amp;aacute;c DN kh&amp;aacute;c &#273;ang ph&#7843;i ch&#7883;u m&#7913;c t&#7891;n kho t&#259;ng cao v&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;m s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t. C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Gang th&amp;eacute;p Th&amp;aacute;i Nguy&amp;ecirc;n DN th&amp;eacute;p l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c cho bi&#7871;t, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p th&#7901;i gian qua c&#7911;a &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; ch&#7881; b&#7857;ng 70-71% so v&#7899;i c&amp;ugrave;ng k&#7923; 2010 v&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&#7843;i c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t m&#7913;c 15%. Th&amp;eacute;p H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t, DN l&#7899;n th&#7913; 2 c&#361;ng cho bi&#7871;t, &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&#7843;i c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m 20% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t do kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng. C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Vina Kyoei c&#361;ng gi&#7843;m h&#417;n 7% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t so v&#7899;i n&#259;m 2010, ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m gi&#7843;m g&#7847;n 15%...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &amp;ocirc;ng Ph&#7841;m Ch&amp;iacute; C&#432;&#7901;ng, Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p VN th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n l&#7855;m r&#7891;i, n&#7871;u t&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng n&amp;agrave;y k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i th&amp;ecirc;m v&amp;agrave;i ba th&amp;aacute;ng n&#7919;a th&amp;igrave; ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n m&#7885;i kho&#7843;n l&amp;atilde;i c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m s&#7869; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ograve;n, th&#7853;m ch&amp;iacute; l&amp;agrave; &amp;acirc;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&#7915;a qua, m&#7897;t s&#7889; DN th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&amp;atilde; ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n b&amp;aacute;n l&#7895;, ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; v&amp;agrave; gi&#7843;m l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho. Theo &amp;ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng, n&#7871;u t&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;uacute;c n&amp;agrave;y th&amp;igrave; gi&amp;aacute; ph&amp;ocirc;i th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang &#7903; m&#7913;c 14 tri&#7879;u/t&#7845;n, n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7875; h&amp;ograve;a v&#7889;n DN ph&#7843;i b&amp;aacute;n th&amp;eacute;p &#7903; m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; 15,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. Th&#7871; nh&#432;ng, c&amp;aacute;c DN &#273;ang ch&amp;agrave;o gi&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p h&#417;n t&#7915; 200.000- 300.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, nhu c&#7847;u chung c&#7911;a n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871; gi&#7843;m n&amp;ecirc;n d&amp;ugrave; c&amp;oacute; gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;igrave; c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7875; b&amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&amp;agrave; bao, &amp;ocirc;ng C&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;H&#432;&#7899;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u th&amp;eacute;p th&#7901;i gian qua c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nhi&#7873;u DN &#273;&#7849;y m&#7841;nh. Trong 11 th&amp;aacute;ng qua, c&amp;aacute;c DN &#273;&amp;atilde; xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u 1,727 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i, thu v&#7873; 1,639 t&#7927; USD. &#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; n&#259;m VN c&amp;oacute; kim ng&#7841;ch xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u th&amp;eacute;p l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t t&#7915; tr&#432;&#7899;c t&#7899;i nay. Th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u th&amp;eacute;p l&#7899;n c&#7911;a VN l&amp;agrave; M&#7929; v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c ASEAN nh&#432; Indonesia, Th&amp;aacute;i Lan, Malaysia, Campuchia... Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n th&amp;eacute;p xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam &#273;ang b&#7883; 1 s&#7889; n&#432;&#7899;c ki&#7879;n ch&#7889;ng b&amp;aacute;n ph&amp;aacute; gi&amp;aacute; v&amp;agrave; c&#361;ng ph&#7843;i c&#7841;nh tranh r&#7845;t gay g&#7855;t v&#7899;i th&amp;eacute;p xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u c&#7911;a Trung Qu&#7889;c, Th&amp;aacute;i Lan...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7883; thu h&#7865;p, l&#432;&#7907;ng h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7891;n kho l&#7899;n, trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute;, DN ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p v&#7851;n ch&#432;a th&#7875; ti&#7871;p c&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ngu&#7891;n v&#7889;n vay. Hi&#7879;n nay c&amp;aacute;c ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;ang &amp;quot;c&#7843;nh gi&amp;aacute;c&amp;quot; v&#7899;i &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; vay v&#7889;n t&#7915; doanh nghi&#7879;p li&amp;ecirc;n quan t&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;eacute;p. Cho vay li&amp;ecirc;n quan t&#7899;i th&amp;eacute;p th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i ti&#7873;m &#7849;n r&#7911;i ro cao n&amp;ecirc;n ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng c&#361;ng r&#7845;t lo ng&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7889;ng k&amp;ecirc; cho th&#7845;y hi&#7879;n ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;oacute; kho&#7843;ng 30 doanh nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p quy m&amp;ocirc; l&#7899;n v&amp;agrave; tr&amp;ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i 100 doanh nghi&#7879;p s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&amp;eacute;p quy m&amp;ocirc; nh&#7887;. Theo Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p, hi&#7879;n nay h&#7847;u h&#7871;t doanh nghi&#7879;p th&amp;eacute;p v&#7915;a v&amp;agrave; nh&#7887; &#273;ang r&#417;i v&amp;agrave;o c&#7843;nh &amp;quot;s&#7889;ng d&#7903; ch&#7871;t d&#7903;&amp;quot;, c&amp;aacute;c DN n&amp;agrave;y ch&#7881; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&#7841;t 50% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; nhi&#7873;u. Nh&#7919;ng DN d&amp;ugrave;ng nhi&#7873;u v&#7889;n vay, m&#7899;i &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng v&amp;agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t l&#7841;c h&#7853;u g&#7863;p nhi&#7873;u kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n nh&#7845;t, nguy c&#417; r&#7911;i ro cao, kh&amp;oacute; t&#7891;n t&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o c&#7911;a B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng, ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng, t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng c&#7911;a Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n s&#7869; c&amp;ograve;n k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i, v&#7899;i &#273;&amp;agrave; n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; c&amp;ograve;n k&amp;eacute;o d&amp;agrave;i sang n&#259;m 2012. Trong khi &#273;&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7871;n nay v&#7851;n ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; l&#7889;i tho&amp;aacute;t n&amp;agrave;o kh&#7843; d&#297; cho c&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p. Chuy&#7879;n t&#7891;n kho th&amp;eacute;p cao c&amp;aacute;c c&#417; quan qu&#7843;n l&amp;yacute; &#273;&#7873;u &#273;&amp;atilde; bi&#7871;t, nh&#432;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng t&amp;igrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&amp;aacute;ch n&amp;agrave;o h&#7895; tr&#7907;, v&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c gi&#7843;i ph&amp;aacute;p &#273;&#432;a ra &#273;&#7873;u vi ph&#7841;m quy &#273;&#7883;nh WTO v&#7873; h&#7895; tr&#7907; ng&amp;agrave;nh. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute; th&amp;igrave; nguy c&#417; nh&amp;igrave;n th&#7845;y l&amp;agrave; th&amp;eacute;p ngo&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; tr&amp;agrave;n v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&#7849;y c&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave;o t&amp;igrave;nh th&#7871; kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#432;&#417;ng lai c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&#432;&#7907;c cho l&amp;agrave; r&#7845;t s&amp;aacute;ng s&#7911;a, nhu c&#7847;u th&amp;eacute;p trong nh&#7919;ng n&#259;m t&#7899;i c&amp;ograve;n nhi&#7873;u. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n cho &#273;&#7871;n nay th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang ng&#7853;p ch&amp;igrave;m trong kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n ch&#432;a bi&#7871;t ng&amp;agrave;y n&amp;agrave;o tho&amp;aacute;t ra. Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Th&amp;eacute;p VN c&#361;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;a ra c&#7843;nh b&amp;aacute;o, s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; kho&#7843;ng 20% s&#7889; DN th&amp;eacute;p ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n trong n&#259;m 2012 t&#7899;i.&lt;/p&gt;','27/12/2011','27/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/doanh-nghie-thep.jpg',23,2,1966,'huyennt',1,'ngan-hang-ngoanh-mat-voi-doanh-nghiep-thep','th&eacute;p, t&iacute;n d&#7909;ng, ph&ocirc;i th&eacute;p, kinh doanh th&eacute;p, B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng, ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng, c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, doanh nghi&#7879;p, Indonesia, Th&aacute;i Lan, Malaysia, Campuchia',NULL,NULL,NULL,'th&eacute;p, t&iacute;n d&#7909;ng, ph&ocirc;i th&eacute;p, kinh doanh th&eacute;p, B&#7897; C&ocirc;ng Th&#432;&#417;ng, ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng, c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t, doanh nghi&#7879;p, Indonesia, Th&aacute;i Lan, Malaysia, Campuchia',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'',1,1,0,1),(161,'C&aacute;ch h&oacute;a gi&#7843;i nh&agrave; c&oacute; c&#7917;a ch&iacute;nh &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n c&#7917;a h&#7853;u','Nh&agrave; t&ocirc;i x&acirc;y c&aacute;ch &#273;&acirc;y 5 n&#259;m theo ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c bi&#7879;t th&#7921;, ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;ch r&#7897;ng v&agrave; tho&aacute;ng c&oacute; thi&#7871;t k&#7871; c&#7917;a h&#7853;u d&#7851;n ra khu v&#7921;c ph&iacute;a sau, nh&#432;ng t&ocirc;i nghe n&oacute;i khi c&#7917;a ch&iacute;nh &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n c&#7917;a h&#7853;u nh&#432; v&#7853;y s&#7869; g&acirc;y t&#7893;n t&agrave;i. Kh&ocirc;ng bi&#7871;t th&#7921;c h&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;o n&ecirc;n nh&#7901; c&aacute;c KTS t&#432; v&#7845;n gi&uacute;p, n&#7871;u nh&#432; v&#7853;y th&#7853;t th&igrave; ph&#7843;i x&#7917; l&yacute; ra sao. Xin ch&acirc;n th&agrave;nh c&#7843;m &#417;n!','\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tr&#7843; l&#7901;i:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh c&#7911;a ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; l&amp;agrave; n&#417;i ph&amp;acirc;n c&amp;aacute;ch gi&#7919;a th&#7871; gi&#7899;i ri&amp;ecirc;ng c&#7911;a m&#7895;i gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh v&#7899;i x&amp;atilde; h&#7897;i b&amp;ecirc;n ngo&amp;agrave;i. L&amp;agrave; l&#7889;i ra v&amp;agrave;o c&#7911;a t&#7845;t c&#7843; m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i trong gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh, khi c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7863;t &#273;&amp;uacute;ng v&amp;agrave;o c&amp;aacute;t ph&#432;&#417;ng th&amp;igrave; gi&amp;oacute; v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; t&#7915; c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh th&#7893;i t&#7899;i &#273;&#7873;u mang theo may m&#7855;n. N&#7871;u c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng &#7903; h&#432;&#7899;ng hung s&#7869; g&amp;acirc;y b&#7845;t l&#7907;i cho nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7889;ng trong ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;oacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo phong thu&#7927;, c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;agrave; c&#7917;a h&#7853;u tr&amp;aacute;nh &#273;&#7863;t &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n v&#7899;i nhau b&#7903;i nh&#432; th&#7871; khi kh&amp;iacute; &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o s&#7869; l&#7853;p t&#7913;c tho&amp;aacute;t ra theo c&#7917;a h&#7853;u m&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; lu&amp;acirc;n chuy&#7875;n trong nh&amp;agrave;. Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p n&amp;agrave;y, b&#7841;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7863;t m&#7897;t ch&#7853;u c&amp;acirc;y cao hay thi&#7871;t k&#7871; t&#7845;m ch&#7855;n gi&#7919;a hai c&#7917;a &#273;&#7875; ng&#259;n kh&amp;iacute; &#273;i theo &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng th&#7859;ng tho&amp;aacute;t ra ngay khi v&#7915;a v&amp;agrave;o nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh th&amp;ocirc;ng v&#7899;i c&#7917;a h&#7853;u v&amp;agrave; c&#7917;a gi&#7919;a (n&#7871;u c&amp;oacute;) th&amp;igrave; t&#7841;p th&amp;agrave;nh th&#7871; ba c&#7917;a th&amp;ocirc;ng nhau. Kh&amp;iacute; v&amp;agrave;o s&#7869; b&#7883; th&#7845;t t&amp;aacute;n h&#7871;t, ch&#7911; ti&#7873;n t&amp;agrave;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng v&#432;&#7907;ng, hao t&#7893;n ti&#7873;n t&amp;agrave;i, kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7847;m gi&#7919; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&amp;agrave;i l&#7897;c. Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng c&#7847;n s&#7917;a l&#7841;i c&#7917;a ho&#7863;c &#273;&#7863;t b&amp;igrave;nh phong ch&#7855;n &#7903; gi&#7919;a &#273;&#7875; c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;agrave; c&#7917;a ph&#7909; kh&amp;ocirc;ng nh&amp;igrave;n th&#7845;y nhau n&#7919;a. D&amp;ugrave;ng c&#7847;u thu&#7927; tinh treo &#7903; v&#7883; tr&amp;iacute; th&amp;ocirc;ng gi&#7919;a hai c&#7917;a, d&amp;ugrave;ng t&#432;&#7907;ng r&amp;ugrave;a &#273;&#7847;u r&#7891;ng ho&#7863;c t&#432;&#7907;ng Tam &#272;a che ch&#7855;n &#7903; ph&amp;iacute;a c&#7917;a ph&#7909;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;500&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/cua-chinh-doi-dien-cua-hau.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNgo&amp;agrave;i ra ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i c&amp;oacute; th&amp;ecirc;m l&#7901;i khuy&amp;ecirc;n khi c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n c&#7917;a s&#7893; nh&#432; sau:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n c&#7917;a s&#7893; trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7917;a s&#7893; kh&amp;ocirc;ng qu&amp;aacute; nhi&#7873;u th&amp;igrave; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng qu&amp;aacute; l&#7899;n. Nh&#432;ng gi&#7843; s&#7917; c&#7917;a s&#7893; v&#7915;a nhi&#7873;u v&#7915;a l&#7899;n th&amp;igrave; s&#7869; ng&#259;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng cho nh&#7919;ng c&amp;aacute;t kh&amp;iacute; n&amp;agrave;y t&#7909; l&#7841;i trong ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;. Do &#273;&amp;oacute; s&#7869; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n v&#7853;n m&#7879;nh c&#7911;a ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;, b&#7845;t l&#7907;i &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i t&amp;agrave;i v&#7853;n. R&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i khi thi&#7871;t k&#7871; &#273;&#7873;u ph&#7841;m l&#7895;i n&amp;agrave;y, ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&amp;aacute;p h&amp;oacute;a gi&#7843;i &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; gia ch&#7911; tr&#7891;ng m&#7897;t v&amp;agrave;i c&amp;acirc;y tr&#432;&#7899;c c&#7917;a s&#7893; (lo&#7841;i c&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; gai) l&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7871; ng&#259;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng cho c&amp;aacute;t kh&amp;iacute; ph&amp;aacute;t t&amp;aacute;n ra ngo&amp;agrave;i. N&#7871;u t&amp;agrave;i v&#7853;n c&#7911;a ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; th&#7853;t s&#7921; x&#7845;u &#273;i v&amp;igrave; l&amp;iacute; do n&amp;agrave;y th&amp;igrave; sau khi tr&#7891;ng c&amp;acirc;y m&#7897;t th&#7901;i gian, t&amp;agrave;i v&#7853;n t&#7921; kh&#7855;c s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng chuy&#7875;n bi&#7871;n t&#7889;t &#273;&#7865;p.&lt;/p&gt;','27/12/2011','28/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/cua-chinh-doi-dien-cua-hau.jpg',38,11,2156,'huyennt',1,'cach-hoa-giai-nha-co-cua-chinh-doi-dien-cua-hau','h&oacute;a gi&#7843;i, th&#7871; c&#7917;a, khong gian song, phong th&#7911;y',NULL,NULL,NULL,'h&oacute;a gi&#7843;i, th&#7871; c&#7917;a, khong gian song, phong th&#7911;y',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'',1,0,0,0),(162,'Mua nh&agrave; m&#7899;i &#273;em l&#7841;i t&agrave;i l&#7897;c','M&#7897;t kh&ocirc;ng gian s&#7889;ng v&agrave; l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c mang n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng d&#432;&#417;ng, tr&agrave;n &#273;&#7847;y nh&#7919;ng xung &#273;&#7897;ng t&iacute;ch c&#7921;c c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&uacute;p b&#7841;n xua tan nh&#7919;ng suy ngh&#297; ti&ecirc;u c&#7921;c hay c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c kh&oacute; ch&#7883;u.','&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;Ch&#7885;n h&#432;&#7899;ng nh&amp;agrave; t&#7889;t v&#7899;i cung m&#7879;nh c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i, ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute; &#273;&#7871;n nh&#7919;ng y&#7871;u t&#7889; quan tr&#7885;ng mang l&#7841;i may m&#7855;n, y&amp;ecirc;n l&amp;agrave;nh cho c&#7843; gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh l&amp;agrave; vi&#7879;c r&#7845;t n&amp;ecirc;n quan t&amp;acirc;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ch&#7885;n h&#432;&#7899;ng nh&amp;agrave; t&#7889;t v&#7899;i cung m&#7879;nh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mua-nha-moi.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i thu&#7897;c nh&amp;oacute;m T&amp;acirc;y t&#7913; tr&#7841;ch n&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7885;n nh&amp;agrave; thu&#7897;c nh&amp;oacute;m h&#432;&#7899;ng T&amp;acirc;y, T&amp;acirc;y Nam, T&amp;acirc;y B&#7855;c, &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng B&#7855;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&amp;oacute;m &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng t&#7913; tr&#7841;ch n&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7885;n nh&amp;agrave; nh&amp;oacute;m h&#432;&#7899;ng t&#7889;t g&#7891;m Nam, B&#7855;c, &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng, &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng Nam.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nh&#7919;ng y&#7871;u t&#7889; ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute; khi mua nh&amp;agrave;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Khi &#273;i mua nh&amp;agrave;, b&#7841;n c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i t&amp;igrave;m hi&#7875;u k&#7929; lai l&#7883;ch c&#7911;a ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;. N&#7871;u mua &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;agrave; ch&#7911; c&#361; v&#7915;a m&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#259;ng ch&#7913;c, tr&amp;uacute;ng x&#7893; s&#7889; v&amp;agrave; chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7871;n m&#7897;t ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; m&#7899;i khang trang h&#417;n l&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u r&#7845;t may m&#7855;n, t&#7889;t v&#7873; phong th&#7911;y v&amp;agrave; t&#7841;o ra nh&#7919;ng n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng t&amp;iacute;ch c&#7921;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNg&#432;&#7907;c l&#7841;i, b&#7841;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng n&amp;ecirc;n mua m&#7897;t ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; n&#7871;u ch&#7911; c&#361; v&#7915;a m&#7899;i ly h&amp;ocirc;n, b&#7883; t&#7883;ch thu nh&amp;agrave;, hay m&#7855;c m&#7897;t lo&#7841;i b&#7879;nh hi&#7875;m ngh&amp;egrave;o, b&#7883; t&amp;ugrave; t&#7897;i, ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n&amp;hellip; B&#7903;i mua m&#7897;t ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; nh&#432; th&#7871;, c&amp;oacute; ngh&#297;a l&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n &#273;&amp;atilde; mua nh&#7919;ng r&#7855;c r&#7889;i v&amp;agrave;o m&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mua-nha-moi1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, b&#7841;n c&#361;ng c&#7847;n quan t&amp;acirc;m &#273;&#7871;n th&#7871; &#273;&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; h&amp;igrave;nh d&amp;aacute;ng c&#7911;a khu &#273;&#7845;t. H&amp;igrave;nh d&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7865;p nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a khu &#273;&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; h&amp;igrave;nh vu&amp;ocirc;ng, h&amp;igrave;nh ch&#7919; nh&#7853;t. &#272;&#7857;ng sau c&#7911;a khu &#273;&#7845;t r&#7897;ng h&#417;n v&amp;agrave; cao h&#417;n &#273;&#7857;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c (n&#7903; h&#7853;u) l&amp;agrave; &#273;i&#7873;u t&#7889;t l&amp;agrave;nh. Ng&#432;&#7907;c l&#7841;i, &#273;&#7857;ng sau h&#7865;p h&#417;n, th&#7845;p h&#417;n, s&#7869; t&#7841;o ra s&#7921; m&#7845;t m&amp;aacute;t, kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nh&#7919;ng c&#7845;u tr&amp;uacute;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; mang l&#7841;i v&#7853;n r&#7911;i&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ki&#7875;u d&amp;aacute;ng thi&#7871;t k&#7871; c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i c&amp;oacute; qu&amp;aacute; nhi&#7873;u g&amp;oacute;c c&#7841;nh c&#7897;t t&#7847;ng l&#7847;u c&amp;ugrave;ng nhi&#7873;u h&amp;igrave;nh d&#7841;ng kh&amp;aacute;c nhau c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; v&amp;ocirc; t&amp;igrave;nh ph&amp;aacute;t ra m&#361;i t&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7897;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&amp;ecirc;n tr&amp;aacute;nh nh&#7919;ng c&#7845;u tr&amp;uacute;c th&#7859;ng d&amp;agrave;i nh&#432; m&#7897;t con &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&amp;acirc;m th&#7859;ng v&amp;agrave;o c&#7917;a tr&#432;&#7899;c, ho&#7863;c m&#7897;t h&amp;agrave;nh lang d&amp;agrave;i ch&#297;a th&#7859;ng v&amp;agrave;o ph&amp;ograve;ng. Nh&#7919;ng c&#7845;u tr&amp;uacute;c b&amp;eacute;n nh&#7885;n nh&#432; c&#7841;nh c&#7911;a m&#7897;t t&amp;ograve;a nh&amp;agrave; g&#7847;n &#273;&amp;oacute; h&#432;&#7899;ng th&#7859;ng &#273;&#7871;n ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n, ho&#7863;c c&#7841;nh c&#7911;a m&#7897;t c&amp;acirc;y c&#7897;t trong ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch nh&#7855;m th&#7859;ng v&amp;agrave;o ch&#7895; b&#7841;n ng&#7891;i; nh&#7919;ng c&#7845;u tr&amp;uacute;c h&amp;igrave;nh tam gi&amp;aacute;c nh&#432; &#273;&amp;ograve;n tay m&amp;aacute;i nh&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;ng x&amp;oacute;m ch&#297;a th&#7859;ng v&amp;agrave;o c&#7917;a tr&#432;&#7899;c ho&#7863;c c&#7917;a s&#7893; nh&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &#273;em &#273;&#7871;n nh&#7919;ng r&#7911;i ro cho b&#7841;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nC&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem l&amp;agrave; c&#7917;a kh&#7849;u c&#7911;a ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; l&amp;agrave; n&#417;i &#273;&amp;oacute;n nh&#7853;n v&#7853;n may t&amp;agrave;i l&#7897;c. H&#432;&#7899;ng c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;agrave; y&#7871;u t&#7889; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng m&#7841;nh nh&#7845;t &#273;&#7871;n l&#7907;i &amp;iacute;ch c&#7911;a t&#7915;ng th&amp;agrave;nh vi&amp;ecirc;n trong gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh. T&#7889;t nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh c&amp;ugrave;ng h&#432;&#7899;ng v&#7899;i ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;. &#272;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y gi&amp;uacute;p n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng xung quanh ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&amp;ograve;a h&#7907;p v&amp;agrave; c&amp;acirc;n b&#7857;ng. Trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;ugrave;ng h&#432;&#7899;ng v&#7899;i ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;, n&amp;ecirc;n t&#7841;o ra c&#7917;a ph&#7909; ho&#7863;c c&#7917;a s&#7893; &#273;&#7863;t &#7903; h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&amp;oacute;. V&#7883; tr&amp;iacute; x&#7845;u nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;agrave; khi c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh n&#7857;m &#7903; h&#432;&#7899;ng x&#7845;u nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&amp;iacute; d&#7909;, nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n h&#432;&#7899;ng Nam, c&#7917;a &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n h&#432;&#7899;ng &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng Nam l&amp;agrave; t&#7889;t; c&#7917;a &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n h&#432;&#7899;ng T&amp;acirc;y Nam th&amp;igrave; x&#7845;u.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n h&#432;&#7899;ng B&#7855;c, c&#7917;a &#273;&#7893;i di&#7879;n h&#432;&#7899;ng &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng B&#7855;c l&amp;agrave; x&#7845;u, c&#7917;a &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n h&#432;&#7899;ng T&amp;acirc;y B&#7855;c l&amp;agrave; t&#7889;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n h&#432;&#7899;ng T&amp;acirc;y, c&#7917;a &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n h&#432;&#7899;ng T&amp;acirc;y Nam l&amp;agrave; t&#7889;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n h&#432;&#7899;ng &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng, c&#7917;a &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n h&#432;&#7899;ng &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng B&#7855;c l&amp;agrave; x&#7845;u, c&#7917;a &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n h&#432;&#7899;ng &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng Nam th&amp;igrave; t&#7889;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&amp;aacute;ch b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; c&amp;aacute;c ph&amp;ograve;ng trong ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&amp;agrave; b&#7871;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7863;t &#7903; b&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7843;i c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh (theo h&#432;&#7899;ng t&amp;iacute;nh t&#7915; ngo&amp;agrave;i v&amp;agrave;o nh&amp;agrave;) v&amp;igrave; n&#259;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng kh&amp;iacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&amp;iacute;ch t&#7909; &#7903; &#273;&amp;acirc;y theo th&#7901;i gian c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; g&amp;acirc;y hi&#7873;m kh&amp;iacute;ch trong gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kh&amp;ocirc;ng n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7863;t nh&amp;agrave; b&#7871;p &#7903; khu v&#7921;c T&amp;acirc;y B&#7855;c c&#7911;a ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; v&amp;igrave; &#273;i&#7873;u n&amp;agrave;y t&#7841;o ra v&#7853;n r&#7911;i v&amp;agrave; th&#7845;t tho&amp;aacute;t t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh cho ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#7911; c&#7911;a gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&amp;agrave; v&#7879; sinh kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t &#7903; g&#7847;n c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh ho&#7863;c &#273;&#7889;i di&#7879;n ho&#7863;c ngay ph&amp;iacute;a tr&amp;ecirc;n c&#7911;a c&#7917;a ch&amp;iacute;nh, v&amp;igrave; nh&#432; v&#7853;y v&#7853;n may trong nh&amp;agrave; s&#7869; b&#7883; ti&amp;ecirc;u hao h&#7871;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u y&#7871;u t&#7889; c&#7847;n ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute; khi mua m&#7897;t ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; m&#7899;i, vi&#7879;c ch&#7885;n l&#7921;a k&#7929; l&#432;&#7905;ng, &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i c&#7847;n tham kh&#7843;o nh&#7919;ng c&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;oacute;a gi&#7843;i &#273;i&#7875;m x&#7845;u trong ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7875; c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian s&#7889;ng tho&#7843;i m&amp;aacute;i, &#273;em l&#7841;i v&#432;&#7907;ng kh&amp;iacute; cho c&#7843; gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;','27/12/2011','28/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/mua-nha-moi.jpg',38,11,2022,'huyennt',1,'mua-nha-moi-dem-lai-tai-loc','nh&agrave; m&#7899;i, t&agrave;i l&#7897;c, kh&ocirc;ng gian s&#7889;ng, b&#7889; tr&iacute;, khong gian song, nha moi',NULL,NULL,NULL,'nh&agrave; m&#7899;i, t&agrave;i l&#7897;c, kh&ocirc;ng gian s&#7889;ng, b&#7889; tr&iacute;, khong gian song, nha moi',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'',1,0,0,0),(163,'C&#259;n h&#7897; The Hyco4 Tower gi&aacute; t&#7915; 1,1 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng','C&ocirc;ng ty c&#7893; ph&#7847;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; B&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n Th&#7911;y L&#7907;i 4A v&#7915;a m&#7903; b&aacute;n c&#259;n h&#7897; d&#7921; &aacute;n The Hyco4 Tower v&#7899;i gi&aacute; t&#7915; 1,1 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng/c&#259;n.','&lt;p&gt;The Hyco4 Tower &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n tr&amp;ecirc;n khu&amp;ocirc;n vi&amp;ecirc;n r&#7897;ng 7.000m2, m&#7853;t &#273;&#7897; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng 40%, tr&amp;ecirc;n tr&#7909;c &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng Nguy&#7877;n X&amp;iacute;, k&#7871;t n&#7889;i v&#7899;i v&amp;agrave;nh &#273;ai B&amp;igrave;nh L&#7907;i &amp;ndash; T&amp;acirc;n S&#417;n Nh&#7845;t 800m, c&amp;aacute;ch b&#7871;n xe Mi&#7873;n &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng 500m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/phoicanhhyco_89863.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nD&#7921; &amp;aacute;n g&#7891;m 03 t&amp;ograve;a nh&amp;agrave; cao 17 t&#7847;ng, t&#7915; t&#7847;ng h&#7847;m &#273;&#7871;n t&#7847;ng 2 d&amp;agrave;nh cho trung t&amp;acirc;m th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i c&amp;ugrave;ng ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch n&#7897;i khu, t&#7915; t&#7847;ng 3 &amp;ndash; 17 l&amp;agrave; 330 c&#259;n h&#7897; v&#7899;i di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch t&#7915; 52,2 &amp;ndash; 131,36m2. Ri&amp;ecirc;ng t&#7847;ng 17 c&amp;oacute; 06 c&#259;n h&#7897; penthouse v&#7899;i di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch 161,5 &amp;ndash; 220,07m2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;ang thi c&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7871;n t&#7847;ng 5 v&amp;agrave; d&#7921; ki&#7871;n b&amp;agrave;n giao c&#259;n h&#7897; ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n cho kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng v&amp;agrave;o qu&amp;yacute; II/2013.&lt;/p&gt;','27/12/2011','28/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/phoicanhhyco_89863.jpg',31,8,1935,'huyennt',1,'can-ho-the-hyco4-tower-gia-tu-1-1-ty-dong','C&#259;n h&#7897;, d&#7921; &aacute;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'C&#259;n h&#7897;, d&#7921; &aacute;n',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'',1,0,0,0),(164,'Xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7871;n ch&acirc;u Phi','Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam &#432;&#7899;c t&iacute;nh, trong n&#259;m 2012, l&#432;&#7907;ng xi m&#259;ng ti&ecirc;u th&#7909; t&#7841;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&#7897;i &#273;&#7883;a &#273;&#7841;t t&#7915; 52 - 53 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n v&agrave; l&#432;&#7907;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u v&agrave;o kho&#7843;ng 6 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nN&#259;m 2011, to&amp;agrave;n ng&amp;agrave;nh xi m&#259;ng m&#7899;i s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t &#273;&#7841;t 85% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/ximang.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;Ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n V&#259;n &#272;i&#7879;p, Ch&amp;aacute;nh v&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i Xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam cho bi&#7871;t, n&#259;m 2011, do ch&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ch th&#7855;t ch&#7863;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; c&amp;ocirc;ng, l&amp;atilde;i su&#7845;t cho vay &#7903; m&#7913;c cao&amp;hellip; &#273;&amp;atilde; khi&#7871;n nhi&#7873;u c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng b&#7883; c&#7855;t gi&#7843;m, b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n &#7871; &#7849;m&amp;hellip; Nh&#7919;ng y&#7871;u t&#7889; tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&amp;atilde; khi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; xi m&#259;ng trong n&#432;&#7899;c c&#7843; n&#259;m ch&#7881; &#7903; m&#7913;c 49,15 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n. L&#432;&#7907;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u l&amp;agrave; 5,5 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, c&#7897;ng v&#7899;i l&#432;&#7907;ng d&#7921; tr&#7919; kho&#7843;ng 3 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n. Theo &#273;&amp;oacute;, s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a to&amp;agrave;n ng&amp;agrave;nh m&#7899;i &#273;&#7841;t 85% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871; (t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t thi&#7871;t k&#7871; l&amp;agrave; 67 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n) v&amp;agrave; l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; &#273;&#7841;t 91% k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch c&#7911;a n&#259;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong n&#259;m 2012, theo &amp;ocirc;ng &#272;i&#7879;p s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; th&amp;ecirc;m 8 nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y xi m&#259;ng m&#7899;i v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t 6,9 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng, n&amp;acirc;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t c&#7911;a to&amp;agrave;n ng&amp;agrave;nh l&amp;ecirc;n 73 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n. Trong khi, t&#7893;ng l&#432;&#7907;ng ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; xi m&#259;ng trong n&#259;m t&#7899;i c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam m&#7899;i ch&#7881; &#273;&#7841;t g&#7847;n 60 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n, t&#7913;c chi&#7871;m kho&#7843;ng 86% c&amp;ocirc;ng su&#7845;t c&#7911;a to&amp;agrave;n ng&amp;agrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong 6 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m d&#7921; ki&#7871;n s&#7869; xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2012, s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; kho&#7843;ng 500 ngh&amp;igrave;n t&#7845;n xi m&#259;ng v&amp;agrave; 5,5 tri&#7879;u t&#7845;n clinker. V&#7873; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, &amp;ocirc;ng &#272;i&#7879;p cho r&#7857;ng v&#7851;n ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c &#7903; ch&amp;acirc;u Phi.&lt;/p&gt;','28/12/2011','28/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/ximang.jpg',23,2,1867,'huyennt',1,'xuat-khau-xi-mang-viet-nam-huong-den-chau-phi','xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t nam, nh&agrave; m&aacute;y xi m&#259;ng, Vi&#7879;t Nam, ch&acirc;u Phi',NULL,NULL,NULL,'xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, xi m&#259;ng Vi&#7879;t nam, nh&agrave; m&aacute;y xi m&#259;ng, Vi&#7879;t Nam, ch&acirc;u Phi',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(165,'M&#7865;o l&agrave;m &#7845;m nh&agrave; khi s&#7917; d&#7909;ng nh&#7919;ng gam m&agrave;u &ldquo;l&#7841;nh to&aacute;t&rdquo;','S&#7917; d&#7909;ng nh&#7919;ng gam m&agrave;u l&#7841;nh l&agrave;m s&aacute;ng nh&agrave; ho&#7863;c gi&uacute;p ng&ocirc;i nh&agrave; tr&#7903; n&ecirc;n r&#7897;ng h&#417;n l&agrave; m&#7897;t m&#7865;o trong thi&#7871;t k&#7871; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t. V&agrave;o m&ugrave;a h&egrave; th&igrave; &#273;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng g&igrave; t&#7899;i sinh ho&#7841;t gia &#273;&igrave;nh th&#7871; nh&#432;ng n&#7871;u l&agrave; v&agrave;o m&ugrave;a &#273;&ocirc;ng th&igrave; &#7855;t s&#7869; t&#7841;o b&#7847;u kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; l&#7841;nh l&#7869;o, &#7843;m &#273;&#7841;m cho ng&ocirc;i nh&agrave;.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; n&amp;agrave;y c&#7921;c k&#7923; d&#7877; d&amp;agrave;ng thay &#273;&#7893;i n&#7871;u nh&#432; b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n bi&#7871;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh tr&#7903; n&amp;ecirc;n &#7845;m c&amp;uacute;ng h&#417;n. C&#7909; th&#7875; nh&#432; sau:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;B&#7893; sung s&#7855;c m&amp;agrave;u cho c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng &amp;ldquo;tr&#7855;ng &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897;&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u m&#7897;t c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng to&amp;agrave;n b&#7897; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng t&#7915; m&amp;agrave;u s&#417;n t&#7899;i n&#7897;i th&#7845;t th&amp;igrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i &#7903; m&#7897;t v&amp;agrave;i chi ti&#7871;t nh&#7887;. Nguy&amp;ecirc;n t&#7855;c &#273;&#7875; ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; tr&#7903; n&amp;ecirc;n &#7845;m c&amp;uacute;ng h&#417;n ch&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;agrave; trang tr&amp;iacute; nh&amp;agrave; v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng gam m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;oacute;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;381&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/phong-khach-mua-dong-1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/phong-khach-mua-dong-2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#417;n t&#432;&#7901;ng kh&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i tu&#7923; theo &amp;yacute; th&amp;iacute;ch c&#7911;a gia ch&#7911; theo m&amp;ugrave;a v&amp;igrave; kh&amp;aacute; m&#7845;t th&#7901;i gian v&amp;agrave; chi ph&amp;iacute; b&#7887; ra c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7887;. V&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y &#273;a ph&#7847;n m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n ph&#432;&#417;ng &amp;aacute;n thay &#273;&#7893;i di&#7879;n m&#7841;o n&#7897;i th&#7845;t trong nh&amp;agrave; nh&#432; r&amp;egrave;m, sofa, th&#7843;m&amp;hellip;.&#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n m&amp;agrave; c&#7921;c k&#7923; hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;. C&#7909; th&#7875;, r&amp;egrave;m c&#7917;a m&amp;agrave;u nh&#7841;t ho&#7863;c m&amp;agrave;u ghi n&amp;ecirc;n thay b&#7857;ng m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c ho&#7863;c l&amp;agrave; t&#432;&#417;i m&#7899;i ho&#7863;c l&amp;agrave; &#7845;m c&amp;uacute;ng nh&#432; v&amp;agrave;ng, &#273;&#7887; s&#7851;m, cam, n&amp;acirc;u&amp;hellip;.Gh&#7871; sofa n&#7871;u b&#7857;ng v&#7843;i c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; thay th&#7871; v&#7887; c&#361;ng b&#7857;ng nh&#7919;ng gam m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;oacute;ng, n&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; gh&#7871; da gia ch&#7911; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7855;m th&amp;ecirc;m m&#7897;t v&amp;agrave;i chi&#7871;c g&#7889;i t&#7921;a &amp;ecirc;m &amp;aacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/phong-khach-mua-dong-3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nT&#432;&#7901;ng nh&amp;agrave; n&amp;ecirc;n b&amp;agrave;i tr&amp;iacute; th&amp;ecirc;m m&#7897;t b&#7913;c tranh s&#417;n d&#7847;u b&#7903;i b&#7913;c s&#417;n d&#7847;u &#273;&#7865;p s&#7869; ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian nh&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n v&#7899;i v&#7867; k&#7923; b&amp;iacute; c&#7911;a m&amp;ugrave;a &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng. Tranh s&#417;n d&#7847;u c&amp;oacute; s&#7913;c m&amp;ecirc; ho&#7863;c gh&amp;ecirc; g&#7899;m v&amp;igrave; lo&#7841;i h&amp;igrave;nh ngh&#7879; thu&#7853;t n&amp;agrave;y c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ph&amp;ocirc; di&#7877;n ra v&#7867; &#273;&#7865;p k&#7923; di&#7879;u c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng mi&#7873;n tuy&#7871;t ph&#7911; xa x&amp;ocirc;i. Ngo&amp;agrave;i vi&#7879;c mang v&#7867; &#273;&#7865;p c&#7911;a m&amp;ugrave;a &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7871;n v&#7899;i ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n th&amp;igrave; treo tranh c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave;&amp;nbsp;c&amp;aacute;ch l&#7845;p &#273;&#7847;y nh&#7919;ng m&#7843;ng t&#432;&#7901;ng tr&#7889;ng tr&#7855;ng tinh, l&#7841;nh l&#7869;o. Gi&amp;uacute;p c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; c&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;c &amp;ldquo;&#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7863;n&amp;rdquo; h&#417;n, nhi&#7873;u &#273;&#7891; v&#7853;t x&amp;iacute;ch l&#7841;i g&#7847;n nhau h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/phong-khach-mua-dong-4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&amp;agrave;n nh&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;n nay ph&#7893;i bi&#7871;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng lo&#7841;i &#273;&amp;aacute; hoa s&amp;aacute;ng m&amp;agrave;u t&#7841;o c&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;c r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i, s&#7841;ch s&#7869;. N&amp;ecirc;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng th&#7843;m cho khu v&#7921;c n&amp;agrave;y v&amp;agrave; ch&#7885;n ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u th&#7843;m d&amp;agrave;y nh&#432; th&#7843;m l&amp;ocirc;ng ho&#7863;c th&#7843;m len.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&amp;ecirc;m ho&#7863;c thay &#273;&#7893;i ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u n&#7897;i th&#7845;t v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&amp;agrave;u ghi, x&amp;aacute;m&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/phong-khach-mua-dong-5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;ograve;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&amp;agrave;u ghi, x&amp;aacute;m&amp;hellip;.hay nh&#7919;ng m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c trung t&amp;iacute;nh th&#432;&#7901;ng mang l&#7841;i v&#7867; &#273;&#7865;p thanh l&#7883;ch, nh&#7865; nh&amp;agrave;ng v&amp;agrave; cu&#7889;n h&amp;uacute;t. Nh&#7919;ng gam m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;agrave;y d&amp;ugrave;ng &#7903; s&#7855;c &#273;&#7897; nh&#7865; n&amp;ecirc;n d&#7877; t&#7841;o thi&#7879;n c&#7843;m v&#7899;i ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng, ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; trang tr&amp;iacute; theo phong c&amp;aacute;ch hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, t&#7889;i gi&#7843;n. N&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n an to&amp;agrave;n ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i m&#7885;i ki&#7875;u th&#7901;i ti&#7871;t, k&#7875; c&#7843; m&amp;ugrave;a &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng l&#7841;nh l&#7869;o. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, &#273;&#7875; c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng c&amp;oacute; v&#7867; &#7845;m &amp;aacute;p h&#417;n trong m&amp;ugrave;a &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng, c&amp;aacute;c gia ch&#7911; v&#7851;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i m&#7897;t ch&amp;uacute;t, &#273;&amp;oacute; c&#361;ng l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;ch refresh cho kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian m&#7899;i m&#7867;, h&#7845;p d&#7851;n h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/phong-khach-mua-dong-6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/phong-khach-mua-dong-7.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7891; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t c&amp;oacute; ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u v&#7843;i nh&#432; gh&#7871; sofa, r&amp;egrave;m c&#7917;a,&amp;hellip;n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thay b&#7857;ng nh&#7919;ng lo&#7841;i v&#7843;i d&amp;agrave;y th&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p cho m&amp;ugrave;a &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#432; len, d&#7841;, n&#7881; nhung&amp;hellip;N&#7871;u nh&#432; m&amp;ugrave;a h&amp;egrave; v&#7843;i b&#7885;c gh&#7871; th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c d&amp;ugrave;ng l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng gam m&amp;agrave;u l&#7841;nh nh&#432; m&amp;agrave;u kem, xanh da tr&#7901;i, m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng&amp;hellip;th&amp;igrave; v&#7899;i m&amp;ugrave;a &#273;&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7841;n n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng nh&#7919;ng gam m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;oacute;ng, nh&#432; &#273;&#7887;, v&amp;agrave;ng n&amp;acirc;u, cam..&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng c&#361;ng n&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thay &#273;&#7893;i. Thay v&amp;igrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng tr&#7855;ng t&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c b&amp;oacute;ng &#273;&amp;egrave;n neon hay &#273;&amp;egrave;n LED, n&amp;ecirc;n d&amp;ugrave;ng c&amp;aacute;c b&amp;oacute;ng &#273;&amp;egrave;n s&#7907;i &#273;&#7889;t cho &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng v&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#7887;. S&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &amp;iacute;t ho&#7863;c nhi&#7873;u t&amp;ugrave;y v&amp;agrave;o nhu c&#7847;u trang tr&amp;iacute; v&amp;agrave; v&#7883; tr&amp;iacute; t&#7841;o &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n trong thi&#7871;t k&#7871;t. Gam m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;agrave;y s&#7869; t&#7841;o nhi&#7873;u s&#7921; &#7845;m &amp;aacute;p h&#417;n cho c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng.&lt;/p&gt;','28/12/2011','28/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian/phong-khach-mua-dong-5.jpg',38,11,2850,'huyennt',1,'meo-lam-am-nha-khi-su-dung-nhung-gam-mau-“lanh-toat”','m&ugrave;a &#273;&ocirc;ng, n&#7897;i th&#7845;t, nh&agrave; &#7903;, kh&ocirc;ng gian, r&egrave;m, th&#7843;m, sofa',NULL,NULL,NULL,'m&ugrave;a &#273;&ocirc;ng, n&#7897;i th&#7845;t, nh&agrave; &#7903;, kh&ocirc;ng gian, r&egrave;m, th&#7843;m, sofa',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(166,'Kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; vi&#7879;c DN th&eacute;p ph&aacute; s&#7843;n h&agrave;ng lo&#7841;t','M&#7897;t s&#7889; DN th&eacute;p ph&aacute; s&#7843;n ho&#7863;c ph&#7843;i &#273;&oacute;ng c&#7917;a b&aacute;n nh&agrave; m&aacute;y l&agrave; DN sai l&#7847;m trong chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, &#273;&acirc;y kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; b&#7913;c tranh to&agrave;n c&#7843;nh c&#7911;a c&#7843; ng&agrave;nh.','&lt;p&gt;Tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n m&#7897;t s&#7889; th&amp;ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; s&#7921; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n c&#7911;a DN th&amp;eacute;p v&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t s&#7889; DN th&amp;eacute;p g&#7863;p kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, theo t&amp;igrave;m hi&#7875;u c&#7911;a &#272;TCK, m&#7897;t s&#7889; DN th&amp;eacute;p ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n ho&#7863;c ph&#7843;i &#273;&amp;oacute;ng c&#7917;a b&amp;aacute;n nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;aacute;y l&amp;agrave; DN sai l&#7847;m trong chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;, &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; kh&amp;ocirc;ng hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; ho&#7863;c l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng DN xu&#7845;t nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7889;n vay qu&amp;aacute; l&#7899;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;ograve;n nhi&#7873;u DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p kh&amp;aacute;c ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh v&amp;agrave; v&#7851;n c&amp;oacute; l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n &#273;&#7873;u &#273;&#7873;u nh&#432; H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t, Pomina, &#272;&#7841;i Thi&amp;ecirc;n L&#7897;c, Hoa Sen, SMC&amp;hellip;, d&amp;ugrave; t&#7927; su&#7845;t l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n &#7903; m&#7895;i DN kh&amp;aacute;c nhau. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; chuy&#7879;n DN th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&amp;igrave;nh &#273;&#7889;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t hay ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n h&amp;agrave;ng lo&#7841;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c DN ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p, n&#259;m t&#7899;i, n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871; v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n nhi&#7873;u kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng chung c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh, nh&#432;ng b&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, c&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p v&#7851;n c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7889; thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i, nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; khi B&#7897; C&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#417;ng d&#7921; b&amp;aacute;o t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p n&#259;m t&#7899;i kho&#7843;ng 5 - 7%. Nhu c&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;u th&#7909; th&amp;eacute;p g&#7855;n li&#7873;n v&#7899;i t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7911;a n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871;. N&#259;m 2012, ch&#7881; ti&amp;ecirc;u t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng GDP &#7903; m&#7913;c 6%, th&#7845;p h&#417;n t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng c&#7911;a n&#259;m nay. V&amp;igrave; th&#7871;, c&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p ph&#7843;i chu&#7849;n b&#7883; tinh th&#7847;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i ph&amp;oacute; v&#7899;i m&#7897;t n&#259;m kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n h&#417;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i ng&amp;agrave;nh, nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; khi gi&amp;aacute; &#273;i&#7879;n, y&#7871;u t&#7889; &#273;&#7847;u v&amp;agrave;o quan tr&#7885;ng c&#7911;a ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#259;ng 5%.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/dn-thep.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;C&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p ph&#7843;i chu&#7849;n b&#7883; tinh th&#7847;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7889;i ph&amp;oacute; v&#7899;i m&#7897;t n&#259;m kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n h&#417;n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng &#272;&#7895; Duy Th&amp;aacute;i, T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c C&amp;ocirc;ng ty Th&amp;eacute;p Pomina cho bi&#7871;t, n&#259;m nay, t&#7841;i th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng khu v&#7921;c ph&amp;iacute;a Nam, s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a Pomina gi&#7843;m h&#417;n 20% d&amp;ugrave; C&amp;ocirc;ng ty v&#7851;n d&#7851;n &#273;&#7847;u v&#7873; th&#7883; ph&#7847;n th&amp;eacute;p. &amp;quot;Ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng hy v&#7885;ng Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; s&#7869; n&#7899;i t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng, b&#7903;i &#273;&#7875; &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh v&#297; m&amp;ocirc; th&amp;igrave; th&amp;igrave; si&#7871;t t&amp;iacute;n d&#7909;ng l&amp;agrave; c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t&amp;quot;, &amp;ocirc;ng Th&amp;aacute;i n&amp;oacute;i. &amp;Ocirc;ng Th&amp;aacute;i v&#7915;a c&amp;oacute; chuy&#7871;n &#273;i &#273;&#7871;n m&#7897;t lo&#7841;t t&#7881;nh, th&amp;agrave;nh ph&amp;iacute;a Nam &#273;&#7875; &#273;&amp;ocirc;n &#273;&#7889;c ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng b&amp;aacute;n h&amp;agrave;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7841;i gia ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p &#7903; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng ph&amp;iacute;a B&#7855;c c&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; chung nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7873; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng th&amp;eacute;p n&#259;m 2012. &amp;Ocirc;ng Tr&#7847;n Tu&#7845;n D&#432;&#417;ng, T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c T&#7853;p &#273;o&amp;agrave;n H&amp;ograve;a Ph&amp;aacute;t (HPG) d&#7921; ki&#7871;n, n&#259;m 2012 l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t n&#259;m m&amp;agrave; DN th&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p v&#432;&#7907;t kh&amp;oacute; cam go h&#417;n c&#7843; n&#259;m nay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;T&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;igrave;n kinh t&#7871; v&#297; m&amp;ocirc; n&#259;m 2012 v&#7899;i quan &#273;i&#7875;m th&#7853;n tr&#7885;ng, nh&#432;ng c&#361;ng c&amp;oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7889; &#273;i&#7875;m l&#7841;c quan c&amp;oacute; c&#417; s&#7903; cho ng&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;eacute;p, khi ng&amp;agrave;nh n&amp;agrave;y v&#7851;n t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c DN l&#7899;n &#273;&#7873;u ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh. T&#7915; n&#259;m ngo&amp;aacute;i, ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i &#273;&amp;atilde; x&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh d&#7921;a v&amp;agrave;o ti&#7873;m l&#7921;c c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh l&amp;agrave; ch&amp;iacute;nh, ch&#7913; kh&amp;ocirc;ng hy v&#7885;ng c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; h&#7895; tr&#7907; t&#7915; b&amp;ecirc;n ngo&amp;agrave;i&amp;quot;, &amp;ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n Ng&#7885;c Anh, T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c C&amp;ocirc;ng ty SMC n&amp;oacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Anh cho bi&#7871;t, n&#259;m nay SMC &#273;&#7841;t h&#417;n 76 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n sau thu&#7871; v&amp;agrave; d&#7921; ki&#7871;n n&#259;m t&#7899;i s&#7869; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch &#7903; m&#7913;c 80 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng. C&amp;aacute;c DN s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t quy m&amp;ocirc; l&#7899;n h&#417;n tuy ch&#432;a c&amp;oacute; k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch c&#7909; th&#7875; nh&#432;ng &#273;&#7873;u cho bi&#7871;t, s&#7869; ph&#7845;n &#273;&#7845;u t&#259;ng th&#7883; ph&#7847;n v&amp;agrave; doanh thu, nh&#432;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7863;t n&#7863;ng t&#259;ng tr&#432;&#7903;ng l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n trong t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh hi&#7879;n nay.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u tu&#7847;n qua, c&amp;aacute;c DN th&amp;eacute;p &#273;ang quan s&amp;aacute;t th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7875; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; n&amp;acirc;ng gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n t&#7915; 200.000 - 300.000 &#273;&#7891;ng/t&#7845;n v&amp;agrave;o d&#7883;p cu&#7889;i n&#259;m ho&#7863;c &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m m&#7899;i, v&amp;igrave; gi&amp;aacute; nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u &#273;&amp;atilde; t&#259;ng nh&#7865; 15 USD/t&#7845;n do c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t l&#7899;n tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i &#273;&amp;atilde; b&#7883; l&#7895;. Ri&amp;ecirc;ng &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i ng&amp;agrave;nh h&amp;agrave;ng th&amp;eacute;p t&#7845;m, gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng th&#7871; gi&#7899;i v&#7915;a tr&#7843;i qua m&#7897;t &#273;&#7907;t bi&#7871;n &#273;&#7897;ng kh&amp;aacute; m&#7841;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong 2 tu&#7847;n qua, gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;eacute;p c&amp;aacute;n n&amp;oacute;ng nh&amp;iacute;ch l&amp;ecirc;n m&#7897;t ch&amp;uacute;t kho&#7843;ng 10 - 15 USD/t&#7845;n sau m&#7897;t chu&#7895;i ng&amp;agrave;y gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; li&amp;ecirc;n t&#7909;c t&#7899;i 100 USD/t&#7845;n, t&#7915; 740 USD v&#7873; 640 USD/t&#7845;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ocirc;ng Nguy&#7877;n Thanh Ngh&#297;a, T&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c CTCP &#272;&#7841;i Thi&amp;ecirc;n L&#7897;c (DTL) cho bi&#7871;t, cu&#7889;i n&#259;m DTL c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; ph&#7843;i tr&amp;iacute;ch l&#7853;p d&#7921; ph&amp;ograve;ng gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; cho h&#417;n 10.000 t&#7845;n c&amp;aacute;n n&amp;oacute;ng nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u, do ch&amp;ecirc;nh l&#7879;ch gi&amp;aacute; v&#7889;n v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng. DTL nh&#7853;p l&amp;ocirc; h&amp;agrave;ng n&amp;agrave;y ph&#7909;c v&#7909; ch&#7841;y d&amp;acirc;y chuy&#7873;n c&amp;aacute;n ngu&#7897;i m&#7899;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy ph&#7843;i tr&amp;iacute;ch d&#7921; ph&amp;ograve;ng gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;, nh&#432;ng v&#7899;i m&#7863;t b&#7857;ng gi&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m hi&#7879;n nay, khi &#273;&#432;a l&amp;ocirc; c&amp;aacute;n n&amp;oacute;ng n&amp;agrave;y v&amp;agrave;o s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t ra s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m, l&#7907;i nhu&#7853;n &#7903; c&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;acirc;u c&amp;aacute;n ngu&#7897;i, m&#7841; l&#7841;nh, m&#7841; m&amp;agrave;u s&#7869; gi&amp;uacute;p DTL ho&amp;agrave;n v&#7889;n, kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7883; l&#7895;. B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&#7897;i &#273;&#7883;a, th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u v&#7851;n l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t k&amp;ecirc;nh &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng doanh thu v&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7911;a DTL.&lt;/p&gt;','29/12/2011','29/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/dn-thep.jpg',23,2,1877,'huyennt',1,'khong-co-viec-dn-thep-pha-san-hang-loat','doanh nghi&#7879;p, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, th&eacute;p, ph&aacute; s&#7843;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'doanh nghi&#7879;p, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u, th&eacute;p, ph&aacute; s&#7843;n',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,1),(167,'Knight Frank ti&#7871;p th&#7883; v&#259;n ph&ograve;ng Saigon One Tower','C&ocirc;ng ty c&#7893; ph&#7847;n &#273;&#7883;a &#7889;c Saigon M&amp;C &#273;&atilde; b&#7893; nhi&#7879;m Knight Frank Vi&#7879;t Nam l&agrave; &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n ti&#7871;p th&#7883; v&agrave; cho thu&ecirc; &#273;&#7897;c quy&#7873;n kh&#7889;i v&#259;n ph&ograve;ng c&#7911;a d&#7921; &aacute;n ph&#7913;c h&#7907;p Saigon One Tower.','&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;Saigon One Tower cao 41 t&#7847;ng t&#7885;a l&#7841;c t&#7841;i giao l&#7897; H&amp;agrave;m Nghi v&amp;agrave; T&amp;ocirc;n &#272;&#7913;c Th&#7855;ng, d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n v&#7899;i kho&#7843;ng 40.000 m&amp;eacute;t vu&amp;ocirc;ng v&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng cho thu&amp;ecirc; n&amp;agrave;y s&#7869; l&amp;agrave; khu v&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng h&#7841;ng A &#273;&#7841;t ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n qu&#7889;c t&#7871; l&#7899;n nh&#7845;t t&#7841;i TP.HCM.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/sgone-tower1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&#7842;nh minh h&#7885;a.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;D&#7921; ki&#7871;n ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh v&amp;agrave;o th&amp;aacute;ng 04/2012, d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n bao g&#7891;m hai th&amp;aacute;p kh&#7889;i &#273;&#7871; v&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng v&amp;agrave; c&#259;n h&#7897; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&#7889;i k&#7871;t b&#7903;i khu trung t&amp;acirc;m th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i&lt;/p&gt;','29/12/2011','29/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/sgone-tower1.jpg',29,8,1992,'huyennt',1,'knight-frank-tiep-thi-van-phong-saigon-one-tower','Knight Frank, Saigon One Tower, v&#259;n ph&ograve;ng, c&#259;n h&#7897;, ti&#7871;p th&#7883;, &#273;&#7897;c quy&#7873;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Knight Frank, Saigon One Tower, v&#259;n ph&ograve;ng, c&#259;n h&#7897;, ti&#7871;p th&#7883;, &#273;&#7897;c quy&#7873;n',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(168,'Ki&ecirc;n Giang: X&acirc;y t&ograve;a th&aacute;p &#273;&ocirc;i cao 12 t&#7847;ng','Ph&oacute; Ch&#7911; t&#7883;ch UBND t&#7881;nh Ki&ecirc;n Giang Ph&#7841;m V&#361; H&#7891;ng v&#7915;a th&ocirc;ng qua l&#7847;n cu&#7889;i quy ho&#7841;ch chi ti&#7871;t khu h&agrave;nh ch&iacute;nh t&#7853;p trung c&#7911;a t&#7881;nh t&#7841;i &#273;i&#7875;m cu&#7889;i &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng Tr&#7847;n Quang Kh&#7843;i, ph&#432;&#7901;ng An Ho&agrave;, TP R&#7841;ch Gi&aacute;.','\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;278&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/phoi-canh-du-an.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;Ph&#7889;i c&#7843;nh d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nD&#7921; &amp;aacute;n g&#7891;m ph&#7847;n &#273;&#7845;t li&#7873;n v&amp;agrave; ph&#7847;n l&#7845;n bi&#7875;n. Trong &#273;&amp;oacute;, ph&#7847;n &#273;&#7845;t li&#7873;n b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; 2 l&amp;ocirc;, m&#7895;i l&amp;ocirc; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng to&amp;agrave; th&amp;aacute;p &#273;&amp;ocirc;i cao 12 t&#7847;ng, di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch s&amp;agrave;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng m&#7895;i th&amp;aacute;p &#273;&amp;ocirc;i kho&#7843;ng 35.800m2, t&#7893;ng v&#7889;n &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; l&amp;agrave; 752,85 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Khu l&#7845;n bi&#7875;n m&#7903; r&#7897;ng 29,41ha &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh l&amp;agrave; khu h&amp;agrave;nh ch&amp;iacute;nh d&#7921; tr&#7919; c&amp;oacute; chi ph&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; kh&amp;aacute;i to&amp;aacute;n kho&#7843;ng 90 t&#7927; &#273;&#7891;ng, d&#7921; ki&#7871;n s&#7869; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng to&amp;agrave; nh&amp;agrave; cao 5 t&#7847;ng v&#7899;i t&#7893;ng di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch s&amp;agrave;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kho&#7843;ng 7.000m2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Su&#7845;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; trung b&amp;igrave;nh c&#7911;a d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n khu h&amp;agrave;nh ch&amp;iacute;nh t&#7853;p trung t&#7881;nh Ki&amp;ecirc;n Giang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh v&amp;agrave;o kho&#7843;ng 9,5 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Sau khi x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng xong, khu h&amp;agrave;nh ch&amp;iacute;nh t&#7853;p trung d&#7921; ki&#7871;n cung c&#7845;p n&#417;i l&amp;agrave;m vi&#7879;c th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&amp;ecirc;n cho kho&#7843;ng 2.440 c&amp;aacute;n b&#7897;, c&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7913;c, vi&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7913;c. Vi&#7879;c quy ho&#7841;ch x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng khu h&amp;agrave;nh ch&amp;iacute;nh t&#7853;p trung c&#361;ng nh&#7857;m tr&amp;aacute;nh l&amp;atilde;ng ph&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7845;t c&amp;ocirc;ng, t&#7841;o &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897; v&#7873; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng gi&#7919;a c&amp;aacute;c c&#417; quan nh&amp;agrave; n&#432;&#7899;c.&lt;/p&gt;','29/12/2011','29/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/phoi-canh-du-an.jpg',36,8,1910,'huyennt',1,'kien-giang-xay-toa-thap-doi-cao-12-tang','quy ho&#7841;ch, t&ograve;a th&aacute;p, ph&#7889;i c&#7843;nh, d&#7921; &aacute;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'quy ho&#7841;ch, t&ograve;a th&aacute;p, ph&#7889;i c&#7843;nh, d&#7921; &aacute;n',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(169,'B&agrave;i tr&iacute; c&acirc;y c&#7843;nh trong nh&agrave;','M&ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng &ocirc; nhi&#7877;m &#273;&atilde; t&#7841;o &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n thu&#7853;n l&#7907;i cho c&aacute;c ch&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;c h&#7841;i v&agrave; d&#7883; &#7913;ng sinh s&ocirc;i. V&igrave; th&#7871;, c&acirc;y c&#7843;nh &#273;&#7875; trang tr&iacute; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t l&agrave; m&#7897;t y&#7871;u t&#7889; kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; thi&#7871;u c&#7911;a m&#7895;i ng&ocirc;i nh&agrave; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPh&#432;&#417;ng ph&amp;aacute;p m&#7899;i &#273;&#7875; duy tr&amp;igrave; m&#7913;c &#273;&#7897; kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; an to&amp;agrave;n v&amp;agrave; tinh khi&#7871;t do C&#7909;c Qu&#7843;n tr&#7883; h&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian qu&#7889;c gia (NASA) nghi&amp;ecirc;n c&#7913;u l&amp;agrave; &#273;em c&amp;acirc;y c&#7843;nh v&amp;agrave;o nh&amp;agrave;, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t m&#7897;t s&#7889; lo&#7841;i c&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; s&#7889;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c khi thi&#7871;u &amp;aacute;nh m&#7863;t tr&#7901;i m&amp;agrave; c&amp;ograve;n cung c&#7845;p b&#7847;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; trong l&amp;agrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;H&amp;atilde;y &#273;i&#7875;m m&#7863;t nh&#7919;ng lo&#7841;i c&amp;acirc;y gi&amp;uacute;p l&amp;aacute; ph&#7893;i c&#7911;a ch&amp;uacute;ng ta kh&#7887;e m&#7841;nh v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;ch b&amp;agrave;i tr&amp;iacute; ch&amp;uacute;ng trong ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; c&#7911;a m&amp;igrave;nh:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&amp;acirc;y c&#7885;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;300&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha_1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;acirc;y c&#7885; l&amp;agrave; lo&amp;agrave;i th&#7921;c v&#7853;t mang v&#7867; &#273;&#7865;p trang nh&amp;atilde;, th&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p cho ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; mang &#273;&#7871;n v&#7867; th&#7849;m m&#7929; cho ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;, c&amp;acirc;y c&#7885; c&amp;ograve;n gi&amp;uacute;p gi&#7919; &#7849;m kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute;, lo&#7841;i b&#7887; c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7897;c t&#7889;, kh&amp;iacute; CO2.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&amp;acirc;y l&#432;&#7905;i m&amp;egrave;o&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nC&amp;acirc;y l&#432;&#7905;i m&amp;egrave;o l&amp;agrave; lo&#7841;i c&amp;acirc;y d&amp;agrave;nh cho ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911;. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#432; nh&#7919;ng lo&#7841;i c&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;aacute;c th&#432;&#7901;ng cung c&#7845;p kh&amp;iacute; oxy v&amp;agrave;o ban ng&amp;agrave;y, c&amp;acirc;y l&#432;&#7905;i m&amp;egrave;o c&amp;oacute; qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh ng&#432;&#7907;c l&#7841;i, cho kh&amp;iacute; oxy v&amp;agrave;o ban &#273;&amp;ecirc;m v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;uacute;p duy tr&amp;igrave; m&#7913;c &#273;&#7897; kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; c&amp;oacute; l&#7907;i cho s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e trong l&amp;uacute;c b&#7841;n ng&#7911;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&amp;acirc;y tr&#7847;u b&amp;agrave;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;acirc;y tr&#7847;u b&amp;agrave; gi&amp;uacute;p lo&#7841;i b&#7887; ch&#7845;t g&amp;acirc;y ung th&#432; formaldehydes v&amp;agrave; nhi&#7873;u ch&#7845;t h&amp;oacute;a h&#7885;c d&#7877; bay h&#417;i kh&amp;aacute;c. Th&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p &#273;&#7875; tr&#7891;ng trang tr&amp;iacute; kh&#7855;p nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Nh&#7919;ng lo&#7841;i c&amp;acirc;y trang tr&amp;iacute; kh&amp;aacute;c&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u b&#7841;n tr&#7891;ng c&amp;acirc;y trong nh&amp;agrave; v&#7899;i m&#7909;c &#273;&amp;iacute;ch trang tr&amp;iacute; l&amp;agrave; ch&amp;iacute;nh th&amp;igrave; sau &#273;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng m&#7851;u c&amp;acirc;y &#273;&#7897;c &#273;&amp;aacute;o v&amp;agrave; t&#432;&#417;i &#273;&#7865;p, gi&amp;uacute;p kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian trong nh&amp;agrave; th&amp;ecirc;m ph&#7847;n th&amp;acirc;n thi&#7879;n v&amp;agrave; trang nh&amp;atilde;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; d&#7841;ng c&amp;acirc;y treo t&#432;&#7901;ng, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t trong ch&#7853;u k&amp;iacute;n &#273;&#7875; tr&amp;aacute;nh l&amp;agrave;m &#273;&#7893; &#273;&#7845;t khi treo.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha7.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha8.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&#7919;ng ch&#7853;u c&amp;acirc;y tr&amp;ocirc;ng gi&#7889;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i ngo&amp;agrave;i h&amp;agrave;nh tinh s&#7869; t&amp;ocirc; &#273;i&#7875;m cho ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; b&#7841;n th&amp;ecirc;m n&amp;eacute;t c&amp;aacute; t&amp;iacute;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha9.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7897;c &#273;&amp;aacute;o v&#7899;i c&amp;acirc;y treo ng&#432;&#7907;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha10.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;acirc;y tr&#7891;ng &#273;a d&#7841;ng trong ch&#7853;u v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;agrave;n treo.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha11.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha12.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha13.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha14.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','29/12/2011','29/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/trang-tri-trong-nha/cay-xanh-trong-nha5.jpg',38,11,3483,'huyennt',1,'bai-tri-cay-canh-trong-nha','khong gian, kh&ocirc;ng gian &#273;&#7865;p, c&acirc;y c&#7843;nh, trang tr&iacute;',NULL,NULL,NULL,'khong gian, kh&ocirc;ng gian &#273;&#7865;p, c&acirc;y c&#7843;nh, trang tr&iacute;',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'',1,0,0,0),(170,'Bi&#7879;t th&#7921; bi&#7875;n Acenza Villas','Khu bi&#7879;t th&#7921; Acenza Villas thu&#7897;c khu ph&#7889; 5, ph&#432;&#7901;ng Ph&uacute; H&agrave;i, TP Phan Thi&#7871;t.','&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n c&amp;oacute; quy m&amp;ocirc; 26 ha g&#7891;m: khu th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i d&#7883;ch v&#7909;, vui ch&#417;i, gi&#7843;i tr&amp;iacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng, kh&amp;aacute;ch s&#7841;n 4 sao, h&#7879; th&#7889;ng nh&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;ng, khu massage v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c d&#7883;ch v&#7909; kh&amp;aacute;c, bi&#7879;t th&#7921; v&#432;&#7901;n, c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;acirc;y xanh. Trong &#273;&amp;oacute;, t&#7893; h&#7907;p kh&amp;aacute;ch s&#7841;n, nh&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;ng v&amp;agrave; khu vui ch&#417;i gi&#7843;i tr&amp;iacute; chi&#7871;m di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch 1,89 ha trong d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n. H&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng s&amp;aacute;, c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n, c&amp;acirc;y xanh, c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng c&#7897;ng chi&#7871;m di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch kho&#7843;ng 10 ha. Khu &#7903; chi&#7871;m 13,93 ha. D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n s&#7869; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng h&#417;n 200 c&#259;n bi&#7879;t th&#7921; sang tr&#7885;ng, di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch t&#7915; 400 &#273;&#7871;n 700 m2 m&#7897;t c&#259;n, m&#7853;t &#273;&#7897; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kho&#7843;ng 50%, v&#7899;i 3 m&#7851;u bi&#7879;t th&#7921; kh&amp;aacute;c nhau.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/bietthu.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nC&amp;aacute;c bi&#7879;t th&#7921; ngh&#7881; d&#432;&#7905;ng t&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y thi&#7871;t k&#7871; theo phong c&amp;aacute;ch hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, c&amp;oacute; t&#7915; 3 &#273;&#7871;n 4 ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; c&amp;ugrave;ng nh&#7919;ng khu v&#7921;c v&amp;agrave; g&amp;oacute;c th&#432; gi&amp;atilde;n kh&amp;aacute;c nhau. Bi&#7879;t th&#7921; Acenza Villas bao g&#7891;m 3 lo&#7841;i, phong c&amp;aacute;ch ch&amp;acirc;u &amp;Acirc;u, kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian tho&amp;aacute;ng m&amp;aacute;t, ti&#7879;n nghi v&amp;agrave; h&#7907;p l&amp;yacute;. Khu bi&#7879;t th&#7921; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; h&amp;agrave;i h&amp;ograve;a v&#7899;i khung c&#7843;nh thi&amp;ecirc;n nhi&amp;ecirc;n v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch kh&amp;aacute;c c&#7911;a d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/bietthu1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nT&#7845;t c&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c c&#259;n bi&#7879;t th&#7921; &#273;&#7873;u c&amp;oacute; ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch n&#7857;m d&#432;&#7899;i kho&#7843;ng th&amp;ocirc;ng t&#7847;ng l&#7899;n h&#432;&#7899;ng ra s&amp;acirc;n v&#432;&#7901;n v&#7899;i view nh&amp;igrave;n &#273;&#7865;p ra bi&#7875;n; s&amp;acirc;n th&#432;&#7907;ng l&#7899;n; ph&amp;ograve;ng sinh ho&#7841;t gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh hay ph&amp;ograve;ng l&amp;agrave;m vi&#7879;c ri&amp;ecirc;ng; m&#7897;t b&#7871;p nh&#7887; ngo&amp;agrave;i tr&#7901;i n&#7857;m trong khu&amp;ocirc;n vi&amp;ecirc;n s&amp;acirc;n v&#432;&#7901;n v&#7899;i h&#7891; b&#417;i. &#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; khu v&#7921;c sinh ho&#7841;t v&amp;agrave; khu v&#7921;c ngh&#7881; ng&#417;i c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/bietthu2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nS&amp;agrave;n giao d&#7883;ch b&#7845;t &#273;&#7897;ng s&#7843;n Sacomreal-S (TP HCM) &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; giao &#273;&#7897;c quy&#7873;n ti&#7871;p th&#7883;, ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i c&amp;aacute;c di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch n&#7873;n trong d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n, v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; kh&#7903;i &#273;i&#7875;m l&amp;agrave; 3,6 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng m&#7897;t m2.&lt;/p&gt;','31/12/2011','31/12/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/12-2011/bietthu1.jpg',31,8,2153,'huyennt',1,'biet-thu-bien-acenza-villas','Acenza Villas, bi&#7879;t th&#7921;, d&#7921; &aacute;n',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Acenza Villas, bi&#7879;t th&#7921;, d&#7921; &aacute;n',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',