73;u ph&amp;ograve;ng VIP v&#7899;i gi&amp;aacute; cao v&amp;agrave; d&#297; nhi&amp;ecirc;n &#273;i &#273;&amp;ocirc;i v&#7899;i n&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng ph&#7909;c v&#7909; &amp;ldquo;mi&#7877;n b&amp;agrave;n&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/khach-san.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nL&#7889;i &#273;i v&amp;agrave;o kh&amp;aacute;ch s&#7841;n c&amp;oacute; ph&amp;ograve;ng thu&amp;ecirc; &#273;&#7855;t nh&#7845;t th&#7871; gi&#7899;i&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/khach-san1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7891; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t trong c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng &#273;&#7873;u l&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;ng hi&#7879;u cao c&#7845;p&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/khach-san2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/khach-san3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/khach-san4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: c