pg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&#272;i&#7875;m c&#7897;ng cho c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; n&amp;agrave;y ch&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;agrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian khu v&#7921;c ngo&amp;agrave;i tr&#7901;i. Tr&amp;ecirc;n t&#7893;ng di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch 120 m2, ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; s&#7861;n s&amp;agrave;ng d&amp;agrave;nh ra 40m2 &#273;&#7875; l&amp;agrave;m s&amp;acirc;n th&#432;&#7907;ng ngo&amp;agrave;i tr&#7901;i ng&#7855;m c&#7843;nh &#273;&#7865;p c&#7911;a Paris m&#7897;ng m&#417;. Ch&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;igrave; v&#7853;y n&amp;oacute; r&#7845;t ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng c&#7863;p v&#7907; ch&#7891;ng tr&#7867;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/CANHO5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPh&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; tr&#7855;ng khi&#7871;n cho kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian th&amp;ecirc;m s&#7841;ch s&#7869; v&amp;agrave; r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i h&#417;n so v&#7899;i di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch th&#7921;c c&#7911;a t&amp;ograve;a nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/CANHO6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;Ph&amp;ograve;ng ng&#7911; kh&amp;aacute;c cho tr&#7867; nh&#7887;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/CANHO7.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;Ph&amp;ograve;ng t&#7855;m nh&amp;igrave;n ra khu v&#432;&#7901;n tr&#432;&#7899;c nh&amp;agrave;. N&#417;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y th&#7921;c s&#7921; l&amp;agrave; thi&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng v&amp;agrave; kh&#417;i ngu&#7891;n c&#7843;m h&#7913;ng c&#7911;a m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i.&lt;/p&gt;','12/01/2012','12/01/2012','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/CANHO1.jpg',38,11,3311,'huyennt',1,'can-ho-mau-trang-don-gian-ma-quyen-ru','quy&#7871;n r&#361;, c&#259;n h&#7897; m&agrave;u tr&#7855;ng, phong c&#7843;nh &#273;&#7865;p, h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh',NULL,NULL,NULL,'quy&#7871;n r&#361;, c&#259;n h&#7897; m&agrave;u tr&#7855;ng, phong c&#7843;nh &#273;&#7865;p, h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(190,'T&acirc;n trang nh&agrave; c&#7917;a nghinh &#273;&oacute;n xu&acirc;n v&#7873;','T&#7871;t &#273;&atilde; c&#7853;n k&#7873;, c&ugrave;ng nhau d&#7885;n nh&agrave; s&#7855;m s&#7917;a &#273;&oacute;n xu&acirc;n &#273;&atilde; tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh t&#7909;c l&#7879; c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i Vi&#7879;t, ch&agrave;o &#273;&oacute;n n&#259;m m&#7899;i r&#7897;n r&agrave;ng t&#432;&#417;i vui &#273;&#7847;y s&#7855;c th&#7855;m th&ocirc;ng qua nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#7891; v&#7853;t kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; thi&#7871;u.','&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; Kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian &#273;&#7865;p tham kh&#7843;o:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- &amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Hinh-anh/?aid=BD&quot;&gt;C&#259;n h&#7897; m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n m&amp;agrave; quy&#7871;n r&#361;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Hinh-anh/?aid=BC&quot;&gt;  Nh&amp;agrave; g&#7895; ven s&amp;ocirc;ng&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;-  &lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Hinh-anh/?aid=B8&quot;&gt;D&#7885;n d&#7865;p ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&amp;oacute;n n&#259;m m&#7899;i&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;-&lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Hinh-anh/?aid=B6&quot;&gt; Kh&amp;aacute;ch s&#7841;n si&amp;ecirc;u sang&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; &quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;Apple-interchange-newline&quot; /&gt;\r\n1. M&amp;acirc;m ng&#361; qu&#7843;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Xu&#7845;t ph&amp;aacute;t t&#7915; quan ni&#7879;m v&#7873; chu&#7897;ng s&#7889; l&#7867; c&#7911;a v&#259;n h&amp;oacute;a ph&#432;&#417;ng &#272;&amp;ocirc;ng, v&#7873; b&#7897; ng&#361; ho&amp;agrave;n h&#7843;o (ng&#361; h&amp;agrave;nh, ng&#361; v&#7883;, ng&#361; s&#7855;c&amp;hellip;), v&#7873; s&#7921; &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; (nh&#432; b&amp;agrave;n tay 5 ng&amp;oacute;n)&amp;hellip; m&amp;agrave; m&amp;acirc;m tr&amp;aacute;i c&amp;acirc;y d&amp;acirc;ng c&amp;uacute;ng t&#7893; ti&amp;ecirc;n v&amp;agrave; ch&#432;ng ng&amp;agrave;y t&#7871;t c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i Vi&#7879;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7885;i l&amp;agrave; m&amp;acirc;m ng&#361; qu&#7843;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/nghinh-don-xuan-ve-1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;X&amp;eacute;t v&#7873; m&#7863;t &amp;acirc;m d&#432;&#417;ng - ng&#361; h&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;igrave; m&#7897;t m&amp;acirc;m ng&#361; qu&#7843; h&amp;agrave;i h&amp;ograve;a n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;oacute; c&amp;aacute;c y&#7871;u t&#7889; b&#7893; sung, t&#432;&#417;ng h&#7895; cho nhau, nh&#432; b&#7843;n ch&#7845;t cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng trong t&#7921; nhi&amp;ecirc;n v&amp;agrave; x&amp;atilde; h&#7897;i &#273;&amp;ograve;i h&#7887;i nh&#432; v&#7853;y. C&#7847;n c&amp;acirc;n &#273;&#7889;i gi&#7919;a nh&#7919;ng tr&amp;aacute;i c&amp;acirc;y c&amp;oacute; m&amp;agrave;u xanh hay m&amp;agrave;u nh&#7841;t, d&#7883;u m&amp;aacute;t t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#432;ng cho &amp;acirc;m v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c tr&amp;aacute;i m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;oacute;ng nh&#432; &#273;&#7887; cam, v&amp;agrave;ng r&#7921;c&amp;hellip; t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#432;ng cho d&#432;&#417;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ng&#432;&#7901;i Vi&#7879;t c&#361;ng thi&amp;ecirc;n nhi&#7873;u v&#7873; hai h&amp;agrave;nh th&#7893; (sinh kim, ti&#7873;n t&amp;agrave;i) v&amp;agrave; m&#7897;c (ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n, n&#7843;y l&#7897;c, b&amp;aacute;m r&#7877; l&amp;acirc;u b&#7873;n) n&amp;ecirc;n m&amp;acirc;m ng&#361; qu&#7843; ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c tr&amp;aacute;i c&amp;oacute; v&#7883; ng&#7885;t (thu&#7897;c th&#7893;) nh&#432; l&amp;ecirc;, d&#432;a h&#7845;u, &#273;u &#273;&#7911;, xo&amp;agrave;i&amp;hellip; v&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng tr&amp;aacute;i c&amp;oacute; v&#7883; chua (thu&#7897;c m&#7897;c) nh&#432; b&#432;&#7903;i, cam.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;2. C&amp;acirc;u &#273;&#7889;i&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; trang ho&amp;agrave;ng nh&amp;agrave; c&#7917;a v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7875; th&#432;&#7903;ng Xu&amp;acirc;n, tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&amp;acirc;y t&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; nho cho t&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i b&amp;igrave;nh d&amp;acirc;n &amp;quot;t&#7891;n c&#7893;&amp;quot; v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n tr&#7885;ng t&#7909;c treo &amp;quot;c&amp;acirc;u &#273;&#7889;i &#273;&#7887;&amp;quot; nh&amp;acirc;n ng&amp;agrave;y T&#7871;t. Nh&#7919;ng c&amp;acirc;u &#273;&#7889;i n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c vi&#7871;t b&#7857;ng ch&#7919; nho (m&amp;agrave;u &#273;en hay v&amp;agrave;ng) tr&amp;ecirc;n nh&#7919;ng t&#7845;m gi&#7845;y &#273;&#7887; hay h&#7891;ng &#273;&amp;agrave;o n&amp;ecirc;n th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7885;i chung l&amp;agrave; c&amp;acirc;u &#273;&#7889;i &#273;&#7887;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/nghinh-don-xuan-ve-2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/nghinh-don-xuan-ve-3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7919; ngh&#297;a &#7903; c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;acirc;u &#273;&#7889;i n&amp;agrave;y th&#432;&#7901;ng l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng ch&amp;uacute;c t&#7909;ng nh&amp;acirc;n n&#259;m m&#7899;i, ch&#7859;ng h&#7841;n nh&#432;: Ph&#432;&#7899;c th&amp;acirc;m t&#7921; h&#7843;i (h&#7841;nh ph&amp;uacute;c nhi&#7873;u s&amp;acirc;u nh&#432; bi&#7875;n), L&#7897;c cao nh&#432; s&#417;n (c&#7911;a c&#7843;i nhi&#7873;u cao nh&#432; n&amp;uacute;i) hay: Thi&amp;ecirc;n t&#259;ng tu&#7871; nguy&#7879;t, nh&amp;acirc;n t&#259;ng th&#7885; (Tr&#7901;i &#273;&#7845;t ng&amp;agrave;y gia t&#259;ng ng&amp;agrave;y th&amp;aacute;ng v&amp;iacute; nh&#432; con ng&#432;&#7901;i m&#7895;i n&#259;m t&#259;ng th&amp;ecirc;m tu&#7893;i th&#7885;), Xu&amp;acirc;n m&amp;atilde;n c&amp;agrave;n kh&amp;ocirc;n, ph&amp;uacute;c m&amp;atilde;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng (m&amp;ugrave;a xu&amp;acirc;n v&#7873; &#273;&#7847;y trong Tr&#7901;i &#273;&#7845;t v&amp;iacute; nh&#432; h&#7841;nh ph&amp;uacute;c &#273;&#7847;y nh&amp;agrave;)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. V&#7853;t ph&#7849;m c&amp;aacute;t t&#432;&#7901;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ng&amp;agrave;y t&#7871;t b&amp;agrave;i tr&amp;iacute; v&#7853;t ph&#7849;m trong nh&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; mang l&#7841;i may m&#7855;n, t&amp;agrave;i v&#7853;n, s&#7921; gi&amp;agrave;u sang ph&amp;uacute; qu&amp;yacute; cho gia ch&#7911;. &#272;i&#7875;n h&amp;igrave;nh l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng v&#7853;t ph&#7849;m sau:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/nghinh-don-xuan-ve-4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Th&#7847;n t&amp;agrave;i: R&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh v&amp;agrave; nhi&#7873;u c&amp;ocirc;ng ty hi&#7879;n nay &#273;&#7863;t t&#432;&#7907;ng th&#7847;n T&amp;agrave;i (quan C&amp;ocirc;ng) trong nh&amp;agrave;. T&#432;&#7907;ng th&#7847;n T&amp;agrave;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem l&amp;agrave; ph&amp;aacute;p kh&amp;iacute; mang l&#7841;i t&amp;agrave;i l&#7897;c v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;uacute; qu&amp;yacute; trong phong th&#7911;y. T&#432;&#7907;ng th&#7847;n T&amp;agrave;i th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t trong ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch ho&#7863;c tr&amp;ecirc;n b&amp;agrave;n l&amp;agrave;m vi&#7879;c v&#7899;i hy v&#7885;ng &#273;&amp;oacute;n nhi&#7873;u v&#7853;n kh&amp;iacute; m&#7899;i t&#7889;t l&amp;agrave;nh v&amp;agrave;o nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- T&#432;&#7907;ng r&#7891;ng: H&amp;igrave;nh t&#432;&#7907;ng r&#7891;ng th&#7875; hi&#7879;n s&#7913;c m&#7841;nh v&#361; tr&#7909;. Hai con r&#7891;ng th&#7875; hi&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;nh bao tr&amp;ugrave;m c&#7911;a &amp;Acirc;m D&#432;&#417;ng c&amp;ugrave;ng ch&#7847;u v&amp;agrave;o bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng m&#7863;t tr&#7901;i l&amp;agrave; Th&amp;aacute;i C&#7921;c sinh l&#432;&#7905;ng nghi (Hai con r&#7891;ng). D&amp;ugrave;ng t&#432;&#7907;ng r&#7891;ng t&#7841;i ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch trong nh&amp;agrave; s&#7869; t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n long kh&amp;iacute;, m&#7897;t ngu&#7891;n sinh kh&amp;iacute; c&amp;oacute; t&amp;aacute;c d&#7909;ng to l&#7899;n trong phong th&#7911;y, gi&amp;uacute;p cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng y&amp;ecirc;n l&amp;agrave;nh, c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#432;&#7907;t b&#7853;c&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- B&#7897; Tam &#272;a: Tam &#272;a ch&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;agrave; Ph&amp;uacute;c L&#7897;c Th&#7885;. B&#7897; Tam &#272;a c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; b&#7857;ng g&#7889;m s&#7913;, b&#7857;ng &#273;&#7891;ng, b&#7857;ng &#273;&amp;aacute; qu&amp;yacute;, b&#7857;ng h&amp;igrave;nh t&#432;&#7907;ng Phong Th&#7911;y Lu&amp;acirc;n, b&#7857;ng tranh Ph&amp;uacute;c L&#7897;c Th&#7885; to&amp;agrave;n &#273;&#7891;. Bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng Tam &#272;a t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#432;ng cho 3 v&#7883; Th&#7847;n &#273;em l&#7841;i may m&#7855;n, s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e, h&#7841;nh ph&amp;uacute;c cho m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i, m&#7885;i nh&amp;agrave; n&amp;ecirc;n th&#432;&#7901;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i ta hay tr&#432;ng, b&amp;agrave;y trong nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;4. C&amp;acirc;y c&#7843;nh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;M&amp;ugrave;a xu&amp;acirc;n l&amp;agrave; m&amp;ugrave;a c&#7911;a c&amp;acirc;y c&#7889;i &#273;&amp;acirc;m ch&#7891;i n&#7843;y l&#7897;c, m&amp;ugrave;a c&#7911;a s&#7855;c hoa t&#432;&#417;i th&#7855;m m&#7885;i nh&amp;agrave;. N&#7871;u kh&amp;eacute;o ch&#7885;n sao cho h&amp;agrave;i h&amp;ograve;a &amp;acirc;m d&#432;&#417;ng, ng&#361; h&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7919;ng &#273;em l&#7841;i th&#7849;m m&#7929; cao m&amp;agrave; c&amp;ograve;n th&amp;uacute;c &#273;&#7849;y sinh kh&amp;iacute;, h&#432;ng v&#432;&#7907;ng cho n&#417;i c&#432; ng&#7909; trong d&#7883;p xu&amp;acirc;n v&#7873;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/nghinh-don-xuan-ve-5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7885;n c&amp;acirc;y theo H&amp;agrave;nh:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong ch&#7885;n c&amp;acirc;y tr&#432;ng t&#7871;t th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;ch l&amp;agrave;m theo phong th&#7911;y l&amp;agrave; ch&#7885;n c&amp;acirc;y theo h&amp;agrave;nh l&amp;agrave;m ch&#7911; &#273;&#7841;o (h&amp;agrave;nh m&#7879;nh gia ch&#7911;), r&#7891;i b&#7893; sung th&amp;ecirc;m h&amp;agrave;nh sinh ch&#7911; v&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;nh ch&#7911; sinh, &#273;i&#7875;m xuy&#7871;t h&amp;agrave;nh ch&#7911; kh&#7855;c t&#7841;i c&amp;aacute;c v&#7883; tr&amp;iacute; x&#7845;u, c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i &#273;&#7875; t&#7921; nhi&amp;ecirc;n v&amp;agrave; b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; theo c&amp;ocirc;ng n&#259;ng, th&#7849;m m&#7929;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&amp;iacute; d&#7909; m&#7897;t ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; v&#7899;i gia ch&#7911; thu&#7897;c h&amp;agrave;nh kim, nh&amp;agrave; s&#417;n m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng x&amp;aacute;m, th&amp;igrave; n&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7885;n c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;acirc;y x&amp;eacute;n tr&amp;ograve;n, &#273;&#7863;t trong ch&#7853;u vu&amp;ocirc;ng ho&#7863;c tr&amp;ograve;n (th&#7893; sinh kim), &#273;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; th&amp;ecirc;m m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&amp;acirc;y th&#7911;y sinh &#273;&#7875; kim sinh th&#7911;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nC&#361;ng n&amp;ecirc;n c&#259;n c&#7913; v&amp;agrave;o &#273;&#7863;c t&amp;iacute;nh c&#7911;a n&#417;i b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; c&amp;acirc;y ch&#7913; kh&amp;ocirc;ng ch&#7881; thu&#7847;n y&#7871;u t&#7889; c&amp;aacute; nh&amp;acirc;n, v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; l&amp;uacute;c kh&#7855;c l&#7841;i t&#7889;t h&#417;n l&amp;agrave; sinh. V&amp;iacute; d&#7909; n&#7871;u ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch c&amp;oacute; m&#7843;ng s&#417;n m&amp;agrave;u &#273;&#7887; cam, thu&#7897;c h&#7887;a, th&amp;igrave; c&amp;acirc;y ch&#432;ng &#273;&amp;oacute; n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;oacute; d&#7841;ng th&#7845;p v&amp;agrave; nh&#7845;p nh&amp;ocirc;, t&amp;aacute;n tr&amp;ograve;n, l&amp;aacute; xanh &#273;&#7853;m c&amp;oacute; &amp;aacute;nh tr&#7855;ng (thu&#7897;c kim v&amp;agrave; th&#7911;y, l&amp;agrave; hai h&amp;agrave;nh xung kh&#7855;c v&#7899;i h&#7887;a) &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m b&#7899;t t&amp;iacute;nh h&#7887;a.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7885;n c&amp;acirc;y theo t&amp;ecirc;n:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&#7919;ng lo&#7841;i c&amp;acirc;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c phong thu&#7927; xem l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;t t&#432;&#7901;ng, mang l&#7841;i sinh kh&amp;iacute; trong nh&amp;agrave; &#7903; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng trong m&#7897;t s&#7889; b&#7897; c&amp;acirc;y ch&amp;iacute;nh sau:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&#7897; t&#7913; linh: &#273;a - sung - sanh - si, v&#7889;n l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng c&amp;acirc;y l&amp;acirc;u n&#259;m, d&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&#7865;p, r&#7877; b&amp;aacute;m b&#7873;n ch&#7855;c v&amp;agrave; c&amp;agrave;nh l&amp;aacute; sum su&amp;ecirc;, nh&#7919;ng c&amp;acirc;y n&amp;agrave;y hay &#273;&#432;&#7907;c u&#7889;n theo c&amp;aacute;c th&#7871; truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng th&#7875; hi&#7879;n ti&#7875;u v&#361; tr&#7909; trong &#273;&#7841;i v&#361; tr&#7909; bao la.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&#7897; t&#7913; qu&amp;yacute;: mai - lan - c&amp;uacute;c - tr&amp;uacute;c t&#432;&#417;ng &#7913;ng theo b&#7889;n m&amp;ugrave;a trong n&#259;m, ho&#7863;c l&amp;agrave; t&amp;ugrave;ng - tr&amp;uacute;c - c&amp;uacute;c - mai t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#432;ng cho tu&#7893;i thanh xu&amp;acirc;n v&amp;agrave; kh&amp;iacute; ti&#7871;t c&#7911;a con ng&#432;&#7901;i, trong &#273;&amp;oacute; t&amp;ugrave;ng v&amp;agrave; tr&amp;uacute;c c&amp;oacute; d&amp;aacute;ng v&#432;&#417;n cao t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#432;ng cho nam t&#7917; tr&#432;&#7907;ng phu, c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;uacute;c - mai t&#432;&#417;i &#273;&#7865;p m&#7873;m m&#7841;i ti&amp;ecirc;u bi&#7875;u cho n&#7919; nhi hi&#7873;n th&#7909;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nB&#7897; tam &#273;a: g&#7891;m c&amp;oacute; c&amp;acirc;y sung sai qu&#7843; (ho&#7863;c c&amp;acirc;y &#273;a) &#7903; d&#7841;ng bonsai t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#432;ng cho ph&amp;uacute;c. C&amp;acirc;y l&#7897;c v&#7915;ng ho&#7863;c ph&amp;aacute;t t&amp;agrave;i t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#432;ng cho l&#7897;c. C&amp;acirc;y b&amp;aacute;ch tu&#7871;, thi&amp;ecirc;n tu&#7871; hay v&#7841;n tu&#7871;, v&#7841;n ni&amp;ecirc;n t&amp;ugrave;ng, s&#7889;ng &#273;&#7901;i&amp;hellip; t&#432;&#7907;ng tr&#432;ng cho th&#7885;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. L&amp;igrave; x&amp;igrave;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/nghinh-don-xuan-ve-6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;L&amp;igrave; x&amp;igrave; ng&amp;agrave;y T&#7871;t ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7899;n th&#432;&#7901;ng t&#7863;ng tr&#7867; em ti&#7873;n b&#7887; trong m&#7897;t bao gi&#7845;y &#273;&#7887;, g&#7885;i l&amp;agrave; &amp;ldquo;l&amp;igrave; x&amp;igrave;&amp;rdquo; v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng l&#7901;i ch&amp;uacute;c m&#7915;ng &#259;n no, ch&amp;oacute;ng l&#7899;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n','12/01/2012','12/01/2012','/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/nghinh-don-xuan-ve-2.jpg',38,11,3723,'huyennt',1,'tan-trang-nha-cua-nghinh-don-xuan-ve','t&acirc;n trang , &#273;&oacute;n xu&acirc;n, kh&ocirc;ng gian &#273;&#7865;p',NULL,NULL,NULL,'t&acirc;n trang , &#273;&oacute;n xu&acirc;n, kh&ocirc;ng gian &#273;&#7865;p',0,0,0,'','','huyennt',3,'',1,0,0,0),(191,'D&#7921; &aacute;n Sky Garden gi&aacute; t&#7915; 18 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2','T&#7893; h&#7907;p v&#259;n ph&ograve;ng, trung t&acirc;m th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i v&agrave; c&#259;n h&#7897; cao c&#7845;p Sky Garden do C&ocirc;ng ty TNHH &#272;&#7883;nh C&ocirc;ng, th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a V&acirc;n Th&aacute;i Group l&agrave;m ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432;.','&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; T&amp;ograve;a th&amp;aacute;p &#273;&amp;ocirc;i cao 28 t&#7847;ng. t&#7893;ng di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch s&amp;agrave;n x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng g&#7847;n 75.000, g&#7891;m 400 c&#259;n h&#7897; v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u lo&#7841;i di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch t&#7915; 89 &amp;ndash; 124 m2. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch khu &#273;&#7845;t r&#7897;ng h&#417;n 7.000m2 nh&#432;ng m&#7853;t &#273;&#7897; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng ch&#7881; chi&#7871;m 40%, ph&#7847;n &#273;&#7845;t c&amp;ograve;n l&#7841;i d&amp;agrave;nh cho khu vui ch&#417;i gi&#7843;i tr&amp;iacute;, c&amp;aacute;c ti&#7879;n &amp;iacute;ch hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i nh&#432; h&#7891; b&#417;i, s&amp;acirc;n tennis, ph&amp;ograve;ng t&#7853;p Gym, c&amp;aacute;c c&#7909;m c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n xanh&amp;hellip; C&amp;aacute;c h&#7841;ng m&#7909;c n&amp;agrave;y s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#432;a v&amp;agrave;o s&#7917; d&#7909;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c khi b&amp;agrave;n giao c&#259;n h&#7897;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/1-2012/du-an/sky-garden2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(128, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;D&#7921; &amp;aacute;n Sky Garden gi&amp;aacute; t&#7915; 18 tri&#7879;u/m2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCh&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; th&#7847;u &#273;ang h&#7841; quy&#7871;t t&amp;acirc;m ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh h&#7841;ng m&#7909;c m&amp;oacute;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh v&amp;agrave;o th&amp;aacute;ng 6/2012 &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch b&amp;agrave;n giao c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh v&amp;agrave;o qu&amp;yacute; 3/2014.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo &#272;&#7845;t Xanh mi&#7873;n B&#7855;c, &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; ph&amp;acirc;n ph&#7889;i d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n, ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; &#273;&amp;atilde; ch&amp;iacute;nh th&#7913;c &#273;&#432;a ra ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh g&amp;oacute;p v&#7889;n c&#7911;a d&#7921; &amp;aacute;n v&#7899;i m&#7913;c gi&amp;aacute; ch&#7881; t&#7915; 18 tri&#7879;u &#273;&#7891;ng/m2 (&#273;&amp;oacute;ng ti&#7873;n 15% cho &#273;&#7907;t &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n). Ch&#7881; v&#7899;i kho&#7843;ng 1,6 t&#7927; &#273;&#7871;n 1,9 t&#7927;, kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7903; h&#7919;u m&#7897;t c&#259;n h&#7897; v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n cao c&#7845;p.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, nh&amp;acirc;n d&#7883;p &#273;&#7847;u xu&amp;acirc;n n&#259;m m&#7899;i, ch&#7911; &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh t&#7863;ng 01 xe &amp;ocirc; t&amp;ocirc; Ford Fiesta 1.6 Trend 4 c&#7917;a cho 100 kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n khi mua c&#259;n h&#7897; SkyGarden, th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m t&amp;iacute;nh b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u t&#7915; ng&amp;agrave;y 7/1/2012.&lt;/p&gt;','13/01/2012','13/01/2012','/home/uploads/image/news/1-2012/du-an/sky-garden2.jpg',36,8,1943,'huyennt',1,'du-an-sky-garden-gia-tu-18-trieu-dong/m2','tin d&#7921; &aacute;n, d&#7921; &aacute;n,  Sky Garden',NULL,NULL,NULL,'tin d&#7921; &aacute;n, d&#7921; &aacute;n,  Sky Garden',0,0,0,'','','',3,'',1,0,0,0),(192,'Ph&ograve;ng b&#7871;p trang nh&atilde; v&#7899;i gam trung t&iacute;nh','Theo xu h&#432;&#7899;ng b&#7871;p hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, nh&#7919;ng m&agrave;u s&#7855;c trung t&iacute;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&aacute;c nh&agrave; thi&#7871;t k&#7871; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng nhi&#7873;u. Gam m&agrave;u n&agrave;y c&oacute; t&aacute;c d&#7909;ng duy d&#432;&#7905;ng v&#7873; t&igrave;nh c&#7843;m, cho ta &yacute; ni&#7879;m v&#7873; s&#7921; thanh b&igrave;nh, &#7845;m &aacute;p.','&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian &#273;&#7865;p tham kh&#7843;o:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Hinh-anh/?aid=B8&quot;&gt;D&#7885;n d&#7865;p ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch &#273;&amp;oacute;n n&#259;m m&#7899;i&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Hinh-anh/?aid=BE&quot;&gt;T&amp;acirc;n trang nh&amp;agrave; c&#7917;a nghinh &#273;&amp;oacute;n xu&amp;acirc;n v&#7873;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mikadoceramic.vn/home/Hinh-anh/?aid=BD&quot;&gt;C&#259;n h&#7897; m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n m&amp;agrave; quy&#7871;n r&#361;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;273&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/anh-1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTrong c&#259;n b&#7871;p &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; khoa h&#7885;c th&amp;igrave; vi&#7879;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n l&#432;&#7907;ng &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng th&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p s&#7869; l&amp;agrave;m thay &#273;&#7893;i r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u &#273;&#7871;n phong c&amp;aacute;ch b&amp;ecirc;n trong.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/anh-2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;B&#7873; m&#7863;t tr&#417;n v&amp;agrave; nh&#7861;n c&#7911;a n&#7897;i th&#7845;t b&amp;ecirc;n trong ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i s&#7855;c d&#7883;u c&#7911;a m&amp;agrave;u kem lu&amp;ocirc;n &#273;em &#273;&#7871;n c&amp;aacute;i nh&amp;igrave;n m&#7899;i m&#7867; v&amp;agrave; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/anh-3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#432;&#7901;ng g&#7841;ch th&amp;ocirc; v&#7851;n c&amp;ograve;n hi&#7879;n r&amp;otilde; v&#7879;t v&#7919;a tr&amp;aacute;t &#273;&#7889;i l&#7853;p v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng d&#7909;ng c&#7909; l&amp;agrave;m b&#7871;p v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c thi&#7871;t b&#7883; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;t, t&#7841;o ra nhi&#7873;u hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; nh&#7845;t &#273;&#7883;nh, t&#7915; s&#7921; tinh t&#7871; m&#432;&#7907;t m&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7871;n s&#7921; &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n, th&amp;ocirc; s&#417;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/khong-gian-dep/khong-gian-dep/1-2012/anh-4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;H&#7879; th&#7889;ng &#273;&amp;egrave;n m&#7855;t tr&amp;acirc;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7855;p ph&amp;iacute;a b&amp;ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i t&#7911; k&#7879; &#273;&#7875; soi &#273;&#7871;n c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng g&amp;oacute;c nh&#7887; v&amp;agrave; khu&#7845;t. C&#259;n b&#7871;p c&#7911;a b&#7841;n th&amp;ecirc;m lung linh v&amp;agrave; b&#7889; tr&amp;iacute; kh&amp;eacute;o l&amp;eacute;o gi&amp;uacute;p ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&amp;oacute; c&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;c h&#7885; &#273;ang l&#432;&#7899;t tr&amp;ecirc;n h&amp;ograve;n &#273;&#7843;o nh&#7887;, th&#7887;a s&#7913;c kh&amp;aacute;m ph&amp;aacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: cente